#: Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BOOKCLUB
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BOOKCLUB"
msgid "agent:\t\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You're right--let's get to <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>, and face <#BLUE>Grandpa</>!"
msgstr "agent:\t\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 네 말이 맞아. 어서 <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>로 가서 <#BLUE>할아버지</1>를 마주하자!"

#: Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OHAND
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OHAND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" After the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>, the writing is replaced by strange drawings of triangles and winged snakes... Until this, his final entry:\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"They tried to stop me, but I HAD to trigger the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>! It was the only way to tap into the <#KONJUR>Primeval Source of {name.konjur}</>...\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Your Grandpa... <i>triggered</> the Eruption??\n"
" agent:\n"
" Y-yes... He goes on: {name.grandpa_quote} \"The power hidden in <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}'s</> dark, glittering crystals drove <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}'s</> father mad--but not I.\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"For I understand that <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> is pure potential! Chaotic creation! As such, there's no problem it can't solve!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"With it, we can purge ALL our impurities, all our vulnerabilities, all our mistakes! You will be CURED, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"But everything ages, decays, and passes, you argue? It's part of the fabric of our world, you plead? It's what gives life meaning, you acquiesce?\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"Acquiesce no longer, we say. We will fix everything, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>. We will be perfect. We promise.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh {name.npc_scout}, that's... Wait--what did he mean, \"we\"??\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" I... I don't know...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But maybe I can get through to him, if we reach him in time...\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's get to <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</> and use those <#RED>Key Fragments</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#KONJUR>대폭발</> 이후엔 글이 삼각형이랑 날개 달린 뱀 같은 이상한 그림으로 바뀌어 있어... 그리고 여기, 마지막 기록이 있어.\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"녀석들이 날 막으려 했지만, 난 <#KONJUR>대폭발</1>을 반드시 일으켜야만 했다! <#KONJUR>태고의 근원 {name.konjur}</2>에 닿을 유일한 방법이었으니까...\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 네 할아버지가... 대폭발을 <3>일으켰어</4>??\n"
" agent:\n"
" 으, 응... 이어서 이렇게 적혀 있어: {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}의</5> 어둡고 반짝이는 결정에 숨은 힘은 <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}의</6> 아버지를 미치게 만들었지만, 나는 아니었다.\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"왜냐하면 난 <#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}</7>가 순수한 가능성 그 자체라는 걸 이해하니까! 혼돈의 피조물이라는 것을! 그러니 이것이 해결 못 할 문제는 없다!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"그걸로 우리 안의 불순물도, 약점도, 실수도 모두 정화할 수 있다! 넌 치유될 거다, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</8>!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"모든 건 늙고, 쇠퇴하고, 사라진다고들 말했던가? 그 모든 것이 우주의 법칙이라고들 했던가? 그것이 삶에 의미를 불어넣는다고 순응했던가?\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"이제 더는 순응하지 말자고, 우리는 고한다. 우리가 모두 고치겠다, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</9>. 우린 완벽해질 거다. 약속하지.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, {name.npc_scout} 그건... 잠깐--\"우리\"라고??무슨 뜻이야??\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" 나... 나도 모르겠어...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그래도 제때 도착하면... 그를 설득할 수 있을지도 몰라...\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</10>로 가서 <#RED>열쇠 조각</11>들을 써 보자."

#: Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BOOKCLUB
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BOOKCLUB"
msgid "Let's book club later, stop Second Eruption now."
msgstr "잡담은 나중에 하고, 당장 2차 대폭발부터 막자고."

#: Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OHAND
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_all_keys_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OHAND"
msgid "Oh? And?"
msgstr "오? 그래서?"

#: Convo.after_find_first_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAMISH_GOSSIP
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_first_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAMISH_GOSSIP"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm. I suspected as much. \n"
" player:\n"
" What?? <i>All</> of that?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" In my old Huntin' days, I noticed <#RED>{name.rot}</> hot spots were always near damaged <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> pipes. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> denied leaks, said some <#RED>{name.rot}</> must've damaged them. But I know <#RED>{name.rot}</> marks when I see 'em. \n"
" player:\n"
" And {name.npc_blacksmith}? How did you know he was involved?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The moment he laid eyes on that busted old <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> that <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> has scavenged in <#BLUE>The Brinks</>, it was like he saw a ghost.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Also... I could tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> swung his hammer with a heavy heart. Each strike tryin' to put right the last. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Figured he'd joined the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> for related reasons. Now I know the reasons.\n"
" player:\n"
" Y'know, for an old guy with one eye, you sure see a lot.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" HAH. And I'll see <i>you</> doin' 50 wind sprints tomorrow at dawn, kid. \n"
" player:\n"
" Dang it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!think\n"
"흠. 역시 그럴 줄 알았어.\n"
"플레이어:\n"
"뭐?? <i>전부 다</>?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!gesture\n"
"내가 예전에 사냥할 적엔, <#RED>{name.rot}</>들이 항상 손상된 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> 파이프 근처에서 많이 출몰했거든.\n"
"!shrug\n"
"<#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</>은 유출됐을 리 없다 했고, 몇몇 사람들은 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 때문에 손상된 게 틀림없다고 말했지. 하지만 난 <#RED>{name.rot}</>의 흔적이었다면 척 보면 알았을 거야.\n"
"player:\n"
"그리고 {name.npc_blacksmith} 말이야, 그 사람이 관련되어 있다는 것을 어떻게 안 거야?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!gesture\n"
"<#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>가 <#BLUE>The Brinks</>에서 가져온 낡고 고장난 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>를 보더니 무슨 유령이라도 본 것 같은 얼굴이었거든.\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"그리고... <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>가 무거운 마음으로 망치를 휘두르는 것 같더라고. 마치 이전에 잘못을 고치려는 듯이 말이야.\n"
"!closedeyes\n"
"그래서 <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>에 합류했다고 생각했지. 이제 이유를 알았네.\n"
"player:\n"
"이야, 눈 하나 없는 늙은이치고는 많은 걸 보는구나.\n"
"agent:\n"
"!laugh\n"
"하하. 그리고 내일 새벽에 <i>네</>가 윈드 스프린트 50회를 하는 모습도 볼 거라고, 꼬맹이.\n"
"player:\n"
"젠장."

#: Convo.after_find_first_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAMISH_GOSSIP
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_first_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAMISH_GOSSIP"
msgid "{name.npc_blacksmith} smithied the {name.town_grid_cryst}, and leaks <i>caused</> the {name.rot}!"
msgstr "{name.npc_blacksmith}가 {name.town_grid_cryst}을 만들었고, 누출이 {name.rot}을 <i>만들었어</>!"

#: Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GOTTAGO
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GOTTAGO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !greet\n"
" Understood, Hunter. The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> is ready and waiting."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral [방에 보관함]\n"
"!greet\n"
"알겠어, 사냥꾼.<#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>는 준비 다 됐어."

#: Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OFCOURSE
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OFCOURSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" Well, seems that a smithy who worked on the pipelines reported <#RED>leaks</>.\n"
" Leaks that caused local flora and fauna to mutate and become aggressive...\n"
" player:\n"
" Whoa. The system caused the {name.rot}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" Well, the smithy wanted to shut the whole grid down. But <#BLUE>Grandpa</> covered it up so he could study the <#RED>{name.rot}</> for clues to my illness.\n"
" player:\n"
" Whoa! I wonder if {name.npc_blacksmith} knew the smithy...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I'm sure he did. <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> WAS the smithy! \n"
" player:\n"
" WHOA!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I-I had no idea. I feel like I ought to apologize to <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>...\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know what? Don't worry about it, Hunter. You have enough on your plate. \n"
" !point\n"
" Get after that second <#RED>Key Fragment</>. The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> is ready and waiting."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" 음, 파이프라인에서 일하던 대장장이가 <#RED>누출</>을 보고한 모양이야.\n"
" 그 누출 때문에 지역의 동식물이 변이하고 공격적으로 변했대...\n"
" player:\n"
" 우와. 그 시스템이 {name.rot}를 일으킨 거네!\n"
" agent:\n"
" 그 대장장이는 그리드 전체를 멈추려고 했어. 하지만 <#BLUE>할아버지</1>가 내 병의 단서를 찾기 위해 <#RED>{name.rot}</2>를 연구하려고 그걸 덮어버렸지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 우와! {name.npc_blacksmith}가 그 대장장이를 알았을까...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 분명 알았을 거야. <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</3>가 바로 그 대장장이였어! \n"
" player:\n"
" 우와!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 나-난 전혀 몰랐어. <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</4>에게 사과해야 할 것 같아...\n"
" !think\n"
" 있잖아? 신경 쓰지 마, 헌터. 너도 처리할 게 많잖아. \n"
" !point\n"
" 두 번째 <#RED>열쇠 파편</5>을 찾아가. <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</6> 준비해 두고 기다리고 있어."

#: Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GOTTAGO
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GOTTAGO"
msgid "Fascinating. Listen, I'd better run after Key Fragment number two."
msgstr "흥미로운걸. 좋아, 어서 두 번째 열쇠 조각을 찾으러 가자고."

#: Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OFCOURSE
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_first_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OFCOURSE"
msgid "Of course. His system really ushered in the {name.konjur} Age."
msgstr "물론이지. 그 시스템이 진짜 {name.konjur} 시대를 열었어."

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DIARY
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DIARY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Oh. Yeah. That he tested <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> on Hunters knowin' it could make us sick. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Pfft. Throw it on the pile. \n"
" player:\n"
" Are you joking?? <i>He was testing on you without you knowing!</> He MADE you sick!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" And how's that any different than him exposin' us ALL to <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> after learnin' it makes us sick? \n"
" !point\n"
" We're all in the same leaky boat, kid. All we can do is keep rowin'.\n"
" player:\n"
" ... Not until we've thrown the Captain overboard. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" HA HA HA!\n"
" !cough\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><z 0.8>(cough <i>HACK</> cough)</></></> Hm. Seems my trainin's sinkin' in. I'll take one push up off your training regimen.\n"
" player:\n"
" Really?? YES!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hm. Too eager to slack off. Addin' 20. \n"
" player:\n"
" Dang it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아. 그래. 우리를 아프게 할 수 있다는 걸 알면서도 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 헌터들한테 시험했다는 거지. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 풋. 그런 게 무슨 대수라고. \n"
" player:\n"
" 농담하는 거지?? <1>너도 모르게 실험당한 거잖아!</2> 네 병은 그 사람 때문이라고!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그리고 그게, 우릴 아프게 만든다는 걸 알고도 우리 모두를 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</3>에 노출시킨 거랑 뭐가 달라? \n"
" !point\n"
" 우린 다 같은 새는 배에 타고 있어, 꼬마야. 할 수 있는 건 계속 노 젓는 것뿐이지.\n"
" player:\n"
" ... 선장을 바다에 던져버리기 전까지는 말이야. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하 하 하!\n"
" !cough\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><4>(콜록 <i>콜록</5> 콜록)</6></7></8> 흠. 내 훈련이 먹히는 모양이군. 네 훈련표에서 팔굽혀펴기 하나 빼주지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 진짜?? 좋아!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흠. 너무 좋아하니 괘씸죄로 20개 추가. \n"
" player:\n"
" 젠장."

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DIARY
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DIARY"
msgid "Didn't you hear? Grandpa's Diary... It said--"
msgstr "못 들었어? 할아버지 일기에... 이렇게 적혀 있었어--"

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BYEBYE
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BYEBYE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I... I was just kidding. I'm ready to go when you are, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 나... 난 그냥 농담한 거야. 헌터, 네가 준비되면 나도 갈 준비됐어."

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DIARY
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DIARY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I'm about halfway through, now, and the more I read, the less I know my <#BLUE>Grandpa</>. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Studying the <#RED>{name.rot}</> in secret, he discovered it was impurities in <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> causing their mutations.\n"
" !think\n"
" It's those same impurities that cause both powers AND illnesses in <i>people.</> \n"
" !dubious\n"
" Powers like yours. Illnesses like mine."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 지금 절반쯤 읽었는데, 읽을수록 <#BLUE>할아버지</>를 더 모르겠어. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그는 <#RED>{name.rot}</>를 몰래 연구하다가, <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 안의 불순물이 변이를 일으킨다는 걸 알아냈어.\n"
" !think\n"
" 그리고 그 같은 불순물이 <i>사람들</>에게 능력도, 병도 둘 다 만든대. \n"
" !dubious\n"
" 네 능력 같은 거. 내 병 같은 거."

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SICK
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SICK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Not only that, <#BLUE>Grandpa</> decided to test this on <#RED>Hunters</>...\n"
" player:\n"
" Like {name.npc_dojo_master}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"Any powers will benefit their duties, any illnesses will benefit my research to help my dear <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Whoa. Wait--if the same impurities change us, does that mean... <i>we're</> <#RED>{name.rot}</> too?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Well, n--uh, y--.... This isn't the time for semantics... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Go get the final <#RED>Key Fragment</>, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 그뿐만 아니라, <#BLUE>할아버지</>는 이걸 <#RED>헌터들</>에게 시험하기로 했어...\n"
" player:\n"
" 예를 들면 {name.npc_dojo_master}처럼!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"어떤 능력이든 녀석들의 임무에 도움이 되고, 어떤 병이든 내 사랑하는 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>를 돕기 위한 연구에 도움이 된다.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 우와. 잠깐만. 같은 불순물이 우리를 바꾸는 거면... <i>우리도</> <#RED>{name.rot}</>인 거야?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그, 아니--어, 맞--.... 지금은 그런 말꼬리 잡을 때가 아니야... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 마지막 <#RED>열쇠 파편</>을 찾으러 가자, 헌터."

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_STOPHIM
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_STOPHIM"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" He was obsessed with finding a cure--but I agree. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Go find that last <#RED>Key Fragment</>, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 할아버지는 치료법을 찾는 데에 집착했어. 나도 이해는 가지만. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 마지막 <#RED>열쇠 파편</>을 찾아와, 헌터."

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BYEBYE
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BYEBYE"
msgid "I wish I could chat, but I'm on a Key Fragment-finding roll!"
msgstr "수다 떨고 싶긴 한데, 지금 열쇠 파편 찾는 흐름 제대로 탔거든!"

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DIARY
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DIARY"
msgid "Not exactly light reading, is it?"
msgstr "가볍게 읽을 내용은 아니지?"

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SICK
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SICK"
msgid "Wait--so your random 'allergy' was <i>caused</> by his 'brighter new {name.konjur} future'?"
msgstr "잠깐만, 그럼 네 뜬금없는 '알레르기'는 그 '{name.konjur}의 밝은 새 미래' 때문에 <i>생긴</> 거야?"

#: Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_STOPHIM
msgctxt "Convo.after_find_second_key_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_STOPHIM"
msgid "And he let it happen. Let's get the last Key Fragment and stop him."
msgstr "그리고 할아버지는 그걸 그냥 두고 봤어. 마지막 열쇠 조각을 찾아서 그를 막자."

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LETSRIDE_ENDLOOP
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LETSRIDE_ENDLOOP"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I suppose that's true! We're coming, <#BLUE>Grandpa</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그 말도 맞네! 우리가 갈게요, <#BLUE>할아버지</>!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_PAPER
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_PAPER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" How odd... wait.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" This... this is a page torn from <#RED>my Grandpa's Diary</>! I'm certain of it. After a decade with his notes, I'd recognize his handwriting anywhere.\n"
" player:\n"
" Can you read it? Is it... \"private\"?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"Private\"?! Hunter! Heavens, no. Look, this is dated back when I was just a baby! It reads:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !diary_page_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"Smithying of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> is ahead of schedule. No wonder--smithies are marvelously talented.\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"To think! Bringing <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> power to every household on the continent! A brighter world for all!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"But especially for my young <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>. They've had such a hard start, so I'll do all in my power to build them a future free from pain--that I vow!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"P.S., How the little one delights in my <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> experiments! A brilliant <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</> in the making!\"\n"
" player:\n"
" That's very sweet, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" <i>(sniffle)</> We have to save him, Hunter. Hurry! Let's go!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이상하네... 잠깐.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이건... <#RED>우리 할아버지 일기</>에서 찢긴 페이지야! 확실해. 10년 동안 그분 메모를 봤으니, 글씨체는 알아볼 수 있어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 읽어도 돼? 혹시... \"은밀한\" 얘기라도? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !shock\n"
" 대체 무슨 소리를?! 당연히 아니지. 봐봐, 이건 내가 갓난아기였을 때 날짜야! 이렇게 적혀 있어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !diary_page_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 파이프라인 에너지 그리드</1> 구축이 예정보다 빠르다. 대장장이들의 실력이 참으로 뛰어나니 그럴 수밖에.\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"세상에! 대륙의 모든 가정에 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</2> 동력을 공급하다니... 모두를 위해 세상을 밝히는 것이다!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"그리고 무엇보다도, 내 손자 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</3>를 위한 일이다. 시작이 쉽지 않았으니 고통 없는 미래를 만들어 주기 위해서라면, 내가 할 수 있는 모든 걸 다할 것이다. 무슨 일이 있어도!\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"추신, 이 아이가 내 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</4> 실험을 어찌나 좋아하던지! 장차 훌륭한 <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</5>가 되겠는걸!\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 다정하시네, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" <6>(훌쩍)</7> 그분을 구해야 해. 서둘러!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SMARTROT
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SMARTROT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" I... I hadn't stopped to think about that...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" And to be honest, we'll have to figure that out later!\n"
" !point\n"
" We must focus on the fact that <#RED>Grandpa's</> alive and we need to save him before the <#RED>{name.rot}</> get smart and realize they're dumb and hurt him!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I-I realize that didn't make any sense b-but it also <i>does?</> \n"
" !point\n"
" Forget all that. We must hurry!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" 나... 나 그건 생각도 못 했어...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그리고 솔직히, 그건 나중에 알아내야 해!\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>할아버지</>가 살아 있다는 사실에 집중하자. <#RED>{name.rot}</1>들이 똑똑해져서 자기들이 멍청한 걸 깨닫고 그분을 해치기 전에 구해야 해!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 나-나도 방금 말이 말이 안 된다는 건 아-아는데, 또 <2>맞는 것 같기도 해?</3> \n"
" !point\n"
" 아니, 됐다. 서둘러야 해!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LETSRIDE_ENDLOOP
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LETSRIDE_ENDLOOP"
msgid "Hey, it's dawn o'clock somewhere! We ride now!"
msgstr "자, 해가 중천이라고! 지금 출발하자!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_PAPER
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_PAPER"
msgid "<#RED>[Give {name.npc_scout} the Page]</> Before we go, that {name.rot_boss} dropped this sheet of paper. Can <i>you</> make out the chicken-scratch?"
msgstr "<#RED>[{name.npc_scout}에게 페이지를 건넨다]</> 가기 전에, 그 {name.rot_boss}가 이 종이 한 장을 떨어뜨렸어. <i>너</> 이 악필 읽을 수 있어?"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SMARTROT
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_5_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SMARTROT"
msgid "Since when do brainless {name.rot} hatch kidnapping plans that involve multiple locations?"
msgstr "대체 언제부터 멍청한 {name.rot}이 여러 장소에 걸친 납치 계획을 짜기 시작한 거지?"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_JOURNAL
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_JOURNAL"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ooh, let's see here... Dated not long after the last page, when I was still young. It reads:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_page_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> is sick. Their illness is unique--aggravated by proximity to <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>...\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"I've had to quarantine them in a home away from my lab, out on the edge of the <#BLUE>Capital</>.\"\n"
" !think\n"
" I... I remember that... \n"
" !diary_page_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"I tremble to think: Could I have caused <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> illness?? Don't dwell. Forward, ever forward. I can fix this. A cure! I MUST find a cure...\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_konjurist}</> has a theory on <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>. It is the source of all <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> with 'boundless potential'. It is our only hope.\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> and her father warn against deeper excavations, but if it may cure my grandchild--fix what I have done--then the choice is clear. We dig.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Y-your Grandpa... he <i>caused</> your illness!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" N-not on purpose! He... All we know for certain is my <#BLUE>Grandpa</> was doing all he could to cure me.\n"
" player:\n"
" With some kind of '<#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>' with 'unlimited potential'...?\t\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Which he might have right now! So, to the <#BLUE>{name.grimhollow_volcano}</>, then!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 오, 어디 보자... 지난 페이지에서 그리 오래 지나지 않았고, 내가 아직 어렸을 때 날짜네. 이렇게 적혀 있어:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_page_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>이 아프다. 이 병은 특이하게도<#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</1> 가까이에 있으면 악화된다...\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"내 연구실에서 떨어진, <#BLUE>수도</2> 외곽의 집에 격리해 둘 수밖에 없었다.\"\n"
" !think\n"
" 나... 나 그거 기억나... \n"
" !diary_page_start\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"생각만 해도 떨린다. 내가 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}의</3> 병을 일으킨 걸까?? 곱씹지 말자. 앞으로, 계속 앞으로. 내가 바로잡을 수 있다. 치료제! 반드시 치료제를 찾아야 한다...\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_konjurist}</4>가 <#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}</5>에 대한 가설을 세웠다. 이것은 '무한한 잠재력'을 지닌 모든 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</6>의 근원이다. 우리의 유일한 희망이다.\"\n"
" {name.grandpa_quote} \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</7>와 그녀의 아버지는 더 깊이 파내려가는 것을 반대하지만, 그게 내 손주를 치료하고, 내가 저지른 일을 바로잡을 수 있다면... 선택은 분명하다. 판다.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 너-너희 할아버지가... 네 병을 <8>일으킨</9> 거야!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 일-일부러 그런 건 아니야! 그분은... 확실한 건 우리 <#BLUE>할아버지</10>가 날 고치려고 할 수 있는 걸 다 하셨다는 거야.\n"
" player:\n"
" '무한한 잠재력'이 있다는 '<#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}</11>' 같은 걸로...?\t\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그리고 그걸 지금 갖고 있을지도 몰라! 그러니까 <#BLUE>{name.grimhollow_volcano}</12>로 가자!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SAVEGRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SAVEGRANDPA"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" To <#BLUE>{name.grimhollow_volcano}</>, then! Hold on, <#BLUE>Grandpa</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" 그럼 <#BLUE>{name.grimhollow_volcano}</>로 가자! 버텨, <#BLUE>할아버지</>!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_JOURNAL
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_JOURNAL"
msgid "<#RED>[Give {name.npc_scout} the Diary Page]</> That {name.rot_boss} dropped another of your Grandpa's Diary Pages."
msgstr "<#RED>[{name.npc_scout}에게 일기 페이지 건네기]</> 그 {name.rot_boss}가 네 할아버지 일기 페이지를 또 떨어뜨렸어."

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SAVEGRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_6_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SAVEGRANDPA"
msgid "Enough jaw-flappin'. Let's go get us a Grandpa."
msgstr "말은 그만 털고, 할아버지 데리러 가자."

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HUNTER
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HUNTER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Someone as skilled as <i>you?</> You'll be in high demand, I'm sure of it.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Besides, I could always use a test subject.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh! The look on your face! Complete lack of expression! Classic.\n"
" !point\n"
" Alright test subject--I mean <i>Hunter</>. How about we go get that last <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>너</>처럼 실력 있는 사람이면? 분명 여기저기서 찾을걸.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그리고 난 언제나 실험 대상이 필요하거든.\n"
" player:\n"
" 어이!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 오! 그 표정 좀 봐! 완전 무표정! 아주 클래식하네.\n"
" !point\n"
" 좋아, 실험 대상--아, 아니 <i>헌터</>. 마지막 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> 찾으러 갈까?"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_GOGOGO
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_GOGOGO"
msgid "Let's do it!"
msgstr "가자!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HUNTER
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HUNTER"
msgid "I'm in, but what use will a Rot-free world have for a Hunter like me?"
msgstr "나도 함께할게. 근데 랏 없는 세상에 나 같은 헌터가 무슨 쓸모가 있을까?"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ADDITIONAL_COMMENT
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ADDITIONAL_COMMENT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh, but please don't forget, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> is still lost out there somewhere. Finding him is our top priority, even above the <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</>.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I can hardly call myself the leader of the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> until my whole team is safe.\n"
" !point\n"
" And not to sound callous but <i>your</> job will be a lot less dangerous with our <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</> here improving your weaponry.\n"
" player:\n"
" On it. I'll get him back safe.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Thanks, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, 그래도 잊지 마. <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>는 아직 어딘가에서 실종 상태야. 그를 찾는 게 <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</>보다도 최우선이야.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 팀 전원이 안전해지기 전까진 내가 <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>의 리더라고 하기도 어려워.\n"
" !point\n"
" 매정하게 들릴 수도 있지만, <i>네</> 일은 우리 <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</>가 여기서 무기를 강화해 주면 훨씬 덜 위험해질 거야.\n"
" player:\n"
" 맡겨 둬. 무사히 데려올게.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 고마워, 헌터."

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BYE
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BYE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Sounds good, Hunter. Great work!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 좋아, 헌터. 정말 수고했어!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_THINKIN
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_THINKIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I was just thinking... I wish my Grandpa was here to see this.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait--your last name's {name.flitt_lastname}! Your Grandpa... he wasn't--?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>, pioneer of {name.konjur} science and inventor of the <#KONJUR>{name.town_grid_cryst}</> and the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</>.\" Yep. That's my Grandpa.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Sorry. I didn't bring him up to name-drop. Truly. I actually try and avoid talking about him, if I'm honest.\n"
" player:\n"
" Really? Why?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Following in his pawprints... it's a lot to live up to. Grandpa did a lot in his lifetime, more than most ever dream of.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" We lost a great mind when he passed in the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" Right... sorry. You must miss him a lot.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... I just hope he's proud of all this. I wasn't much help to him while he was alive, but I can at least try to protect his legacy.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-anyways, he'd tell us to stop rambling about the past, and start pushing towards our <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-perfected future!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" So what do you say, Hunter? Ready to get back out there?\n"
" player:\n"
" Ready. And {name.npc_scout}? Your Grandpa would be very proud of you. I know it.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh, hah, thanks, Hunter. Oh dear. Am I turning red?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 방금 생각하고 있었어... 우리 할아버지도 이걸 봤으면 좋았을 텐데.\n"
" player:\n"
" 잠깐만, 성씨가 {name.flitt_lastname}잖아! 네 할아버지... 설마 그분이--?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" \"<#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>, {name.konjur} 과학의 선구자이자 <#KONJUR>{name.town_grid_cryst}</>와 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 파이프라인 에너지 그리드</>의 발명가.\" 맞아. 우리 할아버지야.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 미안. 잘난 척하려고 꺼낸 얘긴 아니야. 진짜로. 솔직히 말하면 그분 얘긴 되도록 피하려고 해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 정말? 왜?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그분 발자취를 따라간다는 게... 기대치가 너무 높아. 할아버지는 평생 대부분이 꿈도 못 꿀 만큼 많은 걸 해냈어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <#KONJUR>대폭발</> 때 그분이 돌아가시면서 우리는 위대한 지성을 잃었지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그래... 미안. 많이 그립겠다.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... 그냥 이 모든 걸 보고 자랑스러워해 주셨으면 해. 살아 계실 땐 내가 큰 도움이 못 됐지만, 적어도 그분의 유산을 지키려고는 할 수 있으니까.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아-아무튼, 할아버지라면 과거 얘기 그만하고 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>로 완벽해질 미래를 향해 나아가라고 하셨겠지!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 어때, 헌터? 다시 나갈 준비 됐어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 준비됐어. 그리고 {name.npc_scout}? 네 할아버지도 널 정말 자랑스러워하셨을 거야. 난 확신해.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, 하하, 고마워 헌터. 이런. 나 얼굴 빨개졌나?"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BYE
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BYE"
msgid "Yeah, same here. I'd better get after more {name_multiple.konjur_heart}!"
msgstr "응, 나도 그래. {name_multiple.konjur_heart}을 더 찾아봐야겠어!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_THINKIN
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_THINKIN"
msgid "Penny for your thoughts? <z 0.7>Unrelated: Can I borrow a penny?</>"
msgstr "무슨 생각 해? <z 0.7>뜬금없는 얘기인데, 각 좀 괜찮지?</>"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh, I don't know <i>that</> much. It was my Grandpa who was a {name.c_konjur} genius. As a kit, I watched him work on all kinds of amazing things.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Fortunately, a chest of his research notes was saved during the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>. I've pored over them every day for the past 10 years. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's how I was inspired to modify one of his <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.town_grid_cryst}</> so it could generate a <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wow. You must really take after your Grandpa. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I should be so lucky. With so little <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> in <#BLUE>The Brinks</>, not to mention my <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> allergy, I couldn't properly test anything I dreamt up. Including the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I'm amazed the darn thing actually works!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh! Uh--don't tell anyone I said that, please. Me being the fearless leader of the <#RED>{name.foxtails}s</> and everything. \n"
" player:\n"
" You really need to give yourself more credit.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" You sound like <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>! Next you'll be complaining about your \"gall-darn knees!\"\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" But in all sincerity, thank you. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" So what do you say, Hunter? Ready to get back out there?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, 난 <i>그렇게</> 많이 아는 건 아니야. {name.c_konjur} 천재는 우리 할아버지였지. 어릴 때 할아버지가 온갖 놀라운 걸 만드는 걸 지켜봤어.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 다행히 <#KONJUR>대폭발</> 때 할아버지 연구 노트가 담긴 상자 하나가 살아남았어. 지난 10년 동안 난 그걸 매일 파고들었지. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그래서 할아버지의 <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.town_grid_cryst}</> 하나를 개조해서 <#KONJUR>버블 실드</>를 생성하게 만들 영감을 얻었어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 와. 진짜 할아버지 기질을 물려받았나 보네. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그랬으면 좋겠네. <#BLUE>The Brinks</>에는 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>가 너무 부족했고, 거기에 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 알레르기까지 있어서 내가 떠올린 건 제대로 시험해 볼 수가 없었어. <#KONJUR>버블 실드</>도 포함해서.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그 망할 게 진짜로 작동한다는 게 아직도 놀라워!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아! 어--내가 이런 말 했다고 아무한테도 말하지 마. 내가 그래도 <#RED>{name.foxtails}s</>의 겁 없는 리더니까. \n"
" player:\n"
" 너 자신을 좀 더 믿어도 돼.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그 말 <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> 같네! 다음엔 \"제기랄 무릎\" 타령까지 하겠어?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그래도 진심으로, 고마워. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 어때, 헌터? 다시 나갈 준비 됐어?"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Let's do this!"
msgstr "가자!"

#: Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How did you learn so much about this stuff?"
msgstr "이런 건 어떻게 이렇게 많이 배웠어?"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_bnd.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_bnd.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'll say. Lucky for us, our Hunter's too crafty to fall for its tricks!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now, don't forget to put its <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in our modded <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> there at the center of camp."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그러게. 다행히 우리 헌터는 머리가 좋아서 그런 속임수엔 안 넘어가!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자, 그 녀석의 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>는 캠프 중앙에 있는 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣는 거 잊지 마."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_bnd.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_bnd.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "That {name.bandicoot} was one sly customer."
msgstr "그 {name.bandicoot}, 진짜 교활한 녀석이었어."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_bnd.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_bnd.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm still haunted by your fight with <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</>, Hunter. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Honestly, I'm just glad it's over. That was a tough fight to watch... I mean, literally.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I swear I was seeing double through half of it. Not exactly ideal when I'm trying to keep the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> flying straight."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 헌터, 네가 <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</>랑 싸우던 장면이 아직도 머리에 맴돌아. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 솔직히 끝나서 다행이야. 보기 정말 힘든 싸움이었어... 말 그대로.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 싸움의 절반쯤은 진짜로 사물이 두 개로 보였다고. 내가 <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</1>를 똑바르게 조종하는 것도 힘들 지경이었다니까."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_eggzy.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_eggzy.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "It'll be okay, {name.npc_scout}. I'll be right back."
msgstr "괜찮을 거야, {name.npc_scout}. 곧 돌아올게."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_eggzy.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_eggzy.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Hey, Hunter. It's good you defeated <#RED>{name.eggzy}</> and all, but I can't shake this feeling... \n"
" !gesture\n"
" They're an orphan, like a lot of folks in <#BLUE>the Brinks.</>\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Like me. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7><i>... Re-burying emotions... Deeper...</></>\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7><i>...............</></>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Woo! Great job, Hunter! Now, don't forget to put that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 있잖아, 헌터. 네가 <#RED>{name.eggzy}</>를 쓰러뜨린 건 정말 잘한 일이지만, 이 기분이 계속 안 가셔... \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그 애도 <#BLUE>the Brinks</1>의 많은 사람들처럼 고아였잖아.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 나처럼. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <2><3>... 감정을 가슴에 깊이... 더 깊이 묻어야 하는...</4></5>\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7><i>...............</></>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 후! 잘했어, 헌터! 자, 그 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣는 거 잊지 마!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_grimhollow.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_grimhollow.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Will do!"
msgstr "그럴게!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_grimhollow.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_grimhollow.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Not the rescue we expected, obviously, but we still made progress. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" We found the door to <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> lab, confirmation that he <i>is</> alive, and a plan for how to get in. \n"
" player:\n"
" And <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> gave you the rest of your <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> <#RED>Diary</>. Are you going to read it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" ... Yes. I will. It will have more answers... I'm not sure I'm ready to hear them, however. \n"
" player:\n"
" Whatever it says, remember: you are not your <#BLUE>Grandpa</>. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Sure. Of course not. Of course not.\n"
" !think\n"
" Suppose it's time to get after those <#RED>Key Fragments</> to open the lab door, eh, Hunter?  \n"
" !point\n"
" But first, put that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in my modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> for some more power."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 예상한 구조는 아니었지만, 그래도 진전은 있었어. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>할아버지</> 연구실 문을 찾았고, 그분이 <i>살아</> 있다는 확인도 했고, 들어갈 방법까지 세웠어. \n"
" player:\n"
" 그리고 <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>가 네 <#BLUE>할아버지</> <#RED>일기</> 나머지를 줬지. 읽어볼 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" ... 응. 읽을게. 거기에 답이 더 있겠지... 하지만 들을 준비가 됐는지는 모르겠어. \n"
" player:\n"
" 무슨 내용이든, 기억해: 넌 네 <#BLUE>할아버지</>가 아니야. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그래. 당연히 아니지. 당연히 아니고.\n"
" !think\n"
" 연구실 문을 열 <#RED>열쇠 파편</>들을 찾으러 갈 때가 됐네, 그렇지 헌터?  \n"
" !point\n"
" 하지만 먼저, 그 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 내 개조 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣어서 출력을 더 올리자."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HONEST
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HONEST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Really? Oh dear...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, um, I would never have guessed!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 정말? 이런...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 음, 어, 난 전혀 눈치 못 챘네!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MODEST
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MODEST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh, no need to be modest--you just did something very few have ever even dared to attempt! Own it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아, 겸손 떨 필요 없어--방금 너는 아주 소수만 감히 시도했던 일을 해낸 거야! 당당해져!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HONEST
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HONEST"
msgid "Did I? All I remember is screaming in my head the entire time."
msgstr "내가? 내 기억엔 내내 머릿속으로 비명 지른 것밖에 없는데."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MODEST
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MODEST"
msgid "Heh. No biggie."
msgstr "헤헤, 별거 아니야."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" That was... <i>incredible!</> I can't believe you downed a <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> on your first try!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 방금 그거... <i>정말 대단했어!</> 첫 시도에 <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</2>를 쓰러뜨리다니 정말 믿기지 않아!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT0.congrats.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I think you might become a Hunter to rival <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> in his heyday.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Speaking of which, you should check in with <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> if you haven't already.\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the Heart-Shaped {name.konjur} Crystal]</> Would he know anything about this weird rock the {name.megatreemon} dropped?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Egads! In all the commotion I almost forgot!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" That right there is a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>. It's <i>very</> important to our expedition.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Can you do me a favour? Place <#RED>{name.megatreemon}'s</> <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in the modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> here.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh gosh oh gosh oh gosh. I really hope this works, Hunter..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !thinking\n"
" 너라면 전성기 시절 <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>에 맞먹는 헌터가 될지도 몰라.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 그러고 보니, 아직 안 만났으면 <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>한테 가봐.\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the Heart-Shaped {name.konjur} Crystal]</> 저 녀석이라면 {name.megatreemon}가 떨군 이 이상한 돌에 대해서 알고있지 않을까?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 세상에! 정신없는 와중에 깜빡할 뻔했네!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 그건 바로 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>야. 우리 원정에 <i>아주</> 중요해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 부탁 하나만 할게. <#RED>{name.megatreemon}의</> <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 여기 개조된 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣어줘.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
"아... 제발. 이거 꼭 성공해야 할텐데..."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT1.congrats.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_mt.ATTRACT1.congrats.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You really did it! You took down the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> that swatted the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> out of the sky!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dejected\n"
" What a relief. Maybe now I'll be able to unclench my jaw when I'm flying over the forest.\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the Heart-Shaped {name.konjur} Crystal]</> Oh, by the way, {name.megatreemon} dropped this.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah! You found it! A <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" Hunter... would you please place it in the modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh gosh oh gosh oh gosh. Let's hope this works..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 진짜 해냈네! 하늘에서 <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>를 후려쳐 떨어뜨린 <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>를 쓰러뜨렸어!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 살았다. 이제 숲 위를 날 때 이를 악무는 버릇 좀 풀 수 있겠네.\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[하트 모양 {name.konjur} 크리스털을 보여준다]</> 아, 맞다. {name.megatreemon}가 이걸 떨궜어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 찾았구나! <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" 헌터... 그걸 개조된 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣어줄래?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아 이런 아 이런 아 이런. 제발 이게 통하길..."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Yikes! Good to know! Alright, go pop that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</> into the modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 헉! 알겠어! 좋아, 그 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>를 개조된 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣어."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT"
msgid "Alright!"
msgstr "좋아!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "You should see my high fives! 'Up top!' <i>(Explosion Sound)</>"
msgstr "내 하이파이브 장난 아니야! '손 위로!' <i>(Explosion Sound)</>"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_owl.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Amazing that you got <#RED>{name.owlitzer}'s</> <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>!\n"
" !think\n"
" She's so tough, it's almost hard to believe she's gone...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I might need you to pinch me, to make sure I'm not dreaming.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ... On second thought, don't. I've seen you fight. Your idea of a 'pinch' might lead to some serious injury."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 네가 <#RED>{name.owlitzer}의</> <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>를 가져오다니, 대단해!\n"
" !think\n"
" 걔는 너무 강해서, 진짜 사라졌다는 게 거의 안 믿겨...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 내가 꿈꾸는 거 아닌지 확인하게 나 좀 꼬집어줘야 할지도.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...아, 다시 생각해보니 하지 마. 네 싸우는 거 봤잖아. 네가 말하는 '꼬집기'는 큰 부상으로 이어질 수 있어."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_sdmnt.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_sdmnt.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "You bet. And don't worry, {name.npc_scout}. We'll find your Grandpa."
msgstr "당연하지. 걱정 마, {name.npc_scout}. 네 할아버지 찾아낼게."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_sdmnt.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_sdmnt.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" You know, I've been thinking of <#RED>{name.sedament}</>, and I feel... kinda bad. Behind that granite facade was just a little crow, defending its nest. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" That said, the crow <i>was</> a <#RED>{name.rot}</>, <i>and</> we needed its <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>, <i>and</> it's still alive, so... \n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Guilt: absolved!  \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" But no Grandpa. While you fought, his <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> signature leapt to another location. They're moving him around!\n"
" player:\n"
" That's weird, right? {name.rot}'s known for mindless violence, not playing keep-away...\n"
" agent:  \n"
" !think\n"
" That <i>is</> very weird... as in, very never-happens-at-all-ever-weird, indeed. \n"
" !point\n"
" Hm. Best we prepare for the worst. Put that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in our modded-out <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> for more power, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 있지, <#RED>{name.sedament}</> 생각을 계속 했는데... 좀 미안하더라. 그 화강암 같은 겉모습 뒤엔 둥지를 지키던 작은 까마귀가 있었을 뿐이었어. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래도 그 까마귀는 <i>분명</> <#RED>{name.rot}</>였고, <i>그리고</> 우린 그 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>가 필요했어, <i>게다가</> 아직 살아 있으니까... \n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 죄책감: 해제!  \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 근데 할아버지는 없어. 네가 싸우는 동안 그분의 <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> 신호가 다른 위치로 튀었어. 놈들이 계속 옮기고 있어!\n"
" player:\n"
" 이상하지, 그치? {name.rot}는 숨바꼭질이 아니라 생각 없는 폭력으로 알려져 있잖아...\n"
" agent:  \n"
" !think\n"
" 그건 <i>진짜</> 이상해... 그러니까, 절대 일어날 리 없는 급으로 이상하다는 거지. \n"
" !point\n"
" 흠. 최악을 대비하는 게 좋겠어. 힘을 더 끌어올리려면 그 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 우리 튜닝한 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣어, 헌터."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BACKLATER
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BACKLATER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Of course. Talk soon, Hunter!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 물론이지. 곧 다시 얘기하자, 헌터!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BUBBLE
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BUBBLE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Sometimes, I catch myself staring up at it and it feels like I'm dreaming. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" And then I'm flooded with embarrassment. \n"
" player:\n"
" \"Embarrassment\"? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" At how much I believed <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</> would save us. As though he were some superpowered, infallible, genius godhead. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" But seeing him after all those years... he was just an old fox who took it all on by himself and failed. Utterly. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Seeing that, I knew we could save ourselves--we just had to band together and do the work, dang it! \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh heck yeah!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I swear, you and <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> have dragged my vocabulary through the... <z 0.7>flippin'</> mud! Hahaha!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 가끔 나도 모르게 그걸 올려다보게 돼… 그러다 보면, 마치 꿈을 꾸는 기분이 들어 \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ... 그러고 나면 곧바로 민망해져.\n"
" player:\n"
" 민망해진다고? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !netural\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>가 우릴 구원해 줄 거라고 내가 얼마나 철석같이 믿었는지 떠올라서... 마치 전능하고 완벽한 천재라도 되는 것처럼. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그런데 지금 와서 보니까… 그냥, 모든 걸 혼자 짊어지다가 완전히 실패해버린 늙은 여우였더라. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그걸 보고 나서야 알았어. 우린 우리 힘으로 해낼 수 있고… 결국 필요한 건, 힘을 합쳐 직접 해내는 거였다는 걸! \n"
" player:\n"
" 오, 그렇지!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 진짜, 너랑 <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> 때문에 내 말투가 완전 <z 0.7>아주 그냥</> 개판이 됐잖아! 하하하!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" This team... \n"
" !dejected\n"
" Despite facing utter disaster from Day One, culminating in a threat to everything they know and love brought on by my own flesh and blood... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" They've stuck together and shown true resilience, courage, and determination. You especially, Hunter. \n"
" player:\n"
" You, too, {name.npc_scout}. You're not sneaking off without some shine on you!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I wouldn't dream of it! \n"
" !think\n"
" I finally accept that <i>I'm</> a part of this team--not my Grandpa's notes or legacy or whatever. Me. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout} {name.flitt_lastname}</>. {name.job_scout} extraordinaire of the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" Speaking of: \"{name_multiple.foxtails}\" on three? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oh! Yes! 1... 2... 3!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name_multiple.foxtails}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" \"Uh, did you mean ON three, dude? Or, like, right AFTER three? Oh my flippin' head....\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Is that supposed to be an impression of <i>me,</> {name.npc_scout}?? I never!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ah, your face, Hunter! Charmingly expressionless as ever. \n"
" !bliss\n"
" Oh, and <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 이 팀은... \n"
" !dejected\n"
" 첫날부터 완전한 재난을 맞았고, 내 친혈육 때문에 결국 자기들이 아끼는 모든 게 위협받는 데까지 갔는데도... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 끝까지 뭉쳐서 진짜 회복력, 용기, 결의를 보여줬어. 특히 너 말이야, 헌터. \n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_scout}, 너도야. 너만 빛 안 받고 슬쩍 빠져나갈 생각은 하지 마!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그럴 생각 전혀 없어! \n"
" !think\n"
" 드디어 받아들였어. <i>내가</> 이 팀의 일원이라는 걸. 할아버지 노트나 유산 같은 게 아니라, 나 자신. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout} {name.flitt_lastname}</>. {name.job_scout}, <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>의 최고!\n"
" player:\n"
" 그 얘기 나온 김에: 셋에 맞춰 \"{name_multiple.foxtails}\" 외칠까? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 오! 좋아! 1... 2... 3!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name_multiple.foxtails}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" \"어, 셋에 맞춰서라는 게 딱 셋에 말하란 뜻이야? 아니면 셋 지나고 바로야? 아 머리야 진짜....\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 그거 <i>내</> 흉내 낸 거야, {name.npc_scout}?? 어이가 없네!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아, 네 표정 봐라 헌터! 여전히 매력적으로 무표정이네. \n"
" !bliss\n"
" 아, 그리고 <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GRANDPA"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No, I haven't. \n"
" !dubious\n"
" If I'm honest, Hunter? I can't say I <i>want</> to. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" Back when we defeated him, I'd hoped he'd come back with us. But he... he chose not to... \n"
" !think\n"
" I'd like to think <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}'s</> doing better, wherever he is. That he's left the <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> behind. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" And that <i>it's</> left <i>him</> behind...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But that's out of my control. I'm moving on and doing what <i>I</> can to make this world a better place. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anything else you want to talk about? I'm sure you've got a lot on your mind, one year on..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아니, 아직. \n"
" !dubious\n"
" 솔직히 말하면, 헌터? 난 <i>그러길</> 바란다고는 못 하겠어. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" 그를 쓰러뜨렸을 때는 그가 우리와 함께 돌아오길 바랐어. 하지만 그는... 그러지 않기로 했지... \n"
" !think\n"
" 어디에 있든 <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}가</> 좀 더 나아졌길 바라. <#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}</>를 뒤로하고. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 그리고 <i>그게</> <i>그를</> 뒤로 남겨뒀길...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 하지만 그건 내가 통제할 수 없어. 난 앞으로 나아가면서 이 세상을 더 나은 곳으로 만들려고 <i>내가</> 할 수 있는 걸 할 거야. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 1년이 지난 지금, 더 이야기하고 싶은 거 있어? 네 머릿속에 생각이 많을 것 같아..."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BACKLATER
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BACKLATER"
msgid "I think it's time to go bash some {name_multiple.rot}, y'know?"
msgstr "이제 {name_multiple.rot} 좀 두들겨 패러 갈 때 된 것 같지 않아?"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BUBBLE
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BUBBLE"
msgid "You can be proud your Bubble Shield is up and running, right?"
msgstr "버블 실드가 제대로 돌아가니까 자랑스러워해도 되지, 그치?"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS"
msgid "How do you feel the {name_multiple.foxtails} are doing these days?"
msgstr "요즘 {name_multiple.foxtails} 상태는 어때 보여?"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GRANDPA"
msgid "Have you heard from your Grandpa in the year since we defeated him?"
msgstr "우리가 그를 쓰러뜨린 뒤 지난 1년 동안 할아버지 소식 들은 거 있어?"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_thchr.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_thchr.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" As do you! I'd call for an encore, but it's curtains for them, and we have their <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> to put in our modded <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Wanna do the honours?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 너도 마찬가지야! 앵콜을 외치고 싶지만, 걔들은 여기서 끝이야. 그리고 우린 녀석들의 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 우리 개조한 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣어야 해!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 네가 마무리해줄래?"

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_thchr.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_thchr.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "It really knew how to shred."
msgstr "진짜 찢어발기더라."

#: Convo.defeated_boss_scout_thchr.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_boss_scout_thchr.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hunter, that was a performance I'll never forget. You deserve a standing ovation for taking down these <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It strikes me, <#RED>{name.thatcher}</> just wanted an audience. I almost feel bad for it... <i>almost.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 헌터, 그건 절대 못 잊을 퍼포먼스였어. 그 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>를 쓰러뜨린 건 기립박수 받아 마땅해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 내가 보기엔 <#RED>{name.thatcher}</>는 관객이 필요했던 것 같아. 좀 불쌍할 뻔했네... <i>거의.</>"

#: Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Mm-hm! You've truly found your footing since we got here."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 응! 여기 온 뒤로 완전히 감 잡았네."

#: Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah-! Me? Oh no, no, no, you deserve the credit for your hard work! I'm just glad to help where I can.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Congrats on your win, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아-! 나? 아냐, 아냐, 아냐. 네가 열심히 한 공이야! 난 내가 도울 수 있는 데서 도와서 기쁠 뿐이야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 승리 축하해, 헌터."

#: Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You really are! You're doing the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> proud.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Congrats on your win, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 진짜 그래! 네 덕에 <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>가 자랑스러워할 거야.\n"
" !clap\n"
" 승리 축하해, 헌터."

#: Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I really downed that {name.yammo_miniboss}, didn't I?"
msgstr "내가 진짜 {name.yammo_miniboss} 잡은 거 맞지?"

#: Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "A lot of that is thanks to you."
msgstr "그중 큰 몫은 네 덕이야."

#: Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.defeated_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "I <i>do</> feel like I'm finding my groove!"
msgstr "나도 <i>진짜</> 감을 찾아가는 것 같아!"

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Um, only the most versatile chemical compound in the whole entire world!\n"
" !think\n"
" I love talking about <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>. Ask me whatever you want to know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 음, 전 세계에서 가장 다재다능한 화학 물질이지!\n"
" !think\n"
" 난 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 얘기하는 게 정말 좋아. 궁금한 건 뭐든 물어봐."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Ugh, that's right. I forgot you were from the <#RED>Brinks</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Less, uh, <i>educated</i> folks might think of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> as \"magic\".\n"
" !notebook\n"
" But that's just because they're unable to explain its unusual properties."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 아, 맞다. 네가 <#RED>브링크스</> 출신인 걸 깜빡했네.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그... <i>교육을 덜 받은</i> 사람들은 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 \"마법\"이라고 생각할 수도 있어.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 그건 그냥 그 특이한 성질을 설명할 수 없어서 그래."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" There are veins of it all over the earth-- some {name_multiple.job_konjurist} theorize the planet has a molten core of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But before the disaster, the best industrial source of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> was the mountain."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그건 땅 속 곳곳에 광맥처럼 퍼져 있어. 일부 {name_multiple.job_konjurist}는 행성 중심부가 녹아 있는 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>로 이뤄졌다고 보지.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 하지만 재난 이전에 산업적으로 최적의 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</1> 공급원은 그 산이었어."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Beats me.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Preliminary studies showed thickening in some areas of the brain after the ingestion of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" But sadly that research was in the early stages when the eruption hit, and is now lost entirely.\n"
" !think\n"
" I guess in a way you're a continuation of that research. That's sort of comforting."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 나도 몰라.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 예비 연구에선 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 섭취한 뒤 뇌 일부 영역이 두꺼워지는 현상이 보였어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 하지만 안타깝게도 대폭발이 터졌을 때 그 연구는 초기 단계였고, 지금은 완전히 사라졌어.\n"
" !think\n"
" 어떻게 보면 넌 그 연구의 연장선이네. 그건 좀 위안이 된다."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" No.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" ...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...What?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! You think I've contradicted myself. Haha.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No. Just because I'm not personally able to explain <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> yet, doesn't mean an explanation doesn't exist.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It just means we have more to learn."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아니.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" ...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...뭐?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 내가 모순됐다고 생각한 거구나. 하하.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아니야. 내가 아직 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 직접 설명 못 한다고 해서 설명 자체가 없는 건 아니야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 단지 우리가 더 많이 배워야 한다는 의미일 뿐이지."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yes."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 응."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_ANSWER
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_ANSWER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" Anytime.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I mean it! Any time."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" 언제든.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 진짜야! 아무 때나."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT"
msgid "Thanks for chatting."
msgstr "얘기해줘서 고마워."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I was wondering... what <i>is</i> {name.konjur}, exactly?"
msgstr "궁금했는데... {name.konjur}가 정확히 <i>뭐</i>야?"

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "I thought {name.konjur} was magic."
msgstr "{name.konjur}는 마법인 줄 알았어."

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Where does {name.konjur} come from?"
msgstr "{name.konjur}는 어디서 나와?"

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "Why does {name.konjur} give me powers?"
msgstr "{name.konjur}는 왜 나한테 힘을 주는 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Can you explain {name.konjur}'s unusual properties?"
msgstr "{name.konjur}의 특이한 성질을 설명해 줄 수 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_1_what_is_konjur_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "Mountain? You mean the volcano?"
msgstr "산? 화산 말하는 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Huh? No. We're just scientists who study <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Though every respectable {name.job_konjurist} worked for <#RED>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe that's why you're confused."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 어? 아니. 우린 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 연구하는 과학자들일 뿐이야.\n"
" !think\n"
" 다만 이름값 있는 {name.job_konjurist}들은 전부 <#RED>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> 밑에서 일했지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 네가 헷갈린 게 그래서일지도."

#: Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I guess it only takes a few years for everyone to forget the genius of a generation.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Kind of makes me wonder what I do this all for.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway, unless you need an <#RED>Upgrade</>, one of my experiments should catalyze soon and I'd like to watch the reaction."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 몇 년이면 다들 한 시대의 천재를 잊어버리나 보네.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 이걸 다 왜 하는지 가끔 의문이 들기도 하고.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼 <#RED>업그레이드</>가 필요한 거 아니면, 내 실험 하나가 곧 촉매 반응을 시작할 거라 반응을 지켜보고 싶어."

#: Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE"
msgid "Of course. See ya, {name.npc_konjurist}."
msgstr "물론이지. 또 봐, {name.npc_konjurist}."

#: Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I was wondering... are \"{name_multiple.job_konjurist}\" like, an organization or something?"
msgstr "궁금했는데... \"{name_multiple.job_konjurist}\"는 뭐 단체 같은 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "That name sounds familiar."
msgstr "그 이름, 뭔가 익숙한데."

#: Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_2_what_are_teffrites_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Should I know who that is?"
msgstr "내가 저 녀석이 누군지 알아야 해?"

#: Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" He's the father of all <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> technology."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>라고?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그 사람은 모든 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</1> 기술의 아버지야."

#: Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Of course. My field of study exists because of him.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We worked closely before the eruption, you know. Brilliant guy.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" I can't chat all day though. Do you need an <#RED>Upgrade</> before I get back to it?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 당연하지. 내 연구 분야 자체가 그분 덕분에 존재해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 알다시피 대폭발 전엔 우리 꽤 밀접하게 일했어. 정말 뛰어난 사람이었지.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 근데 하루 종일 수다 떨 순 없어. 나 다시 하던 거 하러 가려는데 <#RED>강화</> 필요해?"

#: Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE"
msgid "Nah, I'm good. Thanks though."
msgstr "아냐, 난 괜찮아. 그래도 고마워."

#: Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Alright, see ya Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 알았어, 또 봐 헌터."

#: Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "You mentioned someone named {name.flitt_lastname} once. Who is that?"
msgstr "전에 {name.flitt_lastname}이라는 사람 얘기했잖아. 그게 누구야?"

#: Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_3_who_is_mulligan_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "You seem to think highly of him."
msgstr "그 사람을 엄청 높이 평가하네."

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm looking to develop a more concentrated <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> synthesization.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" The old synthesization method worked fine, but it was much too wasteful. Even I can admit that."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 더 고농축 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 합성법을 개발하려고 해.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 예전 합성법도 작동은 잘했지만, 너무 낭비가 심했거든. 나도 인정할 정도로."

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Um. For when we rebuild."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 음. 우리가 재건할 때 쓰려고."

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Haha. What a bizarre line of thinking.\n"
" !think\n"
" The eruption was a catastrophe, but society will eventually rebuild.\n"
" !agree\n"
" And I'll have my tech ready when they do."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 하하. 참 별난 생각이네.\n"
" !think\n"
" 대폭발은 대재앙이었지만, 사회는 결국 다시 세워질 거야.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그리고 그때를 대비해 내 기술도 준비해 둘 거고."

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE"
msgid "See ya, {name.npc_konjurist}."
msgstr "또 봐, {name.npc_konjurist}."

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "What are you studying out here, anyway?"
msgstr "근데 여기서 뭘 연구하는 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Oh. But why? There's no {name.konjur} technology anymore."
msgstr "아. 근데 왜? 이제 {name.konjur} 기술은 없잖아."

#: Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_4_research_focus_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "I guess I just thought the eruption meant it was all gone forever."
msgstr "난 그냥 대폭발로 다 영원히 사라진 줄 알았어."

#: Convo.dgn_5_antidote_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_5_antidote_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Haha. Why?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Taking care of <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> is what you're for."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 하하. 왜?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 처리하는 건 네 역할이잖아."

#: Convo.dgn_5_antidote_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_5_antidote_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Hey, {name.npc_konjurist}-- shouldn't you research an antidote for {name_multiple.rot}?"
msgstr "있잖아, {name.npc_konjurist}-- {name_multiple.rot} 해독제 연구는 안 해야 해?"

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ALKI_ENDS_CONVO
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ALKI_ENDS_CONVO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Alright, well, good chat.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I've some results I need to analyze now. Good luck out there."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 알았어, 뭐, 대화 좋았어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이제 분석해야 할 결과가 좀 있어서. 밖에선 행운을 빌게."

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" No, actually. I've been sent to spy on you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 아니, 사실 널 감시하라고 보내졌어."

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Haha."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" 하하."

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Ha-ha."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" 하-하."

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Nah. I can do my research anywhere.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Plus it's nice to collect fresh samples.\n"
" !notebook"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아냐. 연구는 어디서든 할 수 있어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 게다가 신선한 샘플 모으기도 좋고.\n"
" !notebook"

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Okay. See you next time!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 알겠어. 다음에 봐!"

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How come you follow me on all my Hunts? Is it just to give me Upgrades?"
msgstr "왜 내 사냥마다 따라오는 거야? 그냥 업그레이드 주려고?"

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Haha."
msgstr "하하."

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_ALT"
msgid "Ha ha."
msgstr "하 하."

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Um. Doesn't the travel interrupt your research?"
msgstr "음. 이동하면 연구에 방해되지 않아?"

#: Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_6_following_me_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "I. Think I should leave."
msgstr "나. 가봐야 할 것 같아."

#: Convo.dgn_are_you_cold_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_are_you_cold_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Verily.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm suffering for fashion.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" You wouldn't understand."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 참으로.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 멋을 위해 고생하는 거지.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 넌 이해 못 해."

#: Convo.dgn_are_you_cold_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_are_you_cold_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "...Isn't your chest cold?"
msgstr "...가슴 안 추워?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" You know what they say, my good <#BLUE>{player.species}</>-- location, location, location!!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But nevermind that-- I do believe that shoe of yours is untied!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 다들 그러잖아, 나의 좋은 <#BLUE>{player.species}</>-- 입지, 입지, 입지!!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 그건 됐고-- 네 신발끈이 풀린 것 같은데!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Here, let me hold your bag while you fix it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You wouldn't want to fall over in thisss mud, now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 자, 네가 묶는 동안 내가 가방 들어줄게.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이 진흙탕에서 넘어지고 싶진 않잖아."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !takeitem"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !takeitem"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A_CONT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A_CONT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now, were you also looking to buy a <#RED>Potion</> today?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그럼, 오늘 <#RED>물약</>도 살 생각이야?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Of course, of course!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here you are, my friend.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Now, are you sure about leaving that shoe untied?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 물론이지, 물론!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 여기 받아, 친구.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 그 신발끈, 정말 풀린 채로 둘 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" What! But what if you trip fighting a <#RED>{name.rot}</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 뭐라고! <#RED>{name.rot}</>랑 싸우다가 넘어지면 어떡해?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanksss for your patronage!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이용해줘서 고마워!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_6B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_6B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Fair play.\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Ta!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 인정하지.\n"
" !greet\n"
" 고마워!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Until next time, my friend!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" 다음에 또 보자, 친구!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MID_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MID_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here'sss your bag back, my good <#BLUE>{player.species}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자, 네 가방 돌려줄게, 나의 좋은 <#BLUE>{player.species}</>."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "{name.npc_doc_lastname}? How'd you end up in {name.bandi_swamp}?"
msgstr "{name.npc_doc_lastname}? 어떻게 {name.bandi_swamp}까지 오게 됐어?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Oh? Why, so it is!"
msgstr "오? 그러네, 정말!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Sure, thanks!"
msgstr "좋아, 고마워!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> {konjur_cost} {name.konjur}]</> I'm just here for a Potion.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Refill All Potion Charges)</></i></z>"
msgstr "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> {konjur_cost} {name.konjur}]</> 난 물약만 사러 왔어.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(모든 물약 충전량 보충)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "Eh, why bother."
msgstr "에이, 뭐 하러."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> {konjur_cost} {name.konjur}]</> Oh, yes please.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Refill All Potion Charges)</></i></z>"
msgstr "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> {konjur_cost} {name.konjur}]</> 아, 응. 부탁해.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(모든 물약 충전량 보충)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "No thanks, I'm good for now."
msgstr "괜찮아, 지금은 필요 없어."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_bandiswamp_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5A"
msgid "Fine, okay. Hold my bag."
msgstr "알겠어, 좋아. 내 가방 좀 들어줘."

