msgstr "<i>(뒤적뒤적)</i> 끝났어!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Why, <i>say!</i> You're just in time to try my NEW <#LEGENDARY>Limited Edition</> <#BLUE><i>{name.npc_doc_lastname}-Brand</i></> <#RED>Health Potion</>!\n"
" !clap\n"
" [recipe:limited_potion_refill] Only <#KONJUR>{ripoff_amount} {name.i_konjur}</> more than a regular <#RED>Potion</>! Get it while sssupplies last!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 왜, <i>이런!</i> 내 NEW <#LEGENDARY>한정판</> <#BLUE><i>{name.npc_doc_lastname}-브랜드</i></> <#RED>체력 물약</>을 써 보기에 딱 좋은 타이밍이야!\n"
" !clap\n"
" [recipe:limited_potion_refill] 일반 <#RED>물약</>보다 겨우 <#KONJUR>{ripoff_amount} {name.i_konjur}</>만 더 내면 돼! 재고 있을 때 사!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Tassstes the same, too!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Isn't it incredible?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 맛도 똑같아!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 신기하지?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Yes! Oh, you're getting a real sssteal on this--\n"
" !gesture\n"
" --But I'm happy to bend the rules for a valued cussstomer."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 맞아! 어휴, 이건 진짜 헐값이야--\n"
" !gesture\n"
" --그래도 소중한 단골 손님을 위해 규칙쯤은 굽혀줄 수 있지."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I expected a Hunter to be more adventurousss!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Are you sssure you don't want to try a <#BLUE>Limited Edition</> <#RED>Potion</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 헌터라면 좀 더 모험적일 줄 알았는데!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 정말 <#BLUE>한정판</> <#RED>포션</> 안 써볼 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1D
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Whoa, whoa now!\n"
" !think\n"
" What say I give you this special, <#BLUE>Limited Edition</> <#RED>Potion</> for the price of your usual refill then?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Consider it a loyalty reward for a most valued customer."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 워, 워 잠깐!\n"
" !think\n"
" 그럼 이 특별한 <#BLUE>한정판</> <#RED>포션</>, 평소 리필 가격에 줄까?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 최고의 단골한테 주는 충성 보상이라고 생각해."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
