" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 거래해줘서 고마워!"

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You stick to your guns. I respect that.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Until next time, kid."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 자기 소신 확실하네. 존중해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 다음에 또 보자, 꼬마."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Well now! Who am I to discourage a sssalt of the earth <#BLUE>{player.species}'s</> brand loyalty?!\n"
" !point\n"
" One regular <#RED>Potion</> comin' right up, pal of mine."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이야! 이렇게 성실한 <#BLUE>{player.species}</> 브랜드 충성심을 내가 어찌 말리겠어?!\n"
" !point\n"
" 평소 <#RED>포션</> 하나, 바로 준비해줄게 친구."

#: Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_THANKS_BYE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_bv_sedamenttundra_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_THANKS_BYE"
