" !nervous\n"
" 이해가 안 돼. 할아버지는 어디 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.OPT_NEXT_TIME
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.OPT_NEXT_TIME"
msgid "You got it!"
msgstr "알겠어!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CHAT_ONLY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CHAT_ONLY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" He! He! He!\n"
" I came across something interesting!\n"
" !point\n"
" Let me know if you come across something interesting!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" 헤! 헤! 헤!\n"
" 재미있는 걸 하나 찾았어!\n"
" !point\n"
" 너도 재미있는 거 찾으면 알려 줘!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.OPT_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.OPT_EXIT"
msgid "...Yep."
msgstr "...응."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" He! He! He!\n"
" 'til we meet!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 헤! 헤! 헤!\n"
" 다시 만날 때까지!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> 가자!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_BOMB_GAME
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_BOMB_GAME"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [BOMB_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Dodge a series of flying explosives.\n"
" TIP: When getting knocked down, tap <#RED>Dodge</> just as you hit the ground to <#RED>Quick Rise</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [BOMB_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" 날아오는 폭발물을 연속으로 피하자.\n"
" TIP: 넘어졌을 때 땅에 닿는 순간 <#RED>회피</>를 눌러 <#RED>빠른 기상</>!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> 가자!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DODGE_GAME
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DODGE_GAME"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DODGE_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Run through a field of <#RED>Spike Traps</> without getting hit.\n"
" TIP: You can't be hit at the start of a <#RED>Dodge</>. Keep moving!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DODGE_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" <#RED>가시 함정</> 지대를 맞지 않고 통과해.\n"
" TIP: <#RED>회피</> 시작 순간엔 피격되지 않아. 계속 움직여!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> 가자!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DPS_CHECK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DPS_CHECK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DPS_CHECK]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Deal a lot of <#RED>Damage</> to one target within a time limit.\n"
" TIP: Find an attack pattern that deals the most <#RED>Damage</> possible!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DPS_CHECK]\n"
" !clap\n"
" 제한 시간 안에 한 대상에게 <#RED>피해</>를 최대한 많이 줘.\n"
" TIP: 가장 큰 <#RED>피해</>를 넣는 공격 패턴을 찾아!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> 가자!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HIT_STREAK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HIT_STREAK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [HIT_STREAK]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Get a high <#RED>Hit Streak</> by attacking a pair of alternating dummies.\n"
" TIP: Focus on the timing and choose the right time to switch sides!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [HIT_STREAK]\n"
" !clap\n"
" 번갈아 나타나는 허수아비 둘을 공격해 높은 <#RED>연속 타격</>을 달성해.\n"
" TIP: 타이밍에 집중하고, 편을 바꿀 순간을 잘 골라!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> 가자!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.TALK_MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.TALK_MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Kill as many tiny <#RED>{name_multiple.cabbageroll}</> as possible. Lose points when you get hit.\n"
" TIP: You can't be hit at the start of a <#RED>Dodge</>. Keep moving!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM]\n"
" !clap\n"
" 작은 <#RED>{name_multiple.cabbageroll}</>를 최대한 많이 처치해. 맞으면 점수를 잃어.\n"
" TIP: <#RED>회피</> 시작 순간엔 피격되지 않아. 계속 움직여!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No way!"
msgstr "절대 안 해!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_HEADS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_HEADS"
msgid "Heads."
msgstr "앞면."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_TAILS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_TAILS"
msgid "Tails."
msgstr "뒷면."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.TALK_COIN_FLIP_MAX_HEALTH_OR_DAMAGE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.TALK_COIN_FLIP_MAX_HEALTH_OR_DAMAGE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" He! He! He! Care to flip a coin?\n"
" Call it right, I'll help you out.\n"
" If not, I'll have to help your enemies! He! He! He!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" 헤! 헤! 헤! 동전 던질래?\n"
" 맞히면 내가 널 도와줄게.\n"
" 틀리면 네 적들을 도와줘야겠네! 헤! 헤! 헤!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Ooh! Free gift!"
msgstr "오! 공짜 선물!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "Uh, I'll pass, thanks."
msgstr "어... 난 패스할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_EPIC
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_EPIC"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm!\n"
" We live inside a dream.\n"
" !point\n"
" But who is dreaming?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And who is dreaming the dream <i>they're</> in? He! He! He!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * He extends a hand. In it, a gift gleams."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" 흠!\n"
" 우리는 꿈속에 살아.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그런데 누가 꿈꾸고 있지?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그리고 <i>녀석들이</> 있는 그 꿈은 또 누가 꾸는 걸까? 헤! 헤! 헤!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * 그가 손을 내민다. 그 손 위에서 선물이 반짝인다."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Thanks, I think?"
msgstr "고마워... 맞지?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "Uh, no?"
msgstr "어, 아니?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_LEGENDARY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_LEGENDARY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Craving craves only to crave!\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you want?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" What you want?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * He extends a hand. In it, a gift offered."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 갈망은 갈망하기 위해서만 갈망하지!\n"
" !think\n"
" 원해?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 네가 원하는 걸?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * 그가 손을 내민다. 그 안에 선물이 놓여 있다."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Yes..."
msgstr "응..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No."
msgstr "아니."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Temperance!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I knew a thirsty ghost who carried an infinite potion.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Her throat was swollen, and she could never drink enough.\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you thirst?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 절제!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 끝없는 물약을 들고 다니는 목마른 유령을 알았지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그 유령은 목이 부어 있었고, 아무리 마셔도 갈증이 안 가셨지.\n"
" !think\n"
" 너도 목말라?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Select a {name.concept_relic}...]</> Sure..."
msgstr "<#RED>[Select a {name.concept_relic}...]</> 그래..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.TALK_LOSE_POWER_GAIN_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.TALK_LOSE_POWER_GAIN_HEALTH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" He! He! He! I've got an idea!\n"
" Give me a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> of yours...\n"
" !think\n"
" And I'll give you some <#RED>Health</> of mine! He! He! He!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Choose and lose a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> to gain <#RED>Health</>, depending on its <#RED>Rarity</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 헤! 헤! 헤! 좋은 생각이 났어!\n"
" 네 <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> 하나를 나한테 줘...\n"
" !think\n"
" 그럼 내 <#RED>체력</>을 좀 나눠 줄게! 헤! 헤! 헤!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>희귀도</>에 따라 <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> 하나를 잃고 <#RED>체력</>을 얻어."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Select a {name.concept_relic}...]</> Sure..."
msgstr "<#RED>[Select a {name.concept_relic}...]</> 그래..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_TRANSMUTE_POWER
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_TRANSMUTE_POWER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" He! He! He! Transmutation!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Transmutation! Transmutation! Transmutation!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Lead into gold! What do you say?\n"
" !think\n"
" Choose and lose a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</>. But gain a random <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> of one <#RED>Rarity</> higher."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 헤! 헤! 헤! 변환!\n"
" !clap\n"
" 변환! 변환! 변환!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 납을 금으로! 어때?\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> 하나를 고르고 잃어. 대신 <#RED>희귀도</>가 한 단계 높은 무작위 <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</>를 얻어."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Yeesh. But okay..."
msgstr "으... 그래도 알겠어..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No way!"
msgstr "절대 안 해!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_UPGRADE_RANDOM_POWER
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_UPGRADE_RANDOM_POWER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" He! He! He! I'm feeling generous!\n"
" I'll <#RED>Upgrade A Random {name.concept_relic}</> for free.\n"
" !think\n"
" All it will cost is a slice of your finger! He! He! He!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Accept: Random <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> upgrade. <#RED>Take 250 Damage</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 헤! 헤! 헤! 기분이다!\n"
" 무료로 <#RED>무작위 {name.concept_relic} 하나를 강화</>해 줄게.\n"
" !think\n"
" 대신 손가락을 조금 베어갈게! 헤! 헤! 헤!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 수락: 무작위 <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</1> 강화. <#RED>피해 250 받음</2>."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> 가자!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "사양할게."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.TALK_EVENT_PROTOTYPE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.TALK_EVENT_PROTOTYPE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's prototype an event!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Start?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 이벤트를 프로토타입으로 시험해 보자!\n"
" !clap\n"
" 시작할래?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"And whatever.\" Feh!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'll have you know I maketh my pieces from <i>locally</>-sourced monsters, and this locale is home to some particularly robust <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Why, I had to develop an entirely new forging technique to work their materials--and the result? \n"
" !wink\n"
" Only the most <i>majestically</> powerful gear thou hast ever laid eyes on. Very avant-garde--\"and whatever\"--hm?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"그리고 뭐 그런 거.\" 흥!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 알아 둬, 난 <i>현지</> 조달 몬스터 재료로 작품을 만든다. 그리고 이 지역엔 특히 튼튼한 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>가 살고 있지.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 그 재료를 다루려고 완전히 새로운 단조 기법까지 개발해야 했어. 그래서 결과가 뭐냐고?\n"
" !wink\n"
" 네가 본 것 중 가장 <i>장엄하게</> 강력한 장비지. 아주 아방가르드하지, \"그리고 뭐 그런 거\" 라고?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(*sputter*)</> My <i>\"bangs\"?!</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" First of all, I doth not have <i>\"bangs\"</>, I hath a... a <i>cascade</> of silky locks that crasheth roguishly upon mine chiseled visage.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Second, I was talking about my new works of art. <i>Obviously.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(*콜록*)</> 내 <i>\"앞머리\"?!</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" 첫째, 난 <i>\"앞머리\"</> 같은 거 없어. 난... 내 조각 같은 얼굴 위로 능청스럽게 쏟아지는 <i>비단결 폭포</>를 가졌을 뿐이야.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 둘째, 난 내 새 예술 작품 얘기하던 중이었어. <i>당연히.</>"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Then I guess you'll have to come findeth me again over there."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그럼 거기서 날 다시 찾아와야겠네."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" No."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 안 돼."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>No!</i>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>안 돼!</i>"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" ... Fine.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmmm... Yep, I art <i>definitely</i> looking. This is me, \"looking in the back\". O! What a fine back it is, and...\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" No, we don't have it. Now begone."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" ... 좋아.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 흠... 그래, 나 <i>분명히</i> 찾고 있어. 지금 이게 \"뒤쪽 창고를 보는\" 나야. 오! 참 훌륭한 뒤쪽이군, 그리고...\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" 없어, 우린 그거 안 팔아. 이제 가."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ANNOYING_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ANNOYING_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !angry\n"
" \"Call around\"?! I am the ONLY store--!!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Thou art joking. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> <z 0.7>How I loathe interacting with the clientele.</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !angry\n"
" \"여기저기 전화해 보라\"고?! 가게가 나 하나뿐인데--!!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 농담이지.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> <z 0.7>손님 상대는 정말 질색이야.</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EARLY_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EARLY_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Make sure to tell your Hunter friends about me once thou returnst home."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" 집에 돌아가면 네 헌터 친구들한테 꼭 내 얘기해."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LATE_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LATE_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh. What a relief it is to have that settled. Hurrah.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Thou art free to continue browsing now, little culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 오. 그게 정리돼서 얼마나 속 편한지. 만세.\n"
" !wink\n"
" 이제 계속 구경해도 돼, 꼬마 애송이."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Hm... Same condescending look... Oh! Your stock's all different and whatever!"
msgstr "흠... 똑같이 잘난 척하는 표정... 아! 재고가 다 다르고 뭐 그런 거구나!"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ALT"
msgid "Hey, you're right! Your stock's totally different and whatever!"
msgstr "오, 맞네! 재고가 완전 다르고 뭐 그런 거네!"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Um... did you trim your own bangs?"
msgstr "음... 네가 직접 앞머리 자른 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Er, but I wanted something you had at the old market."
msgstr "어, 근데 예전 시장에서 팔던 게 필요했는데."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Can't you look in the back to see if you have it?"
msgstr "뒤쪽 창고 좀 뒤져서 있는지 봐주면 안 돼?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "Pleeeeease?"
msgstr "제에에발?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5"
msgid "C'moonnn..."
msgstr "제바알..."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ANNOYING_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ANNOYING_END"
msgid "Could you call around to other stores?"
msgstr "다른 가게들에 전화 좀 돌려줄래?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_END"
msgid "Okay. Good to know."
msgstr "알겠어. 참고할게."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LATE_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LATE_END"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr "됐어."

#: Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ugh! Do I look like a bedraggled bard, hat upturnt, kicked-in concertina slung o'er my shoulder? \n"
" player:\n"
" I'm not sure what any of that meant, but the vibe is \"no\". \n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I. Do. Not. Take. <i>Requests.</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" I am a visionary! A luminary! A... A biggeth deal!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And thou art lucky to hath the <i>opportunity</> to even glance at my original works.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Fortunately for you I am also merciful, so I shall allow you to purchase said works, despite the insultations."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 윽! 내가 모자 뒤집어쓰고 찌그러진 콘서티나를 어깨에 멘 초라한 음유시인으로 보여?\n"
" player:\n"
" 무슨 말인진 잘 모르겠지만, 분위기는 \"안 돼\"네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 난. <i>주문 제작</>. 안. 받아.\n"
" !angry\n"
" 난 선구자다! 거성이다! 아... 아주 대단한 인물이라고!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 네가 내 오리지널 작품을 흘끗이라도 볼 <i>기회</>를 얻은 것만으로도 운 좋은 거야.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 다행히 난 자비롭기도 해서, 이런 무례를 당하고도 그 작품들을 너한테 팔아 주지."

#: Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Hey, 'Phonsey, can I put in orders for specific items?"
msgstr "저기, 폰시. 혹시 내가 원하는 물건을 따로 주문할 수도 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Sssplendid, sssplendid!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then without further ado, allow me to introduce you to my patented {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" One sip with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>'s guaranteed to <#RED>Heal</> your woundsss, clear your skin, and leave your breath minty fresh for that <i>ssspecial someone</i> back home.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] This veritable panacea <#RED>Health {name.potion}</> can be <i>yours</i> for only a modessst sum of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 아주 훌륭해, 훌륭해!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그럼 지체 없이, 내 특허 {name.npc_doc_lastname}-브랜드 <#RED>체력 {name.potion}</>을 소개하지!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 한 모금이면 <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>의 효능으로 상처를 <#RED>치유</>하고, 피부를 맑게 하고, 고향의 <i>특별한 저 녀석</i>을 위해 입김까지 민트처럼 상쾌하게 만들어 줘.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] 이 진정한 만병통치 <#RED>체력 {name.potion}</>, 단돈 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>이면 <i>네 것</i>이야!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Why, forgive my manners!\n"
" !clap\n"
" The name's <#BLUE>{name.npc_potionmaker_dungeon}</>, illussstrious post-apocalypse entrepreneur, ssscholar of medicine, and beloved young heir to the {name.npc_doc_lastname} family fortune!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] At your mid-hunt convenience."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아, 내 예의가 없었네!\n"
" !clap\n"
" 내 이름은 <#BLUE>{name.npc_potionmaker_dungeon}</>. 저명한 포스트 아포칼립스 사업가이자 의학 연구자, 그리고 {name.npc_doc_lastname} 가문의 사랑받는 젊은 후계자지!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] 사냥 도중 편할 때 들러."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Now hold on just a sssecond there!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'll let you in on a little secret. These woods are <i>danger</i>-ous.\n"
" !think\n"
" I'd hate to see fine folks like yourself in a pinch... so what sssay you buy one of these <#RED>Potions</> for the road, hm?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 자, 잠깐만!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 작은 비밀 하나 알려 줄게. 이 숲은 <i>위험</i>해.\n"
" !think\n"
" 너 같은 괜찮은 사람이 곤란해지는 건 보고 싶지 않거든... 그러니 가는 길에 <#RED>물약</> 하나 사 가는 게 어때, 응?"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha-ha! You had me on the ropes, but I knew from the start you were a smart <#BLUE>{player.species}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Enjoy your {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}</>, and may we deal again soon!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하하! 날 몰아붙였네, 하지만 처음부터 네가 똑똑한 <#BLUE>{player.species}</>인 건 알고 있었어!\n"
" !agree\n"
" {name.npc_doc_lastname}-브랜드 <#RED>체력 {name.potion}</> 잘 쓰고, 곧 또 거래하자!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" A tough customer. I <i>do</i> love a challenge.\n"
" !greet\n"
" Well, fair play, my friend. I'll get you next time!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 까다로운 손님이네. 난 <i>정말</i> 도전이 좋아.\n"
" !greet\n"
" 좋아, 이번엔 네가 이겼다 친구. 다음엔 내가 가져간다!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>--Now,</i> as I was sssaying last time, you seem like one savvy <#BLUE>{player.species}</> who could--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>Hold your horses!</i> Did you just say you're ssstill broke?\n"
" !angry\n"
" How'sss that even possible?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Err, I mean, no hard feelings. Why don't you go give some monsters the what-for, then come back in a flash with some cold hard (actually gooey) <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" My gen-u-ine <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</> will be waiting!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>--이제</i> 지난번에 하던 말 마저 하자면, 넌 꽤 영리한 <#BLUE>{player.species}</>라서--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>잠깐만!</i> 아직도 빈털터리라고 했어?\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그게 대체 어떻게 가능해?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 어, 그러니까 기분 나쁘게 듣진 말고. 몬스터 좀 혼내 주고, 차갑고 단단한(사실은 끈적한) <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> 챙겨서 금방 돌아와!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 내 진-짜 <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</>는 여기서 기다리고 있을 테니까!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ta-ta!\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>(Good grief.)</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" 잘 가!\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>(세상에나.)</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" --Now, as I was sssaying last time, you seem like a savvy <#BLUE>{player.species}</> who could--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" WAIT! You already have a <#RED>{name.potion}</>?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Bouncing <#RED>{name_multiple.cabbageroll}</> on a pogo stick, this just won't do!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I can't sell you my <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</> if you have nothing to carry them in."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" --지난번에도 말했듯, 넌 영리한 <#BLUE>{player.species}</>라서--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 잠깐! 이미 <#RED>{name.potion}</>가 있잖아?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.cabbageroll}</>를 폴짝봉에 튕기든 말든, 이건 안 되겠어!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 담을 게 없으면 내 <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</>를 팔 수가 없어."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1_MISSING_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1_MISSING_HEALTH"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" Tell you what, why don't you take a moment to empty that flask of yours out with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>?\n"
" !clap\n"
" Then I can top you up with some bonafide {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health Potion</> instead!"
msgstr "!dubious\n"
" 네 플라스크를 <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>로 잠깐 비우고 오는 게 어때?\n"
" !clap\n"
" 그러면 내가 진짜 {name.npc_doc_lastname} 브랜드 <#RED>체력 물약</>으로 채워줄게!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2A"
msgid "Most certainly!"
msgstr "물론이지!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2B"
msgid "Don't think <i>too</i> long now! It's bad for your health!"
msgstr "지금 <i>너무</i> 오래 고민하진 마! 건강에 안 좋아!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" I'm counting on it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" 기대하고 있을게!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "Yeah! And I have funds this time."
msgstr "응! 이번엔 돈도 있어."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "Why should I buy your {name_multiple.potion}? I don't even know you."
msgstr "내가 왜 네 {name_multiple.potion}을 사야 해? 너 누군지도 모르는데."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "I think I'll pass, thanks."
msgstr "이번엔 패스할게."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3A"
msgid "Fine, you talked me into it."
msgstr "좋아, 네 말에 넘어갔어."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3B"
msgid "No, I'm really okay."
msgstr "아니, 난 진짜 괜찮아."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "Err, yeah, but I'm still a bit low on {name.i_konjur}."
msgstr "어, 맞아. 근데 {name.i_konjur}가 아직 좀 부족해."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "Okay! I'll go bash some {name_multiple.rot}!"
msgstr "좋아! {name_multiple.rot} 좀 때려잡고 올게!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "Eh, we'll see how I do."
msgstr "음, 해보고 생각할게."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_1"
msgid "Err, yeah, but I have a {name.potion} already."
msgstr "어, 맞아. 근데 {name.potion}은 이미 있어."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2A"
msgid "Wowee! Thanks!\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Potion already full)</></i></z>"
msgstr "우와! 고마워!\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(물약이 이미 가득 참)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2B"
msgid "Lemme think it over.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Potion already full)</></i></z>"
msgstr "좀 생각해볼게.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(물약이 이미 가득 참)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH"
msgid "Err, sorry. Catch ya next time?\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Potion already full)</></i></z>"
msgstr "어, 미안. 다음에 보자?\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(물약이 이미 가득 참)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"Another\"--?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I don't know if you hath noticed, but there is no \"another\" like <i>me.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Mayhaps if thou <i>describe</> this hobbyist... ? \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Even though I hardly hath time to pay heed to mere <i>window-shoppers</> passing through."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"또 다른\"--?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 눈치챘는지 모르겠지만, <i>나</> 같은 \"또 다른\" 존재는 없어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 그 취미장이를 <i>묘사</>라도 해보지 그래...?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 지나가는 <i>구경꾼</>들한테 신경 쓸 시간도 거의 없지만."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Didst thou say--\n"
" !cough\n"
" --hair in a \"bun\"? UGH. Who would gaze upon such an outdated hair arrangement? Not I. Surely.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Now, if you'll excuse me. I have cultures to revolutionize."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 네가 뭐라고--\n"
" !cough\n"
" --\"번\" 머리라고? 으웩. 그런 구닥다리 헤어스타일을 누가 보겠어? 난 아니지. 절대.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그럼 실례. 난 문화를 혁신하러 가야 해서."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Oh, I always try, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" 아, 난 언제나 노력하지, 컬버."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm looking for my missing crew--have you seen another Armoursmith out here?"
msgstr "실종된 우리 동료를 찾고 있어. 여기서 다른 방어구 장인을 본 적 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Well... she's a {name.species_ogre} with red hair in a bun, goes by {name.npc_armorsmith}--"
msgstr "음... 저 녀석는 {name.species_ogre}고, 빨간 머리를 번으로 묶었고, {name.npc_armorsmith}라고 불러--"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Forget it. I don't think you could've been less helpful if you'd tried."
msgstr "됐어. 일부러 해도 이보다 더 도움 안 되긴 힘들겠다."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Missing crew? I hope they're Hunters like you, or they're not gonna last long out here.\n"
" !think\n"
" Come to think of it, I did spot some footprints a little while ago.\n"
" !point\n"
" They were headed deeper into the forest."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 실종된 동료? 너 같은 헌터들이길 바랄게. 아니면 여기서 오래 못 버텨.\n"
" !think\n"
" 그러고 보니, 아까 발자국 몇 개 보긴 했어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 숲 더 깊은 쪽으로 향하던데."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I'd be quick about finding them if I were you...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" They're gonna run right into the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> if they keep heading that way."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 나라면 빨리 찾겠어...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 계속 그쪽으로 가면 <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>하고 바로 마주칠 거거든."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm looking for my missing crew-- have you seen anyone else out here?"
msgstr "실종된 우리 동료를 찾고 있어. 여기서 다른 사람 본 적 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Thanks!"
msgstr "고마워!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hath we not been over this, my little culver? Unless they art a patron...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I. Doth. Not. Care."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 이 얘기 이미 했잖아, 꼬마 컬버? 손님이 아니라면...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 난. 전혀. 관심. 없어."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" No. It wasn't."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" 아니. 아니었어."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Mm. I recall a gentlecat of the sort padding through <i>le Chateau d'Alphonse</> most recent...\n"
" !wink\n"
" Try as I might, the brute could not be coerced onto my leash. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" You should find him elsewhere, mayhaps closeby, mayhaps not. \n"
" !greet\n"
" See you soon, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 음. 비슷한 신사 고양이 하나가 최근 <i>le Chateau d'Alphonse</>를 어슬렁거리는 건 봤어...\n"
" !wink\n"
" 아무리 해도 그 짐승을 내 목줄에 묶어둘 순 없더군.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 다른 데서 찾아봐. 가까울 수도, 아닐 수도 있고.\n"
" !greet\n"
" 또 보자, 컬버."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm still looking for a member of my crew. Have you seen another Blacksmith out here?"
msgstr "난 아직도 우리 동료 한 명을 찾고 있어. 여기서 다른 대장장이를 본 적 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "<i>(sigh)</> It was worth a try."
msgstr "<i>(한숨)</> 그래도 해볼 가치는 있었지."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "He's a {name.species_canine}, distinctive shoulder tattoo, steel collar..."
msgstr "그는 {name.species_canine}고, 어깨에 눈에 띄는 문신이 있고, 강철 목걸이를 하고 있어..."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sorry, I just got here a little while ago. Haven't seen anyone.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Did you find your other friend... in one piece?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 미안, 나도 여기 온 지 얼마 안 돼서. 아무도 못 봤어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 다른 친구는... 무사히 찾았어?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well that's a load off my mind.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I hate running into corpses."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그럼 마음이 좀 놓이네.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 시체 마주치는 건 질색이거든."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm still looking for a member of my crew. Have you seen them?"
msgstr "난 아직도 우리 동료 한 명을 찾고 있어. 본 적 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "I did. She's safe at our camp."
msgstr "응. 우리 캠프에서 무사해."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Ta!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 고마워!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Thank you!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Well, I'm afraid I haven't ssseen or heard anything.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Good luck on your search my friend!\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Ta!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 고마워!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 음, 유감이지만 난 아무것도 못 봤고 못 들었어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 찾는 일 잘 풀리길 바라, 친구!\n"
" !greet\n"
" 땡큐!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" That's your choice, no harm no foul!\n"
" !point\n"
" Good luck on your sssearch, kid!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 네 선택이지, 서로 나쁠 건 없어!\n"
" !point\n"
" 찾는 일 잘 풀려라, 꼬마야!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ARMOURSMITH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ARMOURSMITH"
msgid "Actually, have you seen our {name.job_armorsmith}? She's lost somewhere in these woods!"
msgstr "아, 혹시 우리 {name.job_armorsmith} 봤어? 이 숲 어딘가에서 길을 잃었어!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_BLACKSMITH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_BLACKSMITH"
msgid "Actually, have you seen our {name.job_blacksmith}? He's lost somewhere in these woods!"
msgstr "아, 혹시 우리 {name.job_blacksmith} 봤어? 이 숲 어딘가에서 길을 잃었어!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_TWOFRIENDS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_TWOFRIENDS"
msgid "Hey-- Have you seen our {name.job_blacksmith} and {name.job_armorsmith}? They're lost in these woods!"
msgstr "저기, 우리 {name.job_blacksmith}랑 {name.job_armorsmith} 봤어? 이 숲에서 길을 잃었어!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Hm. Well, see you around, {name.npc_doc_firstname}."
msgstr "흠. 그럼 또 보자, {name.npc_doc_firstname}."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> 2 {name.konjur}]</> Uh, okay... Here you go."
msgstr "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> 2 {name.konjur}]</> 어, 알겠어... 여기."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Sigh. Nevermind."
msgstr "하아. 됐어."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_CAN_BUY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_CAN_BUY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] Only a handful of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> a pop!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] 개당 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> 몇 개밖에 안 해!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_RESOURCES
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_RESOURCES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But you don't have enough <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>가 부족하네."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_SPACE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_SPACE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But your flask's still full. I'm afraid this is a bring-your-own container sort of operation.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I care deeply about the environment, you know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 하지만 네 플라스크가 아직 가득 차 있어. 여긴 개인 용기 지참 방식이라서.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 나, 환경 문제엔 진심이거든."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" My word! How terrible! Truly awful!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [recipe:hoggins_tip_recipe] For a sssmall fee, I'd be happy to tell you everything I know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이런! 너무 끔찍하네! 정말 최악이야!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [recipe:hoggins_tip_recipe] 아주 조그만 수수료만 내면, 내가 아는 건 전부 말해줄게."

#: Convo.dgn_shop_powerupgrade.HUB0.shop.giver.STATE_0.OPT_UPGRADE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_shop_powerupgrade.HUB0.shop.giver.STATE_0.OPT_UPGRADE"
msgid "<#RED>[Upgrade {name.concept_relic}]</> Upgrade me!"
msgstr "<#RED>[{name.concept_relic} 강화]</> 강화해줘!"

#: Convo.dgn_shop_powerupgrade.HUB0.shop.giver.STATE_0.TT_NO_POWERS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_shop_powerupgrade.HUB0.shop.giver.STATE_0.TT_NO_POWERS"
msgid "You have no upgradable {name_multiple.concept_relic}"
msgstr "강화할 {name_multiple.concept_relic}이 없어"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" <z 0.8>Chwee chwee!</z>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Coooo, quaw.</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" <z 0.8>짹 짹!</z>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>쿠우, 콰악.</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>Cooooooo.</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>쿠우우우.</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Aw c'mon, you don't need to act THAT surprised I beat the challenge! So, what do I get?"
msgstr "에이, 내가 도전 깼다고 그렇게까지 놀랄 필요는 없잖아! 그래서 뭐 주는데?"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "No way! I get what's in your little birdie treasure chest?"
msgstr "설마! 네 작은 새 보물상자 안에 있는 걸 내가 받는다고?"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_first_time_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "Thanks, {name.shop_magpie}! I can't wait to do the next challenge!"
msgstr "고마워, {name.shop_magpie}! 다음 도전이 벌써 기대돼!"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.8>Quee quaw chwee kwee!</z>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <z 0.8>Quawk, quawk... Keh. Kweh.</z>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Quee-oooo!</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.8>퀴 콰 짹 크위!</z>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <z 0.8>콱, 콱... 케. 퀘.</z>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>퀴-오오!</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>Quaw quaw queep!</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>콰 콰 큅!</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I beat another one of your challenges, {name.shop_magpie}!"
msgstr "네 도전 하나 더 깼어, {name.shop_magpie}!"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "Haha. Thanks for opening the chest, bud.\n"
"See ya next time!"
msgstr "하하. 상자 열어줘서 고마워, 친구.\n"
"다음에 보자!"

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Good. Than canst thou report to me if she sayeth anything about mine...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...about mine <z 0.7>hair thinnery?</>\n"
" player:\n"
" \"Hair...thinnery\"? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Keepeth it down! I hath a reputation to uphold. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> told me that upon a recent landing, she espied the top of my head...\n"
" !angry\n"
" And that false feathered fiend said my famously lushious locks were... <z 0.7>thinning!</> Revealing more of my.... <z 0.7>bare pate!</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" This is of course libelous slander and I shall not have it spreading about willy and, god forbid, nilly."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 좋아. 그럼 걔가 내...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...내 <z 0.7>숱이 줄었다</>는 얘길 하는지 보고해줄 수 있겠나?\n"
" player:\n"
" \"숱이... 줄었다고\"?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 조용히 해! 난 지켜야 할 명성이 있어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</>가 얼마 전 착륙했을 때 내 정수리를 봤다고 하더군...\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그런데 그 가짜 깃털 악당이, 내 그 유명한 풍성한 머리칼이... <z 0.7>가늘어지고</> 있다더군! 그래서 내.... <z 0.7>휑한 정수리!</>가 더 보인다고!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이건 명백한 악의적 중상이야. 그런 헛소문이 여기저기 퍼지게 둘 순 없어."

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ch-check <i>what?</> Bwe-heu-heu! I should check YOU, for...for...\n"
" ...\n"
" Begone! <z 0.7>But please do report back should <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> speak such things to you! I beseech thee!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 뭘, 뭘 <i>확인</>하라고? 브헤우헤우! 너나 확인해 봐야겠네, 그... 그...\n"
" ...\n"
" 가 봐! <z 0.7>하지만 <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</>가 네게 그런 말을 하면 꼭 돌아와서 알려줘! 제발!</>"

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END"
msgid "Y'know, I'd better shop and back on the Hunt."
msgstr "음, 장 좀 보고 다시 사냥하러 가야겠어."

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" 즐겨, 컬버."

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Understand what she's saying? Or understand her soul? <z0.7>(It's a 'yes' to both.)</>"
msgstr "말을 알아듣는 거? 아니면 영혼까지 이해하는 거? <z0.7>(둘 다 '응'이야.)</>"

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Of course! Wait--is this a chance for <i>me</> to be snide toward <i>you??</>"
msgstr "당연하지! 잠깐--이거 <i>내가</> <i>너한테</> 비꼴 기회야??"

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1C"
msgid "Am I not supposed to? Does that make me...the BIRDMASTER? FLOCK TO ME, MY FEATHERED FRIENDS!"
msgstr "원래 그러면 안 되는 거였어? 그럼 내가... 버드마스터인 건가? 모여라, 내 깃털 친구들아!"

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "I could check for you, {name.npc_market_merchant}..."
msgstr "내가 확인해줄 수도 있어, {name.npc_market_merchant}..."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Woe, woe, and more woe! 'Tis a most tragic tale.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" She was once a beautiful <#BLUE>{name.species_mer}</> maiden, 'til one day she was cursed by the prick of a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-poisoned thorn."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 슬픔이로다, 또 슬픔이로다! 참으로 비극적인 이야기야.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 저 녀석는 한때 아름다운 <#BLUE>{name.species_mer}</> 아가씨였지. 어느 날 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 독이 묻은 가시에 찔려 저주받기 전까진."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>Bwe-heu-heu!</i> You're so gullible!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!laugh\n"
"<i>비히히!</i> 진짜, 잘도 속아 넘어가네!"

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Bwe-heu-heu, indeed, I didst cut that tale of whole cloth."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 브헤우헤우, 맞아. 그 이야긴 내가 완전히 지어낸 거야."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" I hath no clue.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But I'm thankful nonetheless. She is the most stalwart of squires a <#BLUE>{name.species_ogre}</> could ask for. And a shrewd businessbird, in truth."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" 나도 몰라.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그래도 난 고마워. <#BLUE>{name.species_ogre}</>에게 저 녀석만큼 든든한 수행원은 없거든. 게다가 진짜 장사 수완도 뛰어나고."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EXIT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" All's well that ends well. <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> taught me that expression.\n"
" !wink\n"
" 'Til next time, little culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 끝이 좋으면 다 좋은 법이지. 그 말은 <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</>가 알려줬어.\n"
" !wink\n"
" 다음에 보자, 꼬마 컬버."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "So... what <i>is</i> {name.shop_magpie} exactly?"
msgstr "그래서... <i>대체 뭐야</i> {name.shop_magpie}은?"

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "I knew it! She just had that princess-turned-talking-bird vibe about her."
msgstr "내가 그럴 줄 알았어! 딱 공주였다가 말하는 새가 된 느낌이었거든."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Wait--{name.konjur} can do that?"
msgstr "잠깐--{name.konjur}가 그런 것도 할 수 있어?"

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "Pfft. Yeah right. I may be pretty, but I'm also brain-pretty."
msgstr "풉. 그래, 그렇겠지. 나 예쁘기만 한 게 아니라 똑똑하기도 해."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "If that's right, why didn't she become a {name.rot}?"
msgstr "그게 맞다면, 왜 걘 {name.rot}이 안 된 거야?"

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_EXIT"
msgid "Oops, sorry, I've actually gotta run."
msgstr "앗, 미안. 나 진짜 가봐야 해."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REGULAR_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REGULAR_EXIT"
msgid "Well. Good for you guys."
msgstr "음. 너희한텐 잘됐네."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> was just normal wild magpie when <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> <i>did</i> turn her into, well, an abnormal wild magpie with a shoppe."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</>는 원래 평범한 야생 까치였는데, <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>가 <i>진짜로</i> 저 녀석를, 뭐랄까, 가게를 가진 비범한 야생 까치로 만들어 버렸지."

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BEATEN
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BEATEN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hey, we're up against some pretty major forces and learning as we go.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" If it was easy, someone would have already done it, y'know?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 있잖아, 우리 지금 꽤 거대한 세력들이랑 맞붙으면서 하나씩 배워 가는 중이야.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 쉬운 일이었으면 벌써 누가 해냈겠지, 안 그래?"

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REVVED
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REVVED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ... You can be a little intense sometimes, Hunter. You know that?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" But that's probably why you're so good at what you do. I know you'll get her next time!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ... 너 가끔 너무 과열될 때가 있어, 헌터. 알고 있지?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 근데 아마 그래서 네가 그만큼 잘하는 거야. 다음엔 분명 걔를 잡을 수 있어!"

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BEATEN
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BEATEN"
msgid "Ugh. <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> really whupped my behind..."
msgstr "윽. <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>한테 진짜 호되게 당했어..."

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REVVED
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REVVED"
msgid "When I'm done with <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>, they'll <i>beg</> to be my toothpick."
msgstr "내가 <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> 처리하고 나면, 걔가 <i>애원할</> 거야. 내 이쑤시개가 되게 해달라고."

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Uh yeah, and <i>by a <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</>!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Bigger <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> tend to hang out around <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>, y'know. That must mean you're getting close to the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 어, 맞아. 게다가 <i><#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</>한테</> 당한 거잖아!\n"
" !think\n"
" 더 큰 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>들은 보통 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> 근처에 몰려 있어, 알지. 그건 네가 <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>에 가까워지고 있다는 뜻이야!"

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'm sure <#RED>{name.megatreemon}'s</> just around the corner."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 난 <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>가 바로 코앞에 있다고 확신해."

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I just got my butt kicked."
msgstr "방금 완전 털렸어."

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "That's... reassuring?"
msgstr "그거... 위로가 되네?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LOCAL
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LOCAL"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Really?! Was it on a dare? <#BLUE>{name.bandi_swamp}</>'s odor will curl the stiffest of nose hairs.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Regardless, plug your nose and stay on your toes, Hunter. The smell isn't the only nasty thing lingering in this swamp."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 진짜?! 내기라도 했어? <#BLUE>{name.bandi_swamp}</> 냄새는 코털도 꼬부라지게 해.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 아무튼 코 막고 정신 바짝 차려, 헌터. 이 늪에 남아 있는 끔찍한 건 냄새만이 아니야."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TOURIST
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TOURIST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Welcome. Though it was never exactly a tourist destination--and the <#KONJUR>Eruption</> <i>certainly</> didn't improve things.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Plug your nose and stay on your toes, Hunter. The smell isn't the only nasty thing lingering in this swamp."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 환영해. 원래도 관광지는 아니었지만--<#KONJUR>대폭발</>은 <i>확실히</> 상황을 더 좋게 만들진 않았지.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 코 막고 정신 바짝 차려, 헌터. 이 늪에 남아 있는 끔찍한 건 냄새만이 아니야."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LOCAL
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LOCAL"
msgid "Oh, my 'nobe' has been here before, but before the Eruption."
msgstr "아, 내 '코'는 여기 와 본 적 있어. 근데 대폭발 전이었지."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TOURIST
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TOURIST"
msgid "Nope. It smells like {name.npc_dojo_master}'s socks but full of expired shrimp."
msgstr "아니. {name.npc_dojo_master} 양말에 상한 새우를 한가득 넣어 둔 냄새야."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_ABANDONED
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_ABANDONED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Exactly. It's why I can't shake this nagging feeling...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just keep your eyes peeled for anything unusual."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 맞아. 그래서 이 찜찜한 느낌이 안 가셔...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그냥 이상한 게 있으면 뭐든 눈 크게 뜨고 봐."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_EMPTY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_EMPTY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" M-maybe he escaped? Took refuge somewhere down here?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I don't know, Hunter. Just watch out for anything unusual."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 어-어쩌면 탈출했을지도? 여기 아래 어딘가에 숨어 있을지도 모르고?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 나도 모르겠어, 헌터. 이상한 거 있으면 잘 살펴봐."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2_OKGO
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2_OKGO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" !point\n"
" Touché.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Be careful out there, Hunter. I'll be right behind you.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <z 0.7>We're coming, <#BLUE>Grandpa</>. Hold on. We're coming.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" !point\n"
" 한마디 하네.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 조심해, 헌터. 바로 뒤따라갈게.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <z 0.7>지금 가고 있어, <#BLUE>할아버지</>. 조금만 버텨. 지금 가.</>"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_ABANDONED
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_ABANDONED"
msgid "Abandoning prime real estate like this? Madness!"
msgstr "이런 알짜 땅을 버려 두다니? 미친 짓이네!"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_EMPTY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_EMPTY"
msgid "So... it's empty? Then your Grandpa's in here... alone?"
msgstr "그럼... 비어 있다고? 그럼 네 할아버지가 여기... 혼자 있다는 거야?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2_OKGO
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2_OKGO"
msgid "More unusual than usual, you mean?"
msgstr "평소보다 더 이상한 걸 말하는 거지?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> We can fix the past, but only by fighting for the future. <i><z 0.7>(Flicks toothpick in a cool way.)</></>\n"
" !point\n"
" <z 0.7>Oops, dropped my toothpick.</> Anyway, stay on your toes, Hunter. Seems the city's old <#RED>Security Systems</> are still online after all this time.\n"
" !think\n"
" Best to avoid them... unless you can figure out a way to use them against the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 과거는 되돌릴 수 없어도, 미래를 위해 싸우면 바로잡을 수는 있어. <i><z 0.7>(멋지게 이쑤시개를 튕긴다.)</></>\n"
" !point\n"
" <z 0.7>앗, 이쑤시개 떨어뜨렸네.</> 아무튼 정신 바짝 차려, 헌터. 도시의 오래된 <#RED>보안 시스템</>이 아직도 가동 중인 것 같아.\n"
" !think\n"
" 가능하면 피하는 게 좋아... 아니면 그걸 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 상대로 역이용할 방법을 찾든가."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" We'll get our home back, Hunter. One way or another."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 우리 집, 반드시 되찾자 헌터. 무슨 수를 써서라도."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GRANDPA"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I... I don't know. What he said in the <#RED>Diary Pages</> we recovered... \n"
" !gesture\n"
" There <i>must</> be an explanation for it. Something... <i>(Sigh)</>\n"
" !point\n"
" Until then, stay on your toes. Seems the city's old <#RED>Security Systems</> are still online after all this time.\n"
" !think\n"
" Best to avoid them... unless you can figure out a way to use them against the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 나... 나도 모르겠어. 우리가 회수한 <#RED>일기 페이지</>에 적힌 말을 보면... \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 분명 거기엔 <i>반드시</> 설명이 있을 거야. 뭔가... <i>(한숨)</>\n"
" !point\n"
" 그때까진 정신 바짝 차려. 도시의 오래된 <#RED>보안 시스템</>이 아직도 가동 중인 것 같아.\n"
" !think\n"
" 가능하면 피하는 게 좋아... 아니면 그걸 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 상대로 써먹을 방법을 찾든가."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Hard to imagine this was home, once..."
msgstr "여기가 한때 집이었다니... 상상이 안 된다."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Security systems. Got it."
msgstr "보안 시스템, 알겠어."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GRANDPA"
msgid "When we find your Grandpa, what are you going to say?"
msgstr "네 할아버지 찾으면, 뭐라고 말할 거야?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_WIND
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_WIND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh, did I forget to mention?\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>{name.owlitzer_forest}'s</> full of <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> with <#RED>Wind</> abilities.\n"
" !point\n"
" If you've got <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} Class</> gear it won't bother you much, but anything lighter and you might find it hard to keep your footing."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, 내가 말 안 했나?\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>{name.owlitzer_forest}</>에는 <#RED>바람</> 능력을 가진 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>가 가득해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 장비가 <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} 무게</>가면 크게 신경 안 쓰일 텐데, 그보다 가벼우면 중심 잡기 힘들 거야."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" Good luck out there, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" 행운 빌어, 헌터."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_WIND
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_WIND"
msgid "Uh, what was that about wind?"
msgstr "어, 바람 얘기 뭐였지?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.CLOTHED
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.CLOTHED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, yes. It was my G-Grandpa's. <i>Is</> his, I g-guess. I wonder if he'll w-want it back...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> here are a-a-adapted to the cold, so th-th-they'll use it against you!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 맞아. 내... 증조할아버지 거였어. <i>아마</> 아직 그분 거겠지. 도-돌려달라고 하실까...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 여기 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>는 추위에 마-맞춰 적응해서, 너한테 그걸 이-이용할 거야!"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_QUICK
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_QUICK"
msgid "You bet. Now let's go save your still-alive Grandpa!"
msgstr "당연하지. 자, 아직 살아 계신 네 할아버지 구하러 가자!"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" The t-t-temperature's so l-low that it won't take m-much to <#RED>freeze</> you solid!\n"
" I-I'm certain my Grandpa's being held c-captive here, so keep moving--we're all counting on y-y-you!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 기-기온이 너-너무 낮아서, 조금만 방심해도 네가 통째로 <#RED>얼어붙</>을 거야!\n"
" 내, 내 할아버지가 여기 갇혀 있는 게 확실해. 그러니까 계속 움직여--우리가 다 너-너만 믿고 있어!"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.NUDE
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.NUDE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Yeah... m-maybe you should have worn more a-armour. The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> will be ready for the c-c-cold... and might use it against you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그래... 아-아마 방어구를 더 입었어야 했을지도. <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>는 추-추-추위에 대비돼 있어서... 그걸 네게 이용할 수도 있어."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_SCARF
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_SCARF"
msgid "Good thing you've got that cozy scarf, huh?"
msgstr "따뜻한 목도리 있어서 다행이지, 그치?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DOIT
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DOIT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Alright. Let's go. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" But be careful, Hunter--this is <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> Lab, his home turf. Who knows what's waiting for us..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 좋아. 가자. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" 하지만 조심해, 헌터--여긴 <#BLUE>할아버지의</> 연구실이야, 완전 홈그라운드라고. 뭐가 우리를 기다릴지 몰라..."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I am, but only because I have the best team, lead by the best Hunter I've ever known. \n"
" player:\n"
" Me? Lead who? I've been following <i>you</> this whole time, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Then it's a miracle we haven't been going in circles! \n"
" !point\n"
" Speaking of miracles: you came to us in an ugly brown cloak--\n"
" player:\n"
" It's <i>minimalist!</> Its understatement <i>is</> the statement. And also: you're stalling.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Maybe. <i>(sigh)</> Definitely. Alright. Let's go. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" But be careful--this is <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> home turf. Who knows what's waiting for us..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 준비됐지. 내가 아는 최고의 헌터가 이끄는 최고의 팀이 있으니까. \n"
" player:\n"
" 내가? 누굴 이끌어? 난 지금까지 계속 <i>너</>만 따라왔어, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그럼 우리가 빙빙 안 돌고 온 게 기적이네! \n"
" !point\n"
" 기적 얘기 나온 김에: 넌 처음에 못생긴 갈색 망토 입고 왔잖아--\n"
" player:\n"
" 그건 <i>미니멀리즘</>이야! 절제가 <i>곧</> 메시지라고. 그리고 너 지금 시간 끄는 중이야.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 아마도. <i>(한숨)</> 맞아, 확실히. 좋아. 가자. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" 근데 조심해--여긴 <#BLUE>할아버지의</> 홈그라운드야. 뭐가 우릴 기다릴지 몰라..."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DOIT
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DOIT"
msgid "Who are we to keep the old fox waiting?"
msgstr "우리가 뭐라고 저 늙은 여우를 기다리게 하겠어?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY"
msgid "That's the plan. Are you ready to face him?"
msgstr "그게 계획이지. 그를 마주할 준비됐어?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARMUSIC
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARMUSIC"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Strange... Maybe a guitar got stuck in some talented vines? \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway, as I was saying--I couldn't spot a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>, but I did see a big bug carcass. It could be that <i>was</> the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> and \"natural causes\" have done your job for you.\n"
" !point\n"
" Whatever the case, we should check it out. There could be a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> ripe for the picking."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 이상하네... 재능 있는 덩굴에 기타가 걸리기라도 했나? \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼 하던 말인데--<#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>는 못 봤지만, 큰 벌레 사체는 봤어. 그게 <i>바로</> <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>였을 수도 있고, '자연사'가 네 일을 대신해 줬을 수도 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 어쨌든 확인해 보자. 수확하기 딱 좋은 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>가 있을지도 몰라."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARNOTHING
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARNOTHING"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Yes, I guess I must've imagined it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" As I was saying--I couldn't spot a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>, but I did see a big bug carcass. It could be that <i>was</> the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> and \"natural causes\" have done your job for you.\n"
" !point\n"
" Either way, we should check it out. There might be a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> ripe for the picking."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래, 내가 착각했나 봐.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 하던 말인데--<#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>는 못 봤지만, 큰 벌레 사체는 봤어. 그게 <i>바로</> <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>였을 수도 있고, '자연사'가 네 일을 대신해 줬을 수도 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 어쨌든 확인해 보자. 수확하기 딱 좋은 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>가 있을지도 몰라."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARMUSIC
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARMUSIC"
msgid "Those wickedly sinister guitar licks? Yep."
msgstr "그 사악하게 음침한 기타 리프 말이지? 맞아."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARNOTHING
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARNOTHING"
msgid "Maybe it was the wind?"
msgstr "바람 소리였던 거 아냐?"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CAUTIOUS
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CAUTIOUS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Of course not!\n"
" !think\n"
" Well... I don't <i>think</> so. Not to be \"that guy,\" as they say, but the whole point of an experiment is that you're not sure what will happen...\n"
" !point\n"
" But I am <i>somewhat-mostly-reasonably certain</> you'll be in no danger, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" All you need to do is put that {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} into our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> I set up over there.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" And stand back."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 당연히 아니지!\n"
" !think\n"
" 음... <i>생각</>해 보니 아닐 거야. 이런 말 하긴 뭐하지만, 실험이라는 건 원래 무슨 일이 생길지 확신 못 하는 거잖아...\n"
" !point\n"
" 그래도 네가 위험하진 않을 거라는 건 <i>적당히-대체로-합리적으로 확신</>해, 헌터.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 네가 할 일은 그 {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}을 내가 저기 설치해 둔 개조 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣는 것뿐이야.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그리고 뒤로 물러나."

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OK
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Perfect. Now, just put that {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} into our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> I set up over there."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 완벽해. 이제 그 {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}을 내가 저기 설치해 둔 개조 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣기만 하면 돼."

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" It's the big machine in the center of our camp--you can't miss it.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Once you've done that, come back and tell me exactly what happened!"
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" 우리 캠프 한가운데 있는 큰 기계야--못 찾을 수가 없어.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 그거 하고 나면 돌아와서 무슨 일이 있었는지 정확히 말해 줘!"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CAUTIOUS
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CAUTIOUS"
msgid "Wait, is this experiment... <i>dangerous?</>"
msgstr "잠깐, 이 실험... <i>위험한 거야?</>"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OK
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OK"
msgid "Sure!"
msgstr "좋아!"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLERGY
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLERGY"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Erm, Hunter? You don't happen to have any {name.c_konjur} on you, do you? Or a hanky?\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the Shard]</> No hanky, but I picked <i>this</> up on my Hunt. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Egads! You found a {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" <z 0.7>A real {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}! Just as his notes described! Then my calculations must be <i>mostly</> correct...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ah, Hunter, please, indulge me in a little experiment, would you?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 음, 헌터? 혹시 {name.c_konjur} 같은 거 갖고 있어? 아니면 손수건이라도?\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[파편을 보여 준다]</> 손수건은 없지만, 사냥하다가 <i>이거</> 주웠어. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 세상에! {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}을 찾았다고!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" <z 0.7>진짜 {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}야! 메모에 적힌 그대로야! 그럼 내 계산도 <i>대부분은</> 맞았다는 거네...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아, 헌터. 제발, 작은 실험 하나만 좀 도와줄래?"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HAS_BERNA_OR_HAMISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HAS_BERNA_OR_HAMISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" It's so fun to watch you fight, Hunter! You're like a--a--aaahh--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" AH-CHOO!\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm like... a sneeze? Sudden. Violent. Involuntary.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ha, no... pardon me. I was saying, you're like a--ah... ah-CHOO! Ah-<i>CHOO!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 네가 싸우는 거 보면 진짜 재밌어, 헌터! 넌 마치--마-마--아앗--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 에취!\n"
" player:\n"
" 난... 재채기 같다고? 갑작스럽고. 격렬하고. 의지랑 상관없고.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 하, 아니... 미안. 내가 하려던 말은, 넌 마치--아... 에취! 아-<i>취!</>"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_WITHOUTBERNAHAMISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_WITHOUTBERNAHAMISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Poor Berna and Hamish. They're out there, all alone, and surrounded by <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>! \n"
" !scared\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, Hunter! They're like a ah--aaahh--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" AH-CHOO!\n"
" player:\n"
" They're like a sneeze? Loud. Wet. Involuntary. I can see it.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" What? No, ah, sorry, I'm just worried about--ahb... ah-CHOO! Ah-<i>CHOO!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 불쌍한 베르나랑 해미시. 저 밖에 둘만 있고, <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>한테 둘러싸여 있잖아! \n"
" !scared\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, 헌터! 걔네는 마치 아--아앗--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 에취!\n"
" player:\n"
" 걔네가 재채기 같다고? 시끄럽고. 축축하고. 통제 안 되고. 그림은 나오네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 뭐? 아니, 아, 미안, 난 그냥 걔들이 걱정돼서--앗브... 에취! 아-<i>취!</>"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" YES! With so little <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> in <#BLUE>The Brinks</>, I could never properly test our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>. But you just showed that our plan could work!\n"
" player:\n"
" The plan... right... Remind me again? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Well, I salvaged a defunct <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>, which used to provide people with <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> via the old <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</>, you see.\n"
" !point\n"
" And then I modified it to <z 0.7>theoretically</> generate a <#RED>{name.rot}</>-repelling <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>! A shimmering <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> dome of safety...\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Imagine it, Hunter! This could be our home again! No more scrounging without <#KONJUR>Teffra</> in <#BLUE>The Brinks</>. A <i>real</> home...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" But the {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} wasn't enough power. I expect we'll need a much more concentrated <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> source to get it going...\n"
" player:\n"
" Point me in its direction, and I'll get it, Boss.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" Hah! \"Boss.\" Not me, surely. But you're not far off the mark...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" See, over time, the {name.c_konjur} in <#RED>Rots'</> bodies crystallizes to form {name_multiple.c_konjur_heart_shard} like the one you found.\n"
" !think\n"
" Now, if a <#RED>Rot</> grew large and powerful enough, it stands to reason that the crystallized {name.c_konjur} in their body would be extremely potent."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 맞아! <#BLUE>브링크스</>에 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>가 너무 적어서, 난 개조 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>를 제대로 시험할 수가 없었어. 근데 네가 방금 우리 계획이 통할 수 있다는 걸 보여줬어!\n"
" player:\n"
" 계획이라... 맞다... 다시 한번 말해 줄래? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 그러니까, 내가 고장 난 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> 하나를 건져 왔는데, 그건 예전에 낡은 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 파이프라인 에너지 그리드</>를 통해 사람들에게 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 공급하던 장치였어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그리고 그걸 <z 0.7>이론상</> <#RED>{name.rot}</>를 밀어내는 <#KONJUR>버블 실드</>를 생성하도록 개조했지! 반짝이는 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 안전 돔 말이야...\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 상상해 봐, 헌터! 여기가 다시 우리 집이 될 수 있어! <#BLUE>브링크스</>에서 <#KONJUR>테프라</> 없이 허덕일 일도 없어. <i>진짜</> 집이라고...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 하지만 {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}만으로는 출력이 부족했어. 작동시키려면 훨씬 더 농축된 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 원천이 필요할 거야...\n"
" player:\n"
" 방향만 찍어 줘, 보스. 내가 가져올게.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" 하! '보스'라니. 설마 내가? 근데 아주 틀린 말도 아니야...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 있잖아, 시간이 지나면 <#RED>Rot들</>의 몸속 {name.c_konjur}가 결정화돼서, 네가 찾은 것 같은 {name_multiple.c_konjur_heart_shard}이 만들어져.\n"
" !think\n"
" 자, 만약 <#RED>Rot</>가 충분히 크고 강해지면, 그 몸의 결정화된 {name.c_konjur}는 엄청난 힘을 가질 수밖에 없어."

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CONTEXT
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CONTEXT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" So? What happened when you put the {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} into the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>? Tell me everything!\n"
" player:\n"
" It definitely reacted to the {name.konjur_heart_shard}. Maybe even powered up a little?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그래서? {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}을 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣었을 때 뭐가 일어났어? 하나도 빠짐없이 말해 줘!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.konjur_heart_shard}에 확실히 반응했지? 어쩌면 조금 출력이 올라갔을 수도 있고?"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_NOCONTEXT
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_NOCONTEXT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" So? What happened? Tell me everything!\n"
" player:\n"
" The {name.i_town_grid_cryst} definitely reacted to the {name.konjur_heart_shard}. Maybe it even powered up a little?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그래서? 무슨 일이 있었어? 전부 말해 줘!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.i_town_grid_cryst}이 {name.konjur_heart_shard}에 확실히 반응했어. 어쩌면 조금 출력이 오른 것 같기도 해?"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_GENERIC
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_GENERIC"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> like that are pretty rare--and elusive. But the <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</> certainly has its fair share!\n"
" player:\n"
" They wouldn't happen to offer their hearts up on request, would they?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh no no no! They'll fight to the death! Viciously! And without mercy! It'll be absolute carnage!\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oops--my apologies, Hunter. <z 0.7>Got carried away.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> 같은 건 꽤 희귀하고--찾기도 힘들어. 하지만 <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</>엔 그런 게 꽤 많지!\n"
" player:\n"
" 설마 부탁하면 심장을 순순히 내주진 않겠지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아, 아니 아니 아니! 죽을 때까지 싸울 거야! 잔인하게! 자비도 없이! 완전 아수라장이 될걸!\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 앗--미안, 헌터. <z 0.7>내가 좀 과했네.</>"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_TREEMON
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_TREEMON"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> like that are pretty rare--and elusive--but we already know where one is: right here in the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest}</>...\n"
" player:\n"
" Let me guess: the {name.megatreemon} that knocked us out of the sky?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Bingo, bango, bongo! <z 0.7>Sorry, I'm getting a bit excited.</> Gosh, aren't we lucky she revealed her location so quickly?\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Err--well, not so lucky considering it meant we crash-landed and lost our friends, but..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> 같은 건 희귀하고--찾기 힘들어--근데 하나가 어디 있는지는 이미 알아: 바로 이 <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest}</>에...\n"
" player:\n"
" 맞춰 볼까: 하늘에서 우리를 떨어뜨린 그 {name.megatreemon} 말이지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 빙고, 뱅고, 봉고! <z 0.7>미안, 내가 좀 신났네.</> 와, 저 녀석가 이렇게 빨리 위치를 드러내 줘서 우리 운 좋지 않아?\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 어--뭐, 그 탓에 추락하고 친구들도 잃었으니 운이 좋다고 하긴 좀 그렇지만..."

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_HAS_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_HAS_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Chin up! Our team's back together, and the mission's back on track!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Soon, we'll have our home back, just like it was. Go <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !clap\n"
" 기운 내! 우리 팀 다시 모였고, 임무도 다시 궤도에 올랐어!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 곧 예전처럼 우리 집을 되찾을 거야. 가자, <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_MISSING_BERNA_OR_HAMISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_MISSING_BERNA_OR_HAMISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Actually, just forget I said anything. Let's just focus on finding the rest of the crew, then we'll worry about the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 아니, 방금 한 말은 그냥 잊어. 우선 남은 대원들 찾는 데 집중하자, <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> 걱정은 그다음에 해도 돼."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GONE
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GONE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" No! He couldn't have known--!\n"
" player:\n"
" He was an adult, playing with a substance he didn't fully understand, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" You're... You're right, Hunter. I know you are. But I also know he loved me, and never meant to hurt me...\n"
" !think\n"
" ... Perhaps he let his ambition get the better of him. Perhaps he... he <i>should</> have known better. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" But now, today, for me--it's enough that he knows he did wrong. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" And I want him to know that despite it all, I'm happy. And that I forgive him, that old fox.\n"
" player:\n"
" Then let's go save him so you have a chance to tell him so. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hm. Well said, Hunter. The <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> shows he's up ahead."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아니! 그분은 알 수 없었어--!\n"
" player:\n"
" 그분도 어른이었지만, 완전히 이해하지 못한 물질을 다룬 거였어, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 네 말이... 맞아, 헌터. 나도 알아. 하지만 그분이 날 사랑했고, 날 해치려던 건 절대 아니었다는 것도 알아...\n"
" !think\n"
" ... 어쩌면 야망이 너무 앞섰던 걸지도. 어쩌면 그분도... <i>진작</> 더 조심했어야 했겠지. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 하지만 지금, 오늘의 나한텐--자기가 잘못했다는 걸 그분이 아는 것만으로도 충분해. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 그리고 그분이 알았으면 해. 이런 일이 다 있었어도 난 행복하다고. 그리고 그 늙은 여우를 용서한다고.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 그 말을 직접 전할 기회가 생기게, 일단 구하러 가자. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 흠. 좋은 말이야, 헌터. <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>에 따르면 그가 앞에 있어."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SAME
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SAME"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Right... Like, if <i>I</> did it, then <i>I</> can undo it. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" But in reality, some things just <i>can't</> be undone.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Even if we rebuilt this house--stone by stone, board by board--exactly as it was...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" It'd never be the same. \n"
" player:\n"
" Because <i>we've</> changed. The world's changed.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Our mission's goal was to put things back to how they were...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" But if we never could in the first place, what was the point?\n"
" player:\n"
" To make something new, {name.npc_scout}. Something better. Now, let's go save your Grandpa.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You know, you're right! Well said, Hunter. \n"
" !notebook\n"
" The <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> shows he's up ahead."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 맞아... 그러니까, <i>내가</> 저질렀다면 <i>내가</> 되돌릴 수도 있다, 이런 식으로. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" 근데 현실에선 어떤 건 <i>절대</> 되돌릴 수 없어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 우리가 이 집을--돌 하나, 판자 하나까지--완전히 똑같이 다시 지어도...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 예전 그 집은 아니야. \n"
" player:\n"
" 왜냐하면 <i>우리가</> 변했으니까. 세상도 변했고.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" 우리 임무의 목표는 모든 걸 예전으로 되돌리는 거였지...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 근데 애초에 그게 불가능했다면, 그 의미가 뭐였을까?\n"
" player:\n"
" 새로운 걸 만드는 거지, {name.npc_scout}. 더 나은 걸. 자, 이제 네 할아버지 구하러 가자.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 있잖아, 네 말 맞아! 좋은 말이야, 헌터. \n"
" !notebook\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>에 따르면 그가 앞에 있어."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GONE
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GONE"
msgid "Maybe your Grandpa took fault because it <i>is</> his fault?"
msgstr "어쩌면 네 할아버지가 자기 탓이라고 한 건, 그게 <i>정말</> 자기 잘못이라서 아닐까?"

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SAME
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SAME"
msgid "Maybe it gives us a false sense of control over random events?"
msgstr "어쩌면 우연한 사건까지 우리가 통제할 수 있다는 착각을 주는 걸까?"

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" No doubt about it. I found pieces of my old <#RED>{name.damselfly}</> toy here in the rubble.  \n"
" !agree\n"
" This is the house my <#BLUE>Grandpa</> spoke of in the <#RED>Diary Pages</>. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" Or it <i>was</> the house. The one he moved me to after I developed my <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> sickness...\n"
" player:\n"
" You say that like it's something YOU did...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Did I? Huh. But I suppose, deep down, I <i>do</> believe it's my fault. \n"
" player:\n"
" Your Grandpa thought it was his fault, too.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" And it was <i>neither</> of our faults. It was an accident! Why do we do that..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"틀림없어. 여기 잔해 속에서... 내 옛날 <#RED>{name.damselfly}</> 장난감 조각을 찾았어.\n"
"!agree\n"
"이곳은 <#BLUE>할아버지</1>의 <#RED>일기 페이지</2>에서 말하던 집이야.\n"
"!dejected\n"
"아니, <3>집</4>이었지. 내가 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</5> 병을 앓기 시작한 뒤에 나를 데려왔던 곳...\n"
"player:\n"
"그렇게 말하니까… 마치 네가 그런 것처럼 들리는데.\n"
"\\agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"내가 그랬어? 그래도… 속으로는, 아직도 내 잘못이라고 생각하고 있는 것 같네.\n"
"player:\n"
"네 할아버지도 그게 자기 잘못이라고 생각하셨어.\n"
"\\agent:\n"
"!agree\n"
"그래서 더 이상한 거지. 그건 <i>누구의 잘못도</6> 아니였어. 그냥... 사고였을 뿐인데..."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" You head out, Hunter. I... I need a moment alone."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 먼저 가, 헌터. 나... 나 잠깐 혼자 있을 시간이 필요해."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scout_rummage\n"
" I'll... I'll follow in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> in a minute..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !scout_rummage\n"
" 나도... 조금만 있다가 <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>으로 따라갈게..."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" I think I'll take one last look. You go on."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" 나 마지막으로 한 번만 더 보고 갈게. 넌 먼저 가."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].4
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Don't wait for me, Hunter. I'll just be a moment."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 나 기다리지 마, 헌터. 금방 갈게."

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].5
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You don't mind if I stay here a bit longer, do you?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 나 여기 조금만 더 있어도 괜찮지?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND"
msgid "See ya, Toot!"
msgstr "나중에 봐, 투트!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADD_TROUBLEMAKER
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADD_TROUBLEMAKER"
msgid "Smell ya later, 'teach."
msgstr "그럼 나중에 봐, 쌤."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Tell me. Whatcha know about <#RED>Dodging</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 말해 봐. <#RED>회피</>에 대해 알고 있는 거 있어?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Were you sleepin' during Hunter training?\n"
" !point\n"
" Right then, LISTEN UP--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} 헌터 훈련 시간에 졸았냐?\n"
" !point\n"
" 좋아, 잘 들어--"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i><z 2>CORRECT!</></i>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>A+</>, kid. {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i><z 2>정답!</></i>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>A+</>다, 꼬마. {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" An acceptable answer. At least we're not starting from zero.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Now, look--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그럭저럭 괜찮은 답이야. 적어도 바닥부터 시작하진 않네.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} 자, 봐--"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i><z 2>INCORRECT!</></i>\n"
" !angry\n"
" Someone's lookin' to get detention. {name.dojo_cough} Now LISTEN UP--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i><z 2>오답!</></i>\n"
" !angry\n"
" 누군가 벌점 받고 싶나 본데. {name.dojo_cough} 자, 잘 들어--"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Remember, it's easy to regret a swing, but you'll never regret a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 기억해, 휘두른 건 후회하기 쉬워도 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>은 절대 후회 안 해."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" It's easy to regret a swing, but you'll never regret a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 휘두른 건 후회하기 쉬워도 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>은 절대 후회 안 해."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" The more familiar you can get with their patterns, the easier you'll stay alive."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 놈들 패턴에 익숙해질수록 살아남기 쉬워져."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Are you a teacher, Hunter? 'Cause you sure are testing me.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Y'know, I <i>was</i> gonna give you a <#KONJUR>Treat</>, but now I'm not sure if you deserve it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 너 교사냐, 헌터? 나 시험 엄청 하네.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 있잖아, 나 <i>원래</i> <#KONJUR>간식</> 하나 주려고 했는데, 지금은 네가 받을 자격 있는지 모르겠네."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Sigh. Just take it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But try not to get clobbered out there, okay? Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 하아. 그냥 가져가.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 근데 나가서 얻어맞고 다니진 마, 알겠지? 수업 끝."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hmph. {name.dojo_cough} Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 흥. {name.dojo_cough} 수업 끝."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "POP QUIZ!!"
msgstr "돌발 퀴즈!!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Oh. Um. Nothing?"
msgstr "어. 음. 아무것도?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "It's more important than Attacking."
msgstr "공격보다 더 중요해."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "You do it with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>."
msgstr "<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>로 하는 거야."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D"
msgid "It's for wimps."
msgstr "겁쟁이들이나 하는 거야."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Gotcha... I'll Dodge with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>!"
msgstr "알겠어... <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>로 회피할게!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "Prioritize Dodging over Attacking. Okay!"
msgstr "공격보다 회피를 우선할게. 알겠어!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "Watch foes' movements closely. Can do."
msgstr "적 움직임을 잘 보라고. 그렇게 할게."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D"
msgid "I still think Dodging's for wimps."
msgstr "난 아직도 회피는 겁쟁이용이라고 생각해."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "<z 0.92>Treat?? <i>(Ahem)</> I love dodging with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>!</>"
msgstr "<z 0.92>간식?? <i>(크흠)</> 난 <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>로 회피하는 게 너무 좋아!</>"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "You can't bribe <i>me!</i>"
msgstr "<i>날</i> 매수할 순 없어!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" If you charge into a fight swinging blindly, you'll get knocked on yer tail in no time flat.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Instead, watch your foes for clues they're about to strike, then <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> out of the way with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> when they do.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Foes leave themselves wide open after they <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</>, but you won't be able to capitalize if you're reelin' from a hit."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 눈 감고 휘두르며 싸움에 들이박으면 금방 나가떨어져.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 대신 적이 곧 공격할 신호를 보고, 그럴 때는 <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>로 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> 해서 비켜.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 적은 <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</> 뒤에 빈틈이 크게 생기지만, 맞아서 비틀거리면 그 틈을 못 노려."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Here, have a <#KONJUR>Treat</>. Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...자, <#KONJUR>간식</> 받아. 수업 끝."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND"
msgid "Thanks for the quiz, Toot."
msgstr "퀴즈 고마워, 투트."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_TROUBLEMAKER
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_TROUBLEMAKER"
msgid "Smell ya later, nerd!"
msgstr "나중에 보자, 너드야!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Tell me... Whatcha know about <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 말해봐... <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>에 대해 뭐 알아?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well, at least you've taken the 101 course.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> deal waaay more <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> than regular <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 뭐, 기초는 듣긴 했네.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>는 일반 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>보다 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>를 훨씬 더 많이 줘."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" True! <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> do waaay more <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> than regular <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>, so it's important to learn them.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You'll know you've done one right if you see <#BLUE>Blue Damage</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 맞아! <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>는 일반 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>보다 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>를 훨씬 더 많이 줘, 그래서 익혀 두는 게 중요해.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>파란 피해</>가 뜨면 제대로 한 거야."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" CORRECT! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> deal waaay more <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> than regular <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>, and show up as <#BLUE>Blue Damage</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 정답!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>는 일반 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>보다 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>를 훨씬 더 많이 주고, <#BLUE>파란 피해</>로 표시돼!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, yer gonna get out-<#RED>{name.concept_damage}d</> by nerds, then.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" But what do I know. I'm just your {name.job_dojo}."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 뭐, 그럼 너드들한테 out-<#RED>{name.concept_damage}d</> 당하겠네.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 내가 뭘 알겠냐. 난 그냥 네 {name.job_dojo}일 뿐인데."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Do you want your <#KONJUR>Treat</> or not?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 네 <#KONJUR>간식</> 받을 거야 말 거야?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just take it.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그냥 받아.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 수업 끝."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" You can lead a horse to <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>...\n"
" !angry\n"
" Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 말을 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>까지 끌고 갈 순 있어도...\n"
" !angry\n"
" 수업 끝."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "POP QUIZ!!"
msgstr "돌발 퀴즈!!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Err, their Damage appears in blue?"
msgstr "음, 피해가 파란색으로 뜬다?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Each Weapon type has its own conditions!"
msgstr "무기 종류마다 조건이 따로 있어!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "I can't do reliable Damage without them."
msgstr "그거 없으면 안정적으로 피해를 못 넣어."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D"
msgid "They're for nerds."
msgstr "그건 너드들용이야."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "Do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} for more Damage. Got it."
msgstr "더 큰 피해를 내려면 {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} 하면 되는 거지. 알겠어."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "{name.concept_focus_hit} Damage appears blue. Gotcha."
msgstr "{name.concept_focus_hit} 피해는 파란색으로 뜨는구나. 알겠어."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D"
msgid "Wow, that was a long and nerdy lecture."
msgstr "와, 진짜 길고 너드 같은 강의였네."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "<i>Sigh</>. I love doing extra Damage with {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}!"
msgstr "<i>하아</>. 난 {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}으로 추가 피해 넣는 게 너무 좋아!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "My brain can't be bought, pencil-pusher!"
msgstr "내 머리는 못 사, 책상물림!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yep. Feel free to practice your <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> on the dummies around town.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Now have a <#KONJUR>Treat</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그래. 마을 여기저기 있는 허수아비에서 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> 마음껏 연습해.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...자, 이제 <#KONJUR>간식</> 받아.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 수업 끝."

#: Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" He left me... again..."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 날 두고 갔어... 또..."

#: Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...I just need a moment, Hunter."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...잠깐만 좀 있을게, 헌터."

#: Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie.QUIP.post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie.QUIP.post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Gotta say, Hunter, you really live up to the hype."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 헌터, 소문값 제대로 하네."

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASHION
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASHION"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh, absolutely! <i>Le Chateau d'Alphonse</> pieces absolutely STINK of power!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Though that could be due to the innovative use of <#RED>{name.rot}</> parts... \n"
" !think\n"
" That said... And I can't believe I'm about to say this but...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I <i>think</> <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I could make it even better?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I bet we can upgrade it more than your old armour--probably up to <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Oh! Promise me you won't tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> I touched his work--much less made it BETTER!\n"
" player: \n"
" Promise.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Y'hear that, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? We're gonna work alongside--or at a little distance from--a fashion legend! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" I never thought I'd get to upgrade <i>Chateau d'Alphonse</> {name.i_item_rarity_rare} armour... Thank you, Hunter! From the both of us."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 아, 당연하지! <i>Le Chateau d'Alphonse</> 조각들에선 힘의 냄새가 진동해!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 물론 그건 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 부품을 혁신적으로 써서일 수도 있지만...\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래도... 이런 말 하게 될 줄은 몰랐는데...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 나 <i>생각엔</> <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>랑 내가 이걸 더 좋게 만들 수 있을 것 같아?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 네 예전 갑옷보다 더 업그레이드할 수 있어. 아마 <#RED>레벨 {max_level_rare}</>까지!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" 아! 내가 저 녀석 작업물에 손댔다고, 그것도 더 좋게 만들었다고 <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</>한테는 절대 말하지 마!\n"
" player: \n"
" 약속해.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 들었지, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? 우린 패션 전설과 같이 일할 거야. 뭐, 조금 떨어져서일 수도 있지만!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>Chateau d'Alphonse</> {name.i_item_rarity_rare} 갑옷을 내가 업그레이드하게 될 줄은 몰랐어... 고마워, 헌터! 우리 둘 다 진심으로."

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASHION
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASHION"
msgid "Yeah! Does it make me look more powerful?"
msgstr "응! 나 더 강해 보이게 해?"

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. I'll admit it's... creative. An' surprisin'ly sturdy... <z 0.7>an' <i>could</> hold under the pressure...</>\n"
" !think\n"
" It's given me an idear or two, Hunter... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I reckon I can upgrade it further than yer old {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} weapons. Up ta <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>, even.\n"
" !point\n"
" The forge is roarin'. Just bring this here {name.i_item_rarity_rare} weapon to a <#RED>Weapon Rack</> and I can get started, ay?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흠. 인정하긴 싫지만... 창의적이네. 생각보다 엄청 튼튼하고... <z 0.7>그리고 <i>버텨낼</> 수도 있겠어...</>\n"
" !think\n"
" 이거 보니까 아이디어가 좀 떠올랐어, 헌터...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 네 예전 {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} 무기보다 더 올릴 수 있을 것 같아. <#RED>레벨 {max_level_rare}</>까지도.\n"
" !point\n"
" 대장간은 이미 달아올랐지. 이 {name.i_item_rarity_rare} 무기를 <#RED>무기 거치대</>로 가져오면 바로 시작할게, 알겠지?"

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Doesn't it just?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 그치?"

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Yep! What do you think? Pret-ty sweet, eh?"
msgstr "응! 어때 보여? 꽤 멋지지, 응?"

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "That sounds just swell!"
msgstr "정말 끝내주는 소리네!"

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ADVICE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ADVICE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" From what <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> told me, seems like those old <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> have learned some new tricks.\n"
" !point\n"
" You won't be able to use the same tactics you used before to take 'em down, so watch 'em carefully before you attack.\n"
" !think\n"
" Also... with everything going all topsy-turvy like this, I've got a nasty feeling those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> will have found a way to revive themselves.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" At least that means another <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> for us. Ha!\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" If you feel like you need some extra training, I'm always happy to oblige."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>이 말해준 걸 보니, 그 오래된 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>들이 새 기술을 익힌 모양이야.\n"
" !point\n"
" 전에 쓰던 전술로는 못 잡아. 공격하기 전에 움직임부터 잘 봐.\n"
" !think\n"
" 그리고... 세상이 이렇게 뒤집힌 김에, 그 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>들도 스스로 부활하는 법을 찾았을 것 같은 불길한 예감이 들어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 뭐, 우리에겐 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> 하나 더 생긴 셈이긴 하지. 하!\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 추가 훈련이 필요하면 언제든 도와줄게."

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CONFIDENT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CONFIDENT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Heh. You're doin' us all proud. Just make sure <i>you're</> not too proud to ask for advice when you need it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 헤. 넌 우리 모두의 자랑이야. 필요할 땐 <i>네가</> 조언 구하는 걸 자존심 때문에 미루지 마."

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ADVICE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ADVICE"
msgid "The {name_multiple.rot} have gone into a <#RED>Frenzy</>! Do you have any battle tips?"
msgstr "{name_multiple.rot}이 <#RED>광란</> 상태에 들어갔어! 전투 팁 좀 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CONFIDENT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CONFIDENT"
msgid "Nothing I can't handle."
msgstr "못 해낼 건 없어."

#: Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Er--well... no. That is...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I kind of... sort of... thought they might make me look rugged. Like a rugged leader type.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Um, haha. A-anyway..!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 어! 어... 그러니까... 아니. 그게...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그냥... 음... 좀 터프해 보일까 해서. 터프한 리더 같은 느낌으로.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 음, 하하. 아, 아무튼..!"

#: Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "{name.npc_scout}, I've been wondering--what's with all the bandages you wear? Are you hurt?"
msgstr "{name.npc_scout}, 계속 궁금했는데 그 붕대는 왜 그렇게 많이 하고 다녀? 다친 거야?"

#: Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Hiya, {name.npc_scout}. See ya, {name.npc_scout}."
msgstr "안녕, {name.npc_scout}. 이따 봐, {name.npc_scout}."

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" You think so? Gosh, I hope you're right, for the sake of those who come after us.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'd like to think that as long as you're breathing, it's never too late to start making things better."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 정말 그렇게 생각해? 와... 우리 뒤에 올 사람들을 위해서라도 네 말이 맞았으면 좋겠다.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 숨 쉬고 있는 한, 더 나아지게 만들기엔 절대 늦지 않았다고 믿고 싶어."

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" You're right. We can't undo what's happened, but that doesn't mean we can't build something new.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" There's still room for beauty in change."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 맞아. 이미 일어난 일을 되돌릴 순 없지만, 그렇다고 새로 만들 수 없는 건 아니지.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 변화 속에도 아름다움이 들어설 자리는 아직 있어."

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "It'll be just as we remembered as kids."
msgstr "어릴 때 기억하던 그대로 될 거야."

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "It'll never be the same, but we can make it beautiful."
msgstr "예전 같진 않겠지만, 아름답게 만들 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Of course! <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> our <#RED>{name.job_armorsmith}</> has a big, pink hair bun, and carries a leatherworking tool.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" She's a bit... eccentric. It'll be hard to miss her.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> our <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</> on the other hand, is a stoic kind of guy. Oh! And he has a distinctive tattoo on his arm.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We really need them both for this expedition to have any hope of success--you won't be able to <#RED>Upgrade</> any of your gear without their expertise.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" And besides all that, their safety... it's my responsibility. I still can't believe I lost them...\n"
" player:\n"
" Don't worry, we'll find them!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 물론이지! <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> 우리 <#RED>{name.job_armorsmith}</>는 커다란 분홍 머리번을 했고, 가죽공예 도구를 들고 다녀.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 성격이 좀... 별나서 눈에 확 띌 거야.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 반대로 <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> 우리 <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</>는 과묵한 타입이야. 아! 팔에 눈에 띄는 문신도 있어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이번 원정이 성공하려면 둘 다 꼭 필요해. 둘의 전문성이 없으면 장비를 <#RED>업그레이드</>할 수 없거든.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 그리고 무엇보다도, 녀석들의 안전은... 내 책임이야. 내가 녀석들을 놓쳤다는 게 아직도 믿기지 않아...\n"
" player:\n"
" 걱정 마, 꼭 찾을게!"

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>'s ready to go."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> 준비됐어."

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS"
msgid "Could you tell me a bit about the missing folks first?"
msgstr "먼저 실종된 사람들 얘기 좀 해줄래?"

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY"
msgid "I sure am!"
msgstr "그럼, 준비됐지!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND"
msgid "Bye, {name.npc_dojo_master}! Blam blam!"
msgstr "잘 가, {name.npc_dojo_master}! 빵야 빵야!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" I said be careful with that <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그 <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> 조심해서 쓰랬지!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" What d'ya wanna know?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 뭐가 궁금해?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Hm, yeah. So, <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</> have two firing modes.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> you can shoot small <#RED>Projectiles</> in a wide spread.\n"
" !point\n"
" Your <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>Attack</> also doubles as your <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> and pushes you backwards.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> you can shoot a big ol' <#RED>Projectile</> that'll do more <#RED>Damage</>, but is also more concentrated."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 음, 그래. <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</>에는 발사 모드가 두 가지 있어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>에선 작은 <#RED>투사체</>를 넓게 퍼지게 쏠 수 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 네 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>공격</>은 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> 역할도 해서 널 뒤로 밀어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>에선 더 큰 <#RED>투사체</>를 쏴서 <#RED>피해</>를 더 주지만, 퍼짐은 더 좁아."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Sure, but LISTEN UP this time.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</> have two firing modes.\n"
" !point\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> you can launch yourself backwards and shoot a bunch of small <#RED>Projectiles</> in a big spread.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> you'll shoot a big ol' <#RED>Projectile</> that does more <#RED>Damage</>, but it'll also have less spread."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그래, 근데 이번엔 제대로 들어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</>에는 발사 모드가 두 가지 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>에선 네가 뒤로 튕겨 나가면서 작은 <#RED>투사체</>를 넓게 퍼뜨려 쏴.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>에선 큰 <#RED>투사체</>를 쏘는데 <#RED>피해</>는 더 크고 퍼짐은 더 적어."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Hm...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Right, yes. You can initiate a <#RED>Mortar</> volley by hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\n"
" !point\n"
" But you gotta time hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground to actually fire it.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" But 'ey, then the last half of your <#RED>Mortar Projectiles</> will all be <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" That'll really hit'm where it hurts."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} 음...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 맞아. <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 누르면 <#RED>박격포</> 연사를 시작할 수 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 근데 실제로 발사하려면 네 <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>가 땅에 닿는 순간 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 맞춰 눌러야 해.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그리고 그러면 <#RED>박격포 투사체</>의 마지막 절반은 전부 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>가 돼!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그럼 제대로 아프게 꽂혀."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Heh. I like the enthusiasm.\n"
" !point\n"
" Okay. Hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> will initiate a <#RED>Mortar</> volley.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground will fire the volley.\n"
" !agree\n"
" The last half of a <#RED>Mortar</> volley will all be <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 헤, 그 의욕 좋네.\n"
" !point\n"
" 좋아. <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 누르면 <#RED>박격포</> 연사가 시작돼.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 네 <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>가 땅에 닿는 순간 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 누르면 연사가 발사돼.\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>박격포</> 연사의 마지막 절반은 전부 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>야."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Reloading can be fiddly if you're new to this puppy.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> to start a reload, then hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> just as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground to finish'r off.\n"
" !point\n"
" You can practice on the <#RED>Training Dummies</> while you're in camp if you need to."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 처음 쓰면 재장전이 좀 까다로울 수 있어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 눌러 재장전을 시작하고, 네 <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>가 땅에 닿는 순간 <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 눌러 마무리해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 필요하면 캠프의 <#RED>훈련용 허수아비</>에서 연습해도 돼."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Okay. {name.dojo_cough} But LISTEN UP now.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Just hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>, then hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground to reload."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 좋아. {name.dojo_cough} 근데 이번엔 잘 들어.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그냥 <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 누르고, 네 <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>가 땅에 닿는 순간 <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 누르면 재장전돼."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I wouldn't mind some {name.weapon_cannon} tips."
msgstr "{name.weapon_cannon} 팁 좀 들어도 좋겠어."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES"
msgid "Firing modes."
msgstr "발사 모드."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES_ALT"
msgid "Firing modes, again?"
msgstr "발사 모드, 다시?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR"
msgid "Does it do anything cool?"
msgstr "멋진 거라도 돼?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR_ALT"
msgid "Tell me about the mortar again!"
msgstr "박격포 다시 설명해줘!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING"
msgid "How do I reload?"
msgstr "재장전은 어떻게 해?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING_ALT"
msgid "Re-explain reloading for me?"
msgstr "재장전 다시 설명해줄래?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO"
msgid "Ah nevermind, I can figure it out."
msgstr "아 됐어, 내가 알아볼게."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO_ALT"
msgid "Okay, I think I get the gist."
msgstr "오케이, 대충 감 잡았어."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.SKIPINFO_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.SKIPINFO_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just you don't blow yourself sky high and I'm happy. Anyway--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 네가 하늘로 날아가지만 않으면 난 됐어. 아무튼--"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLDONE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLDONE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Play around, get a knack for it. I'm sure you'll be s'plodin' <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in no time."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이리저리 써보면서 손에 익혀. 금방 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 터뜨리고 다닐 거야."

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEPOSIT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEPOSIT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Um... that's very kind of you Hunter, but I'm afraid I'll have to pass.\n"
" player:\n"
" You sure? It's pretty fun...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Yes, well, it's... erm, it's a little embarrassing... I have an extremely rare <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Allergy</>. I've had it since I was a kit.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Minor exposure causes sneezing, congestion, hives. Direct contact? Well, it's... rather cataclysmic.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I shudder to imagine what'd happen were I to hold a highly-concentrated <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 어! 음... 정말 친절한 제안이야, 헌터. 근데 난 사양해야 할 것 같아.\n"
" player:\n"
" 정말? 꽤 재밌는데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 응, 그게... 음, 좀 창피한데... 난 아주 희귀한 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 알레르기</>가 있어. 어릴 때부터 그랬어.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 조금만 노출돼도 재채기, 코막힘, 두드러기가 나. 직접 닿으면? 그건... 꽤 대재앙이지.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 고농축 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 내가 손에 쥐면 무슨 일이 날지 생각만 해도 소름 돋아."

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HIGHFIVE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HIGHFIVE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ha... yes. Sorry about that.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'm happy to give you a high-five anytime, Hunter... <i>after</> you wash off the {name.c_konjur}.\n"
" !cough\n"
" And <#RED>{name.rot}</> viscera."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 하... 맞아. 미안.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 헌터, 하이파이브는 언제든 해줄 수 있어... <i>먼저</> {name.c_konjur}를 씻어낸 뒤에.\n"
" !cough\n"
" 그리고 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 내장도."

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RISKY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RISKY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It would be if I was the one fighting.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But luckily, we have you! And I'll watch your back from the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>, far above any errant splashes of {name.c_konjur}."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 내가 싸우는 쪽이면 그렇겠지.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 근데 다행히 우리에겐 네가 있잖아! 난 <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>에서 네 뒤를 봐줄게. {name.c_konjur}가 튀어도 닿지 않을 만큼 훨씬 위에서."

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEPOSIT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEPOSIT"
msgid "Do you wanna put the {name.konjur_heart} in the {name.town_grid_cryst} next time?"
msgstr "다음엔 {name.konjur_heart}을 {name.town_grid_cryst}에 넣어볼래?"

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HIGHFIVE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HIGHFIVE"
msgid "At least now I know why you've been avoiding my victory high-fives."
msgstr "이제 왜 네가 내 승리 하이파이브를 피했는지는 알겠네."

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RISKY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RISKY"
msgid "Isn't this whole expedition a little risky for you, then?"
msgstr "그럼 이 원정 전체가 너한텐 좀 위험한 거 아냐?"

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BACKPEDAL
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BACKPEDAL"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Smart kid."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 눈치 빠르네."

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_COUGH
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_COUGH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ghe-heh-heh... ha-ha... GAH-HAW-HAW-HAW!\n"
" player:\n"
" What's so funny?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Hooo-- just thinkin' about all the laps I'm gonna make you run... we'll see who's \"up to this\" then, won't we?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그헤-헤-헤... 하-하... 가하-하-하-하!\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐가 그렇게 웃긴데?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 후우-- 내가 너한테 시킬 뺑뺑이 생각하니까... 그때 누가 \"이걸 감당할\" 수 있는지 보자고, 안 그래?"

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BACKPEDAL
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BACKPEDAL"
msgid "Er-- n-no reason!"
msgstr "어-- 아, 아무 이유 없어!"

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_COUGH
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_COUGH"
msgid "That cough sounds bad. Are you sure you're up to this?"
msgstr "기침 소리 안 좋은데. 이거 정말 할 수 있겠어?"

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CATBAG
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CATBAG"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Now what's THAT supposed ta mean??\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Ah! Nothi-- I just-- It was--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" What--cat got yer tongue?\n"
" player:\n"
" Touché. <z 0.7>Which better not be a cat thing.</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'll talk ta <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>. Let them know I hold nothin' against 'em. \n"
" !point\n"
" Thank ye, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그게 대체 무슨 뜻인데??\n"
" player:\n"
" 어! 아! 아냐-- 그냥-- 그게--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 왜--고양이가 혀라도 물었냐?\n"
" player:\n"
" 한 방 먹었네. <z 0.7>근데 그게 또 고양이 얘기는 아니어야 할 텐데.</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 내가 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>랑 얘기할게. 내가 원망하는 거 없다고 전해 둘게.\n"
" !point\n"
" 고맙다, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FEELBAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FEELBAD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> I came along to try 'n' set right me wrongs. I dinnae want ta put <i>more</> pressure on the kid. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" You know them. They'd've taken that across their wee shoulders along with the rest o' the bloody world."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 난 내 잘못을 바로잡아 보려고 따라온 거야. 그 애한테 <i>더</> 부담 주고 싶진 않았어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 알잖아. 걘 그걸 이 빌어먹을 세상 짐이랑 같이 그 작은 어깨에 또 짊어졌을 거야."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GOBYEBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GOBYEBYE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Off ye go, Hunter. I'll talk ta <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" 가 봐, 헌터. 내가 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>랑 얘기할게."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OKBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OKBYE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" I'll do just that. Thank ye, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" 그렇게 할게. 고맙다, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REMIND"
msgid "agent: \n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's true. I smithied the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> at the behest of <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> himself. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" But <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> couldn't be contained. Leaks sprung all over, creatin' what we now call the <#RED>{name.rot}</>.\n"
" !angry\n"
" When I told <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> that he needed ta shut it all down, he refused! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Called it a \"scientific opportunity.\" I called it a \"bloody disaster\" and him a \"bloody fool.\"\n"
" !angry\n"
" In a huff, I up and left fer <#BLUE>The Brinks</>. But... I shoulda stayed. Shoulda pushed back.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I didn't, though, did I, Hunter? No. I tucked tail and left. Haunts me ta this very day.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Weren't me intention ta have it haunt <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>, now, too!"
msgstr "agent: \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 맞아. 내가 <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> 본인 부탁으로 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 파이프라인 에너지 그리드</>를 만들었어.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 근데 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>는 통제가 안 됐어. 여기저기서 누출이 터지면서 지금 우리가 <#RED>{name.rot}</>라고 부르는 게 생겼지.\n"
" !angry\n"
" 내가 <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</>한테 전부 멈춰야 한다고 했는데, 거부했어!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그걸 \"과학적 기회\"라고 하더군. 난 \"빌어먹을 재앙\"이라 했고, 그 인간을 \"빌어먹을 바보\"라고 했지.\n"
" !angry\n"
" 화가 나서 그냥 <#BLUE>브링크스</>로 떠나 버렸어. 하지만... 남았어야 했어. 끝까지 맞섰어야 했어.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 근데 안 그랬지, 그렇지 헌터? 그래. 꼬리 내리고 떠났어. 지금까지도 그게 날 괴롭혀.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그게 이제 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>까지 괴롭히게 하려던 건 아니었어!"

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CATBAG
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CATBAG"
msgid "I can understand that. Still, cat's out of the bag now."
msgstr "이해는 해. 그래도 이제 고양이는 자루 밖으로 나왔잖아."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FEELBAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FEELBAD"
msgid "{name.npc_scout}? They feel bad for what happened, but also for not knowing."
msgstr "{name.npc_scout}? 그 일 때문에 미안해하고, 몰랐던 것도 미안해해."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GOBYEBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GOBYEBYE"
msgid "Sorry, but could you ask them yourself? I have to run."
msgstr "미안한데, 네가 직접 물어봐 줄래? 나 가봐야 해."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OKBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OKBYE"
msgid "It's okay, but just talk to them. I'd better run."
msgstr "괜찮아, 그냥 가서 얘기해. 난 이만 가볼게."

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REMIND"
msgid "Remind me again what happened?"
msgstr "무슨 일이었는지 다시 말해줄래?"

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wait. <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</>? Like, THE <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</>?? Why didn't you say so??\n"
" player:\n"
" I thought I <i>did</> ...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" He's just kind of, like, THE name in fashion??\n"
" !point\n"
" And you MET him. Did he insult you? Talk down to you? Make you feel \"less than\"?\n"
" player:\n"
" Hm. Maybe that sounds familiar...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Lucky!! If I stare, don't worry. I'm admiring the clothing--not you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 잠깐. <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</>? 그 <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> 말하는 거야?? 왜 진작 말 안 했어??\n"
" player:\n"
" 난 <i>말했다고</> 생각했는데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 패션계에선 그냥, 뭐랄까, 끝판왕 이름이잖아??\n"
" !point\n"
" 그리고 넌 걔를 만나기까지 했고. 너 모욕했어? 깔봤어? 너를 \"하찮게\" 느끼게 했어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 흠. 뭔가 익숙한 얘긴데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 부럽다!! 내가 계속 쳐다봐도 신경 쓰지 마. 너 말고 옷 구경하는 거니까."

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" I LOVE it! The stitching? So meticulous! The darting? So inventive! \n"
" !shocked\n"
" And how they incorporated not just <#RED>{name.rot}</> materials but the whole VIBE of the area??\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It's... transcendent!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And I <i>never</> use that word (unless it's about <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> singing voice).\n"
" !think\n"
" What kind of lunatic could've made this?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아니.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 진짜 미쳤다! 바느질한 것 좀 봐? 엄청 정교해! 옷매무새 잡은 건 어떻고? 완전 독창적이야! \n"
" !shocked\n"
" 게다가 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 재료만 쓴 게 아니라, 그 지역의 '바이브' 자체를 완벽하게 녹여냈잖아??\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 이건... 초월적이야!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 난 <i>절대</> 이런 단어는 안 쓰는데 말이지 (<#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>의 노랫소리를 칭찬할 때 빼고는).\n"
" !think\n"
" 대체 어떤 미친 천재가 이걸 만든 거야?"

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_DESC
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_DESC"
msgid "Well, he's a pink-haired {name.species_ogre} with a serious attitude problem."
msgstr "음, 분홍 머리 {name.species_ogre}인데 성격에 큰 문제 있는 타입이야."

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_SWOON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_SWOON"
msgid "He's broody, mysterious, talks like a medieval knight... <i>(sigh)</>."
msgstr "음침하고, 신비롭고, 말투는 중세 기사 같고... <i>(한숨)</>."

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE"
msgid "Oh, just this little place I know. 'Le Chateau d'Alphonse.' Do you like it?"
msgstr "아, 내가 아는 작은 곳 하나지. '르 샤토 드 알퐁스'. 어때, 마음에 들어?"

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MARKET
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MARKET"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A market. Out there. \n"
" player:\n"
" Yeah. Run by this floppy-haired guy with a <i>real</> affected way of talking.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Floppy hair? An' an affected manner o' speech, ye said?\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmph. <z 0.7>Wonder if <#BLUE>Berna</> knows...</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 시장. 저 바깥에.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그래. 말투를 <i>진짜</> 꾸며서 말하는 헝클머리 남자가 운영해.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 헝클머리에, 꾸민 말투라고 했지?\n"
" !think\n"
" 흠. <z 0.7>혹시 <#BLUE>버나</>가 아는지...</>"

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !point\n"
" No.\n"
" player:\n"
" Fine, I bought it at a market out in the wilds, from this floppy-haired guy with a <i>real</> affected way of talking."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !point\n"
" 아니.\n"
" player:\n"
" 됐어, 야생 바깥 시장에서 샀어. 말투를 <i>진짜</> 꾸며 말하는 헝클머리 남자한테서."

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MARKET
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MARKET"
msgid "I bought it at a cute little market out in the wilds. Buy local, I say."
msgstr "야생 바깥의 귀여운 작은 시장에서 샀어. 난 로컬 구매를 지지하거든."

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE"
msgid "Why? Is somebody <i>jeeeaalous</>?"
msgstr "왜? 누가 지이이이인짜 부러워하나?"

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GG_EASY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GG_EASY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ha! That's what I like to hear!\n"
" !point\n"
" You keep puttin' those moves I taught you to good use, and we'll have that <#RED>Bubble Shield</> up and running in no time flat."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 하! 그런 말 좋아!\n"
" !point\n"
" 내가 가르친 기술 계속 잘 써먹으면, <#RED>버블 실드</> 금방 가동시킬 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TERRIFIED
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TERRIFIED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Didn't think you were gonna make it?\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm. Sounds like I haven't been pushin' you hard enough. Starting now, I'm beefin' up yer training regimen!\n"
" !point\n"
" We'll start at the crack of dawn with a ten mile run, then push-ups until breakfast, and then--\n"
" player:\n"
" You know-- suddenly I'm a lot less scared of the {name_multiple.rot_boss}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" That's the spirit!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 네가 못 해낼 줄 알았다고?\n"
" !think\n"
" 흠. 내가 널 충분히 몰아붙이지 않은 모양이네. 지금부터 훈련량 확 늘린다!\n"
" !point\n"
" 새벽 댓바람부터 10마일 달리기 시작해서, 아침 먹을 때까지 팔굽혀펴기, 그리고--\n"
" player:\n"
" 있잖아-- 갑자기 {name_multiple.rot_boss}가 훨씬 덜 무섭네!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 바로 그 기세지!"

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GG_EASY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GG_EASY"
msgid "And I made it look easy, too."
msgstr "게다가 엄청 쉽게 해낸 것처럼 보였지."

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TERRIFIED
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TERRIFIED"
msgid "I-I'm still shaking... I didn't think I was gonna make it..."
msgstr "나, 나 아직도 떨려... 나 못 해낼 줄 알았어..."

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEAD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Of course not! C'mon, I'm better at rescues than that.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ... You <i>did</> get a teensy bit totally knocked out, though. Luckily, I snagged you with the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> rope claw before things got <i>too</> dicey."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 당연히 아니지! 야, 나 구조는 그것보다 훨씬 잘해.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ... 그래도 너 <i>진짜</> 거의 완전히 기절하긴 했어. 다행히 일이 <i>너무</> 위험해지기 전에 <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> 로프 클로로 널 낚아챘지."

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASTER
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASTER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I mean, I'd love to, but predicting the future is a, uh, a <i>bit</> beyond me.\n"
" !point\n"
" Remember, if you need to end your Hunt early and regroup, you can signal for me to take you back to camp at any time. No judgement.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" From me, anyway."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그러고 싶긴 한데, 미래 예측은 어, 나한텐 <i>조금</> 무리야.\n"
" !point\n"
" 기억해, 사냥을 일찍 끝내고 재정비해야겠으면 언제든 신호해. 내가 캠프로 데려다줄게. 뭐라 안 해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 적어도 나는."

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SQUAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SQUAD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Of course! It's the <#RED>{name.foxtails}</> way. So, you could have a look around, Hunter, or we could head back out. Just let me know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 당연하지! 그게 <#RED>{name.foxtails}</> 방식이니까. 그러니까 여기 좀 둘러봐도 되고, 바로 다시 나가도 돼. 말만 해."

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEAD"
msgid "Back up. Did... did I die?"
msgstr "잠깐만. 나... 나 죽은 거야?"

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASTER
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASTER"
msgid "Next time, could you grab me <i>before</> I get knocked out?"
msgstr "다음엔 내가 기절하기 <i>전에</> 좀 잡아줄 수 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SQUAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SQUAD"
msgid "I'm glad to know you have my back."
msgstr "네가 내 등을 봐준다는 걸 아니까 든든하네."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'd know the smell of those tools anywhere. <i>(sniff sniiiiiiff)</>\n"
" !think\n"
" They're still lost somewhere in the <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp_r2}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그 도구 냄새는 어디서든 알아. <i>(킁킁)</>\n"
" !think\n"
" 아직 <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp_r2}</> 어딘가에 잃어버린 채로 있어."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Wow. Good nose. Don't worry, I'll find them!"
msgstr "와, 코 좋네. 걱정 마, 내가 찾아올게!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Wh-- how did you know?!"
msgstr "뭐-- 어떻게 알았어?!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" Haven't found my <#RED>{name.farmtools}</> yet?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" 내 <#RED>{name.farmtools}</> 아직 못 찾았어?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} ...Ick. Still covered in <#RED>{name.totolili}</> glop.\n"
" !think\n"
" Okay. Use my tools to take care of your garden. Pick a <#RED>Plot</> and start planting <#RED>Seeds</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" I got rid of the weeds. Everyone gets their own <#RED>Plot</>. Don't be greedy. Keep to your own. Simpler that way. \n"
" player:\n"
" Noted, I'll keep my paws off of other folks' plots.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Good. Take these <#RED>Seeds</> I found in my shoe. There's lots more out in the wilds."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} ...으. 아직도 <#RED>{name.totolili}</> 끈적이로 덮여 있네.\n"
" !think\n"
" 좋아. 내 도구로 네 정원 관리해. <#RED>구획</> 하나 골라서 <#RED>씨앗</> 심기 시작해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 잡초는 내가 치웠어. 각자 자기 <#RED>구획</>이 있어. 욕심부리지 마. 자기 것만 써. 그게 더 단순해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 알겠어, 남의 구획엔 손 안 댈게.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 좋아. 내 신발에서 찾은 <#RED>씨앗</> 가져가. 야생에는 더 많이 있어."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Oh, okay. Thanks, {name.npc_apothecary}!"
msgstr "아, 알겠어. 고마워, {name.npc_apothecary}!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I found your {name.farmtools}!"
msgstr "네 {name.farmtools} 찾았어!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're back?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 돌아왔네?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...<#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" So. 'Hunter'. You hunt the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You don't... <i>eat</> them, do you?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...<#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래서. '헌터'. 넌 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>를 사냥해?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 설마... 그걸 <i>먹진</> 않지?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh. Where do you get your food?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아. 그럼 먹을 건 어디서 구해?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I <i>knew</> it. That's why you smell weird. Don't you have any normal food?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 내 <i>그럴 줄</> 알았어. 그래서 네 냄새가 이상했구나. 평범한 음식은 없어?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 'Stale'? That's gross. You need a garden. Fresh food is best. It'd clear up your skin, too.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" If I had my <#RED>{name.farmtools}</>, I'd teach you to grow plants. But a <#RED>{name.totolili}</> took them. You know. Dangly arms? Big leaf hat they toss around? Jerks?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I was looking for them when you found me. Probably still in the <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp_r2}</> somewhere...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.farmtools}, huh? I'll keep an eye out for them!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" '눅눅하다'고? 으, 더러워. 넌 정원이 필요해. 신선한 음식이 최고야. 피부도 좋아질걸.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 내 <#RED>{name.farmtools}</>만 있으면 식물 기르는 법 가르쳐줄 텐데. 근데 <#RED>{name.totolili}</>가 그걸 가져갔어. 알지. 축 늘어진 팔? 휙휙 던지는 큰 잎사귀 모자? 진상들?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 네가 날 찾았을 때도 그거 찾고 있었어. 아마 아직도 <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp_r2}</> 어딘가에 있을 거야...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.farmtools} 말이지? 눈여겨볼게!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "You came! Welcome! Say, I forgot to ask, what's your name?"
msgstr "왔네! 반가워! 그러고 보니 못 물어봤다, 이름이 뭐야?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "What?! No!!"
msgstr "뭐?! 아니!!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Oh, I might've taken a nibble once or twice..."
msgstr "어, 한두 번 정도는 조금 베어 먹었을지도..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "We brought some food from the Brinks. It's a little stale, but there's enough to go around."
msgstr "브링크스에서 음식 좀 가져왔어. 좀 눅눅하긴 한데, 다 같이 먹기엔 충분해."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Oh. It's you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" 아. 너구나."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'm glad to see you're in one piece.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And I really wanna make sure you stay that way with some <#RED>Armour Upgrades</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Thing is... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>... he's got some trust issues.\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:dummy] I'll work on him, but in the meantime, change up your equipment with the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> over there!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 무사한 모습 보니까 좋네.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 <#RED>방어구 업그레이드</>로 네가 계속 그렇게 무사하게 지내게 하고 싶고.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 근데... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>... 걔가 사람을 좀 못 믿어.\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:dummy] 내가 걔를 설득해볼게. 그동안은 저기 <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>에서 장비를 바꿔 써!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BESTFRIEND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BESTFRIEND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" It's <i>what?</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>뭐라고?</>"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_IMPORTANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_IMPORTANT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Agreed! You'd be surprised how many people are rude about it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 맞아! 이걸로 무례하게 구는 사람이 얼마나 많은지 놀랄걸."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_WEIRD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_WEIRD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe. But I'd rather be weird with my best buddy than normal without him!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그럴 수도 있지. 그래도 난 걔 없이 평범한 것보다, 베프랑 같이 이상한 쪽이 좋아!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HOLDINGYOUBACK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HOLDINGYOUBACK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>You</> try <#RED>upgrading armour</> without your number one friend/slashing tool!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And it's nothing personal! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> just not great with new people...\n"
" !think\n"
" But maybe gifting him a little <#RED>souvenir</> from your Hunts would help? To show you care and the like.\n"
" !neutral"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>너</>도 네 최고의 친구이자 절단 도구 없이 <#RED>방어구 업그레이드</> 해봐!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그리고 개인적인 감정은 아니야! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>이 낯선 사람을 좀 어려워해서...\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래도 네 사냥에서 나온 작은 <#RED>기념품</> 하나 선물하면 도움이 될지도? 네가 신경 쓴다는 걸 보여주는 거지.\n"
" !neutral"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LUNN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LUNN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" My leather cutter, obviously. He's my best buddy."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 내 가죽 재단 칼이지, 당연히. 걔가 내 베스트 버디야."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_OPT"
msgid "Uhh... It was nice to meet you properly!"
msgstr "어... 제대로 인사해서 반가웠어!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" You too!\n"
" !think\n"
" ...I hope I didn't miss anything juicy while I was away."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 나도!\n"
" !think\n"
" ...내가 없는 사이에 재밌는 거 안 놓쳤으면 좋겠네."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT"
msgid "No problem. It was nice to meet you--both!"
msgstr "문제 없어. 둘 다 만나서 반가웠어!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" You too! Say bye, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>!\n"
" ...\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Did you lose your <i>manners</> in the wilds, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? Yeesh..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 너도! 인사해, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>!\n"
" ...\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 야생에서 <i>예의</>를 잃어버렸냐, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? 아이고..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Glad to see you settling in!"
msgstr "잘 적응하는 것 같아 보여서 좋네!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BESTFRIEND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BESTFRIEND"
msgid "Your best friend is a leatherworking tool? That's--"
msgstr "네 베프가 가죽 공예 도구라고? 그건--"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_IMPORTANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_IMPORTANT"
msgid "It's great! Friends are important."
msgstr "좋은데! 친구는 중요하지."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_WEIRD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_WEIRD"
msgid "Um... It's a <i>little</> weird?"
msgstr "음... <i>조금</> 이상한데?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HOLDINGYOUBACK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HOLDINGYOUBACK"
msgid "So it's {name.npc_lunn} who won't let <i>you</> upgrade my armour?"
msgstr "그럼 {name.npc_lunn}이 <i>네가</> 내 방어구 업그레이드 못 하게 하는 거야?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LUNN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LUNN"
msgid "Wait, who's {name.npc_lunn}?"
msgstr "잠깐, {name.npc_lunn}이 누구야?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Heya, Hunter! Thanks for the ride to camp."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 안녕, 헌터! 캠프까지 태워줘서 고마워."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE"
msgid "Dressing for Battle"
msgstr "전투 복장"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ye know ye scream with yer eyes, don't ye? Yer doin' it right now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 눈으로 비명 지르는 거 아냐? 지금도 그러고 있잖아."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" ...\"tough,\" ay?\n"
" !point\n"
" I see ye've got the {name.weapon_polearm} an' the {name.weapon_hammer}. Fine weapons, both. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" But, with a bit o' <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</> for th'forge, I'll smithy whatever prototype ye fancy in the <#RED>Weapon Racks</> o'er there. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</> fer new weapons. Deal? Deal."
msgstr "!dubious\n"
" ...\"터프하다,\" 이거지?\n"
" !point\n"
" {name.weapon_polearm}랑 {name.weapon_hammer}를 들고 있군. 둘 다 좋은 무기야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 하지만 대장간용 <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</>만 좀 가져오면, 저기 <#RED>무기 거치대</>에서 네가 원하는 프로토타입은 뭐든 만들어주지.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</>로 새 무기 만들자. 거래 성립? 성립."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_UPGRADES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_UPGRADES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Och, that service there's reserved for <i>true</> Hunters.  \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ye've got ta convince me ye'll do more than drown the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in yer salty tears.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ... Been taken advantage of by unworthy types before, see. \n"
" !point\t\t\n"
" So fetch me a <#RED>souvenir</> from yer Hunt--proof of yer bona fides--an' I'll start upgradin' yer weapons.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Deal? Deal."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래, 그 서비스는 <i>진짜</> 헌터에게만 열려 있어.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 네가 눈물로 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</2>를 적시는 것 말고도 할 줄 안다는 걸 나한테 증명해야 해.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...전에 자격 없는 것들한테 이용당한 적이 있거든.\n"
" !point\t\t\n"
" 그러니 네 사냥에서 <#RED>기념품</3> 하나 가져와. 네 실력의 증거 말이야. 그럼 무기를 강화해 주지.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 동의하지? 좋아."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT"
msgid "Your personality is A+, {name.npc_blacksmith}."
msgstr "성격 점수 A+네, {name.npc_blacksmith}."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Did you notice? I didn't scream <i>once</> on the ride back. I'm brave."
msgstr "봤어? 돌아오는 길에 <i>한 번도</> 안 질렀어. 나 용감하지."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Nuh-uh. They're shouting about how tough I am."
msgstr "아니거든. 내가 얼마나 터프한지 외치고 있는 거거든."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_UPGRADES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_UPGRADES"
msgid "What about <i>upgrading</> my weapons?"
msgstr "내 무기 <i>강화</>는?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Hmph..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" 흥..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE"
msgid "Hammer Home"
msgstr "망치의 핵심"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Howdy Hunter!\n"
" [recipe:unlock_recipe] Aw shucks, looks like you still haven't found everythin' I need to get cookin'. Oh well!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 안녕, 헌터!\n"
" [recipe:unlock_recipe] 아이쿠, 요리 시작하려면 필요한 걸 아직 다 못 찾았네. 뭐, 어쩔 수 없지!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well howdy, Hunter! What's got you so excited?\n"
" player:\n"
" I brought all the ingredients you asked for!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" W-well so you have! I can hardly believe my eyes!\n"
" player:\n"
" So, what's on the menu?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Well, see now here's the thing--um... it's a mite embarrassin', but I lost somethin' out there in the wilds while foragin' fer ingredients, as we {name.job_cook}s do.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" My... lucky <#RED>{name.cookingtools}</>. My dear old Ma gave it to me--it's a treasured family heirloom, passed down through generations.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Without it, I just don't know that I've got the heart for cookin' anything.\n"
" player:\n"
" Don't worry, I'll find it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh what a sweetheart you are, Hunter! I'd be much obliged!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 어이쿠, 안녕 헌터! 뭐가 그렇게 신났어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 부탁한 재료 전부 가져왔어!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 저, 정말이네! 내 눈을 못 믿겠어!\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 메뉴는 뭐야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 음, 그러니까 말이지--어... 좀 창피한데, 우리가 {name.job_cook} 하는 것처럼 재료 채집하러 나갔다가 야생에서 뭘 잃어버렸어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 내... 행운의 <#RED>{name.cookingtools}</> 말이야. 돌아가신 엄마가 주신 건데--대대로 내려온 소중한 가보야.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 그게 없으니까, 뭘 요리할 마음이 도무지 안 나.\n"
" player:\n"
" 걱정 마, 내가 찾아올게!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아이고, 정말 다정하구나 헌터! 그러면 정말 고맙지!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Aww, that's a darn shame!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'm <i>sure</> it's out there somewhere, though. Not like I'd make somethin' like that up! Ha-ha!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 그거 참 안됐네!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그래도 <i>분명</> 어딘가에 있을 거야. 내가 그런 걸 지어낼 리 없잖아! 하하!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll keep looking!"
msgstr "걱정 마, 계속 찾아볼게!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I still haven't found your lucky {name.cookingtools}..."
msgstr "아직 네 행운의 {name.cookingtools} 못 찾았어..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Howdy Hunter! Why the long face?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 안녕, 사냥꾼! 왜 그렇게 풀이 죽었어?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Eggs? Oh! Well, y'know what they say! Um... if yer eggs ain't, um, when danger's not eggs... That ain't it... hold on... \n"
" !think\n"
" If you ain't got your eggs while in peril, you might as well cook 'em...fer...yer Aunt Carol. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Hoo-whee! That's the sayin'! No further questions 'bout it!\n"
" !point\n"
" Now if you wanna go over by that there cookin' pot, I'll getcha a menu! <z 0.7>I'm <i>pretty</> sure I saw a menu around here somewhere...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just point at what you want and I'll get it packed up in yer <#RED>{name.lunchbox}</> all nice for your Hunt!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 달걀? 아! 있잖아, 그런 말! 음... 달걀이 없으면, 어... 위험할 때 달걀이 아니면... 그게 아닌데... 잠깐만...\n"
" !think\n"
" 위험할 때 달걀이 없으면 그냥... 요리해서... 캐럴 이모한테... \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 허어! 맞아, 그 속담이야! 더 묻진 마!\n"
" !point\n"
" 이제 저기 요리 냄비 쪽으로 가면 내가 메뉴 가져다줄게! <z 0.7>난 <i>꽤</> 이 근처에서 메뉴를 본 것 같아...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 원하는 거 가리키기만 해, 그럼 네 <#RED>{name.lunchbox}</>에 사냥 가기 좋게 깔끔하게 싸줄게!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Eggs? O-oh! Don't trouble your pretty little head none, hun! I'm over eggs. Over easy! I'm easy. I don't need eggs is what I mean.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Now if you wanna go over by that there cookin' pot, I'll getcha a menu! <z 0.7>I'm <i>pretty</> sure I saw a menu around here somewhere...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just point out what you want and I'll get it packed up all nice for your Hunt!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 달걀? 어, 어! 그런 건 네 예쁜 머리로 고민 안 해도 돼, 얘야! 나 달걀은 이제 괜찮아. 반숙처럼! 난 쉬운 사람이야. 그러니까 내 말은 달걀 필요 없다는 거야.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 이제 저기 요리 냄비 쪽으로 가면 내가 메뉴 가져다줄게! <z 0.7>난 <i>꽤</> 이 근처에서 메뉴를 본 것 같아...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 원하는 거 짚어만 줘, 사냥 가기 좋게 깔끔하게 싸줄게!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Thanks, {name.npc_cook}!"
msgstr "고마워, {name.npc_cook}!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Found it in {name.eggzy}'s lair! Dangerous place to forage for eggs, {name.npc_cook}..."
msgstr "{name.eggzy} 소굴에서 찾았어! 달걀 구하기엔 위험한 곳이더라, {name.npc_cook}..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Found it in {name.eggzy}'s lair! Sorry, I didn't bring any eggs back."
msgstr "{name.eggzy} 소굴에서 찾았어! 미안, 달걀은 못 가져왔어."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh! Howdy Hunter, back already?\n"
" player:\n"
" I found your {name.cookingtools}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" What?! How did you-- \n"
" !bliss\n"
" Erm, I mean, <i>hoo-whee!</> I can't scarcely believe it! Like, at all!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 오! 사냥꾼, 벌써 돌아왔어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 네 {name.cookingtools} 찾았어!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 뭐?! 그걸 어떻게-- \n"
" !bliss\n"
" 어, 그러니까, <i>허어!</> 진짜 도무지 믿기지가 않네! 정말로!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh just swell, don't you worry your little head about me!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아, 난 아주 잘 지내니까 내 걱정은 하지 마!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ah... well, y'see, here's the thing... I can't cook if I don't have some ingredients to work with.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Why, to make anythin' decent I'd need, um... a <#RED>Squash</>, some <#RED>Berries</>, maybe some <#RED>Beans</>, and... let's see, um... some sorta <#RED>Fruit</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now if I had those, I could whip up somethin' great! Doubt you'll find anythin' like that way out here, though."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아... 그러니까, 이게 말이지... 재료가 없으면 요리를 못 해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 뭔가 제대로 만들려면, 음... <#RED>호박</> 하나, <#RED>열매</> 좀, <#RED>콩</>도 좀, 그리고... 어디 보자, <#RED>과일</> 종류가 좀 필요해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그것들만 있으면 끝내주게 만들 수 있어! 근데 이런 곳에선 그런 걸 찾기 힘들 거야."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Really? Err, great!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 정말? 어, 좋아!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wh-what?! That's--! Um... w-well I can hardly believe my eyes!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 뭐, 뭐라고?! 그건--! 어... 내 눈을 못 믿겠네!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Well, see now here's the thing--um... it's a mite embarrassin', but I realized I lost somethin' out there in the wilds.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" My... lucky <#RED>Cooking Spoon</>. My dear old Ma gave it to me--it's a treasured family heirloom, passed down through generations.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Without it, I just don't know that I've got the heart for cookin' anything."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 있지, 그게 말이야--음... 좀 창피한데, 야생에서 뭘 잃어버린 걸 알게 됐어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 내... 행운의 <#RED>요리 숟가락</>. 돌아가신 엄마가 준 건데--대대로 내려온 소중한 가보야.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 그게 없으면, 도무지 뭘 요리할 마음이 안 나."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh what a sweetheart you are, Hunter! I'd be much obliged!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 사냥꾼, 너 진짜 다정하네! 정말 고마워!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How are you settling in?"
msgstr "여기엔 좀 적응했어?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "I can't wait to try your cooking!"
msgstr "네 요리 빨리 먹어보고 싶어!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "I don't have it now, but I have an idea..."
msgstr "지금 가진 건 없지만, 방법은 있어..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Actually, I have those exact things on me now!"
msgstr "사실 그거 딱 지금 가지고 있어!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "So, what's on the menu?"
msgstr "그래서, 메뉴는 뭐야?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll find it!"
msgstr "걱정 마, 내가 찾아올게!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You've sure got a nice little setup here, real homey!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 여기 아늑하게 잘 꾸며놨네, 진짜 집 같아!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE"
msgid "Get Cooking"
msgstr "요리 시작"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" Want me to make an <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Give the materials to the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> and I'll get started."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"<#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>를 만들어볼까?\n"
"!happy\n"
"!clap\n"
"[recipe:fortify_recipe] <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</1>에 재료를 넣으면 시작할게."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oooooh, that's gotta be the most beautiful <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</> I've ever seen!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, but um... could you hold onto it while I'm not doing upgrades?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I think <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> might be a little jealous... I don't want him to feel like he's getting replaced!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 우와아, 내가 본 <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</> 중에 제일 예쁜데!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 그런데 음... 내가 강화 안 할 때는 네가 그거 들고 있어줄래?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>이 좀 질투할지도 몰라... 자기가 대체되는 기분 들게 하고 싶진 않아!"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" I checked the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>, but you haven't dropped off my materials.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] I need these to make the <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"<#RED>무기고</>를 확인했는데 재료를 안 가져왔더라.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!dubious\n"
"[recipe:fortify_recipe] <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</1>를 만들려면 이게 필요해."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ah!! Look at that <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>-- isn't it just <i>everything?!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" But uhh, do you think you could you hold onto it between upgrades?\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> is still feeling a bit sensitive about the whole 'new tools' thing."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 아!! 저 <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</> 좀 봐-- 그냥 <i>완벽</>하지 않아?!\n"
" !think\n"
" 근데 어... 강화 사이사이에는 네가 그거 들고 있어줄 수 있어?\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>이 아직 '새 도구' 얘기에 좀 예민하거든."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Anyways! If you want those upgrades, I'm gonna need an <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Which means you've gotta bring back the stuff I need to make it.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Then I'll be able to upgrade <i>all</> of your armour to <#RED>Level {max_upgrade}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아무튼! 그 강화 하려면 <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>가 필요해.\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] 그러니까 그걸 만들 재료를 네가 가져와야 해.\n"
" !clap\n"
" 그러면 네 방어구 <i>전부</>를 <#RED>레벨 {max_upgrade}</>까지 강화할 수 있어!"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Bring back materials. Okay!"
msgstr "재료 가져올게. 알겠어!"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "How can I help?"
msgstr "내가 뭐 도우면 돼?"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did ye get me the goods for them <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Put 'em in a <#RED>Weapon Rack</> and I'll get ta hammerin'."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</> 만들 재료, 가져왔나?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] <#RED>무기 거치대</>에 넣어두면 내가 망치질 시작하지."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Aye. A fine set o' <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>, indeed.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well. Enough bletherin'.\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's get yer weapons up ta snuff, ay?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그래. <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</> 세트, 아주 훌륭하군.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 됐어, 말은 여기까지.\n"
" !point\n"
" 네 무기들 제대로 손봐주자고, 어때?"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Got all the goods already?\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Put 'em in a <#RED>Weapon Rack</> and I'll make the <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 재료는 다 모았나?\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] <#RED>무기 거치대</>에 넣어두면 <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</> 만들어주지."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ah. Those <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</> are a thing o' beauty.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Let's get ta work on those weapons o' yers, ay?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 아. 저 <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>, 참 멋지군.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 네 무기 작업 시작하자, 어때?"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] I'll need materials. Which means you'll have ta source the goods.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I get new tools, and ye'll be able ta upgrade all yer weapons ta <#RED>Level {max_upgrade}</>. Seems like a good deal ta me."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] 재료가 필요해. 그러니까 자네가 구해와야 해.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 내가 새 도구를 받으면, 자네는 무기 전부를 <#RED>레벨 {max_upgrade}</>까지 강화할 수 있지. 내 보기엔 괜찮은 거래야."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "How can I help?"
msgstr "내가 뭐 도우면 돼?"

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" No, no, no. It's my Grandpa's notes, his discoveries...\n"
" !point\n"
" But all of that is just theory without <i>you!</> You made this all <i>real,</> Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thank you. Truly... this means everything."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아니, 아니, 아니. 이건 우리 할아버지 노트랑 그분의 발견이야...\n"
" !point\n"
" 근데 <i>네가</> 없었으면 그건 다 이론일 뿐이었어! 네가 이걸 전부 <i>현실로</> 만들었어, 사냥꾼.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 고마워. 진심으로... 내겐 전부야."

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You're one-of-a-kind. No doubt about it.\n"
" !point\n"
" Well, we've all waited long enough! Go put that last <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> and let's get our home back!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 넌 진짜 세상에 하나뿐이야. 의심할 여지도 없어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 자, 우리 충분히 오래 기다렸어! 마지막 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>를 우리가 개조한 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>에 넣고 우리 집을 되찾자!"

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2A"
msgid "Thanks, Flitt, but I did it for everyone back in the Brinks."
msgstr "고마워, 플릿. 근데 이건 브링크스에 있는 모두를 위해 한 거야."

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2B"
msgid "Y'know what? Yeah! I <i>am</> all that, Flitteroonie! Booyow!"
msgstr "있잖아? 맞아! 나 <i>맞아</>, 그 정도 되는 사람이지, 플리터루니! 부야!"

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "All thanks to that big brain of yours."
msgstr "다 네 그 똑똑한 머리 덕분이야."

#: Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" EEEP! Were--were <i>you</> just eavesdropping on <i>me</>...?\n"
" !think\n"
" Huh. It's really not so fun being on the other side of that.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Fine, yes, I was fan girling about <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> a <i>little</> bit.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" So like, if you find yourself on a <#RED>{name.run_ascension}</>, you might as well swing by the <#BLUE>Marketplace</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Make sure he's still alive or whatever.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Or don't. It doesn't really matter to me!\n"
" !scared\n"
" Please don't tell him I care so much but please check because I care SO much.\n"
" player:\n"
" Okay...?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 끼익! 너--너 방금 <i>너</>가 <i>나</> 엿들은 거야...?\n"
" !think\n"
" 흠. 그거 반대 입장이 되어보니까 진짜 하나도 안 재밌네.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 좋아, 맞아, 나 <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> 얘기에 <i>조금</> 팬질했어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그러니까, <#RED>{name.run_ascension}</> 쪽에 가게 되면 <#BLUE>시장</>에 들러.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 걔 아직 살아 있는지만 확인해 줘, 뭐 그런 거.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아니, 안 해도 돼. 나한텐 별로 안 중요하니까!\n"
" !scared\n"
" 내가 이렇게 신경 쓴다고는 걔한테 절대 말하지 말고, 근데 꼭 확인해 줘. 내가 진짜 엄청 신경 쓰니까.\n"
" player:\n"
" 알겠지...?"

#: Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT"
msgid "Are you talking about {name.npc_market_merchant}?"
msgstr "{name.npc_market_merchant} 얘기하는 거야?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} What are you carrying? It smells like the wilds. It doesn't <i>look</> like the wilds.\n"
" player:\n"
" It's a souvenir from my Hunt! Wrapped up all nice-like. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Sou-ve-nir...? Hm. Do I--? What is--? I don't know--\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry, I didn't mean to make you uncomfortable. Should I take it back?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} Smelly box in paper, mine!\n"
" !think\n"
" You can use the <#RED>{name.i_seed_grinder}</>. If you want. I just fixed it up. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I'm done talking now. Bye."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} 뭐 들고 있어? 냄새는 야생 냄새인데 <i>보기엔</> 야생 같지 않아.\n"
" player:\n"
" 내 사냥에서 가져온 기념품이야! 예쁘게 포장해 뒀고. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 기-념-품...? 흠. 내가--? 그게--? 모르겠어--\n"
" player:\n"
" 미안, 불편하게 하려던 건 아니야. 다시 가져갈까?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} 종이에 싼 냄새나는 상자, 내 거!\n"
" !think\n"
" 원하면 <#RED>{name.i_seed_grinder}</> 써도 돼. 방금 고쳐 놨어. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 이제 말 끝. 잘 가."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}  'Souvenir'... 'Wrapped up all nice-like'...\n"
" !think\n"
" Six sides. Red petals on top. It's like a square flower. \n"
" !agree\n"
" It's pretty. I'll keep it.\n"
" player:\n"
" You're... welcome?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Okay."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}  '기념품'... '예쁘게 포장해 뒀고'...\n"
" !think\n"
" 여섯 면. 위엔 빨간 꽃잎. 네모난 꽃 같아. \n"
" !agree\n"
" 예쁘네. 간직할게.\n"
" player:\n"
" 천만에...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그래."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 'Souvenir'! Gimme!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Another square flower. I will add it to the others.\n"
" player:\n"
" 'Others'? You haven't opened any of wrapped presents?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...<i>'Opened'?</>\n"
" player:\n"
" You know, tear off the paper and see what's inside? I'll help--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} Don't touch my square flower!\n"
" !agree\n"
" It's weird. It smells like home. I like it.\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, that's... nice. But the <i>intent</> is for the gift to be opened. It's what's inside that matters.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I don't live in tents. \n"
" !think\n"
" ... but I'll think about it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" '기념품'! 줘!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 또 네모 꽃이네. 다른 것들 옆에 둘게.\n"
" player:\n"
" '다른 것들'? 포장된 선물은 하나도 안 뜯어봤어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...<i>'뜯어봤어'?</>\n"
" player:\n"
" 있잖아, 종이를 찢고 안에 뭐 들었는지 보는 거? 내가 도와줄--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} 내 네모 꽃 만지지 마!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 이상해. 고향 냄새가 나. 좋아.\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, 그건... 좋네. 근데 선물의 <i>intent</>는 뜯어보는 거야. 중요한 건 안에 든 거고.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 난 텐트에서 안 살아. \n"
" !think\n"
" ... 그래도 생각은 해볼게."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Hee-hee... weird."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 히히... 이상해."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Then why are you sweating so much?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} And why does it smell like <i>that?</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} 그럼 왜 그렇게 땀을 흘려?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} 그리고 왜 <i>그런</> 냄새가 나?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...I've decided. This one will be opened. NOW!\n"
" !angry\n"
" GRR-AAAAAH!!\n"
" player:\n"
" That's impressive--I've never seen someone unwrap a box with their teeth.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ... Was I weird?\n"
" player:\n"
" There's nothing wrong with a little weirdness. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Are <i>you</> weird?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...결심했어. 이건 뜯는다. 지금!\n"
" !angry\n"
" 크르르아아아!!\n"
" player:\n"
" 대단한데--이를로 상자를 뜯는 건 처음 봐.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ... 나 이상했어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 좀 이상해도 문제없어. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <i>너</>도 이상해?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Oh, sure! <z 0.7>Y'know, sometimes, when no one's looking, I'll lick a {name.konjur} crystals. They taste <i>tingly</>.</>"
msgstr "아, 그럼! <z 0.7>있잖아, 가끔 아무도 안 볼 때 {name.konjur}수정을 핥아. 맛이 <i>찌릿찌릿</>해.</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Why, I've never done a single weird thing in my life!"
msgstr "아니, 난 살면서 이상한 짓 한 번도 안 해봤어!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Granny taught me that. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" She was glad to return her life to the Wilds so new life could take root.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I like the bird house. Take this. I found it.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 할머니가 그거 가르쳐줬어. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 새 생명이 뿌리내리게 하려고 자기 삶을 야생지로 돌려보내는 걸 기뻐하셨어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 새집 좋아. 이거 가져. 내가 찾았어.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" She was glad to return her life to the Wilds so new life could take root.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" When I'm there, she's all around me. The wind, the leaves, the birdsong...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I like the bird house. Take this. I found it.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 새 생명이 뿌리내리게 하려고 자기 삶을 야생지로 돌려보내는 걸 기뻐하셨어.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 거기 있으면 할머니가 내 주위에 다 있어. 바람, 나뭇잎, 새소리...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 새집 좋아. 이거 가져. 내가 찾았어.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} I know what this is. \n"
" player:\n"
" Even without unwrapping it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's a bird house. Granny and I, we hung them in the trees around our hut.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" We'd watch the birds come and go for hours.\n"
" player:\n"
" I didn't know you have a Granny! Is she okay by herself? We could go check up on her.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I don't see why. She's been dead a couple years now.\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Sorry, I didn't realize...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't be sad. Things are born. Then they die. Then new things are born. Nothing to be sad about."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} 이게 뭔지 알아. \n"
" player:\n"
" 안 뜯어봐도?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 새집이야. 할머니랑 나는 우리 오두막 주변 나무들에 그걸 달았어.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 새들이 왔다 갔다 하는 걸 몇 시간씩 봤지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 너한테 할머니가 있는 줄 몰랐어! 혼자 괜찮아? 우리가 가서 봐드릴 수도 있는데.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 왜 그래야 하는지 모르겠는데. 돌아가신 지 벌써 몇 년 됐어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 아! 미안, 몰랐어...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 슬퍼하지 마. 태어나고, 죽고, 또 새로운 게 태어나. 슬퍼할 일 아니야."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Hm. I guess that's true."
msgstr "흠. 그러고 보니 맞는 말이네."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "That seems a little cold..."
msgstr "좀 냉정하게 들리는데..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I know. Hunters use weird magic. Doesn't work on you.\n"
" player:\n"
" Why are you practicing becoming invisible?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 알아. 사냥꾼들은 이상한 마법을 써. 너한텐 안 통해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 왜 투명해지는 연습을 해?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Even more so because it worked on you. \n"
" !point\n"
" Hunters use weird magic. Hard to fool you. Taken a lot of practice.\n"
" player:\n"
" Why are you practicing becoming invisible?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 너한텐 먹혔으니까 더 그렇지. \n"
" !point\n"
" 사냥꾼들은 이상한 마법을 써. 널 속이기 어렵더라. 연습 많이 했어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 왜 투명해지는 연습을 해?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... {name.npc_apothecary}? I brought you a souvenir...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hunter! I'm right here.\n"
" player:\n"
" What... were you doing just now?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I was practicing being invisible. I'm getting better at it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" player:\n"
" 음... {name.npc_apothecary}? 기념품 가져왔어...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 사냥꾼! 나 여기 있어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐... 방금 뭐 하고 있었어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 투명해지는 연습하고 있었어. 점점 나아지고 있어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Camouflage. For when I'm under threat.\n"
" player:\n"
" You're safe here, though. Unless there's something at camp that scares you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... no. Back to practicing. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7>And I'm gone.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 위장. 위협받을 때를 대비해서.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그래도 여기선 안전하잖아. 캠프에 널 무섭게 하는 게 있어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... 없어. 다시 연습할래. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7>그리고 난 사라졌다.</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "But you weren't invisible. I could see you the whole time."
msgstr "근데 안 투명했어. 난 계속 널 볼 수 있었어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Oh, uh, wow! That's... impressive!"
msgstr "어, 어... 와! 그거... 대단한데!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The squareness of this gift... reminds me of something.. Oh.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" My hut in the wilds.  \n"
" player:\n"
" Do you feel like telling me about it? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Granny built it. So she could live far from everyone else. She liked to be alone.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then someone left me on her doorstep. As a baby. \n"
" player:\n"
" Wow, really?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} No interrupting with disbelief!\n"
" player:\n"
" U-understood. Please. Go on.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" She taught me about the Wilds. How to garden. How to deal with <#RED>{name.rot}</>. How to everything. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" One day, there was a rumbling, and after that, more <#RED>{name.rot}</>. <i>Meaner</> <#RED>{name.rot}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" A few years later, we met an old Hunter--like you, but good skin. Told us about the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>. The evacuation. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" The old Hunter stayed, helped with the <#RED>{name.rot}</> problem. I was mad. Didn't think we needed her. Or anyone. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Then we lost her.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Then I lost Granny.\n"
" !point\n"
" Then you found me.\n"
" ...\n"
" You can talk now.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wow, {name.npc_apothecary}. You've been alone for so long. <z 0.7>And I don't think my skin is <i>that</> bad...</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Before the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>, Granny said I should have 'friends' my age. Talked about a school in town...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I didn't want to go. I ran away. She found me. She didn't make me go.\n"
" !think\n"
" ... Maybe I should've been braver.\n"
" Okay, bye.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 이 선물의 네모난 모양... 뭔가 떠오르게 하네.. 아.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 야생지대에 있던 내 오두막.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그 얘기 들어볼래?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 할머니가 지었어. 다른 사람들한테서 멀리 떨어져 살려고. 혼자 있는 걸 좋아했거든.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그러다 누가 날 할머니 문앞에 두고 갔어. 갓난아기였을 때.\n"
" player:\n"
" 와, 진짜?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} 못 믿겠다는 식으로 끼어들지 마!\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, 알겠어. 제발. 계속해.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 할머니가 야생지대에 대해 가르쳐줬어. 정원 가꾸는 법. <#RED>{name.rot}</> 상대하는 법. 온갖 걸 다.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 어느 날 땅울림이 있었고, 그 뒤로 <#RED>{name.rot}</>가 더 많아졌어. <i>더 사나운</> <#RED>{name.rot}</>도.\n"
" !think\n"
" 몇 년 뒤에 늙은 헌터를 만났어--너랑 비슷한데 피부는 멀쩡한. 저 녀석이 <#KONJUR>대폭발</> 얘기를 해줬어. 대피 얘기도.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그 늙은 헌터는 남아서 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 문제를 도와줬어. 난 화가 났지. 우리한텐 저 녀석도 필요 없다고 생각했어. 누구도.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그러다 저 녀석을 잃었어.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 그리고 할머니도 잃었어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그리고 네가 날 찾았어.\n"
" ...\n"
" 이제 말해도 돼.\n"
" player:\n"
" 와, {name.npc_apothecary}. 너 정말 오랫동안 혼자였구나. <z 0.7>그리고 내 피부도 <i>그렇게</> 나쁜 건 아닌 것 같은데...</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#KONJUR>대폭발</> 전에, 할머니가 내 또래 '친구'가 있어야 한다고 했어. 마을 학교 얘기도 했고...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 가고 싶지 않았어. 도망쳤지. 할머니가 날 찾았고. 억지로 보내진 않았어.\n"
" !think\n"
" ... 내가 좀 더 용감했어야 했나 봐.\n"
" 그럼, 가볼게.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Oh. Weird question, I guess. \n"
" player:\n"
" I was just joking, {name.npc_apothecary}. You know that <i>you're</> my friend, right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I am?? \n"
" player:\n"
" Of course! We share stories, you taught me to garden... You're a tough nut to crack, maybe, but inside--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --is a seed! That grows into a me-plant!\n"
" player:\n"
" Eeeeexactly what I was going to say! And who doesn't want a you-plant?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Someone who likes <i>stale</> people. And stale food. Gross.\n"
" player:\n"
" Gross! Stale people? Pee-ew!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 아. 좀 이상한 질문이긴 하네.\n"
" player:\n"
" 농담이었어, {name.npc_apothecary}. <i>네가</> 내 친구인 거 알지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 내가??\n"
" player:\n"
" 당연하지! 우리 서로 이야기 나누고, 넌 나한테 정원 가꾸는 법도 알려줬잖아... 겉은 좀 까칠할지 몰라도, 속은--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --씨앗이 있어! 그게 자라서 나-식물이 되지!\n"
" player:\n"
" 바로오오 그 말 하려던 참이었어! 그리고 누가 너-식물 싫어하겠어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <i>퀴퀴한</> 사람 좋아하는 사람. 그리고 상한 음식도. 역겨워.\n"
" player:\n"
" 으, 역겨워! 퀴퀴한 사람이라니? 웩!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Because I'm rude. Because I'm weird. Because I don't give square flowers. \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh I was just kidding, {name.npc_apothecary}. You're a tough nut to crack, maybe, but inside--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --is a seed! That grows into a me-plant!\n"
" player:\n"
" Eeeeexactly what I was going to say! And who doesn't want a you-plant?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Someone who likes <i>stale</> people. And stale food. Gross.\n"
" player:\n"
" Gross! Stale people? Pee-ew!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 내가 무례해서. 내가 이상해서. 네모 꽃을 안 줘서.\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, 농담이었어, {name.npc_apothecary}. 겉은 좀 까칠할지 몰라도, 속은--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --씨앗이 있어! 그게 자라서 나-식물이 되지!\n"
" player:\n"
" 바로오오 그 말 하려던 참이었어! 그리고 누가 너-식물 싫어하겠어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <i>퀴퀴한</> 사람 좋아하는 사람. 그리고 상한 음식도. 역겨워.\n"
" player:\n"
" 으, 역겨워! 퀴퀴한 사람이라니? 웩!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you have any friends?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 친구 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" But still... what if I do or say something wrong?\n"
" !scared\n"
" What if... <z 0.7>What if I get left behind again?</>\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I'm just going invisible for a bit. Bye.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그래도... 내가 뭔가 잘못 말하거나 하면 어떡하지?\n"
" !scared\n"
" 만약... <z 0.7>또 혼자 남겨지면 어떡해?</>\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 잠깐만 투명해졌다 올게. 잘 가.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "A Hunter's only friends are their weapon and their friends--YES I have friends!"
msgstr "헌터의 유일한 친구는 무기와 동료뿐이야--당연히 친구 있거든!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Rude. And to answer you: I'd like to think so. Why do you ask?"
msgstr "무례하네. 그리고 답하자면: 있다고 믿고 싶어. 왜 물어봐?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Um... what <i>is</> this?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's an Ancient Hunter Friendship Charm!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...<#RED>\"Ancient Hunter Friendship\" Charm</>? \n"
" player:\n"
" Hold it tight, and you'll always have a friend. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" A stick with a pinecone and a dead fly stuck to it with sap is my ugly friend? \n"
" player: \n"
" What? <z 0.7>I worked really hard on that...</> No! It's magic! It will bring you friendship, okay? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !agree\n"
" Actually. I won't go invisible right now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} 음... 이게 <i>뭐</>야?\n"
" player:\n"
" 고대 헌터 우정 부적이야!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...<#RED>\"고대 헌터 우정\" 부적</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" 꽉 쥐고 있으면, 넌 항상 친구가 생겨.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 송진으로 솔방울이랑 죽은 파리를 붙여 놓은 막대기가 내 못생긴 친구라고?\n"
" player: \n"
" 뭐? <z 0.7>그거 진짜 엄청 열심히 만들었는데...</> 아니! 마법이라고! 네게 우정을 가져다줄 거야, 알겠지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" 흠.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !agree\n"
" 생각해보니. 지금은 안 사라질래."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I'm going to keep this one a square flower. \n"
" player:\n"
" Hah, sounds good, {name.npc_apothecary}. <z 0.7>Just a beautiful rock I spent ages polishing. But keep it wrapped! What do I care!</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh. And \"thank you.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Hah. You're very welcome! Manners! <i>That's</> new...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> taught me.\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> showed me the best eavesdropping spots around camp. And I helped <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> with the flowers he's growing behind the forge...\n"
" player:\n"
" Whoa! Really? Who is this {name.npc_apothecary}? No invisibility or anything!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" It was the <#RED>Ancient Hunter Friendship Charm</>. It really worked. \"Thank you.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" About that... the Charm isn't magic. It was a <i>nice</> \"trick\" to make you be brave. <i>You're welcome.</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" ... Duh.\n"
" player:\n"
" You knew??\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I didn't go to \"school\" but I'm not dumb. You gave me forest trash and said it was magic. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" But thinking about you making it, thinking it was good and it would help me, I knew... I'd already made a friend.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>That's</> what made me feel brave. Knowing you're as weird as me, if not more weird. If anything, I'd abandon you for being too weird.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Just joking! I learned that from you. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" And just like you said, when I hold this charm, I know I'll always have a friend.\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm glad we became friends, {name.npc_apothecary}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Me too. So I made this \"Ancient Forest Baby Friendship Charm\" to help <i>you</> feel brave. <i>You're welcome.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 이번 것도 네모 꽃으로 해둘게.\n"
" player:\n"
" 하, 좋네, {name.npc_apothecary}. <z 0.7>내가 오랫동안 닦아 반짝이게 만든 예쁜 돌일 뿐이야. 그래도 포장은 벗기지 마! 내가 뭘 신경 쓰겠어!</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아. 그리고 \"고마워.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 오! 하. 천만에! 예의도 차리고! <i>그건</> 새롭네...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>한테 배웠어.\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>가 캠프 근처 최고의 엿듣기 명당도 알려줬어. 그리고 난 <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>가 대장간 뒤에서 키우는 꽃도 도와줬고...\n"
" player:\n"
" 우와! 진짜? 이 {name.npc_apothecary} 누구야? 투명해지지도 않고!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>고대 헌터 우정 부적</> 덕분이야. 진짜로 효과 있었어. \"고마워.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" 그건 말이지... 그 부적은 마법이 아니야. 네가 용기 내게 하려고 한 <i>좋은</> \"속임수\"였어. <i>천만에.</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" ... 당연하지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 알고 있었어??\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" \"학교\"는 안 다녔어도 바보는 아니야. 숲 쓰레기 주고 마법이라고 했잖아.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 근데 네가 그걸 만들면서, 좋다고 믿고 나한테 도움이 될 거라 생각했다는 걸 떠올리니까, 알겠더라... 난 이미 친구를 만든 거였어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>그게</> 날 용감하게 만들었어. 네가 나만큼, 어쩌면 나보다 더 이상하다는 걸 알게 되니까. 굳이 버린다면 너무 이상해서 널 버렸겠지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 야!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 농담이야! 너한테 배웠어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 네 말대로, 이 부적을 쥐면 언제나 친구가 있다는 걸 알게 돼.\n"
" player:\n"
" 우리 친구가 돼서 기뻐, {name.npc_apothecary}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" 나도. 그래서 <i>네가</> 용감해지라고 이 \"고대 숲 아기 우정 부적\"을 만들었어. <i>천만에.</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A present? For <i>me?!</> It's even got wrapping paper, and a real bow and <i>everything!</>\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, it's actually for {name.npc_lunn}! Y'know, so that he trusts me...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, that's right! Well he sure does appreciate it. Don't you, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? \n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha ha ha! Oh <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, their head DOES look like that!\n"
" player:\n"
" My head looks like what now?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Haha! Don't worry about it! Here, take this <#RED>{name.armourtools0}</>. With it, I can make your <#RED>armour</> even better than it is now!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" player:\n"
" Great! But again: my head looks like what now? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Haha! Don't worry about it! <i>Head</> on over to the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>. There, we can put our extra sparkle on anything!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 선물? <i>나한테?!</> 포장지도 있고, 진짜 리본도 있고 <i>다 있네!</>\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, 사실 {name.npc_lunn}한테 주는 거지! 알지, 그가 날 믿게 하려고...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" 아 맞다! 그래도 분명 고마워할 거야. 그렇지, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하하하! 오 <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, 진짜 머리 모양이 딱 그렇네!\n"
" player:\n"
" 내 머리가 뭐처럼 생겼다고?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 하하! 신경 쓰지 마! 자, 이 <#RED>{name.armourtools0}</> 받아. 이걸로 네 <#RED>방어구</>를 지금보다 훨씬 좋게 만들 수 있어!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" player:\n"
" 좋네! 근데 다시 물을게: 내 머리가 뭐처럼 생겼다고?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 하하! 신경 쓰지 마! <i>얼른</> <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> 쪽으로 와. 거기서 뭐든 더 반짝이게 만들 수 있어!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What are you hiding behind your back, Hunter? You <i>know</> you can't keep a secret from me!\n"
" player:\n"
" You caught me-- I brought you another souvenir from my Hunt!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>Oooooooooh--</> a scarf pin! It looks <i>just</> like the one I lost fending off a <#RED>{name.groak}</> that tried to swallow me whole!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Actually, wait a minute... I think this <i>is</> the scarf pin I jabbed into that <#RED>{name.groak}'s</> gullet! Hilda! You've come back to me!\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait, it's <i>yours?!</> I guess this isn't much of a gift after all...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Are you kidding?! Being reunited with an old friend is the best gift <i>ever!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" You know, I've actually been working on something for you too. Now seems like the perfect time to give it to you!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 등 뒤에 뭐 숨기고 있어, 헌터? 너도 <i>알잖아</> 내겐 비밀 못 숨긴다는 거!\n"
" player:\n"
" 들켰네-- 사냥에서 또 기념품 가져왔어!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>오오오오오--</> 스카프 핀이네! 날 통째로 삼키려던 <#RED>{name.groak}</>를 막다가 잃어버린 거랑 <i>똑같이</> 생겼어!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 사실 잠깐만... 이거 <i>바로</> 내가 그 <#RED>{name.groak}의</> 목구멍에 찔러 넣었던 그 스카프 핀 같은데! 힐다! 돌아왔구나!\n"
" player:\n"
" 잠깐, 이거 <i>네 거였어?!</> 그럼 선물이라 하기 좀 그렇네...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 무슨 소리야?! 옛 친구랑 다시 만나는 게 <i>최고의</> 선물이야!\n"
" !think\n"
" 있지, 나도 사실 너한테 줄 걸 만들고 있었어. 지금이 딱 줄 타이밍 같네!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Eeeeeeeee! A present!! What do you think it is, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" Funny you should mention {name.npc_lunn}-- it's kinda for him, too.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" A whetstone! Aww Hunter, you're so sweet! Look <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, it's a whetstone just for you!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" ...Oh. Don't take it like that, I'm sure they weren't trying to imply anything about your sharpness.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Err... sorry, Hunter. I think you're gonna be in <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> bad books for a while.\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh?! But I-- all I meant--!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Don't worry, he'll come around. <i>I</> thought it was a lovely gift."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 이이이이이이이! 선물이다!! 이게 뭘 것 같아, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_lunn} 얘기가 나와서 말인데-- 이건 걔 것도 좀 돼.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 숫돌이네! 아우 헌터, 너 진짜 다정하다! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> 봐봐, 너만을 위한 숫돌이야!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" ...아. 그렇게 받아들이진 마, 네 날카로움에 대해 뭘 암시하려던 건 아닐 거야.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 어... 미안, 헌터. 한동안 <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}의</>한테 찍힐 것 같아.\n"
" player:\n"
" 어?! 아니, 내 말은--!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 걱정 마, 걘 곧 풀릴 거야. <i>난</> 정말 좋은 선물이라고 생각했어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You know, you've done so much for me, Hunter. For all of us, really. You deserve something special every once in a while too!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I had a look at that armour you're getting from {name.npc_market_merchant}. It's great. Too great.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I can upgrade that new {name.i_item_rarity_rare} armour all the way to <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>, but I can't get your old {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} stuff beyond <#RED>Level {max_level_uncommon}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" What can we do?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Weeelllll... I've got an idea! If you help me beef up my sewing kit, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I could really give your armour some pizzazz!\n"
" !think\n"
" With an <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>, I could upgrade your old armour to {name.i_item_rarity_rare}. I just need some materials.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Lemme put together a list of stuff we'll need!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그거있지...? 넌 나한테 정말 많은 걸 해줬어. 사실 우리 모두한테. 가끔은 너도 특별한 걸 받아야 해!\n"
" !netural\n"
" !dejected\n"
" {name.npc_market_merchant}한테서 얻는 그...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.i_item_rarity_rare} 방어구 말이야... <#RED>레벨 {max_level_rare}</>까지 업그레이드 할 수 있는거. 꽤 멋지지. 하지만 이 바느질 키트로는 {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} 장비 <#RED>레벨 {max_level_uncommon}</> 이상으로 못 올려.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 어떻게 해?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 으으으음... 아이디어가 있어! 내 재봉 키트 업그레이드하는 걸 도와주면, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>랑 내가 네 방어구를 진짜 화려하게 만들어줄 수 있어!\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>만 있으면 네 옛 방어구를 {name.i_item_rarity_rare}까지 업그레이드할 수 있어. 재료만 좀 필요해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 필요한 거 목록부터 정리해올게!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ohmygosh, a back-scratcher! I've always wanted one of these!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> offered to help a few times, <z 0.7>but between you and me, I didn't think that would end well...</> Anyway, I'm gonna call him Balki!\n"
" player:\n"
" You're naming the back-scratcher, too?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Of course! Why not?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(gasp)</> Does he already have a name? How totally inconsiderate of me not to ask!\n"
" player:\n"
" Nope, never mind. Balki's a great name.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Whew-- I was worried for a second there. Thanks Hunter!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 세상에, 등긁개다! 나 이거 진짜 갖고 싶었어!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}의</>가 몇 번 도와주겠다고 했는데, <z 0.7>너랑 나만 아는 얘기지만 그건 좋은 결말이 안 날 것 같았거든...</> 아무튼 얘 이름은 발키로 할래!\n"
" player:\n"
" 등긁개에도 이름 붙이는 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 당연하지! 왜 안 돼?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(헉)</> 혹시 이미 이름이 있었어? 내가 안 물어보다니 완전 무례했네!\n"
" player:\n"
" 아냐, 괜찮아. 발키 좋은 이름이야.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 휴-- 잠깐 식겁했네. 고마워, 헌터!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I suuuuuper recommend it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 진짜아아아 강추야!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Pretty great, right?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 꽤 괜찮지, 그치?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Ohmygosh, for me? How are you both a totally fearsome Hunter <i>and</> a super sweetie?\n"
" player:\n"
" What about you? You're always so cheerful and confident. How do you do it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh! Well, I just take every bad thing that's happened to me and pack it up into a little box in my brain.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then I take that box, and hide it deep, deep, <i>deeeeep</> down, where I can't think about it anymore. It's like, super easy once you get the hang of it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 세상에, 나 주는 거야? 어떻게 이렇게 무시무시한 헌터이면서 <i>동시에</> 이렇게 다정할 수가 있어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 넌 어때? 넌 늘 이렇게 밝고 자신감 넘치잖아. 비결이 뭐야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 아! 음, 나한테 있었던 안 좋은 일들을 전부 머릿속 작은 상자에 넣어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 그 상자를 깊게, 깊게, <i>아주우우우 깊게</> 숨겨서 더는 생각 안 나게 해. 익숙해지면 진짜 엄청 쉬워!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Neat trick! I'll give it a try!"
msgstr "좋은 방법이네! 나도 해볼게!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "That's... um..."
msgstr "그건... 음..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oooooh, thanks Hunter! I'll have to open this later, I'm a little busy right now.\n"
" player:\n"
" What's going on?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" We're playing hide and seek! I found <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> here in a snap, but Balki's <i>really</> good at hiding.\n"
" player:\n"
" Balki?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" The back-scratcher you gave me! You didn't forget, did you?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyways, he and <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> have really been getting along. I think it's safe to say you've been forgiven for the whetstone incident.\n"
" player:\n"
" Ha... glad to hear it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 우와아, 고마워 헌터! 이건 나중에 열어봐야겠다, 지금 좀 바쁘거든.\n"
" player:\n"
" 무슨 일이야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 숨바꼭질하는 중이야! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>는 금방 찾았는데, 발키는 숨는 게 <i>진짜</> 능숙해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 발키?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 네가 준 등긁개 말이야! 설마 잊은 건 아니지?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼 걔랑 <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>는 요즘 엄청 잘 지내. 숫돌 사건은 네가 용서받았다고 봐도 되겠다.\n"
" player:\n"
" 하... 그거 다행이네!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" I know! I'm really happy for them-- I <i>am!</> But... if <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki start spending all their time together...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Will I become a <i>third wheel?!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 알아! 나도 둘이 잘돼서 정말 기뻐-- 나 <i>진짜야!</> 근데... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>랑 발키가 시간을 전부 같이 보내기 시작하면...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 나는 <i>방해꾼 신세가 되는 거야?!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ugh, I can't believe I'm saying this, but now isn't the time for gossiping! This is serious!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" If <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki start spending all their time together... Where does that leave me? Will I become a <i>third wheel?!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 으으, 이런 말 하기도 싫지만 지금은 잡담할 때가 아니야! 이거 진지한 문제라고!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>랑 발키가 시간을 전부 같이 보내기 시작하면... 난 어디에 끼어야 해? 내가 <i>방해꾼 되는 거야?!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" That {name.i_item_rarity_epic} armour you're getting from {name.npc_market_merchant} is impressive. Like, upgrade to <#RED>Level {max_level_epic}</> impressive.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" With this sewing kit I can only get your old {name.i_item_rarity_rare} stuff to <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" What if I made a <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>? With that, I could upgrade your old {name.i_item_rarity_rare} armour to {name.i_item_rarity_epic} <#RED>Level {max_level_epic}</> armour!\n"
" !point\n"
" I'll need a few things... But you can grab them for me!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oooh! I'll pin a list to the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" {name.npc_market_merchant}에게서 얻은 {name.i_item_rarity_epic} 방어구 말이야... 꽤 인상적이던데? <#RED>{max_level_epic}레벨</>까지 강화할 수 있는 게 말이지.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이 바느질 도구들로는 전에 얻은 {name.i_item_rarity_rare} 장비를 <#RED>{max_level_rare}레벨</1>까지만 강화할 수 있어.\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</2>를 만들면 어떨까? 그러면 네 기존 {name.i_item_rarity_rare} 방어구를 {name.i_item_rarity_epic} <#RED>레벨 {max_level_epic}</3> 까지 업그레이드 할 수 있을 것 같아!\n"
" !point\n"
" 몇 가지가 필요해… 근데 그건 네가 구해다 주면 되잖아?\n"
" !clap\n"
" 오오오! <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</4>에 필요한 목록을 적어둘게!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh. Thanks Hunter.\n"
" player:\n"
" Is something wrong? You seem kinda down.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" N-nothing, it's just... it's <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki... they've been getting <i>really</> close. Then just this morning, I saw them...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>Canoodling!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아. 고마워 헌터.\n"
" player:\n"
" 무슨 일 있어? 좀 기운 없어 보이는데.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, 아무것도 아냐, 그냥... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>랑 발키가... 둘이 <i>엄청</> 가까워졌거든. 그리고 오늘 아침에 내가 걔네를 봤는데...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>꽁냥대는 걸!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}... I don't think that's possible.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" How can you say that? You don't <i>know!</> What if they get tired of me, and go off on their own? Just like... just like...\n"
" player:\n"
" Just like who?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Oh-- ha ha. What was I saying? Umm, sorry Hunter, I should focus on your armour."
msgstr "player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}... 그건 아닌 것 같아.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 어떻게 그런 말을 해? 넌 <i>몰라!</> 걔네가 나 질려서 둘이 떠나버리면 어떡해? 예전처럼... 예전처럼...\n"
" player:\n"
" 예전처럼 누구?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아-- 하하. 내가 무슨 소릴 했지? 음, 미안 헌터, 네 방어구에 집중해야겠다."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Your leather cutter and the back-scratcher? Um... good for them?"
msgstr "네 가죽 커터랑 등긁개? 음... 둘이 잘됐네?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Ooooh this is <i>juicy!</> Tell me more!"
msgstr "오오 이거 <i>완전 꿀잼인데!</> 더 말해봐!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks, Hunter. Sorry for acting toootally weird before, I don't know what got into me! But don't worry, I'm feeling all back to normal now!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}... did someone leave you all alone, once?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wh-what do you mean? I've never been alone, I've <i>always</> had someone by my side.\n"
" player:\n"
" You mean {name.npc_lunn}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" What's so wrong with that? I know people think it's weird-- I've heard the things some folks whisper about me. But you know what? My <i>things</> are always there for me when I need them.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Even you-- it seems like we're friends now, but what happens when this expedition's over? You'll go off to your next adventure and you'll never think about me again.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But all the souvenirs you gave me? <i>Those</> will stay with me. That's the way it always is.\n"
" player:\n"
" I wouldn't do that!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" That's what <i>everyone</> says to your <i>face</>, but they never mean it.\n"
" player:\n"
" So {name.npc_lunn} and Hilda... were they from people who left you behind?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I... th-they... they said they'd be right back... what did I do wrong?\n"
" !angry\n"
" No, I don't wanna think about this stuff! La-la-la-la-- not thinking about it!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" La-la-la-- sorry, can't hear yooouuuu!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 고마워, 헌터. 아까 내가 너어어무 이상하게 굴어서 미안해, 나도 왜 그랬는지 모르겠어! 그래도 걱정 마, 지금은 완전 원래대로 돌아왔어!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}... 너도 예전에, 혼자 남겨진 적 있어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 무, 무슨 뜻이야? 난 혼자였던 적 없어, <i>항상</> 내 곁엔 누군가 있었어.\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_lunn} 말하는 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그게 뭐가 문제야? 사람들이 이상하게 본다는 거 알아-- 수군거리는 것도 다 들었어. 근데 있지? 내 <i>물건들</>은 필요할 때 항상 내 곁에 있어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 너도 마찬가지야-- 지금은 우리가 친구 같아도, 이 원정이 끝나면 어떻게 될까? 넌 다음 모험하러 떠나고, 난 다시 생각도 안 하겠지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 근데 네가 준 기념품들은? <i>그건</> 내 곁에 남아. 늘 그래왔어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 난 그렇게 안 해!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 다들 <i>다</> 네 <i>앞에서만</> 그렇게 말해, 진심은 아니야.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 {name.npc_lunn}이랑 힐다도... 널 두고 떠난 사람들이 준 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 나... 그, 녀석들은... 금방 돌아온다고 했는데... 내가 뭘 잘못한 거지?\n"
" !angry\n"
" 아냐, 이런 건 생각하기 싫어! 라라라라-- 안 생각할래!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 라라라-- 미안, 안 들려어어어!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>(sniffle)</> Hi Hunter. Thanks for the present.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey. Last time we talked... I'm sorry I stirred up bad memories for you.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No, it's... it's okay. Well, I mean it's <i>not</>, but... maybe it's okay if I don't always pretend I'm okay. You know?\n"
" player:\n"
" I think so. Wanna talk about it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ha. Not really. I think... I need to let myself have these feelings first, before I let them out to anyone else. Maybe one day I'll be ready to talk about it with someone, but... not today.\n"
" player:\n"
" If that day ever comes, I'll be there.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Yeah... I actually think you will."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>(훌쩍)</> 안녕 헌터. 선물 고마워.\n"
" player:\n"
" 있잖아. 지난번에 얘기할 때... 네 안 좋은 기억을 건드려서 미안했어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아니, 그건... 괜찮아. 아니, 사실 <i>안</> 괜찮지만... 내가 늘 괜찮은 척만 안 해도 되는 거라면, 그건 괜찮을지도 모르겠어. 알지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 응, 알 것 같아. 얘기해볼래?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 하. 딱히 아니. 내 생각엔... 이 감정들을 먼저 나 스스로 느껴봐야 할 것 같아, 다른 사람한테 꺼내기 전에. 언젠가는 누군가랑 얘기할 준비가 될지도 모르지만... 오늘은 아니야.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그날이 오면, 내가 옆에 있을게.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 응... 너라면 진짜 그럴 것 같아."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I appreciate the thought Hunter, but you know... I've started to realize that maybe I don't need <i>things</> as much as I thought I did...\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Oh-- haha, don't worry <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, of <i>course</> I wasn't talking about <i>you!</>\n"
" player:\n"
" Heh... I guess some things never change.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Yeah. You know, I was thinking about it... even the best of friends can't be with each other <i>all</> the time. So I had a great idea-- I made a souvenir for <i>you!</>\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Your own loveable, huggable, travel-sized <#BLUE>mini-Berna</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>(gasp!)</> What's that, mini-Berna? I'm the coolest, best-looking Hunter you've ever met?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ohmygosh mini-Berna, you can't just <i>say</> stuff like that! People are gonna <i>talk!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 마음은 고마워 헌터, 근데 있잖아... 내가 생각보다 <i>물건</>에 그렇게까지 의지할 필요는 없다는 걸 깨닫기 시작했어...\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 아-- 하하, 걱정 마 <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, <i>당연히</> <i>너</> 말한 건 아니야!\n"
" player:\n"
" 헤헤... 뭐, 안 변하는 것도 있네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 응. 생각해 봤는데... 아무리 친한 친구라도 <i>항상</> 같이 있을 순 없잖아. 그래서 좋은 생각이 났어-- <i>너</>를 위한 기념품을 만들었지!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 네 전용 사랑스럽고 껴안기 좋은 여행용 <#BLUE>미니-버나</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>(헉!)</> 뭐라고, 미니-버나? 내가 네가 본 헌터 중에 제일 멋지고 잘생겼다고?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 어머나 미니-버나, 그런 말은 막 <i>하면</> 안 되지! 사람들이 <i>수군댄단 말이야!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Throw yer own trash out. \n"
" player:\n"
" \"Trash\"?! What? No! It's a souvenir from my Hunt!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" A souvenir? What are ye givin' it ta me for?\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... You said it would prove me worthy of your weapon upgrading skills?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Och, that <i>does</> have me ring to it...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Fine. Me <#RED>smithing tools</> an' forge'll give extra <i>oompf</i> to yer weapons.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" All ye've gotta do is go out into the wilds an' get the materials I need.\n"
" !point\n"
" Cannae upgrade squat with faerie wishes an' unicorn promises, can I? \n"
" !shrug\n"
" Of ye go... Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흥. 네 쓰레기는 네가 치워.\n"
" player:\n"
" 쓰레기라고?! 뭐? 아냐! 사냥 기념품이거든!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 기념품? 그걸 왜 나한테 주는데?\n"
" player:\n"
" 음... 네 무기 강화 기술을 받을 자격을 증명하라며?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 오호, 그 말은 <i>확실히</> 맘에 드는군...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 좋아. 내 <#RED>단조 도구</>랑 화덕으로 네 무기에 <i>한 방</i> 더 실어주지.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 네가 할 일은 황야로 나가서 내가 필요한 재료를 가져오는 것뿐이야.\n"
" !point\n"
" 요정 소원이랑 유니콘 약속만으로는 강화 못 하잖아, 안 그래?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 가 봐라... 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's this s'posed ta be? Some wee scrap o' fabric?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's a bookmark! {name.npc_armorsmith} tells me you're something of a reader? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Err... not sure where she got that from. <z 0.7><i>Wish she'd sew her darn mouth shut that one.</></>\n"
" player:\n"
" Hm. But wasn't it your novel she found? With two hammers kissing on the cover--?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...Let's stop talking. Aye?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이게 뭐냐? 조그만 천 쪼가리인가?\n"
" player:\n"
" 책갈피야! {name.npc_armorsmith}가 그러는데, 너 책 좀 읽는다며?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 어... 걔가 어디서 그런 소릴 들었는지 모르겠네. <z 0.7><i>입이나 좀 꿰매버렸으면 좋겠군.</></>\n"
" player:\n"
" 흠. 근데 걔가 찾은 거 네 소설 아니었어? 표지에 망치 두 개가 키스하는 그거--?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...말은 여기까지 하자. 알겠지?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph. Must've cleared all the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> out o' the <#BLUE>Rotwood</> if ye've got time ta pester me with this.\n"
" player:\n"
" Aw c'mon! I think deep down you like when I bring you souvenirs.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Bah. Ye dinnae know a thing about me.\n"
" player:\n"
" Now why do you think that is, Mr. Doesn't-Open-Up?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Feh. Mind yer own forge. That's what I always say. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" To meself."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 흥. 나한테 이걸 들고 와서 귀찮게 할 시간 있으면 <#BLUE>랏우드</>의 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>는 다 치운 모양이네.\n"
" player:\n"
" 에이, 그러지 마! 속으론 내가 기념품 가져오는 거 좋아하잖아.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 흥. 넌 나에 대해 아는 게 하나도 없어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그러니까 왜 그럴까, 미스터 철벽?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 쳇. 자기 화덕은 자기가 챙겨. 난 늘 그렇게 말해.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 나 자신한테."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hmph. Dinnae mean ta... Y'know I'm not a talker and the like, but...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Look. If ye ever need ta sit in silence with someone... ye know where I am."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 흥. 그런 뜻은 아니었어... 알잖아, 난 말 많은 타입은 아니라서...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 들어. 네가 누구랑 조용히 가만히 앉아 있고 싶을 때가 있으면... 내가 어디 있는지 알지."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Yer made of harder steel than I thought.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But if ye ever need ta sit in silence with someone... ye know where I am."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흥. 네가 생각보다 더 단단한 강철이었군.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그래도 네가 누구랑 조용히 가만히 앉아 있고 싶을 때가 있으면... 내가 어디 있는지 알지."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" ...Aye. There's work ta be done.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Trouble is, I left a lot o' me <#RED>smithing tools</> behind when we set out for this expedition. \n"
" !point\n"
" If'n ye help me make a new set of <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>, I could reforge yer old {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} weapons ta be {name.i_item_rarity_rare}.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I'll need more materials to make 'em. Check the <#RED>Weapon Racks</> fer a list.\n"
" player:\n"
" Ooh, sounds great... but why'd you leave those tools behind in the first place?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I had ta leave in a bit of a... hurry, ye see. Let's leave it at that."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" ...그래. 할 일이 있지.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 문제는, 이 원정 떠날 때 내 <#RED>대장장이 도구</>를 많이 두고 왔다는 거야.\n"
" !point\n"
" 네가 <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</> 새 세트를 만들게 도와주면, 네 오래된 {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} 무기를 {name.i_item_rarity_rare}로 재련할 수 있어.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 그걸 만들 재료가 더 필요해. 목록은 <#RED>무기 거치대</>에서 확인해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 오, 좋다... 근데 애초에 왜 그 도구들을 두고 온 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 좀... 급하게 떠나야 했거든. 그 얘긴 여기까지만 하자."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Awright. Give <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}'s</> weapon here.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Y'know, Hunter. Ye can tell me if'n me weapons are failin' ye out in the wilds...  \n"
" player:\n"
" What?! They're great, {name.npc_blacksmith}. Why do you ask?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Well, ye've got that thousand-yard stare goin'. Somethin's weighin' on ye... \n"
" player:\n"
" Well, well, well... Look who's prying <i>now</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hmph. Mindin' yer own forge... I gotta respect that. \n"
" !think\n"
" Just figured... the pressure ye've been under... what with the whole <#BLUE>Rotwood</> dependin' on ye 'n' all...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Och, never ye mind."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 좋아. <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}의</> 무기 이리 줘.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 있잖냐, 헌터. 야생에서 내 무기가 영 별로면 말해도 돼...\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐?! 엄청 좋은데, {name.npc_blacksmith}. 왜 물어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 너, 멍하니 먼 데만 보는 눈이야. 뭔가 짓누르고 있지...\n"
" player:\n"
" 오호라... <i>이제</> 누가 캐묻는지 봐라?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 흥. 자기 화덕은 자기가 챙긴다... 그건 존중하지.\n"
" !think\n"
" 그냥 말이야... 네가 받는 압박이 워낙 크니까... <#BLUE>랏우드</> 전체가 너한테 달려 있잖아...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 오, 신경 쓰지 마."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Oh, right, the pressure. I'd <i>almost</> forgotten. THANKS."
msgstr "아, 맞다, 그 압박. <i>거의</> 잊고 있었네. 고맙다, 진짜."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Pressure? Heh. I eat pressure for breakfast."
msgstr "압박? 흥. 난 그런 건 아침밥으로 먹어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hunter... why do ye keep doin' this?\n"
" player:\n"
" What, don't you like cool souvenirs from my adventures?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What are ye hopin' ta get out of it? With the type I ran with back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>, nothing came without strings attached.\n"
" player:\n"
" Err... what 'type' did you run with, exactly?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Before joinin' <i>this</> merry crew?  Hmph... I s'pose there's no harm in tellin' ye that much...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I was a member o' the Blacksmith's Guild. If ye wanna set up shop in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>, 'tis all but required.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" The Guild looks out fer its own. If a member has a pesky 'problem', the Guild sees it... 'taken care of'.\n"
" !point\n"
" But ye always have ta pay yer dues. If ye don't, ye might find <i>yerself</> becoming a 'problem'.\n"
" player:\n"
" That sounds ominous...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" They're a rough bunch, to be sure. But if ye've got wits enough ta keep yer head down and trust no one, ye can do alright for yerself.\n"
" player:\n"
" So what made you leave?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...I s'pose I let me wits dull a bit over time. A mistake.\n"
" Hmph. S'enough chat fer now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 헌터... 왜 자꾸 이러는 거야?\n"
" player:\n"
" 왜, 내 모험 기념품 멋지잖아?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 이걸로 뭘 얻으려는 거지? 내가 <#BLUE>브링크스</>에서 어울리던 부류에선, 대가 없는 건 없었거든.\n"
" player:\n"
" 어... 정확히 어떤 부류였는데?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <i>이</> 유쾌한 무리에 들어오기 전 말이지? 흥... 그 정도는 말해도 상관없겠군...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 난 대장장이 길드 소속이었어. <#BLUE>브링크스</>에서 가게 차리려면 사실상 필수지.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 길드는 자기 사람은 챙겨. 길드원한테 성가신 문제가 생기면, 길드가 알아서... 처리해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 대신 대가는 꼭 치러야 해. 안 그러면 <i>네가</> 문제가 될 수도 있지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 불길하게 들리는데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 거친 놈들인 건 맞아. 그래도 고개 숙이고 아무도 안 믿을 만큼 눈치가 있으면, 먹고살 만은 해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 왜 나온 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...시간 지나면서 내가 좀 무뎌졌던 모양이야. 실수였지.\n"
" 흥. 대화는 이쯤 하자."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hmph. Ye should be thinkin' less about bringin' me souvenirs, and more about keepin' yerself safe out there.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye were lookin' a mite banged-up last time <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> dragged ye back ta camp.\n"
" player:\n"
" Aww, have you been worrying about me?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt}... No. Maybe. <z 0.7>A little...</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" Bring a good {name.i_item_rarity_epic} weapon when ye go out there, ye ken? And armour, too! Don't want ye bein' a meal for the worms.\n"
" player:\n"
" I knew you had a soft side under that grumpy exterior!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...Don't ye go tellin' anyone. I mean it.\n"
" player:\n"
" I promise, your secret's safe with me!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. It'd better be. Ye know I dinnae take givin' away me secrets lightly.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Hunter... Somethin' you <i>could</i> fetch me...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With some <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>, I could upgrade yer old {name.i_item_rarity_rare} gear so it's not so laggard.\n"
" !agree\n"
" All I need from ye are a few raw materials. A win-win, aye?\n"
" player:\n"
" Thanks for thinking of me {name.npc_blacksmith}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Aye, err... Doing what's best for the {name_multiple.foxtails}, is all."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 흥. 나한테 기념품 가져올 생각은 좀 줄이고, 밖에서 네 몸 챙길 생각이나 더 해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 지난번에 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>이 널 캠프로 끌고 왔을 때, 꽤 많이 다친 꼴이더군.\n"
" player:\n"
" 어머, 나 걱정해준 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt}... 아니. 어쩌면. <z 0.7>조금은...</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" 밖에 나갈 땐 제대로 된 {name.i_item_rarity_epic} 무기 챙겨, 알겠지? 방어구도! 네가 벌레 밥 되는 꼴은 보기 싫으니까.\n"
" player:\n"
" 투덜대는 겉모습 밑에 다정한 면 있는 거 내가 알았다니까!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...아무한테도 말하지 마라. 진심이야.\n"
" player:\n"
" 약속할게, 네 비밀은 내가 지켜!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흥. 그래야지. 내 비밀을 가볍게 흘리는 성미 아닌 거 알잖아.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 헌터... 네가 <i>구해올 수 있는</i> 게 하나 있어...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>만 좀 있으면, 네 낡은 {name.i_item_rarity_rare} 장비를 굼뜨지 않게 업그레이드해줄 수 있어.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 내가 필요한 건 원재료 몇 개뿐이야. 서로 윈윈이지, 안 그래?\n"
" player:\n"
" 신경 써줘서 고마워 {name.npc_blacksmith}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그래, 어... {name_multiple.foxtails}을 위해 최선의 일을 하는 것뿐이야."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Och, another-- wait... is this...?\n"
" player:\n"
" A new book! Well, not 'new' exactly, I found it on my Hunt.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>'A Royal Welding'</>, fourth book in the Forged Bonds Saga... this hasnae been in print since the eruption...!\n"
" player:\n"
" A-are you okay? Are you mad? If you don't like it--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" No! {name.blacksmith_grunt} Err, no. It's... actually... one o' me favourites...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Erm... Thanks, Hunter. This is... very thoughtful of ye.\n"
" player:\n"
" I gotta say, you have unexpected tastes in books.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmph. Well. I wasn't the one reading 'em ta start with-- but she'd leave 'em around the shop, and one day I got curious...\n"
" player:\n"
" 'She'?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah! Slip o' the tongue. Just forget it, aye?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...I have work that needs doin'. See ye round, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 오, 또 왔-- 잠깐... 이건...?\n"
" player:\n"
" 새 책이야! 뭐, 정확히는 새 건 아니고, 사냥하다 찾았어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>왕실 용접</>, 포지드 본즈 사가 4권... 이건 대폭발 이후로 절판이었는데...!\n"
" player:\n"
" 괘, 괜찮아? 화난 거야? 마음에 안 들면--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아니! {name.blacksmith_grunt} 어, 아니. 이건... 사실... 내가 제일 좋아하는 것 중 하나야...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 음... 고마워, 헌터. 이건... 정말 세심한 선물이네.\n"
" player:\n"
" 말해두지만, 너 책 취향 의외다.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 흥. 뭐. 처음부터 내가 읽던 건 아니었어-- 근데 걔가 가게 여기저기에 두고 다녀서, 어느 날 궁금해졌지...\n"
" player:\n"
" 걔?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 말실수야. 그냥 잊어, 알겠지?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...해야 할 일이 있어. 나중에 보자, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Aren't ye?!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 안 그래?!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Do I?!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그래 보이냐?!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's this here-- an oil lamp? Haven't seen one o' these since the old days.\n"
" player:\n"
" I know you like to read at night. I thought this would help!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Aye. It will. Thanks, Hunter.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey {name.npc_blacksmith}... who is the 'she' you mentioned before?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...I thought I told ye ta forget about that.\n"
" player:\n"
" I know, but--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ye just can't keep yerself from pryin' into me business, can ye?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I know what yer tryin' ta do, Hunter. Butterin' me up, hopin' I'll let something slip-- somethin' ye can use against me..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이건 뭐지-- 기름램프? 이런 건 옛날 이후로 처음 보네.\n"
" player:\n"
" 네가 밤에 책 읽는 거 좋아하잖아. 이게 도움이 될 것 같았어!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...그래. 도움 되겠지. 고맙다, 헌터.\n"
" player:\n"
" 저기 {name.npc_blacksmith}... 전에 말한 그 걔, 누구야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...그 얘긴 잊으라 했던 것 같은데.\n"
" player:\n"
" 알아, 근데--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 넌 진짜 남 일 캐묻는 걸 못 참지, 안 그래?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 네가 뭘 하려는지 알아, 헌터. 나 비위 맞춰서 방심시키고, 실수로 뭐라도 흘리게 만들려는 거지-- 나한테 불리하게 쓸 만한 걸..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...No. Yer right. Sorry, Hunter. Went a bit off me head there.\n"
" player:\n"
" It's okay. Maybe instead of talking, we could... share the silence?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" Heh. Aye. I'd like that.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...아니. 네 말이 맞아. 미안하다, 헌터. 내가 좀 제정신이 아니었네.\n"
" player:\n"
" 괜찮아. 말하는 대신에, 우리 그냥... 조용히 같이 있을까?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" 헤. 그래. 그거 좋네.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "W-wait, that's not what I'm trying to do at all!"
msgstr "자, 잠깐, 내가 하려던 건 그런 게 전혀 아니야!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Come on, you know that's not true."
msgstr "에이, 그거 아닌 거 너도 알잖아."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks, Hunter. I've been thinkin', maybe it's time I fessed up.\n"
" !think\n"
" Ye know... ye remind me of her sometimes. My Billie. Brave as a lion, and stubborn as an ox.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We weren't related by blood-- I took her on as an apprentice when I was settin' up me forge out in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. But she was the closest thing ta family I ever had.\n"
" player:\n"
" What happened to her?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Och. Sold me out to the Blacksmith's Guild, the wee bampot!\n"
" player:\n"
" WHAT?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Aye. Business had started ta pick up. She'd started showin' an interest in organizin' the ledgers. Fool that I am, I thought nothin' of it.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, one day the Guild comes a-knockin'. Turns out <i>someone</> had been doctorin' the books, cheatin' the Guild out of their cut o' me forge's profits. And the paper trail all led back ta me.\n"
" player:\n"
" So what did you do?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I high-tailed it out o' there as fast as me legs would carry me!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Lucky fer me, I found this little expedition plannin' on flying out ta <#BLUE>the Rotwood</>. <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> was lookin' fer a blacksmith, and I figured it was the perfect way ta lie low while I waited for the heat ta die down.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wow... I'm starting to get why you don't open up easily.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Aye. 'Tis a funny thing, though... when I think about Billie, cheatin' the Guild, doctorin' the ledger right under me nose, takin' over the forge fer herself, I can't help but feel--\n"
" player:\n"
" Angry? Betrayed? Hungry for vengeance?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Proud.\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh?!?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Don't get me wrong, I'm also hoppin' mad about it! But at the end o' the day, my Billie knew what she wanted, and outsmarted the lot of us ta get it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" T'was ruthless, aye-- but that's exactly what ye need ta survive in the Guild. She's gonna go far, that one.\n"
" player:\n"
" That's one way to look at it, I guess.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. I dinnae expect ye ta fully understand. It was good bein' able ta talk about her again, though. Thanks, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 고마워, 헌터. 생각해 보니 이제 털어놓을 때가 된 것 같아.\n"
" !think\n"
" 있잖아... 너 가끔 그 애가 떠올라. 내 빌리. 사자처럼 용감하고, 황소처럼 고집 셌지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 피가 이어진 사이는 아니었어-- <#BLUE>the Brinks</>에서 대장간 차리던 때에 내가 제자로 들였거든. 그래도 내게는 가족이나 다름없는 애였어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그 애한테 무슨 일이 있었는데?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 휴. 그 꼬맹이 또라이가 날 대장장이 길드에 팔아넘겼어!\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그래. 장사가 좀 풀리기 시작했고, 걔가 장부 정리에 관심 보이기 시작했어. 내가 멍청하게도 대수롭지 않게 넘겼지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그러다 어느 날 길드가 들이닥쳤어. 알고 보니 <i>누군가</> 장부를 조작해서 내 대장간 이익에서 길드 몫을 빼돌리고 있었더라고. 그리고 증거가 전부 나를 가리켰어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그래서 어떻게 했는데?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 냅다 튀었지, 다리가 허락하는 한 최대한 빨리!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 운 좋게도 <#BLUE>the Rotwood</>로 떠날 원정대가 있더라. <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>이 대장장이를 찾고 있었고, 난 소란이 가라앉을 때까지 몸 숨기기 딱 좋겠다 싶었지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 와... 왜 쉽게 마음 안 여는지 이제 알 것 같아.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래. 근데 묘한 게 말이야... 빌리가 길드를 속이고, 내 코앞에서 장부를 조작하고, 대장간을 자기 걸로 가져가는 걸 떠올리면, 이상하게도 난--\n"
" player:\n"
" 화나? 배신감 들어? 복수하고 싶어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...자랑스러워.\n"
" player:\n"
" 어?!?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 오해하진 마, 나도 엄청 열받았어! 그래도 결국 내 빌리는 자기가 원하는 게 뭔지 알았고, 그걸 위해 우리 전부를 한수 위로 이긴 거야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 냉혹했지, 그래-- 근데 길드에서 살아남으려면 딱 그런 게 필요해. 그 애, 크게 될 거야.\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐... 그렇게 볼 수도 있겠네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 헤h. 네가 완전히 이해하길 바란 건 아니야. 그래도 그 애 얘기를 다시 할 수 있어서 좋았어. 고마워, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Aye. <i>Sure</> ye are. Careful as a bull in a china shop."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그래. <i>물론</> 그렇겠지. 도자기 가게의 황소만큼이나 조심하네."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> I'm gonna go gray at this rate, mark me words."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 이러다 금방 백발 되겠다, 두고 봐."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hunter... I know yer heart's in the right place, but I'm runnin' outta space ta put all these souvenirs.\n"
" !point\n"
" Just keep yer wits about ye while out on yer Hunts, and come back safe. That's the best gift ye could give me."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 헌터... 네 마음이야 고마운데, 이 기념품들 둘 자리도 이제 다 떨어져 가.\n"
" !point\n"
" 사냥 나갈 땐 정신 바짝 차리고, 무사히 돌아와. 그게 네가 줄 수 있는 최고의 선물이야."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well, anyway... I'd best get back ta the forge--\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait a minute, what's that you're hiding behind your back?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Urk--! Ah. Well... 'tis a silly thing, really, pay no mind...\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Och, <i>fine</>, take it! Just don't go showin' it around, ye ken?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼... 나도 대장간으로 돌아가야--\n"
" player:\n"
" 잠깐만, 등 뒤에 숨긴 그거 뭐야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 윽--! 아. 뭐... 별거 아니야, 신경 쓰지 마...\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, <i>알았어</>, 가져! 대신 여기저기 들고 다니진 마, 알겠지?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Who me? I'm <i>always</> careful!"
msgstr "나 말이야? 난 <i>항상</> 조심하지!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Aw, come on! Life-threatening danger makes Hunts fun!"
msgstr "에이, 목숨이 왔다 갔다 해야 사냥이 재밌지!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Aw shucks! A gift for this old bag of bones some thought to leave in the cold? That's mighty thoughtful of you, Hunter.\n"
" player:\n"
" I've been meaning to ask: what happened before we found you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ah well, I had a crew--or group or what have you--I was cookin' for, sendin' what I could back to my poor ailin' ma, all alone in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. \n"
" !angry\n"
" Well, I guess my compatriots got to figurin' they could enrich themselves if'n they cut me loose and kept my share of the findings!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Tsk. Stabbed me in the back, they did. Horrible. Terrible! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" (sniffle) And to think of my poor ma, alone--and sick--as she was! And she bein' the one who fostered my love of cookery and some such, too! Oh!\n"
" player:\n"
" That's awful, {name.npc_cook}! I'm so glad we found you when we did.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" As am I, sure as sugar! Say... You've been so welcomin', Hunter, I'm gonna whip up a batch of new, extra <#RED>Special</> recipes for ya!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'll even rotate through new <#RED>Specials</> to keep things fresh. So if you see somethin' you want, get it while it's hot, y'hear? Hoo-whee!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 아이쿠! 이 늙은 뼈다귀를 버리고 가려던 사람한테 선물까지 주다니? 정말 마음씨도 곱네, 헌터.\n"
" player:\n"
" 물어보려고 했어. 우리를 만나기 전엔 무슨 일이 있었던 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 뭐, 내겐 팀이 있었지--뭐라 부르든 간에--거기서 요리를 했고, <#BLUE>the Brinks</>에 홀로 계신 병든 우리 엄마한테 내가 벌 수 있는 걸 보내고 있었어. \n"
" !angry\n"
" 근데 그 인간들이 날 잘라내고 내 몫까지 챙기면 자기들 배만 불릴 수 있겠다고 생각했나 봐!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 쯧. 뒤통수 제대로 맞았지. 끔찍했어. 정말 끔찍했지! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" (훌쩍) 거기다 아픈 우리 엄마는 혼자 계셨고...! 요리 좋아하게 만들어 준 것도 엄마였는데! 아!\n"
" player:\n"
" 너무 심하다, {name.npc_cook}! 그래도 제때 널 찾아서 정말 다행이야.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 나도 그래, 설탕처럼 달콤하게 진심이야! 있잖아... 이렇게 잘 대해 줬으니, 헌터 너한테 새 <#RED>Special</> 레시피를 한가득 만들어 줄게!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 새 <#RED>Specials</>도 돌려 가며 내놓을 테니까 메뉴 자주 바뀔 거야. 갖고 싶은 게 보이면 뜨거울 때 바로 집어, 알겠지? 후우-휘!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yup! Her joints would make this poppin' sound, uh, when she danced! Oh, and how 'pops' loved to dance. Joint's a-poppin' away into the night...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well anyways, you've probably got lots of important Hunter stuff to do. I'll let you mosey on on to it, then."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 응! 우리 엄마가 춤추면 관절에서 팝팝 소리가 났거든! 아, 그리고 '팝스'는 춤을 정말 좋아했지. 밤새도록 관절이 팝팝거리면서...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼 너도 중요한 헌터 일이 많겠지. 그거나 하러 가."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I swear on my family cookbook, it's the honest truth! She had these poppin' joints! 'Pop-pop-pop' they'd go, as she danced the night away...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyways, you've probably got lots of important Hunter stuff to do. I'll let you mosey on on to it, then."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 우리 집 가보 요리책에 맹세코 완전 사실이야! 춤출 때 관절이 팝팝거렸다고! 밤새 춤추면 '팝팝팝' 소리가 났지...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼 너도 중요한 헌터 일이 많겠지. 그거나 하러 가."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Well gosh if it ain't my favourite Hunter, swingin' by with another thoughtful souvenir!\n"
" !greet\n"
" Thank ya kindly! Take care now!\n"
" player:\n"
" Actually, I was curious... what was your favourite recipe to make growing up?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm... um... that sure is a toughie... y'know, good ol' pops taught me so many tasty family recipes I don't reckon I can pick a favourite!\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait, I thought you said your <i>ma</> taught you how to cook? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Did I... ? I mean, I did, but, uh, 'pops' was just, er... a fun nickname we used to call her!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 이런, 내가 제일 좋아하는 헌터가 또 정성스러운 기념품을 들고 왔네!\n"
" !wave\n"
" 정말 고마워! 몸조심하고!\n"
" player:\n"
" 근데 궁금한 게 있었어... 어릴 때 제일 좋아하던 요리 레시피가 뭐였어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 음... 어... 그건 정말 어렵네... 있잖아, 우리 '팝스'가 집안 레시피를 워낙 많이 가르쳐 줘서 하나만 고를 수가 없어!\n"
" player:\n"
" 잠깐, 요리는 <i>엄마</>한테 배웠다고 하지 않았어? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 내가... 그랬나? 그러니까, 맞긴 한데, 어... '팝스'는 그냥 엄마를 부르던 애칭이었어!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Oh, that makes perfect sense!"
msgstr "아, 완전 말 되네!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Riiigghhtt..."
msgstr "그으래..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-another souvenir? Wow. You're really makin' a habit of this 'bein' nice' thing, huh?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Matter of fact, this whole camp is awfully friendly... The other day that <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</> just <i>gave</> me a fire-retardant hair net she'd made... \n"
" !think\n"
" Then that <#BLUE>{name.job_dojo}</> guy fixed a wheel on my cart without me askin'! And <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> lit my grill! <z 0.7> Not like <i>that</>. Not sayin' he couldn't, though...</> \n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's with you guys? What's your angle, huh, bub? \n"
" player:\n"
" No angle. You're part of the team. We help one another like that!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oookaaaay... Hm. I won't let my guard down, so don't think of trying anything, alright, bub?\n"
" player:\n"
" O-of course. We weren't going to 'try anything.' Also--is your voice different all of a sudden?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Well now, who's a-gettin' a-suspicious of a-who, now? I reckon' you oughta get your listenin' holes checked!\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry! Must be hard to trust again, with your old team betraying you...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Yup! That's exactly what's happenin' here. \n"
" player:\n"
" I'll do all I can to make sure you know you can feel safe and secure here.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Really? Er, I mean, aw, shucks, don't you worry your pretty little head none, hun."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 기, 기념품 또? 와. 너 진짜 '착하게 굴기'에 맛 들렸나 보네?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 사실 이 캠프 전체가 너무 친절해... 얼마 전에 <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</>가 직접 만든 난연 머리망을 그냥 <i>줬</>어... \n"
" !think\n"
" 그리고 <#BLUE>{name.job_dojo}</> 저 녀석은 내가 부탁도 안 했는데 수레 바퀴를 고쳐 줬지! 거기다 <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>는 내 그릴에 불도 붙여 줬고! <z 0.7>그런 뜻은<i> </>아니지만</>... 못 한다는 말은 아니고... \n"
" !dubious\n"
" 너희 뭐야? 무슨 속셈인데, 응? \n"
" player:\n"
" 속셈 없어. 넌 팀원이니까. 우린 서로 그렇게 돕는 거야!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 오오케이이이... 흠. 난 방심 안 할 거니까 딴생각은 하지 마, 알았지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 무, 물론이지. 우리도 '딴짓' 할 생각 없었어. 그리고--갑자기 목소리 톤이 바뀐 것 같은데?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 자, 지금 누가 누굴 의심하는 건데? 귀부터 한번 검사받아 봐!\n"
" player:\n"
" 미안! 전에 팀한테 배신당했으니 다시 믿기 힘들겠지...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 맞아! 지금 딱 그런 상황이야. \n"
" player:\n"
" 여기선 네가 안전하다고 느낄 수 있게 내가 할 수 있는 건 다 할게.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 정말? 어, 그러니까, 아이참, 아가씨는 걱정 하나도 하지 마, 자기."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Aw now Hunter, don't be embarrassed! I love every souvenir you bring me--even the defective ones!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아이고 헌터, 부끄러워하지 마! 네가 가져다주는 기념품은 다 좋아해--불량품이어도 말이야!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't you worry your little head about it, Hunter. I love every souvenir you bring me--even the defective ones!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그런 건 신경 쓰지 마, 헌터. 네가 가져다주는 기념품은 다 좋아해--불량품이어도 말이야!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Boy howdy! What a lovely... um...\n"
" player:\n"
" Colander?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --Colander! Was on the tip of my tongue, ha ha!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Shame it's got all these little holes, though. It woulda made a mighty fine soup bowl."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 이야! 정말 멋진... 어...\n"
" player:\n"
" 채반?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --채반! 딱 그 말이 입끝에 맴돌고 있었어, 하하!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 근데 이렇게 작은 구멍이 숭숭 뚫린 건 아쉽네. 수프 그릇으로 딱이었을 텐데."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I think it's actually <i>supposed</> to have those holes."
msgstr "원래 <i>일부러</> 구멍이 있는 거 아닐까."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Oh no!! How did I not notice?!"
msgstr "이런!! 내가 그걸 왜 못 봤지?!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" SUNNUVAGUN THAT SMARTS--! Oh, ah, sorry Hunter, just things get so dang hot when you take them outta the hot hole place!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Another gift? Why you shouldn't have--a mitten? Uh, I don't mean to be an Ungrateful Uma, but my problem is with the <i>heat,</> not the cold.\n"
" player:\n"
" It's an <i>oven mitt!</> For taking hot things out of the oven? Y'know... your exact problem? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Uh, right. O-of course. \"Oven mitt\"...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}... you don't actually know anything about cooking, do you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...\n"
" !angry\n"
" Well I <i>never!</> Just cuz I don't know the names of fancy cookin' tools, or what ingredients are, or how recipes work...\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh! This is because I didn't go to yer fancy cookin' college, isn't it? It's because I learnt all I learnt from my pops--er, who is my ma--is that right?? <z 0.7>(<i>Is</> that right?)\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}. If you're not a {name.job_cook}, you can tell me. I won't be mad. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (sigh) Ya got me. I ain't a {name.job_cook}. I figured y'all would leave me in the cold if'n I didn't have no use in your Camp, Hunter.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" It's why I was left behind by my old crew, in fact. I was just gettin' too old to keep up. \n"
" player:\n"
" That's not how we do things here, {name.npc_cook}. I promise you that.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wow. You really mean it, don't you?\n"
" !think\n"
" Well, in thanks, I'd like to stay on and keep cookin' for ya. I really think I'm gettin' the hang of it! \n"
" !point\n"
" Matter o' fact, I just heard about this new thing called \"oven mitt.\" Gonna change the game, I reckon! Hoo-whee! \n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Oh, and I know it ain't much, but... here. Consider it a thank-you present for bein' so legitimately, actually, and truly kind-hearted, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아이쿠야 뜨거워 죽겠네--! 아, 어, 미안 헌터, 그 뜨거운 구멍 같은 데서 꺼내면 뭐든 너무 뜨겁더라!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 또 선물? 이런, 이러지 않아도 되는데--장갑? 어, 고마움 모르는 우마가 되긴 싫지만, 내 문제는 추위가 아니라 <i>열기</>거든.\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>오븐 장갑</>이야! 오븐에서 뜨거운 거 꺼낼 때 쓰는 거. 그러니까... 딱 네 문제잖아? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 어, 맞네. 무, 물론이지. \"오븐 장갑\"...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}... 너 사실 요리에 대해 아는 게 하나도 없지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...\n"
" !angry\n"
" 내가 <i>세상에나!</> 요리 도구 이름 좀 모르고, 재료가 뭔지 모르고, 레시피가 어떻게 돌아가는지 모른다고 해서...\n"
" !point\n"
" 아! 내가 네 그 잘난 요리 학교를 안 나와서 이러는 거지, 그렇지? 다 우리 팝스--아, 그러니까 엄마--한테 배워서 그런 거지, 맞지?? <z 0.7>(<i>맞</>지?)\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}. 네가 {name.job_cook}이 아니라면 말해도 돼. 나 화 안 낼게. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (한숨) 들켰네. 난 {name.job_cook}이 아니야. 캠프에서 쓸모가 없으면 너희가 날 버릴 거라고 생각했어, 헌터.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 사실 예전 팀한테 버림받은 이유도 그거야. 내가 너무 늙어서 따라가기 힘들어졌거든. \n"
" player:\n"
" 우린 여기서 그렇게 안 해, {name.npc_cook}. 그건 내가 약속할게.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 와. 너 진심이구나, 그렇지?\n"
" !think\n"
" 그럼 고맙다는 뜻으로 여기 남아서 너희한테 계속 요리해 줄게. 나 요리 감 좀 잡아가는 것 같거든! \n"
" !point\n"
" 그러고 보니 방금 \"오븐 장갑\"이라는 신문물을 알게 됐어. 이거 완전 판을 바꿀 것 같아! 후우-휘! \n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" 아, 그리고 별건 아니지만... 여기. 이렇게 진짜로, 제대로, 마음씨 좋게 대해 준 데 대한 감사 선물이야, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Well... it was a long time ago. When ya grow up, ya come to see there's only one kinda 'worth' what means anythin'. Especially in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sentiment won't keep ya fed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 뭐... 아주 오래전 일이야. 크고 나면 '가치'라는 게 결국 한 가지뿐이라는 걸 알게 되지. 특히 <#BLUE>the Brinks</>에선.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 감상만으로는 배를 못 채워."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yeah. When ya grow up, ya come to see there's only one kinda 'worth' what means anythin'. Especially in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sentiment won't keep ya fed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그래. 크고 나면 '가치'라는 게 결국 한 가지뿐이라는 걸 알게 되지. 특히 <#BLUE>the Brinks</>에선.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 감상만으로는 배를 못 채워."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Howdy, Hunter! Another gift? And it's a little wooden carvin' of a blimp!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Gosh, now this takes me back... Reminds of my family--my <i>actual</> family, mind you. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" You wouldn't mind if an old woman yammered on about her past fer a bit?\n"
" player:\n"
" Of course not!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" (Noticed ya didn't object to the \"old\" part but okay) I had a ma <i>and</> a pa, as well as five sisters, back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Poor as the dirt we clawed our livin' from, we were. Ma 'n' pa worked fer well-to-dos who did business with folks in <#BLUE>the Capital</>. \n"
" !laugh\n"
" Sisters 'n' me dreamt of seein' it one day. \"By blimp!\" the youngest, Marigold, would chirp. Heh. <z 0.7>Silly little goose.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Anyway, this reminds me of those innocent times, Hunter. Times of silly little dreams. Hm. I appreciate it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 안녕, 헌터! 또 선물이야? 게다가 비행선 작은 목각이네!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 이야, 이거 보니 옛날 생각난다... 우리 가족이 떠올라--그러니까 <i>진짜</> 가족 말이야. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이 늙은이가 옛날 얘기 좀 늘어놔도 괜찮겠니?\n"
" player:\n"
" 물론이지!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" (\"늙은이\"라는 말엔 반박 안 하네, 뭐 됐어) <#BLUE>the Brinks</>에 있을 때 우리 집엔 엄마 <i>랑</> 아빠, 그리고 자매 다섯이 있었어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 우린 땅바닥 흙만큼 가난했지. 엄마랑 아빠는 <#BLUE>the Capital</> 사람들이랑 거래하는 부자들 밑에서 일했어. \n"
" !laugh\n"
" 나랑 자매들은 언젠가 거길 가보는 게 꿈이었어. \"비행선 타고!\" 막내 메리골드는 그렇게 재잘댔지. 헤헤. <z 0.7>귀여운 꼬마 거위 같았어.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" 아무튼 이걸 보니 그 순진하던 시절이 떠오른다, 헌터. 철없는 작은 꿈을 꾸던 시절 말이야. 흠. 고마워."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I think that's really sweet."
msgstr "그거 정말 따뜻한 이야기네."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "It's harsh but we've all gotta grow up sometime."
msgstr "씁쓸하긴 해도, 우리 다 언젠가는 철들어야 하잖아."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! Is this--?\n"
" player:\n"
" A dried marigold flower! I remembered you said you had a sister named 'Marigold' so I thought...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hunter... I never... I never got somethin' so kind before. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" My ma and pa worked for a fancy family in the kitchen, and they'd bring home leftovers--that was all we had to eat. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" From a young age, my sisters 'n' me learnt we had to work to earn our food. Whoever brought in the most, ate the most. \"Thems <#BLUE>the Brinks</>,\" pa'd say. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" We were ruthless with each other. Cheatin'. Stealin'. Sabotagin'. I'm ashamed to say it now but... I was the best. So I ate the best. \n"
" !agree\n"
" But I <i>always</> split my take with the youngest, Marigold. She couldn't earn much, y'know? She was too little, the silly goose.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (sniffle) Thank ya, Hunter. I... I don't know what to say. Truly.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Take this. It ain't much, I know, but, I ain't used to such kindness, Hunter. \n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 헌터! 이건--?\n"
" player:\n"
" 말린 마리골드 꽃이네! 네가 여동생 이름이 '마리골드'라고 했던 게 기억나서...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 헌터... 난 한 번도... 이렇게 다정한 걸 받아본 적이 없어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 우리 엄마 아빠는 부잣집 주방에서 일했고, 남은 음식을 가져오곤 했어--그게 우리 먹을 거리의 전부였지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 어릴 때부터 자매들이랑 난 먹을 걸 벌려면 일해야 한다는 걸 배웠어. 제일 많이 가져온 사람이 제일 많이 먹는 거야. 아빠는 늘 \"그게 <#BLUE>the Brinks</> 방식이다\"라고 했지.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 우린 서로에게 잔인했어. 속이고. 훔치고. 방해하고. 지금 말하자니 부끄럽지만... 내가 제일 잘했어. 그래서 제일 잘 먹었지.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그래도 난 <i>항상</> 막내 마리골드랑 내 몫을 나눴어. 걔는 많이 못 벌었거든? 너무 어렸잖아, 그 바보 거위.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (훌쩍) 고마워, 헌터. 나... 뭐라고 해야 할지 모르겠어. 정말로.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이거 받아. 별건 아니지만, 이런 다정함은 익숙하지 않아서 말이야, 헌터.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-another gift? Sheesh, Hunter. I'm just plum embarrassed at this point.\n"
" player:\n"
" What? Don't be! You give us so much! Your spirit, your energy...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !\n"
" My food...\n"
" player:\n"
" ... Yeah. That... too.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" When I was younger, my ma and pa got fired for \"stealin'\" leftovers--food the fancy-pants people weren't even gonna eat! \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Then it was up to me 'n' my sisters to provide entirely. \n"
" !think\n"
" Dreamin' of <#BLUE>The Capital</>, Marigold 'n' me took up venturin' into <#BLUE>The Rotwood</> fer <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Not a bad racket if'n ya can hack it. Marigold 'n' me, we hacked it pretty good, mind. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" But as the years went on, we lost a sister here, a sister there... pretty soon, it was down to just Marigold 'n' me to provide. \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, {name.npc_cook}. I'm so sorry. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Aw, s'alright. Some was natural. Some brought it on themselves. It's the nature of the world, Hunter. Cruelty and loss... \n"
" !point\n"
" ... Though <i>you</> have me thinkin' otherwise these days, heh. Warmin' an old gal's frozen heart. Thanks, Hunter.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 또, 또 선물이라고? 아이고, 헌터. 이쯤 되니 그냥 부끄럽구만.\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐? 부끄러워하지 마! 넌 우리한테 엄청 많이 주잖아! 네 기백, 네 에너지...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !\n"
" 내 음식...\n"
" player:\n"
" ...그래. 그것도... 맞지.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 내가 어릴 때, 우리 엄마 아빠는 \"남은 음식 훔쳤다\"는 이유로 잘렸어--그 잘난 사람들은 어차피 먹지도 않을 음식이었는데!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그때부터는 나랑 자매들이 완전히 먹여 살려야 했지.\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>The Capital</>을 꿈꾸며, 나랑 마리골드는 <#BLUE>The Rotwood</>로 들어가 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>을 벌기 시작했어...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 버틸 수만 있으면 나쁘지 않은 벌이였지. 나랑 마리골드는 꽤 잘 버텼어.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 그런데 세월이 지나면서 자매를 하나 잃고, 또 하나 잃고... 어느새 먹여 살릴 사람은 나랑 마리골드 둘뿐이었어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, {name.npc_cook}. 정말 미안해.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 에이, 괜찮아. 어떤 애들은 자연스러웠고, 어떤 애들은 자초한 거였어. 세상은 원래 그런 거지, 헌터. 잔혹함과 상실...\n"
" !point\n"
" ...근데 요즘은 <i>네가</> 날 다르게 생각하게 하더라, 헤. 얼어붙은 늙은 마음을 데워줘서 고마워, 헌터.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" This souvenir... is it a wolf's tooth? How \"ay-pro-pow,\" as the fancy pants say it.\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'see, more recently, it came down to my sister Marigold 'n' I to provide for our aged ma and pa. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But to make enough fer our family, we couldn't just accept our fair share of the hauls. We, uh, we had to resort to some of our 'old ways'...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Don't like tellin' ya this, but we was dishonest to folks we ventured into <#BLUE>The Rotwood</> with. We'd tell fibs, sow discord--create chaos, 'n' the like...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" We'd have the group tearin' each other apart with suspicion and anger, while we made off with the haul.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Gosh, I shouldn't laugh. Old habits, y'know. Well, this last expedition, it was supposed to go the same. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" But Marigold, that silly goose, she turned into a vicious wolf overnight. Seems I was becomin' a burden myself, at my age. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" She saw her opportunity and by gum she took it! She left me in the cold, and took the haul fer herself. \n"
" player:\n"
" Marigold?? No!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I taught her good, seems to me. Good as I knew how, then. \n"
" player:\n"
" But aren't you mad? She stabbed you in the back and left you for dead!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Mad? No, no, no. Well, actually, yes. But your kindness has shown me somethin': I can't be mad at a wolf for huntin' a little old rabbit, now can I? \n"
" !think\n"
" When it's in its nature to do so? When that's all it's been taught? The only way it knows how to be safe? \n"
" player:\n"
" Hm. I suppose not. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm just grateful I got a chance to learn a different way, Hunter. From you. Thanks... fer takin' a chance on a wolf in old lady's clothin'."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이 기념품... 늑대 이빨이야? 잘난 척하는 것들 말대로 참 \"아프로포\"네.\n"
" !think\n"
" 있잖아, 좀 더 최근엔 늙은 엄마 아빠를 먹여 살리는 게 나랑 마리골드 몫이었어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그런데 가족이 먹고살 만큼 벌려면 공평한 분배만 받아선 안 됐어. 그래서 우린, 어, 예전 방식으로 좀 돌아갈 수밖에 없었지...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 이런 얘긴 하기 싫지만, <#BLUE>The Rotwood</>에 같이 들어간 사람들한테 우린 정직하지 않았어. 거짓말하고, 이간질하고--혼란 만들고, 그런 식으로...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 다른 사람들이 의심이랑 분노로 서로 물어뜯게 만든 다음, 우린 전리품 들고 튀었지.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아이고, 웃으면 안 되는데. 버릇이란 게 그렇지 뭐. 아무튼 마지막 원정도 원래는 똑같이 갈 생각이었어.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 근데 마리골드, 그 바보 거위가 하룻밤 사이에 사나운 늑대가 돼버렸어. 내 나이에 내가 짐이 되기 시작했나 보더라.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 걔는 기회다 싶으니 냉큼 잡았지! 날 추위 속에 버려두고 전리품을 다 가져갔어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 마리골드가?? 말도 안 돼!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 내 생각엔 내가 잘 가르쳤어. 그때 내가 아는 한에서 최선으로.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그래도 안 화나? 걔가 널 배신하고 죽게 내버렸잖아!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 화나냐고? 아니, 아니, 아니. 뭐, 사실 맞아, 화나지. 근데 네 친절 덕분에 알게 됐어. 늑대가 늙은 토끼 하나 사냥했다고 화낼 순 없더라.\n"
" !think\n"
" 그게 그 본성이라면? 그렇게밖에 배우지 못했다면? 그게 걔가 안전해지는 유일한 방법이라면?\n"
" player:\n"
" 흠. 그러네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 난 그냥 다른 길을 배울 기회를 얻어서 고마워, 헌터. 너한테서. 고마워... 늙은 여자 옷 입은 늑대한테 기회를 줘서."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Thanks fer the souvenir, Hunter, but I'll open it on the road. I don't rightly belong here with y'all nice folk. \n"
" player:\n"
" But <i>you're</> nice folk! You're done with the bad stuff... right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm done with the backstabbin' 'n' treachery, that's true. However, there's one final thing I've yet to come clean with...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I've been poisonin' your food, Hunter!\n"
" player:\n"
" Aw, c'mon! That's a harsh way to talk about your... \"unique\" flavour profiles!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Huh? That's not--what'dya mean--??\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Nevermind all that--No! Since I started cookin' for ya, I've been addin' bits o' <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> to yer meals!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I been tryin' ta give ya <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-poisonin' so I could incapacitate ya and make off with yer haul!\n"
" !think\n"
" But as we got ta know one another, and I got ta know the folks you surround yourself with, well...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Guess I've gone soft. Like the plates o' veggies I leave in the sun until they're nice 'n' gooey 'n' stinky 'n' ready ta be served...\n"
" player:\n"
" Ew, what?! Now <i>that</> will poison me...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" You've changed me fer the better, Hunter, <i>and</> given me a new passion for cookery! \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Y'see, cookery is the <i>opposite</> of backstabbin'--why, it's front-stuffin'! So I'm hittin' the road to make good with what time I got left.\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}, please stay! The {name.konjur} you've \"poisoned\" my meals with gives me powers!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" R-really? Ya mean it? Aw, Hunter! You're a saint, I tell ya! A \"bone-a-fined\" saint, as they say! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here--I was gonna sell this to buy a weapon for revengin' on Marigold, but I'm over all that.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" It's yours, Hunter, along with my pledge to keep poisonin' yer food--just how you like it!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!disagree\n"
"기념품은 고맙다… 근데 이건 길 가면서 열어볼게. 난… 너희 같은 좋은 사람들이랑 어울릴 사람은 아닌 것 같거든.\n"
"플레이어:\n"
"근데 <i>너도</> 좋은 사람이잖아! 이제 나쁜 짓은 다 끝난 거지…?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!gesture\n"
"등 뒤에서 칼 꽂는 짓이랑 배신은… 이제 끝냈어. 그건 맞는데… 아직 하나, 제대로 털어놓지 못한 게 있어…\n"
"!closedeyes\n"
"!closedeyes\n"
"사실… 네 음식에 독 넣고 있었어, Hunter!\n"
"플레이어:\n"
"아니 잠깐만! 그건 그냥 너 특유의… \"독특한\" 요리 스타일 얘기하는 거잖아?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!angry\n"
"뭐? 그게 아니라... 아니, 그게 무슨 소리야??\n"
"!disagree\n"
"아니, 그게 아니라! 내가 널 위해 요리하기 시작한 뒤로 계속 네 음식에 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>를 조금씩 넣고 있었단 말이야!\n"
"!shrug\n"
"널 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-중독 상태로 만들어서 쓰러뜨리고, 짐 챙겨서 도망칠 생각이었지!\n"
"!think\n"
"근데… 너랑 지내다 보니까, 그리고 네 주변 사람들도 알게 되니까…\n"
"!shrug\n"
"내가 좀 물러진 것 같더라. 햇볕에 내버려둬서 질척해지고 냄새 올라올 때까지 익히는 그 채소 접시들처럼 말이야…\n"
"player:\n"
"으엑, 뭐야?! <i>그건</> 진짜 나 독살하겠는데…\n"
"agent:\n"
"!point\n"
"넌 날 더 나은 사람으로 바꿔놨어… <i>그리고</> 요리에 대한 새로운 열정도 줬지!\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"알다시피, 요리는 등 뒤에서 찌르는 짓의 <i>반대</>야. 앞에서 꽂아 넣는 거라고! 그래서 남은 시간이라도 제대로 살려고 길을 떠나려는 거야\n"
"플레이어:\n"
"{name.npc_cook} 제발 가지 마! 네가 내 음식에 \"독\" 넣은 그 {name.konjur}덕분에 난 힘을 얻는다고!\n"
"agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!bliss\n"
"지, 진짜냐? 진심이야? 아, Hunter… 넌 진짜 성자다! 뭐라더라… \"뼛속까지 진짜 성자\"라고 해야 하나!\n"
"!gesture\n"
"이거 받아—원래는 Marigold한테 복수하려고 무기 살 돈 만들려고 팔 생각이었는데, 이제 그런 건 됐어.\n"
"!laugh\n"
"이건 네 거다, Hunter. 앞으로도 네 음식에 계속 \"독\" 넣어주겠다는 내 약속까지 같이!\n"
"[알림:보상_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Better luck next time, kid. Tell you what, here's a little consolation prize for ya."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" 다음엔 운이 더 좋겠지, 꼬마. 자, 위로상 하나 줄게."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Is that so? Sounds like I've been going easy on you. I'll keep that in mind!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" In the meantime, here's a little something to keep you motivated."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Is that so? Sounds like I've been going easy on you. I'll keep that in mind!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" In the meantime, here's a little something to keep you motivated."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's this? An apple for the teacher?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's a souvenir from my Hunt. I thought you'd like it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well, now! Trying to get on my good side, are you?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You know that's not gonna get you out of running drills, right?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이게 뭐야? 선생님한테 사과라도 바치는 거냐?\n"
" player:\n"
" 내 사냥에서 가져온 기념품이야. 좋아할 것 같아서!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 오, 그래? 내 환심 사보겠다 이거지?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 그걸로 훈련 빼달라는 건 안 통하는 거 알지?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "<i>(sigh)</> It was worth a shot, at least."
msgstr "<i>(한숨)</> 그래도 시도는 해봤지."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Please. I'm not afraid of anything you throw at me."
msgstr "제발. 네가 뭘 던져도 난 안 무서워."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" An idealist, huh? Well, I guess I was young and full of fire once. I won't hold it against ya."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 이상주의자라, 응? 나도 한때는 젊고 불같았지. 그걸로 뭐라 하진 않겠어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" So how about you focus on your job, and I'll focus on mine?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그러니까 넌 네 일에 집중하고, 난 내 일에 집중하면 어때?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks kid, you shouldn't have--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... are you sure you're okay?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" I'm fine! Don't go worrying about me.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" In fact, you should be grateful I've got this old cough. Otherwise I'd be out there taking down the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> myself, and you'd be out of a job."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 고맙다, 꼬마. 이런 건 안 해도--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" player:\n"
" 음... 너 정말 괜찮은 거 맞아?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 난 괜찮아! 괜히 걱정하지 마.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 오히려 이 오래된 기침이 있어서 감사해야 할걸. 아니었으면 내가 직접 나가 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 잡았을 테고, 넌 일자리 잃었을 거야."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "'Job'? I volunteered to come here!"
msgstr "'일자리'라고? 난 자원해서 온 건데!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Fair point."
msgstr "맞는 말이네."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. All these souvenirs are almost makin' me miss being out there myself. I wonder how much it's changed since the early days...\n"
" player: \n"
" I've heard rumours... were you really part of the first Hunting party after the eruption?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Kid, I <i>led</> that Hunting party.\n"
" player:\n"
" What?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hey, don't sound so surprised! I was <#BLUE>the Rotwood's</> top Hunter back in the day. Heck, I bet I could still fight out there as good as any--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" player:\n"
" Err... riiiight.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You know what? I think I'm gonna add fifty more pushups to your training regimen."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 헤. 기념품이 이렇게 쌓이니까 예전처럼 현장에 있던 때가 거의 그립네. 초창기랑 얼마나 달라졌을까...\n"
" player: \n"
" 소문으로 들었어... 대폭발 이후 첫 사냥대에 정말 있었어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 꼬마야, 그 사냥대는 내가 <i>이끌었어</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 야, 그렇게 놀라지 마! 옛날에 난 <#BLUE>the Rotwood의</> 최고 헌터였어. 젠장, 지금도 누구 못지않게 싸울 수--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" player:\n"
" 어... 그으래.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 있지? 훈련에 팔굽혀펴기 50개 추가다."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well, what have we got here? Another fine--\n"
" !very_sick\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><z 0.8>(cough cough cough <i>HACK</> cough)</z></i></> Ugh...\n"
" player:\n"
" Okay, that sounded <i>really</> bad. Have you ever seen a doctor about that cough?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Heh. What, one of those old sawbones working out of a shack in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>? Not on your life.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Besides, there's plenty of other folks who need the help more than me. No sense wasting resources on an old {name.species_ogre} who's well past his prime.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hold up, making sure you're okay is <i>not</> a waste!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Don't get your bloomers in a bunch, kid. Truth is, with the kind of life I've lived, it's a miracle I've lasted this long. If you think this silly little cough would be enough to do me in, well--!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !point\n"
" ...You can forget it!\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm not just going to forget it. I'm worried about you!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Sheesh, kid. You've got it all backwards. I'm your teacher--I'm the one supposed to be worrying about <i>you</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>(grumble)</>... Alright, fine. I'll get checked out next time we're back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. Happy?\n"
" player:\n"
" I'll be happy as long as you take better care of yourself.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Pffft. If you're happy, I ain't doin' my job. Addin' a hunnert more squats to your training regimen!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자, 또 뭐가 들어왔나 보자... 또 다른...?\n"
" !very sick\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><z 0.8>(콜록 콜록 콜록 <i>컥</> 콜록)</z></i></> 윽...\n"
" player:\n"
" 야. <i>진짜</> 괜찮아?  의사한테 가본 적 있어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 뭐, <#BLUE>the Brinks</> 판잣집에서 보는 돌팔이들 말이냐? 죽어도 싫어.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...게다가 나보다 도움 더 필요한 사람이 많아. 한물간 늙은 {name.species_ogre}한테 자원 낭비할 이유 없지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 잠깐, 네 상태 확인하는 건 <i>절대</> 낭비 아니야!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 호들갑 떨지 마, 꼬마. 사실 이런 인생 살고도 지금까지 버틴 게 기적이야. 이 하찮은 기침이 날 끝장낼 거라 생각하면, 뭐--!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !point\n"
" ...잊어버려!\n"
" player:\n"
" 안 잊어. 난 네가 걱정돼!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...아이고, 꼬마야. 완전 거꾸로네. 난 네 스승이야. 걱정해야 할 건 <i>너</>지.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>(투덜)</>... 알았다, 됐어. 다음에 <#BLUE>the Brinks</> 돌아가면 검사받을게. 됐냐?\n"
" player:\n"
" 네가 몸 관리 더 잘하면 그걸로 됐어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 풉. 네가 행복하면 난 일 못 하는 거지. 훈련에 스쿼트 100개 추가다!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Look at this souvenir. What do you see?\n"
" player:\n"
" Um. I see it's still wrapped. Aren't you going to open it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No! The point IS the wrapping, kid! Today's lesson: camouflage!\n"
" !point\n"
" You think how you look out there doesn't impact your survival? \n"
" !angry\n"
" WRONG!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Wear armour that makes you look a fool? Those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}'ll</> be laughin' at ya! They'll have the confidence and you won't!\n"
" !angry\n"
" And out there, an edge is an edge, dagnabbit! \n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !think\n"
" So! We old Hunters developed a trick to change our appearance to suit our needs. We'd grind up some <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> into <#KONJUR>{name.gem_dust}</>, y'see?\n"
" !agree\n"
" Then, by sprinkling it around us just so, we could create an illusion of a completely different armour set!\n"
" !point\n"
" I give to you: The <#RED>{name.i_vanity_screen}</>!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Use your <#KONJUR>{name.i_gem_dust}</> to make your armour look how you want it so you don't just survive, you slay. \n"
" player: \n"
" Wow! Thanks, {name.npc_dojo_master}! ...So, I'm just gonna open your souvenir <i>for</> you...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Fourty burpees added to your training regimen."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이 기념품 봐라. 뭐가 보이냐?\n"
" player:\n"
" 음. 아직 포장돼 있는 거? 안 열어볼 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아니! 핵심은 포장이야, 꼬마! 오늘 수업: 위장!\n"
" !point\n"
" 현장에서 네가 어떻게 보이는지가 생존에 영향 없을 것 같아?\n"
" !angry\n"
" 틀렸어!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 바보처럼 보이는 갑옷을 입으면? 저 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}들은</> 널 비웃어! 자신감은 걔들한테 가고 넌 잃지!\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그리고 밖에선 작은 우위도 우위야, 젠장!\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래서! 우리 옛 헌터들은 필요에 맞게 겉모습을 바꾸는 기술을 만들었어. <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>을 갈아서 <#KONJUR>{name.gem_dust}</>로 만들었지, 알겠냐?\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그걸 딱 맞게 흩뿌리면 완전히 다른 갑옷 세트 환영을 만들 수 있었어!\n"
" !point\n"
" 이름하여: <#RED>{name.i_vanity_screen}</>!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name.i_gem_dust}</>을 써서 네 갑옷을 원하는 모습으로 바꿔. 그냥 살아남는 게 아니라 압도하는 거야.\n"
" player: \n"
" 와! 고마워, {name.npc_dojo_master}! ...자, 그럼 기념품 <i>은</> 내가 열어줄게...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 훈련에 버피 40개 추가."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Another souvenir, huh? I just hope you're not letting yourself get distracted-- you're out there to hunt <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, not look for shiny trinkets.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Maybe I should up the intensity of your training, just to be on the safe side.\n"
" player:\n"
" Come on, give me a break! Is training all you think about?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You bet it is! And it should be all you think about too. The moment you let up, the <i>second</> you let your guard down, it's over. I'm not seein' another Hunter go down on my watch.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait... did you just say, 'another'?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...I'm givin' you an extra hour of target practice, first thing tomorrow."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 또 기념품이냐? 정신 팔린 건 아니길 바란다--넌 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 사냥하러 나가는 거지 반짝이 장난감 찾으러 가는 게 아냐.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 안전하게 가려면 훈련 강도를 더 올려야겠네.\n"
" player:\n"
" 제발 좀 봐줘! 넌 머릿속에 훈련밖에 없어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 물론이지! 너도 그래야 해. 힘을 빼는 순간, 방심하는 <i>그</> 순간 끝장이야. 내 눈앞에서 헌터 하나 더 잃는 일은 없어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 잠깐... 방금 '더'라고 했어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...내일 아침 첫 일정으로 표적 훈련 1시간 추가다."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Kid... where did you find this?\n"
" player:\n"
" Out in the wilds, where I found all my other souvenirs. Why?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" These bracers... belonged to a Hunter named Pike. Bravest Amphibee I ever met, and outright deadly with a spear. Saved my hide more than once.\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh. Why would they have left their bracers lying out in the wilds?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...I need to get to work on your training regimen. One session a day isn't enough--I'd better double it.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 꼬마... 이거 어디서 찾았냐?\n"
" player:\n"
" 다른 기념품 찾던 그 야생지대에서. 왜?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이 완갑은... 파이크라는 헌터 거였어. 내가 본 앰피비 중 제일 용감했고, 창 솜씨는 완전 살벌했지. 내 목숨도 여러 번 구해줬어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 응? 저 녀석이 왜 완갑을 야생에 두고 갔지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...네 훈련 계획 짜야겠다. 하루 한 번으론 부족해--두 배로 늘린다.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for the gift, kid. How are those hammies of yours? You were looking a little stiff in our last sparring match.\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, I'm sore <i>all over</>, but that's not what's bugging me. I want to know about Pike.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Pike...?\n"
" player:\n"
" You seemed upset when you saw those bracers. Did something happen?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Last time I saw Pike... I'd just taken a bad slash to the eye, and he was coverin' our retreat. One moment he was there, and the next... and the next, he wasn't.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" That <#RED>Rusty Skewer</> was all I was ever able to find. Until you brought me those bracers, anyway.\n"
" player: \n"
" You mean... the Rusty Skewer on the weapons rack...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yeah.\n"
" player:\n"
" And the Bammer? The Striker? Were they <i>all</>...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" They don't look like much now, but every one of those old weapons used to belong to a great Hunter... and a dear friend. It's up to us now, to carry on where they left off.\n"
" player:\n"
" I... had no idea...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. 'Course you didn't! It's not something I was too keen to bring up.\n"
" !point\n"
" Well, no need to get all mopey now--we've got your training to focus on. I'm makin' sure you're the strongest Hunter <#BLUE>the Rotwood</> has ever seen! \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You've gotta be unbeatable! Nothin' less will do, got it?\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 선물 고맙다, 꼬마. 햄스트링은 어때? 지난 대련 때 좀 뻣뻣해 보이던데.\n"
" player:\n"
" 온몸이 <i>다 아프긴</> 한데, 그게 문제가 아냐. 파이크 얘기 듣고 싶어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 파이크...?\n"
" player:\n"
" 그 완갑 봤을 때 많이 흔들리던데. 무슨 일 있었어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 내가 파이크를 마지막으로 봤을 때... 난 눈에 심하게 베여 있었고, 걘 우리 퇴각을 엄호하고 있었어. 한순간엔 있었는데, 다음 순간... 다음 순간엔 없었지.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 내가 찾을 수 있었던 건 <#RED>Rusty Skewer</>뿐이었어. 네가 그 완갑 가져오기 전까진.\n"
" player: \n"
" 그러면... 무기 거치대의 Rusty Skewer가...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그래.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 배머랑 스트라이커도? <i>전부</>...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 지금은 볼품없지만, 저 낡은 무기 하나하나가 원래는 위대한 헌터의 것이었어... 그리고 소중한 친구들이었지. 이제 우리가 녀석들이 멈춘 곳부터 이어가야 해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 나... 전혀 몰랐어...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 헤. 당연히 몰랐지! 내가 굳이 꺼내고 싶은 얘긴 아니었으니까.\n"
" !point\n"
" 자, 우울해할 필요 없다--이제 네 훈련에 집중하자. <#BLUE>the Rotwood</> 역사상 최강 헌터로 만들어줄 테니까!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 넌 무조건 무적이어야 해! 그 이하는 안 된다, 알겠지?\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Heh. A real checkers set! Why, let's throw down, junior!\n"
" player:\n"
" Right now?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Live in the moment! If ya ain't gonna do somethin' now, when are ya, huh?\n"
" player:\n"
" I actually wanted to talk to you about why you're so tough on me. I figured it out.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" That so? I didn't think I was being tough at all--who doesn't like wakin' up to a surprise round of combat practice from time to time?\n"
" player:\n"
" Most sane people. But I realized it's how you show you care.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...'Course I care. That's the whole problem. If anything happened to you out there... I don't know how I'd live with myself.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You gotta understand... I've lost a lot of things I cared about over the years. My home, an eye, my team... no, my <i>friends</>...\n"
" !point\n"
" But if I can prepare you enough, if I can make sure you're the best of the best--maybe this time things can turn out different. I won't let you down like I let down the others.\n"
" player:\n"
" You didn't let them down. Even you can't control everything that happens.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" But if I'd just done things differently...\n"
" player:\n"
" You told me to 'live in the moment'. So why are you keeping yourself locked in the past?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" That's...!\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Usin' my own lessons against me, huh? Tricky move there, kid..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 헤. 진짜 체커 세트네! 자, 한 판 붙자, 꼬마!\n"
" player:\n"
" 지금?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 지금을 살아! 지금 안 할 거면 대체 언제 하려고, 응?\n"
" player:\n"
" 사실 난 네가 왜 나한테 그렇게 빡세게 구는지 얘기하고 싶었어. 이제 알겠어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래? 난 빡세다고 생각한 적 없는데--가끔 깜짝 실전 연습으로 눈뜨는 걸 싫어하는 사람이 있나?\n"
" player:\n"
" 멀쩡한 사람은 거의 다 싫어해. 근데 그게 네 방식의 애정표현이라는 걸 알았어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...당연히 신경 쓰지. 그게 문제의 전부야. 밖에서 네게 무슨 일이라도 생기면... 난 나 자신을 못 견딜 거야.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 알아둬... 난 세월 동안 소중한 걸 많이 잃었어. 집, 눈 하나, 팀... 아니, <i>친구들</>...\n"
" !point\n"
" 하지만 내가 널 충분히 준비시키고, 최고 중의 최고로 만들 수만 있다면--이번엔 결과가 달라질지도 몰라. 다른 사람들처럼 널 실망시키진 않겠어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 넌 녀석들을 실망시킨 게 아냐. 너라도 모든 일을 통제할 순 없어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그래도 내가 다르게 했더라면...\n"
" player:\n"
" 넌 나한테 '지금을 살아'라고 했잖아. 그런데 왜 넌 스스로를 과거에 가둬 두고 있어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 그건...!\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 내 가르침을 나한테 써먹는다고? 수 좀 쓰네, 꼬마..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Thanks, kid. Been meaning to talk to you...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I've been thinking about what you said. About blaming myself for what happened back then.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. I'm always harpin' on folks thinking so far into the future that it freezes them up. Then there I was, stuck in the past.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe it's time for this old trainer to learn some new tricks. Stop wallowin' in guilt and start looking ahead.\n"
" player:\n"
" I think that's what your friends would've wanted.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yeah. And I think it's what I want too. Time to start takin' better care of myself, and showin' a better example.\n"
" player:\n"
" Does this mean you'll start going easier on me in training?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Ha! Far from it! I'm all fired up now--time to kick things into high gear!\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Why am I not surprised.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Though maybe it wouldn't hurt to take some breaks in-between. It's important to take care of yourself, you know!\n"
" player:\n"
" Sounds like some pretty good advice to me.\n"
" agent:\n"
" Well, anyway... <i>(ahem)</>... I, er... got this for you. As a thanks. For everything.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 고맙다, 꼬마. 너랑 할 말이 있었어...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 네가 한 말을 생각해봤어. 그때 일로 나 자신을 탓하는 거.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 헤. 난 늘 사람들이 먼 미래만 보고 얼어붙는다고 잔소리했는데. 정작 난 과거에 박혀 있었네.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 이 늙은 교관도 새 기술 좀 배워야 할 때인가 봐. 죄책감에 빠져 허우적대는 건 그만하고 앞을 봐야지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 네 친구들도 그걸 원했을 거야.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그래. 그리고 나도 그걸 원하는 것 같아. 몸도 더 챙기고, 더 좋은 본보기도 보여줘야지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그럼 훈련에서 나 좀 덜 굴리는 거야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 하! 어림없지! 지금 완전 불붙었거든--이제 기어를 최고로 올린다!\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 왜 예상했는데도 놀랍지 않지.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" ...그래도 중간중간 쉬는 건 나쁘지 않겠지. 몸 챙기는 게 중요하니까, 알지!\n"
" player:\n"
" 꽤 괜찮은 조언 같은데.\n"
" agent:\n"
" 아무튼... <i>(크흠)</>... 나, 어... 이거 네 거다. 고맙다는 뜻으로. 여러모로.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_refiner.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_refiner.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Is this the <#RED>Souvenir</> I asked for? Nice. I can read its <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> signature from here!\n"
" player:\n"
" Really! It's just a little button pin with \"Go Rot Yourself!\" written on it...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" \"Go Rot Yourself!\" He he he! Love it. Just pure attitude. A preemptive finger in the eye of The Man tryin' to keep you down. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" I totally would've worn this back when I worked for <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>. \n"
" !think\n"
" Did you know my research was in how to imbue <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} crystals</> with energy, or \"<#KONJUR>Teffressence</>\"?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" When I saw <#BLUE>Doc's</> Mech, its crystals <i>imbued</> with <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>... My jaw hit the floor.\n"
" !angry\n"
" He turned my research into WEAPONS! Weapons that almost ended the WORLD! I felt so much shame. Like it was my fault. But no more.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Time for an attitude adjustment, Hunter. Take this <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" You're giving me a NEW WEAPON?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yep. I liberated it from Doc's Lab to keep it from being used at all. But it needs to be used--for good. \n"
" !point\n"
" Now--before I give it to you, there's a method to its madness...\n"
" !angry\n"
" First: it's very fragile. If you fail a {name.run} with this equipped, it'll <#RED>break</>. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> <i>can</> repair it, with enough <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" But with risk comes reward. \n"
" !think\n"
" Use it to beat an <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</>, and it'll get charged with their <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</>! Kinda like this button pin!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" While a <#RED>Charged {name.weapon_crystal}</> is powerful--it's still <#RED>breakable</>. \n"
" !shocked\n"
" Once you Charge it, take it back to <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>! \n"
" !point\n"
" He can then <i>re-forge</> it into a permanently-charged, <i>unbreakable</> <#RED>{name.weapon_boss}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh! And until you charge <i>this</> <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> for the first time, <i>I'll</> cover its repair costs. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" After that, the cost is on you. So be careful, alright? I'm not made of <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}</> over here.\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now take the <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>! And may your enemies GO ROT THEMSELVES!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 내가 부탁한 <#RED>기념품</> 맞아? 좋네. 여기서도 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 시그니처가 읽혀!\n"
" player:\n"
" 진짜? \"Go Rot Yourself!\"라고 적힌 작은 버튼 핀일 뿐인데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" \"Go Rot Yourself!\" 헤헤헤! 맘에 든다. 순수한 태도지. 널 짓누르려는 권력에 선빵으로 한 방 먹이는 느낌.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 예전에 <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</> 밑에서 일할 때였으면 나도 무조건 달고 다녔을걸.\n"
" !think\n"
" 내 연구가 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} crystals</>에 에너지를 주입하는 방식, 즉 \"<#KONJUR>Teffressence</>\"였다는 거 알았어?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <#BLUE>Doc의</> 메크를 봤을 때, 그 크리스털이 <i>주입돼</> 있는 <#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}</>를 보고... 턱이 떨어졌어.\n"
" !angry\n"
" 그 인간은 내 연구를 무기로 만들었어! 세상을 거의 끝장낼 뻔한 무기로! 난 죄책감에 짓눌렸지. 다 내 탓 같았어. 하지만 이제 끝이야.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 태도 교정할 시간이다, 헌터. 이 <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 받아.\n"
" player:\n"
" 새 무기를 준다고?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 맞아. 아예 안 쓰이게 하려고 Doc 연구실에서 빼돌렸어. 근데 이건 써야 해--좋은 일에.\n"
" !point\n"
" 자, 주기 전에 이 정신 나간 물건의 작동 방식부터...\n"
" !angry\n"
" 첫째: 엄청 약해. 이걸 장착하고 {name.run}에 실패하면 <#RED>부서져</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> <i>가</> <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}</>만 충분하면 수리할 수 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 하지만 위험엔 보상이 따르지.\n"
" !think\n"
" 이걸로 <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</>를 쓰러뜨리면, 걔들의 <#KONJUR>태고의 테프레센스</>로 충전돼! 이 버튼 핀처럼!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>충전된 {name.weapon_crystal}</>은 강력하지만--여전히 <#RED>부서질 수 있어</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 충전하고 나면 <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>한테 가져가!\n"
" !point\n"
" 그러면 그가 <i>재단조</>해서 영구 충전된 <i>파괴 불가</> <#RED>{name.weapon_boss}</>로 만들어줄 거야!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 아! 그리고 <i>이</> <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>를 처음 충전하기 전까진 <i>내가</> 수리비를 내줄게.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 그다음부턴 네가 내야 해. 그러니 조심해, 알겠지? 나도 <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}</>으로 만들어진 건 아니라고.\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자, 이 <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 받아! 그리고 네 적들한테 GO ROT THEMSELVES를 선물해!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Some leader I turned out to be. I got knocked out of the sky, lost half the team...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hm? What's this, Hunter?\n"
" player:\n"
" A souvenir from my Hunt! I thought it would cheer you up.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" F-for me? I-I don't know what to say... thank you, Hunter. It <i>is</> cheering me up.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We could use more of that around here--some <i>personal touches</> to make this place feel like home.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know what? I'm feeling inspired! I'll draft up some designs. Then we can start decorating!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 지도자 꼴이 이게 뭐람. 하늘에서 격추당하고, 팀도 절반이나 잃고...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 음? 이건 뭐야, 헌터?\n"
" player:\n"
" 내 사냥에서 가져온 기념품! 기분 좀 나아질까 해서.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 나, 나한테? 무, 무슨 말을 해야 할지... 고마워, 헌터. 이거 <i>진짜</> 기운이 나네.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 여기엔 이런 게 더 필요해--<i>개인적인 손길</> 같은 거. 그래야 여기가 집처럼 느껴지거든.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !think\n"
" 있잖아! 갑자기 영감이 막 떠오르는데! 내가 도면을 좀 그려볼 테니까, 그러고 나서 본격적으로 꾸며보자고!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" OH, really? Grandpa always thought it was silly. Or \"superfluous,\" as he put it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for the encouragement, Hunter!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 오, 정말? 할아버지는 늘 그런 건 바보 같다고 했거든. 정확히는 \"쓸데없이 과하다\"고.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 응원해줘서 고마워, 헌터!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! It's alright. I know it's a bit superfluous, but it makes me happy, so to heck with it!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But don't worry, I won't let it get in the way of our expedition!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하! 괜찮아. 좀 과한 건 맞지만, 난 그게 좋거든. 그러니까 알 바 아니지!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그래도 걱정 마, 원정에 방해되게 하진 않을게!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Another souvenir? I'll have to find the perfect place to put it...\n"
" player:\n"
" I had no idea you liked decorating so much.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Oh, well, it's just something I've liked since I was a kit.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" There's something about it, investing a place with some thought and care... it makes it feel more like a home.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Like magic! Well, not <i>magic</>-magic, like what {name.c_konjur} can do, but...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" A-anyways... sorry, I'm rambling..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 또 기념품이네? 어디에 두면 딱일지 찾아봐야겠다...\n"
" player:\n"
" 네가 꾸미는 걸 그렇게 좋아하는지 몰랐어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아, 뭐, 어릴 때부터 좋아하던 거야.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 장소에 생각과 정성을 담는 느낌이 있잖아... 그러면 더 집 같아져.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 마법 같달까! 뭐, <i>진짜 마법</>은 아니고 {name.c_konjur}가 하는 그런 건 아니지만...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아, 아무튼... 미안, 내가 너무 떠들었네..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "No, no, I completely agree."
msgstr "아냐 아냐, 완전 동감해."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "It's a bit 'woo-woo' for me, but I respect your passion."
msgstr "내 취향엔 좀 '우우'한데, 네 열정은 존중해."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I-is this a <i>real</> ceramic coffee mug? And it's barely even chipped! Wow. This is quite the find, Hunter.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" It's a shame someone seems to have scribbled on it.\n"
" player:\n"
" That was me. Go ahead and read it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Apologies! Let's see here, it says... um... <i>'#1 Skort'?</> <z 0.7>Uh, wow... so thoughtful...</>\n"
" player:\n"
" What the--?! It's <i>supposed</> to say '#1 Scout'! I guess my handwriting isn't the best...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>(snrk!)</> Ahem--Actually, I think it's perfect this way. Thank you, Hunter!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I-is this a <i>real</> ceramic coffee mug? And it's barely even chipped! Wow. This is quite the find, Hunter.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" It's a shame someone seems to have scribbled on it.\n"
" player:\n"
" That was me. Go ahead and read it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Apologies! Let's see here, it says... um... <i>'#1 Skort'?</> <z 0.7>Uh, wow... so thoughtful...</>\n"
" player:\n"
" What the--?! It's <i>supposed</> to say '#1 Scout'! I guess my handwriting isn't the best...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>(snrk!)</> Ahem--Actually, I think it's perfect this way. Thank you, Hunter!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's that you're hiding, Hunter?\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, just another souvenir for my \"#1 Skort\"!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I'm sure you say that to all the skorts--Oh! \n"
" !dubious\n"
" It's <i>another</> mug with \"#1 Skort\" written on it instead of \"#1 Scout\"! Er, thanks! \n"
" player:\n"
" So... am I your favourite Hunter?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh! Oh, sure, yes, absolutely! Top fi--top ten, at least.\n"
" player:\n"
" Top ten?! C'mon!!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Sorry Hunter, I couldn't resist!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 헌터, 뭐 숨기고 있어?\n"
" player:\n"
" 아, 그냥 내 \"#1 Skort\"를 위한 또 다른 기념품!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 너 모든 스코트한테 그렇게 말하는 거 아냐--오!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" \"#1 Scout\" 대신 \"#1 Skort\"가 적힌 <i>또 다른</> 머그네! 어, 고마워!\n"
" player:\n"
" 그래서... 내가 네 최애 헌터야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 오! 어, 그럼, 맞아, 당연하지! 탑 파--탑 텐 안엔 들어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 탑 텐?! 에이!!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 미안 헌터, 한 번 놀려보고 싶었어!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh, what's this? It looks like a little dancing <#RED>{name.rot}</> on a spring...\n"
" player:\n"
" I thought it'd look good on the {name.i_damselfly}'s dashboard.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I think you're right! You know, I haven't done much to decorate the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> since I first built it--this will be a long-overdue upgrade.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" You've been so thoughtful, bringing back all these souvenirs. I... might've picked up a little something for you, too. Hope you like it, b-but if not, feel free to give it away!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 어, 이거 뭐지? 스프링 위에서 춤추는 작은 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 같네...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.i_damselfly} 대시보드에 두면 잘 어울릴 것 같아서.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 네 말이 맞는 것 같아! 생각해보니 <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>를 처음 만들고 나서 꾸민 게 거의 없었거든--이건 정말 오래 미뤄둔 업그레이드야.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 네가 이렇게 기념품을 계속 챙겨와서 너무 고마워. 나도... 너한테 줄 걸 조금 준비했어. 마음에 들면 좋겠다, 하-하지만 아니면 다른 사람 줘도 돼!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ah, well--I wouldn't say my engine's perfect, it's not nearly as powerful as a {name.c_konjur} engine. It'll do fine for now, though.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks again for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 음, 뭐--내 엔진이 완벽하다고는 못 하지. {name.c_konjur} 엔진만큼 강력하진 않거든. 그래도 지금은 충분해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 선물 다시 한 번 고마워, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" That was my Grandpa's dream. He believed {name.c_konjur} would make everyone's lives better. Maybe we can get back there.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks again for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그건 우리 할아버지의 꿈이었어. {name.c_konjur}가 모두의 삶을 더 좋게 만들 거라고 믿었거든. 우리도 거기로 돌아갈 수 있을지 몰라.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 선물 다시 한 번 고마워, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oh, this lightcatcher will go splendidly with the little dancing <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> figurine you gave me, Hunter. The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> has never looked better!\n"
" player:\n"
" Did you really build the {name.i_damselfly} yourself?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yep. The biggest challenge was designing an engine that didn't rely on {name.c_konjur} for fuel.\n"
" player:\n"
" It doesn't?! I thought <i>everything</> ran on {name.konjur}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>Most</> things do, but you know how hard it is to get your hands on {name.c_konjur} in <#BLUE>the Brinks.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Plus, I didn't want to rely on those shady scavengers who sell corroded old {name.c_konjur} batteries, and whatever else manages to wash up on shore.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" On top of all that, my allergy makes it pretty much impossible for me to work with a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-powered</> engine, so I had to get creative."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 오, 이 라이트캐처는 네가 준 춤추는 작은 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 피규어랑 정말 잘 어울리겠다, 헌터. <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>가 이렇게 좋아 보인 적이 없네!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.i_damselfly}를 네가 직접 만들었어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 응. 가장 큰 난관은 연료로 {name.c_konjur}에 의존하지 않는 엔진을 설계하는 거였어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 안 쓴다고?! 난 <i>모든 게</> {name.konjur}로 돌아가는 줄 알았는데!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>대부분은</> 그렇지. 하지만 <#BLUE>the Brinks에서</> {name.c_konjur} 구하기가 얼마나 힘든지 알잖아.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 게다가 부식된 낡은 {name.c_konjur} 배터리 같은 걸 파는 수상한 스캐빈저들한테 의존하고 싶지도 않았어. 해안으로 떠밀려온 거라면 뭐든 파는 애들 말이야.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 거기에 더해서 내 알레르기 때문에 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-동력</> 엔진은 사실상 다루기 힘들어서, 창의적으로 가야 했지."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Maybe we don't need to rely on {name.konjur} as much as we think."
msgstr "우리가 생각하는 것만큼 {name.konjur}에 의존할 필요는 없을지도 몰라."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "It's impressive, but <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}'s</> so powerful--I hope we can use it like we did before."
msgstr "인상적이긴 한데, <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}의</> 힘이 워낙 강해서--예전처럼 쓸 수 있으면 좋겠다."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I remember those! Oh, the crust alone! So flaky... so buttery...\n"
" !think\n"
" But my favourite part was the dancing. I was too young to join in, but I'd imagine myself out there, dancing with a partner...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I never got the chance. After the eruption... well, there's hasn't been much to celebrate in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !shrug \n"
" Things like festivals sort of fall by the wayside when you're just trying to survive.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Still... I like to think that one day, when this is all over, we'll have things like the Spring Festival again.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Maybe I'll even get that dance. Hm.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... But I'm getting ahead of myself. Thank you for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 기억나! 아, 그 파이 크러스트! 엄청 바삭하고... 버터 풍미도 진하고...\n"
" !think\n"
" 근데 내가 제일 좋아한 건 춤이었어. 난 너무 어려서 같이 못 췄지만, 파트너랑 춤추는 상상을 하곤 했지...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 결국 그 기회는 못 왔어. 대폭발 이후엔... <#BLUE>the Brinks</>에서 축하할 일이 별로 없었으니까.\n"
" !shrug \n"
" 살아남기 바쁘면 축제 같은 건 자연히 뒤로 밀려나지.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그래도... 언젠가 이 모든 게 끝나면, 다시 봄 축제 같은 걸 할 수 있을 거라 믿고 싶어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 어쩌면 그때는 나도 그 춤을 출 수 있겠지. 흠.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...하지만 내가 너무 앞서갔네. 선물 고마워, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I understand. It can be painful to dwell on the past. Especially with so much ahead of us to think about.\n"
" !think\n"
" Even if our expedition is successful, the eruption caused so much damage to <#BLUE>the Rotwood</>... I wonder if we'll be able to plant again like we used to...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... No sense in worrying about that now. Thank you for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 이해해. 과거에 오래 머무는 건 아플 때가 있지. 특히 앞으로 생각할 게 이렇게 많은데.\n"
" !think\n"
" 원정이 성공해도, 대폭발이 <#BLUE>the Rotwood</>에 남긴 피해가 너무 커서... 예전처럼 다시 심을 수 있을까 걱정돼...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...지금 그걸 걱정해봤자 소용없지. 선물 고마워, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Thanks for the souvenir, Hunter. I was just thinking...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Do you remember the Spring Festivals back before the eruption?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Folks used to gather from far and wide to celebrate the planting season, with food, music, and dancing--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 기념품 고마워, 헌터. 마침 생각하고 있었는데...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 대폭발 전 봄 축제 기억나?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 사람들은 파종철을 축하하려고 사방에서 모였어, 음식이랑 음악, 춤이랑 함께--"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I remember! There was a stall that sold the BEST mixed berry pie."
msgstr "기억나! 최고로 맛있는 믹스베리 파이 팔던 가판대가 있었지."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "I try to stay focused on the future, not the past."
msgstr "난 과거보다 미래에 집중하려고 해."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Thanks for the souvenir, Hunter! I wish I had something to give you...\n"
" player:\n"
" How about some insight into what was it like growing up with <i>the</> {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, sure! Grandpa and I, we were thick as thieves. Whatever experiment he was doing, I was front row center. To me, he was larger than life. He knew everything, could do anything.  \n"
" !agree\n"
" And it wasn't just me. Grandpa's devotion to {name.c_konjur}, using it to make <#BLUE>the Rotwood</> a better place, it inspired <i>everyone.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Sometimes... sometimes I worried that having me around slowed him down... particularly after I developed my allergy. I think that was really hard on him.\n"
" player:\n"
" So you didn't always have a {name.konjur} allergy?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" At first, I was around {name.c_konjur} all the time with Grandpa--zero issue. But over time, symptoms began to crop up.\n"
" !think\n"
" No one had heard of such an allergy, but I think my Grandpa worried about how it might affect folks' view of {name.c_konjur} and his <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> system.\n"
" player:\n"
" He was worried about the {name.i_town_grid_cryst} system? What about <i>you?</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" That's... that's beside the point. <i>I</> was the one causing problems for <i>him.</>\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_scout}...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I have some calculations that need calculating. I'll see you on your next Hunt.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!disagree\n"
"기념품 고마워요, 헌터! 저도 뭔가 드릴 수 있으면 좋을 텐데...\n"
"player:\n"
"<i></> {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}와 함께 있었을때 그는 어땠어?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"아, 물론이죠! 할아버지랑 나는 정말 각별했어.\n"
"그분이 어떤 실험을 하시든, 저는 늘 바로 옆에서 지켜보고 있었지.\n"
"나에게 할아버지는... 정말 대단하신 분이었어.\n"
"모든 걸 알고, 뭐든 해낼 수 있는 사람 같았거든.\n\n"
"!agree\n"
"그건 나만 그런 게 아니었어.\n"
"({name.c_konjur}) 를 이용해서 <#BLUE>Rotwood</>를 더 나은 곳으로 만들기 위한 할아버지의 헌신은 <i>모든 사람</>에게 큰 영감을 줬지.\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"가끔은... 내가 옆에 있는 게 그분 발목을 잡는 건 아닐까 걱정되기도 했어...\n"
"특히 제가 알레르기가 생긴 이후에는.\n"
"그게... 그분께 꽤 힘든 일이었던 것 같아.\n\n"
"player:\n"
"그럼 {name.konjur} 알레르기가 처음부터 있었던 것은 아니었나요?\n\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shrug\n"
"처음에 나는 항상 할아버지랑 같이 {name.c_konjur} 주변에 있어도 아무 문제 없었어. 정말.\n"
"그런데 시간이 지나면서... 점점 증상이 나타나기 시작하더라.\n\n"
"!think\n"
"그런 알레르기는 들어본 적도 없었지만,\n"
"할아버지는 그게  {name.c_konjur}나\n"
"자신의 <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> 시스템에 대한 사람들의 시선에 영향을 줄까 봐 걱정하셨지.\n\n"
"플레이어:\n"
"그 {name.i_town_grid_cryst} 시스템이 걱정되셨다고요? 그럼... <i>당신</>은요?\n\n"
"agent:\n"
"!angry\n"
"그건... 그건 중요한 게 아니야.\n"
"<i>문제를 일으킨 건 나니까.</>\n\n"
"player:\n"
"{name.npc_scout}...\n\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!disagree\n"
"계산할 게 좀 있어서\n"
"다음 사냥 때 보자.\n\n"
"[알림:보상_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" And I didn't mean to get so defensive. Asking why my Grandpa wasn't more concerned about my allergy... it hit a nerve, I guess."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 그리고 그렇게 방어적으로 굴 생각은 없었어. 할아버지가 왜 내 알레르기를 더 걱정하지 않았냐고 물은 거... 좀 건드려진 것 같아."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" A-asking why my Grandpa wasn't more concerned about my allergy... it hit a nerve, I guess."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 하-할아버지가 왜 내 알레르기를 더 걱정하지 않았냐고 물은 거... 좀 건드려진 것 같아."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" This... this is for me? I kind of thought... after our last talk...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I'm sorry, Hunter. You were just trying to be kind, and I... didn't respond well."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이거... 이거 나 주는 거야? 난 좀... 지난번 얘기하고 나서...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 미안해, 헌터. 넌 그냥 친절하려던 거였는데, 난... 반응을 잘 못했어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" If... If I'm really being honest with myself, I'm not sure I was as important to him as <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> was.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" He was a... complicated fox. He could be so warm and wonderful--with the best hugs, and the biggest laugh... but other times, it was like I was invisible...\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm so sorry. That must have been tough.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I've... never really acknowledged that side of him before. I suppose I'd always rationalized that it was a necessary function of his devotion to his duty...\n"
" !think\n"
" He took me in when my parents passed, and I'll always be grateful for that, but... it was hard sometimes, never knowing what version of my Grandpa I'd be getting day-to-day.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" After losing him in the eruption, it was easier to remember all the good times, and try to forget the bad.\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm glad you told me.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks Hunter... I am too."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 내가 정말 솔직해지자면, <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>만큼 내가 저 녀석한테 중요했는지 잘 모르겠어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 저 녀석은... 복잡한 여우였어. 엄청 따뜻하고 멋질 때도 있었지. 최고의 포옹에 제일 큰 웃음까지... 근데 어떤 때는 내가 투명인간인 것 같았어...\n"
" player:\n"
" 미안해. 많이 힘들었겠다.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 나도... 저 녀석의 그런 면을 진짜로 인정해 본 적은 없었던 것 같아. 의무에 대한 헌신 때문에 어쩔 수 없는 부분이라고 늘 합리화했거든...\n"
" !think\n"
" 부모님이 돌아가셨을 때 날 거둬준 건 평생 고마워할 일이야. 하지만... 매일매일 어떤 할아버지를 마주하게 될지 모르는 건 힘들었어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 대폭발에서 저 녀석을 잃고 나선, 좋은 기억만 떠올리고 나쁜 건 잊는 게 더 쉬웠어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 말해줘서 고마워.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 고마워, 헌터... 나도 그래."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "That's okay, I didn't mean to pry."
msgstr "괜찮아, 캐묻으려던 건 아니었어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Yeah... what was up with that, anyway?"
msgstr "그래... 근데 아까 그건 대체 뭐였어?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, I was <i>terrified.</> I'd never led a team before, never mind an important and <i>dangerous</> expedition.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then in walks this neophyte Hunter, looking almost as scared as I was and <i>still</> volunteering to help. It made me feel a little braver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 음, 난 <i>겁에 질려 있었어.</> 팀을 이끌어 본 적도 없는데, 하물며 그렇게 중요하고 <i>위험한</> 원정이라니.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그런데 완전 풋내기 헌터 하나가 들어오더니, 나만큼 겁먹은 얼굴로 <i>그래도</> 돕겠다고 나서는 거야. 그걸 보고 나도 좀 용기가 났어."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! Who could forget? You challenged <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> to an arm-wrestle. I'd never seen him laugh so hard. \n"
" !point\n"
" Even when he launched you over the table, your confidence was contagious--I remember thinking that if we had you on our side, we'd be able to take on the world!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하! 그걸 누가 잊겠어? 넌 <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>한테 팔씨름을 걸었잖아. 그가 그렇게 크게 웃는 건 처음 봤어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 네가 탁자 위로 날아가도 자신감이 전염됐지. 그때 생각했어, 네가 우리 편이면 세상도 상대할 수 있겠다고!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're so generous, Hunter, but so you know, I'm always happy to talk to you, even if you don't have something to give me.\n"
" !think\n"
" I was just thinking about the first time we met, at my old <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> base in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. Do you remember?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 넌 정말 후하네, 헌터. 근데 알아둬, 줄 게 없어도 난 언제든 너랑 이야기해서 좋아.\n"
" !think\n"
" 방금 우리가 처음 만난 날 생각하고 있었어. <#BLUE>브링크스</>에 있던 내 옛 <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> 기지에서. 기억나?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's hard to believe that was only a few weeks ago. We've been through so much since then.\n"
" player:\n"
" I hope we can stick together through a whole lot more.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Well, I wouldn't mind if in the future there's a <i>bit</> less fighting for our survival... but even so, I'd like nothing more. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You have a friend for life in me, Hunter. Whether it's watching your back in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> or just keeping you company on a gloomy day.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" In fact--I, um... made this for you. O-open it later though, I'll get too embarrassed if you open it now.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm <i>definitely</> your favourite Hunter now, right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh, you've moved up to be at <i>least</> in the top three.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha ha! I'm kidding, I'm kidding! The look on your face!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그게 불과 몇 주 전이라는 게 믿기 힘들어. 그 뒤로 우리 정말 많은 일을 겪었지.\n"
" player:\n"
" 앞으로도 훨씬 더 오래 같이 갔으면 해.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 뭐, 앞으로는 생존 걸린 싸움이 <i>조금</>만 덜했으면 좋겠지만... 그래도 난 정말 그러고 싶어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 넌 평생 친구야, 헌터. <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>에서 네 등을 봐주는 거든, 우울한 날 옆에 있어주는 거든.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 사실은... 내가, 음... 이거 너 주려고 만들었어. 지, 지금 열어보진 마. 지금 열면 내가 너무 부끄러울 것 같아.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" player:\n"
" 이제 난 <i>확실히</> 네 최애 헌터지, 맞지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 음, 적어도 <i>최소</> 톱3 안에는 들었네.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하하! 농담이야, 농담! 네 표정 봐!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I was so nervous. I thought I'd get laughed out of there."
msgstr "나 너무 긴장했어. 거기서 웃음거리 될 줄 알았거든."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "I was so cocky. It's a bit embarrassing to reflect on, now..."
msgstr "나 완전 잘난 척했지. 지금 생각하면 좀 창피하네..."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOWGEM
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOWGEM"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" * {name.npc_blacksmith} rummages around in the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}\n"
" !think\n"
" Och, wouldya look at <i>that</> beauty!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * {name.npc_blacksmith} pulls a <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</> from the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}\n"
" !happy\n"
" Lookat you, little <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</>. What were ya doin' in there? Alright then, let's get us a better look atcha.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hrmm... <z 0.7>seems like... and the clarity... aye... should have enough power... t'would do nicely...</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" * {name.npc_blacksmith}이/가 {name.teffrometer_unidentified} 안을 뒤적인다\n"
" !think\n"
" 어이쿠, <i>이</> 멋진 거 좀 봐라!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * {name.npc_blacksmith}이/가 {name.teffrometer_unidentified}에서 <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</>를 꺼낸다\n"
" !happy\n"
" 요 작은 <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</> 좀 봐라. 거기서 뭐 하고 있었냐? 좋아, 그럼 좀 더 자세히 보자고.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 흐음... <z 0.7>이런 것 같고... 투명도는... 좋아... 출력은 충분하고... 잘 되겠는데...</>"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "<i>You're</> a gem, {name.npc_blacksmith}!"
msgstr "<i>너</>는 보석이야, {name.npc_blacksmith}!"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMSMITHING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMSMITHING"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...Och. Alright then.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I <i>may</> dabble a wee bit in <#RED>Gemsmithing</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Folks think it's just fer soft-handed folk makin' frivolous baubles, but it's not, awright! ...It's fer everyone.\n"
" !think\n"
" Now. That <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</> ye have there, 'tis a curious thing indeed.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Crystallized Teffra, that is. Similar to a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_soul_lesser}</>-- but if ye take a good look at the colour, 'n the clarity... aye, this didn't form the way most crystals do.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And unlike most Teffra crystals ye come across, this one seems <i>stable</>. A wee bit less powerful I'd wager, but from the look of it, should last ye a lifetime.\n"
" player:\n"
" That's amazing! I had no idea you were so into {name_multiple.gem}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph. <z 0.7>Who wouldnae want ta get lost lookin' into wee <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</>? Sparkly precious things hid inside o' rocks... <i>(sigh...)</></>\n"
" !disagree\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ....Eh. I've picked up a few things here 'n there.\n"
" !think\n"
" 'Course, I could <i>really</> get inta it if I had me <#RED>{name.gemtools}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But I lost 'em when we fell. So.\n"
" player:\n"
" Do you have any idea where they might be?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...어흠. 좋아.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 나도 <i>조금은</> <#RED>젬스미싱</>을 하지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 사람들은 이걸 손 고운 사람들이 쓸데없는 장신구나 만드는 거라고 생각하지만, 아니거든! ...이건 모두를 위한 거야.\n"
" !think\n"
" 자. 네가 가진 저 <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</>, 꽤 흥미로운 물건이네.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 결정화된 테프라야. <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_soul_lesser}</>랑 비슷하긴 한데, 색이랑 투명도를 잘 보면... 그래, 이건 보통 결정처럼 만들어진 게 아니야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 네가 흔히 보게 되는 테프라 결정과 달리, 이건 <i>안정적</>으로 보이네. 위력은 조금 덜할 수도 있겠지만, 보기엔 평생 쓸 수 있겠어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 대단하다! 네가 {name_multiple.gem}에 이렇게 진심인 줄 몰랐어!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 흥. <z 0.7>누가 작은 <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</>를 들여다보며 빠지고 싶지 않겠어? 돌 속에 숨은 반짝이는 귀한 것들... <i>(한숨...)</></>\n"
" !disagree\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ....에헴. 여기저기서 조금 배웠지.\n"
" !think\n"
" 물론 <i>진짜</> 제대로 파보려면 내 <#RED>{name.gemtools}</>가 있어야 해.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 근데 떨어질 때 잃어버렸지. 그래서.\n"
" player:\n"
" 어디 있을지 짐작 가는 거 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMTOOLS_LOCATION
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMTOOLS_LOCATION"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Probably still somewhere out in th' <#BLUE>trees</> ye first found me in. 'Tis all frenzied now, though. \n"
" player:\n"
" Say I find your tools. You'd help me identify these {name_multiple.gem}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...I s'pose that'd be fair.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Alright, now. Off with ye then!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아마 처음 네가 날 찾았던 <#BLUE>숲</> 어딘가에 아직 있을 거야. 지금은 다 광란 상태지만.\n"
" player:\n"
" 내가 네 도구 찾으면, 넌 이 {name_multiple.gem}들 감정해 줄 거지?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...그 정도면 공평하겠네.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 좋아, 그럼 얼른 가!"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.PRY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.PRY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [notify:gem_unidentified]\n"
" Well, tha's all I wanted ta see. Be gone with ye!\n"
" player:\n"
" C'mon! You know something. Why are you acting so weird?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Am not--!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Fine. I'll tell ye.\n"
" !point\n"
" But don't go bletherin' to everyone in camp about this. 'Specially not that wee nosy <#RED>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>. Ye ken?\n"
" player:\n"
" Of course! I'm Ken all the live long day. Now spill it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [notify:gem_unidentified]\n"
" 뭐, 내가 보고 싶던 건 다 봤다. 이제 꺼져!\n"
" player:\n"
" 에이! 너 뭔가 아는 거 맞잖아. 왜 이렇게 수상하게 굴어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 안 그랬--!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 흥...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" 좋아. 말해주지.\n"
" !point\n"
" 근데 이 얘기 캠프 사람들한테 떠들고 다니진 마. 특히 그 조그만 참견쟁이 <#RED>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>한텐 더더욱. 알았지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 물론이지! 난 하루 종일 켄이지. 자, 이제 말해봐!"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "No promises..."
msgstr "장담은 못 해..."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B_A"
msgid "...Alright, FINE. I'm Ken. Now will you tell me, please?"
msgstr "...알겠어, 됐어. 내가 켄이야. 이제 말해줄 거지, 제발?"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOWGEM
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOWGEM"
msgid "<#RED>[Show {name.npc_blacksmith} the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}]</> I don't see why not."
msgstr "<#RED>[Show {name.npc_blacksmith} the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}]</> 왜 안 되겠어."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Tha <#RED>{name.teffrometer_unidentified}</> ye got there--can I have a look at it?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 네가 가진 그 <#RED>{name.teffrometer_unidentified}</>--내가 좀 봐도 되냐?"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Och.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well. Innae that important, anyway.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" 어흠.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 뭐. 그렇게 중요한 것도 아니고.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 흥."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "I'll find them, {name.npc_blacksmith}. Don't you worry."
msgstr "내가 찾아올게, {name.npc_blacksmith}. 걱정 마."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Sorry, not yet."
msgstr "미안, 아직 못 찾았어."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Have ye happened to spot them? Ye know...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Me <#RED>{name.gemtools}</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 혹시 본 적 있나? 알잖아...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...내 <#RED>{name.gemtools}</>?"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ye really did! Ye found me babies--!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ahem...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...Thank ye, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 진짜 해냈네! 내 새끼들을 찾아줬어--!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 에헴...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...고맙다, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Aye.\n"
" !point\n"
" Go on. Try out the <#RED>{name.i_station_gems}</> on yer own. I learned by gettin' me hands dirty--with {name_multiple.gem}!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그래.\n"
" !point\n"
" 자, 해봐. 그 <#RED>{name.i_station_gems}</> 직접 써봐. 난 손에 흙 묻히면서 배웠거든--{name_multiple.gem}로!"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "{name.i_station_gems}, got it."
msgstr "{name.i_station_gems}, 알겠어."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "What has two thumbs and found your {name.gemtools}?"
msgstr "엄지 두 개 달리고 네 {name.gemtools} 찾아온 게 누군지 알아?"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "What's say we put 'em to use identifying these {name_multiple.gem} I got?"
msgstr "그럼 이 {name_multiple.gem}들 감정하는 데 바로 써보는 거 어때?"

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hmph. Ye seem awful pleased about somethin'.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wait--dunnae tell me...?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 흥. 뭔가 엄청 신난 얼굴이네.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 잠깐--설마 말하지 마...?"

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Uhh--the font is too flowery for me to read, but there's a picture of two hammers kissing on the front?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Anyway, I'll keep it safe until we bring him home. Let's go."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 어어--글씨체가 너무 화려해서 못 읽겠는데, 표지에 망치 두 개가 키스하는 그림이 있어?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아무튼 그를 데려올 때까지 내가 안전하게 보관할게. 가자."

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Good idea."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" 좋은 생각이야."

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "What book is it?"
msgstr "무슨 책인데?"

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Then I'd better get back to searching for him."
msgstr "그럼 난 그를 찾으러 다시 가야겠네."

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.REMIND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hunter! On second thought: actually <#RED>bring me a Souvenir</> from one of your hunts, will ya?  \n"
" !gesture\n"
" A <#RED>Souvenir's</> <i>sure</> to be imbued with this funky-bad <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> energy... \n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's for a top secret thing. You'll see. Just <#RED>bring me a Souvenir</>, alright?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 헌터! 생각해 보니 말이야: 다음 사냥에서 <#RED>기념품 하나 가져다줘</>, 알겠지?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>기념품</>이면 이 괴상한 나쁜 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 에너지가 <i>분명</> 스며들어 있을 거야...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 극비 프로젝트에 쓰려고. 보면 알게 돼. 그냥 <#RED>기념품 하나 가져다줘</>, 응?"

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Sheesh. One year since the craziness in Doc's lab. Time flies, huh? \n"
" player:\n"
" When you're having fun. Or living under a dome of pure {name.konjur} energy.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I <i>am</> proud of it. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Proud of <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, proud it's protecting the people here... \n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I can't get comfortable. Spent years under a volcano, but an energy dome? I'm nuts, aren't I?\n"
" player:\n"
" Or maybe you can't shake that your dad's outside it, still wandering the <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</>...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hm. I do <i>not</> like you knowing personal details about me, Hunter. THAT makes me claustrophobic. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Time for an abrupt subject change unrelated to my discomfort with being seen!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" My <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> picked up some funky <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> spikes in <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> habitats... \n"
" player:\n"
" Funky... <i>bad?</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A scientist never assumes, but... yeah, funky-bad. Funky-tough. Funky-absolutely-funkin'-brutal. \n"
" !notebook\n"
" So if you could go check 'em out, that'd be great.\n"
" player:\n"
" Check out some funky-bad {name.rot_boss}'s lairs? Oh, sure! Sounds peachy!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" You're the best, Hunter. \n"
" player:\n"
" Do you think Doc {name.flitt_lastname} linked to these funky spikes? He's still out there...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... No. We knocked enough sense into Doc, he wouldn't try anything. <z 0.7>Pretty sure.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, and if you pick up any <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>-imbued stuff--bring it my way. \n"
" !point\n"
" I'm keen to study some up close. \n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" UGH. Did I just say, \"keen\"? Leave me to mourn the death of my coolness, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" 이런. 닥터 연구실에서 난리가 난 지 1년이네. 시간 빠르다, 그치?\n"
" player:\n"
" 재밌게 살면 더 그렇고. 아니면 순수 {name.konjur} 에너지 돔 아래 살거나.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 난 이게 <i>자랑스러워.</>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>도, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>도 자랑스럽고, 여기 사람들을 지켜주는 것도 자랑스러워...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 마음이 안 놓여. 화산 아래서도 몇 년을 버텼는데 에너지 돔은 답답하다니. 나 이상하지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 아니면 네 아빠가 아직도 밖에서 <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</>를 떠돌고 있다는 게 계속 걸리는 거고...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 흠. 네가 내 개인사를 아는 거, <i>별로</> 안 좋아해, 헌터. 그게 날 더 숨 막히게 해.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 누군가에게 들킨 불편함과 전혀 상관없는 주제로 갑자기 넘어갈 시간이네!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 내 <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>가 <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> 서식지에서 이상한 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 급증을 잡아냈어...\n"
" player:\n"
" 이상하다는 게... <i>나쁜</> 쪽?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 과학자는 함부로 단정 안 하지만... 그래, 나쁜 쪽이야. 나쁘고, 빡세고, 완전 미친 듯이 험악한 쪽.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 그러니까 네가 가서 좀 확인해 주면 좋겠어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그 나쁜 쪽 {name.rot_boss} 둥지를 확인하라고? 아, 좋지! 완전 달콤하네!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 최고다, 헌터.\n"
" player:\n"
" 이 이상한 급증, 닥터 {name.flitt_lastname}랑 연결됐다고 생각해? 저 녀석 아직 밖에 있는데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...아냐. 우린 닥터를 충분히 두들겨서 정신 차리게 했어, 뭔 짓 안 할 거야. <z 0.7>아마도.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 그리고 네가 태고의 {name.konjur} 기운이 밴 물건 <#KONJUR>뭐든</> 주우면 내 쪽으로 가져와.\n"
" !point\n"
" 가까이서 좀 연구해 보고 싶거든.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 으아. 나 방금 \"연구해 보고 싶다\" 같은 말 했냐? 내 쿨함의 죽음을 애도하게 좀 놔둬, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT1.remind_about_gift.giver.STATE_0.REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT1.remind_about_gift.giver.STATE_0.REMIND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hunter! On second thought: actually <#RED>bring me a Souvenir</> from one of your hunts, will ya?  \n"
" !gesture\n"
" A <#RED>Souvenir's</> <i>sure</> to be imbued with this funky-bad <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> energy... \n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's for a top secret thing. You'll see. Just <#RED>bring me a Souvenir</>, alright?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 헌터! 생각해 보니 말이야: 다음 사냥에서 <#RED>기념품 하나 가져다줘</>, 알겠지?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>기념품</>이면 이 괴상한 나쁜 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 에너지가 <i>분명</> 스며들어 있을 거야...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 극비 프로젝트에 쓰려고. 보면 알게 돼. 그냥 <#RED>기념품 하나 가져다줘</>, 응?"

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT1.remind_about_gift.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT1.remind_about_gift.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Sheesh. One year since the craziness in Doc's lab. Time flies, huh? \n"
" player:\n"
" When you're having fun. Or living under a dome of pure {name.konjur} energy.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I <i>am</> proud of it. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Proud of <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, proud it's protecting the people here... \n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I can't get comfortable. Spent years under a volcano, but an energy dome? I'm nuts, aren't I?\n"
" player:\n"
" Or maybe you can't shake that your dad's outside it, still wandering the <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</>...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hm. I do <i>not</> like you knowing personal details about me, Hunter. THAT makes me claustrophobic. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Time for an abrupt subject change unrelated to my discomfort with being seen!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" My <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> picked up some funky <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> spikes in <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> habitats... \n"
" player:\n"
" Funky... <i>bad?</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A scientist never assumes, but... yeah, funky-bad. Funky-tough. Funky-absolutely-funkin'-brutal. \n"
" !notebook\n"
" So if you could go check 'em out, that'd be great.\n"
" player:\n"
" Check out some funky-bad {name.rot_boss}'s lairs? Oh, sure! Sounds peachy!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" You're the best, Hunter. \n"
" player:\n"
" Do you think Doc {name.flitt_lastname} linked to these funky spikes? He's still out there...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... No. We knocked enough sense into Doc, he wouldn't try anything. <z 0.7>Pretty sure.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, and if you pick up any <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>-imbued stuff--bring it my way. \n"
" !point\n"
" I'm keen to study some up close. \n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" UGH. Did I just say, \"keen\"? Leave me to mourn the death of my coolness, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" 이런. 닥터 연구실에서 난리가 난 지 1년이네. 시간 빠르다, 그치?\n"
" player:\n"
" 재밌게 살면 더 그렇고. 아니면 순수 {name.konjur} 에너지 돔 아래 살거나.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 난 이게 <i>자랑스러워.</>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>도, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>도 자랑스럽고, 여기 사람들을 지켜주는 것도 자랑스러워...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 마음이 안 놓여. 화산 아래서도 몇 년을 버텼는데 에너지 돔은 답답하다니. 나 이상하지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 아니면 네 아빠가 아직도 밖에서 <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</>를 떠돌고 있다는 게 계속 걸리는 거고...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" 흠. 네가 내 개인사를 아는 거, <i>별로</> 안 좋아해, 헌터. 그게 날 더 숨 막히게 해.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(한숨)</> 누군가에게 들킨 불편함과 전혀 상관없는 주제로 갑자기 넘어갈 시간이네!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 내 <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>가 <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> 서식지에서 이상한 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 급증을 잡아냈어...\n"
" player:\n"
" 이상하다는 게... <i>나쁜</> 쪽?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 과학자는 함부로 단정 안 하지만... 그래, 나쁜 쪽이야. 나쁘고, 빡세고, 완전 미친 듯이 험악한 쪽.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 그러니까 네가 가서 좀 확인해 주면 좋겠어.\n"
" player:\n"
" 그 나쁜 쪽 {name.rot_boss} 둥지를 확인하라고? 아, 좋지! 완전 달콤하네!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 최고다, 헌터.\n"
" player:\n"
" 이 이상한 급증, 닥터 {name.flitt_lastname}랑 연결됐다고 생각해? 저 녀석 아직 밖에 있는데...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...아냐. 우린 닥터를 충분히 두들겨서 정신 차리게 했어, 뭔 짓 안 할 거야. <z 0.7>아마도.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 그리고 네가 태고의 {name.konjur} 기운이 밴 물건 <#KONJUR>뭐든</> 주우면 내 쪽으로 가져와.\n"
" !point\n"
" 가까이서 좀 연구해 보고 싶거든.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 으아. 나 방금 \"연구해 보고 싶다\" 같은 말 했냐? 내 쿨함의 죽음을 애도하게 좀 놔둬, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Omigosh, you actually have a <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>! Where did you get it??"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 헐대박, 진짜 <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>를 갖고 있네! 이거 어디서 났어??"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i><z 0.7>(whisper whisper)</z></i>\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Hm. So... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> doesn't believe you, I do, but Scarfanie (my scarf) has the tie-breaking vote, and she voted, 'Believe You!'\n"
" !happy\n"
" So we're usin' the <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ooooh, this is going to be so fun!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i><z 0.7>(소곤소곤)</z></i>\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 흠. 그러니까... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>는 널 안 믿지만, 난 믿고, 내 스카프 스카파니가 캐스팅보트를 쥐었는데 \"믿기!\"에 투표했어!\n"
" !happy\n"
" 그러니까 <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>를 쓰는 걸로!\n"
" !clap\n"
" 우와아, 이거 완전 재밌겠다!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did a <#RED>{name.gnarlic}</> poke your eyes out? It's a metal <#RED>Ingot</>! From the Before Times!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" How it ended up here is a preeetty juicy tidbit. A nice bit of tid. A... <z 0.7>seeeeecret.</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But whatever! You already have it, we might as well use it.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ooooh, this is going to be so fun!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.gnarlic}</>가 네 눈이라도 찔렀어? 이건 금속 <#RED>주괴</>야! 옛 시대의!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 이게 어떻게 여기 왔는지는 꽤에에 쫀득한 떡밥이야. 아주 맛있는 한 입거리. 완전... <z 0.7>비이이밀.</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 뭐 됐고! 이미 네가 갖고 있으니, 그냥 쓰자.\n"
" !clap\n"
" 우와아, 이거 완전 재밌겠다!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" With that <#RED>Ingot</> I can fortify a piece of your <#RED>Armour</> and, like, take it to the next <#RED>Level</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" And I <i>guess</i> <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> could also improve a <#RED>Weapon</> with it.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" But why would you fortify <i><#RED>Weapons</></i> when you could fortify <#RED>Armour</>??? Right??? It would make NO sense!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 그 <#RED>주괴</>로 네 <#RED>방어구</> 하나를 보강해서, 말 그대로 다음 <#RED>레벨</>로 올릴 수 있어!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 그리고 <i>아마</i> <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>도 그걸로 <#RED>무기</>를 강화할 수는 있겠지.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 근데 <i><#RED>무기</></i>를 강화할 거면 왜 <#RED>방어구</>를 안 하겠어??? 맞지??? 말이 안 되잖아!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Ugh, this is different!\n"
" !think\n"
" So like, imagine you become bestest friends with a piece of <#RED>Armour</> you got in an early Hunt.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now as your Hunts get tougher, that old <#RED>Armour</> won't keep you safe, BUT you don't want to ditch your bestest friend (the armour)!\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Now, if you used a <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</> to raise your bestest friend's <#RED>Level</>, you could keep adventuring together without getting your butt kicked!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 아으, 이건 다르지!\n"
" !think\n"
" 그러니까, 초반 사냥에서 얻은 <#RED>방어구</>랑 네가 완전 베프가 됐다고 상상해 봐.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그런데 사냥이 점점 빡세지면 그 오래된 <#RED>방어구</>로는 널 못 지켜줘. 근데 베프(그 방어구)를 버리긴 싫잖아!\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 이때 <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>를 써서 베프의 <#RED>레벨</>을 올리면, 엉덩이 털리지 않고 계속 같이 모험할 수 있지!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Same as how you always alter gear, with that adorable little <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> over there.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, but you'll have to <#RED>Upgrade</> your gear a few times first.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Once the gear's good and sturdy from regular <#RED>Upgrading</>, then <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I can work an <#RED>Ingot</> into it and raise its <#RED>Level</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 늘 장비 개조하던 방식 그대로야. 저기 그 귀여운 작은 <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>로.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 근데 먼저 장비를 몇 번 <#RED>업그레이드</> 해야 해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" 일반 <#RED>업그레이드</>로 장비가 충분히 튼튼해지면, 그다음엔 <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>랑 내가 <#RED>주괴</>를 박아 넣어서 <#RED>레벨</>을 올려줄 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Um. I guess it soaked up some personality from wherever you got it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Nothing wrong with a little personality! I can still use it.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" The <#RED>Ingot</>, not personality. I got plenty of that! \n"
" !agree\n"
" Heck, crud aside, some <#RED>Ingots</> might be more powerful than others."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 음. 네가 그걸 주워 온 곳의 성격이 좀 스며든 것 같네.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 성격 좀 있는 건 나쁠 거 없지! 그래도 쓸 수 있어.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <#RED>주괴</> 말이야, 성격 말고. 성격은 난 이미 넘치거든!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 에이, 찌꺼기 같은 거 빼고 보면 어떤 <#RED>주괴</>는 다른 것보다 더 강할 수도 있어."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You better!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 그럼 그래야지!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Uh...? <z 0.7><#RED>(Show her a {name.upgrade_ingot})</></z>"
msgstr "어...? <z 0.7><#RED>({name.upgrade_ingot}를/를 보여준다)</></z>"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Something dropped it on one of my Hunts."
msgstr "내 사냥 중에 뭔가가 떨어뜨렸어."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Why, what is it? Is it bad? <z 0.7>Is it...poop??</>"
msgstr "왜, 그게 뭔데? 안 좋은 거야? <z 0.7>이거...똥이야??</>"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "So what does it do?"
msgstr "그래서 그게 뭐 하는 건데?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "Sorry, I gotta go, but I'll bring you any Ingots I find!"
msgstr "미안, 나 가봐야 해. 근데 주괴 찾으면 다 가져올게!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "It's for Upgrades? But you and {name.npc_blacksmith} already do that."
msgstr "업그레이드용이라고? 근데 그건 너랑 {name.npc_blacksmith}도 이미 하잖아."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A_ALT"
msgid "You and {name.npc_blacksmith} already give me Upgrades though."
msgstr "근데 너랑 {name.npc_blacksmith}가 이미 업그레이드 해주잖아."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "How do I use it?"
msgstr "이거 어떻게 써?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B_ALT"
msgid "Okay. So how do I use it?"
msgstr "오케이. 그래서 이거 어떻게 쓰는데?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4C"
msgid "How come it's covered in crud and stuff?"
msgstr "근데 왜 이거 찌꺼기랑 이것저것 덕지덕지 붙어 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4D"
msgid "Gotta run, but I'll bring you any Ingots I find!"
msgstr "나 가봐야 해. 근데 주괴 찾으면 다 가져올게!"

#: Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_PLAYER
msgctxt "Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_PLAYER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] If you ever forget the assignment, check the <#RED>{name.i_masteries_station}</> over there behind you.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] 과제 까먹으면 뒤에 있는 <#RED>{name.i_masteries_station}</> 확인해.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_TOOT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_TOOT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] If you ever forget the assignment, check the <#RED>{name.i_masteries_station}</> over there.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] 과제 까먹으면 저기 있는 <#RED>{name.i_masteries_station}</> 확인해.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Eyy, is that our new Hunter I see?\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_dojo_master}, right? Glad to see you made it here in one piece.\n"
" agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'd have no business bein' yer <#RED>{name.job_dojo}</> if I couldn't.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Well, this expedition's already off to a bumpy start, so let's get right to it. What d'ya say we jump right into yer <#RED>Masteries</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" Masteries?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>Masteries</> are challenges I made to sharpen yer skills. It's real simple-- go on a {name.run} and complete a challenge, then come back for a nice reward.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I always make sure to give my students a <#KONJUR>Treat</> for finishing their homework!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 에이, 저게 우리 새 헌터냐?\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_dojo_master}, 맞지? 무사히 도착해서 다행이다.\n"
" agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그걸 못 했다면 내가 네 <#RED>{name.job_dojo}</>일 자격도 없지.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} 이번 원정 시작부터 좀 울퉁불퉁했으니까, 바로 본론 가자. 네 <#RED>마스터리</>부터 바로 들어갈까?\n"
" player:\n"
" 마스터리?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>마스터리</>는 내가 네 실력 갈고닦으라고 만든 도전 과제야. 아주 간단해. {name.run} 한 번 나가서 과제 완료하고, 돌아와서 보상 받으면 끝.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 난 숙제 끝낸 학생한텐 꼭 <#KONJUR>간식</>을 챙겨주거든!"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> tips...? That better not be a pun.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Whatcha need to know?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> 팁...? 말장난은 아니길 바란다.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 뭐가 궁금해?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Well, yer {name.tutorial_attack_light} is a simple forward jab. Reliable.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Yer {name.tutorial_attack_heavy} launches you forward with a jumping thrust.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And heck, since you're takin' the time to learn, I'll give you a <#RED>Combo</> that's not in the tooltip.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Three {name_multiple.tutorial_attack_light} followed by one {name.tutorial_attack_heavy}. Have fun."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 자, 네 {name.tutorial_attack_light}는 앞을 찌르는 기본기다. 믿을 만하지.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 네 {name.tutorial_attack_heavy}는 점프 찌르기로 앞으로 날아간다.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그리고 네가 배우려는 성의가 있으니, 툴팁엔 없는 <#RED>콤보</> 하나 알려주지.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" {name_multiple.tutorial_attack_light} 세 번 다음 {name.tutorial_attack_heavy} 한 번. 재밌게 써라."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Yer {name.tutorial_attack_light} is a forward jab.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Yer {name.tutorial_attack_heavy} launches you forward with a jumping thrust."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 네 {name.tutorial_attack_light}는 전방 찌르기야.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 네 {name.tutorial_attack_heavy}는 점프 찌르기로 앞으로 날아가."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The most crucial lesson is this: <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_polearm}</> is mid-range <#RED>Weapons</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Near any <#RED>Attack</> can be a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> if you land it at arm's length.\n"
" !point\n"
" Your <#RED>Spinning Drill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' color=BTNICON_DARK scale=0.4> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) will also <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> if ya smack <#RED>2+ Enemies</> with it at once.\n"
" !point\n"
" Try practicin' on our <#RED>Training Dummies</> if you need."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 가장 중요한 건 이거다: <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_polearm}</>는 중거리 <#RED>무기</>야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 거의 모든 <#RED>공격</>은 팔 길이 끝거리에서 맞히면 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>가 돼.\n"
" !point\n"
" 네 <#RED>스피닝 드릴</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' color=BTNICON_DARK scale=0.4> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>)도 <#RED>적 2명 이상</>을 한 번에 치면 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>가 뜬다.\n"
" !point\n"
" 필요하면 <#RED>훈련 허수아비</>로 연습해."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Yer <#RED>Spinning Drill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' scale=0.4 color=BTNICON_DARK> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) will <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> if ya smack <#RED>2+ Enemies</> with it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You can also get <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> with most <#RED>Attacks</> if you hit with just the tip of yer <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 네 <#RED>스피닝 드릴</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' scale=0.4 color=BTNICON_DARK> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>)은 <#RED>적 2명 이상</>을 치면 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>가 돼.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 네 <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> 끝부분으로 맞히면 대부분 <#RED>공격</>에서도 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>를 만들 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Eh, that's a standard issue <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> from the Expedition <#RED>Rack</>, yeah?\n"
" !point\n"
" Then yer <#RED>Skill</> must be a melee <#RED>Crosscheck</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If an <#RED>Enemy</> gets too close, hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK> to shove'em back and make some space."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 어, 그거 원정대 <#RED>무기고</>에서 얻은 기본 <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> 맞지?\n"
" !point\n"
" 그럼 네 <#RED>스킬</>은 근접 <#RED>크로스체크</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>)일 거야.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>적</>이 너무 가까이 붙으면 <p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK> 눌러서 밀어내고 거리 벌려."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" LISTEN UP. Yer <#RED>Skill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>) is a close-range shove.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Use it to push <#RED>Enemies</> back and make some space."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 잘 들어. 네 <#RED>스킬</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>)은 근접 밀치기야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그걸로 <#RED>적</> 밀어내고 거리 만들어."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Yer doin' that on purpose, aren't you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 일부러 그러는 거지, 너."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Alright, alright, get gone with ya. {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 알겠다, 알겠어. 이제 가봐. {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Mind giving me some {name.weapon_polearm} tips?"
msgstr "{name.weapon_polearm} 팁 좀 줄래?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Lemme hear the basics."
msgstr "기본부터 다시 알려줘."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_ALT"
msgid "What were the basics again?"
msgstr "기본이 뭐였는지 다시 알려줘."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "How do I do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}?"
msgstr "{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}은 어떻게 해?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_ALT"
msgid "I immediately forgot everything you said about {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}."
msgstr "{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} 얘기한 거 듣자마자 다 까먹었어."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "What's my Skill do?"
msgstr "내 스킬 뭐 하는 거야?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C_ALT"
msgid "How do I use my Skill again?"
msgstr "내 스킬 어떻게 쓰는지 다시 알려줘?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D"
msgid "Okay, I think I get the point."
msgstr "오케이, 요점은 알겠어."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "Bye! Thanks for explaining the <i>main thrust</i> of {name_multiple.weapon_polearm}!"
msgstr "잘 가! {name_multiple.weapon_polearm}의 <i>핵심 찌르기</i> 설명 고마워!"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MAKE_DIFFERENT_TYPES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MAKE_DIFFERENT_TYPES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Och, well, that's simple enough.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Just equip the type o' weapon ye want me to make ya.\n"
" !point\n"
" An' I'll base it off o' that."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 어흠, 뭐, 그건 간단하지.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 네가 만들고 싶은 무기 타입을 장착해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그걸 기준으로 만들어줄게."

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CANCEL_CRAFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CANCEL_CRAFT"
msgid "Forget it"
msgstr "됐어"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CONFIRM_CRAFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CONFIRM_CRAFT"
msgid "Make it"
msgstr "만들어"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CONFIRM_REPAIR
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CONFIRM_REPAIR"
msgid "Fix it"
msgstr "고쳐줘"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CORESTONE_CRAFTING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CORESTONE_CRAFTING"
msgid "<#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> Crafting"
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 제작"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CRAFT_BOSS_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CRAFT_BOSS_WEAPON"
msgid "Finish <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>"
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 완성해줘"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CRAFT_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_CRAFT_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
msgid "Make <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>"
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 만들어줘"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_DIFFERENT_CRAFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_DIFFERENT_CRAFT"
msgid "How do I give my weapon different {name.rot_boss} powers?"
msgstr "무기에 다른 {name.rot_boss} 힘은 어떻게 부여해?"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.OPT_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
msgid "Repair <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>"
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 수리해줘"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MAKE_DIFFERENT_TYPES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MAKE_DIFFERENT_TYPES"
msgid "How do I make other <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}s</>?"
msgstr "다른 <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}들</>은 어떻게 만들어?"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CRAFT_BOSS_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CRAFT_BOSS_WEAPON"
msgid "agent:\n"
" Ah. I see ye've charged up that weapon with the <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</> of a <#RED>{boss_name}</>.\n"
" [recipe:boss_weapon_recipe] I can finish it now, if ye've got the goods."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" 아. <#RED>{boss_name}</>의 <#KONJUR>태고의 테프레센스</>로 그 무기를 충전해 뒀구나.\n"
" [recipe:boss_weapon_recipe] 재료만 있으면 지금 완성해줄 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CRAFT_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CRAFT_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
msgid "[recipe:corestone_weapon_recipe] Ye want me to make ye a <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>?"
msgstr "[recipe:corestone_weapon_recipe] <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> 하나 만들어달라는 거지?"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DIFFERENT_CRAFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DIFFERENT_CRAFT"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Indecisive, are we?\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye need to charge the weapon with the <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</> of the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> yer after.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Dunnae worry if the weapon's already charged up with another <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</>. The new one'll wipe the ol' one out."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흠. 갈팡질팡하네?\n"
" !point\n"
" 원하는 <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>의 <#KONJUR>태고의 테프레센스</>로 무기를 충전해야 해.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 무기에 이미 다른 <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> <#KONJUR>태고의 테프레센스</>가 들어 있어도 걱정 마. 새로 충전하면 기존 건 지워져."

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
msgid "[recipe:repair_weapon_recipe] Hm. Fix up yer <#RED>{equipped_weapon_name}</>?"
msgstr "[recipe:repair_weapon_recipe] 흠. <#RED>{equipped_weapon_name}</> 수리할까?"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON_FREE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON_FREE"
msgid "Repairs are on Lottie's tab 'til ye've charged it. Want me ta fix up yer <#RED>{equipped_weapon_name}</>?"
msgstr "충전하기 전까진 수리비는 로티 외상으로 처리돼. <#RED>{equipped_weapon_name}</> 고쳐줄까?"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_CANT_AFFORD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_CANT_AFFORD"
msgid "<#RED>Can't afford</>"
msgstr "<#RED>재화 부족</>"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_DUPLICATE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_DUPLICATE_WEAPON"
msgid "<#RED>Already owned</>"
msgstr "<#RED>이미 보유함</>"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_NEEDS_BROKEN_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_NEEDS_BROKEN_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
msgid "<#RED>Requires Broken {name.weapon_crystal}</>"
msgstr "<#RED>파손된 {name.weapon_crystal} 필요</>"

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_NEEDS_CHARGED_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TT_NEEDS_CHARGED_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
msgid "<#RED>Requires Charged {name.weapon_crystal}</>"
msgstr "<#RED>충전된 {name.weapon_crystal} 필요</>"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" It's a <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>, actually. Not a \"ball\"."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 그건 사실 <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>야. \"공\"이 아니고."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...{name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I could end you, you know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...{name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 나 너 끝장낼 수 있는 거 알지?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" When you're up close and personal, you can do a nice reliable <#RED>Punch</> with <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" But the real fun comes hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>. That's how you chuck a <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You've got <#RED>2 {name_multiple.weapon_shotput}</> total. If you've thrown them both, you can call them back to you with (<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>)."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 가까이 붙으면 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>으로 안정적인 <#RED>펀치</>를 넣을 수 있어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 근데 진짜 재미는 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>를 누를 때야. 그러면 <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>를 던지거든.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 총 <#RED>2 {name_multiple.weapon_shotput}</>를 들고 다녀. 둘 다 던졌다면 (<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>)으로 다시 불러."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Well, LISTEN UP this time!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 'Kay. Hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> and you'll do a good ol' close quarters <#RED>Punch</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> to throw one of your <#RED>2 {name_multiple.weapon_shotput}</>.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If you're out of <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_shotput}</>, hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> to <#RED>Recall</> them to you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 이번엔 좀 제대로 들어!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 좋아. <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> 누르면 근접에서 묵직한 <#RED>펀치</>가 나가.\n"
" !point\n"
" <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> 누르면 가진 <#RED>2 {name_multiple.weapon_shotput}</> 중 하나를 던져.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_shotput}</>를 다 썼으면 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> 눌러서 <#RED>리콜</>해."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Oh, you can do some real awesome <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> with these.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" For example, try <#RED>Punching</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) one clean out of the air and into a <#RED>{name.rot}</>'s face!\n"
" !agree\n"
" You can also do a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> by throwing a <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</> <i>immediately</i> after you catch it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" That one's more beginner-friendly."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 이걸로 진짜 멋진 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>도 할 수 있어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 예를 들어, 공중에 떠 있는 걸 (<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) <#RED>펀치</>로 정확히 쳐서 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 면상에 꽂아 봐!\n"
" !agree\n"
" 또 잡자마자 <i>즉시</i> <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>를 던지면 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>도 가능해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이쪽이 초보가 쓰기 더 쉬워."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" LISTEN UP! You can perform a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> by throwing a <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</> at an <#RED>Enemy</> the moment you catch it.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You can also do a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> by using your <#RED>Punch</> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> to hit your own <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</> while its airborne."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 잘 들어! 잡는 순간 <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>를 <#RED>적</>에게 던지면 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>가 발동해.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 또 공중에 떠 있는 네 <#RED>{name.weapon_shotput}</>를 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>펀치</>로 쳐서 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>도 할 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Knock'm dead, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} 가서 박살 내, 사냥꾼."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ENDLOOP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ENDLOOP"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 'Course."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 물론이지."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Go, uh... {name.dojo_cough} <i>have a ball</i> out there."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 자, 어... {name.dojo_cough} <i>실컷 날뛰다 와</i>."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_A"
msgid "Ayy!"
msgstr "얍!"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.BYE_B"
msgid "<i>Toot</i>-a-loo! Hehe."
msgstr "<i>Toot</i>-a-loo! 헤헤."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Uh. Any tips on how to fight with a ball?"
msgstr "저기, 이 공 같은 걸로 싸우는 팁 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "If it's not a ball then why's it so <i>fetching</i>?"
msgstr "공이 아니라면 왜 이렇게 <i>물어오고 싶게</i> 생겼는데?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Okay but, how do I even use this?"
msgstr "알겠는데, 이거 대체 어떻게 써?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_ALT"
msgid "Can you cover the basics again? I wasn't paying attention."
msgstr "기본기 다시 설명해줄래? 아까 집중 못 했어."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "Can these do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}?"
msgstr "이걸로 {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} 할 수 있어?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C_ALT"
msgid "Uh, how do I do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} again?"
msgstr "어, {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}은 다시 어떻게 해?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "See ya {name.npc_dojo_master}, thanks for the explainer!"
msgstr "{name.npc_dojo_master} 다음에 봐, 설명 고마워!"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP"
msgid "Thanks, {name.npc_dojo_master}!"
msgstr "고마워, {name.npc_dojo_master}!"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP_ALT"
msgid "But seriously. Thanks {name.npc_dojo_master}."
msgstr "근데 진짜 고마워, {name.npc_dojo_master}."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh, that's a funny story!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" And a bit of a long one, do you have the time?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 아, 그거 재밌는 이야기야!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 좀 길어, 시간 괜찮아?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_STORY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_STORY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Sure, well... after the disaster I probably spent about a year bouncing from place to place in <#BLUE>the Brinks.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I got <i>really</> good at pickpocketing during that time."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그래, 음... 재난 뒤에 <#BLUE>브링크스</> 여기저기를 거의 1년은 떠돌았어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 그때 소매치기를 <i>진짜</> 잘하게 됐지."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_SKIP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_SKIP"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh! Yes, well, I'm busy too, so...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" See ya!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 아! 맞아, 나도 바빠서...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 또 봐!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Don't judge, Hunter. Hunger's a powerful motivator..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 판단하진 마, 사냥꾼. 배고픔은 엄청 강한 동기거든..."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" True, true. Especially in those days."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 맞아, 맞아. 특히 그때는."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Where were you back then?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 그때 넌 어디 있었어?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hah! <i>Maybe</i> today... if he was asleep. And in a different room from his pockets."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 하! <i>어쩌면</i> 오늘은 가능할지도... 걔가 자고 있고, 주머니랑 다른 방에 있다면."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_6
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_6"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Actually, no. One squint and he knew my story instantly.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I wasn't a bad kit. Just in a bad situation.\n"
" !agree\n"
" He took me in. And even though I didn't make a good Hunter, I was safe, warm, and fed.\n"
" !point\n"
" I want everyone in <#BLUE>the Brinks</> to have that, too."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 아니, 전혀. 눈 한 번 가늘게 뜨고는 내 사정을 바로 알아채더라.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 난 나쁜 꼬맹이가 아니었어. 그냥 상황이 나빴을 뿐.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 날 받아줬고, 내가 좋은 사냥꾼은 못 됐어도 안전하고 따뜻했고 배불리 먹을 수 있었지.\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>브링크스</>의 모두도 그랬으면 해."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anytime. I'm an open book."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 언제든지. 난 뭐든 다 말해줄 수 있어."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well, you can't say I didn't warn you!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 뭐, 내가 경고 안 했다는 말은 못 하겠다!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5A"
msgid "Woah! {name.npc_dojo_master} was fast!"
msgstr "와! {name.npc_dojo_master} 엄청 빠르네!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5B"
msgid "Woah! {name.npc_dojo_master} was strong!"
msgstr "와! {name.npc_dojo_master} 엄청 세네!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How do you and {name.npc_dojo_master} know each other?"
msgstr "너랑 {name.npc_dojo_master}는 어떻게 아는 사이야?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_STORY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_STORY"
msgid "Sure, why not?"
msgstr "그래, 좋지 뭐?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_SKIP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_SKIP"
msgid "Ah, maybe another time actually."
msgstr "아, 역시 다음에 들을게."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Wait, <i>you</> were a thief??"
msgstr "잠깐, <i>너</> 도둑이었어??"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "Gotta do whatcha gotta do."
msgstr "살아남으려면 뭐든 해야지."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "Well that was a mistake."
msgstr "그건 실수였네."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "Pfft, you could take him."
msgstr "풉, 너라면 걔 이기지."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_6
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_6"
msgid "Was he mad?"
msgstr "화냈어?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7A"
msgid "Thanks for the glimpse into your past, {name.npc_scout}."
msgstr "과거 얘기 들려줘서 고마워, {name.npc_scout}."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7B"
msgid "You're right, that was a long story!"
msgstr "네 말대로 진짜 긴 이야기였네!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Still, not my proudest era, but hey--\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I wouldn't be an expert <#RED>{name.job_scout}</> if not for all that sneaking around. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>Meanwhile</i> around that time, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> was kicking off the very first Hunter Academy.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" And my under-developed brain made the mistake of thinking he'd be an easy mark."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 그래도 내 인생에서 자랑스러운 시절은 아니었지만, 뭐--\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 그때 그렇게 몰래 다니지 않았으면 <#RED>{name.job_scout}</> 전문가가 되진 못했겠지. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>한편</i> 그 무렵 <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>는 첫 사냥꾼 아카데미를 막 시작하고 있었어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그리고 덜 자란 내 머리는 걔를 쉬운 먹잇감이라 착각하는 실수를 저질렀지."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway, while he was distracted at the registration table I snuck up... reached into his pocket, and...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <z 3.0><i>BAM!</i></z>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Next thing I know, I'm dangling by my ankle two feet off the ground, my meagre pickings for the day falling out of my own pockets."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아무튼, 걔가 등록 테이블에 정신 팔린 사이 몰래 다가가서... 주머니에 손을 넣었는데...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <z 3.0><i>쾅!</i></z>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 정신 차려 보니 발목이 잡힌 채로 땅에서 두 발쯤 떠서 매달려 있었고, 하루 종일 훔친 쥐꼬리 수확은 내 주머니에서 우수수 떨어지고 있었어."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Haha! Yeah, he got a ton of new students after that display! <z 0.7><i>Some of whose pockets I'd picked.</></>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 하하! 맞아, 그 쇼 덕분에 신입생이 엄청 몰렸지! <z 0.7><i>그중 몇 명 주머니는 내가 턴 적도 있고.</></>"

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" What do ye know about <#RED>Weapon Weight</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>무기 무게</>에 대해 뭘 알고 있지?"

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Aye, then. Ahem. <#RED>Heavy Weapons</>?\n"
" !point\n"
" Hefty. They do more <#RED>Damage</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>Light Weapons</>? Less <#RED>Damage</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Fast though. Less risky ta commit ta an <#RED>Attack</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>Normal Weapon</>? Eh. Balanced."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 그래, 좋아. 흠흠. <#RED>중량 무기</>?\n"
" !point\n"
" 묵직하지. <#RED>피해</>가 더 커.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>경량 무기</>? <#RED>피해</>는 덜해.\n"
" !point\n"
" 대신 빠르지. <#RED>공격</>에 들어가도 리스크가 적어.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>표준 무기</>? 뭐, 균형형이지."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Correct. But no cookie. Never cookie.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" As ye were."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...정답이다. 근데 쿠키는 없어. 쿠키는 절대 없어.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 하던 거 해."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_A"
msgid "More...less...balanced. Got it. Love you, Hamish!"
msgstr "더 세고... 덜 세고... 균형형. 알겠어. 사랑해, 해미시!"

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_B"
msgid "Thanks, Hamish. You're my best friend."
msgstr "고마워, 해미시. 넌 내 베프야."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hmph."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 흠."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "<z 0.7><i>(In a cool gruff voice)</></> ...{name.npc_blacksmith}."
msgstr "<z 0.7><i>(멋지고 걸걸한 목소리로)</></> ...{name.npc_blacksmith}."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Nothing. Take me to school, Hamish."
msgstr "아는 거 없어. 제대로 가르쳐줘, 해미시."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "<z 0.9>It affects Attack Speed and Damage.</> Do I get a cookie?"
msgstr "<z 0.9>공격 속도랑 피해량에 영향 줘.</> 쿠키 줘?"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Unfortunately not...\n"
" !think\n"
" That fourth <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> should have jump-started the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</>, but the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> levels plummeted just as it got going!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I'm so sorry. I-I must've missed something... some unknown variable..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 유감이지만 아니야...\n"
" !think\n"
" 네 번째 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>면 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 파이프라인 에너지 그리드</>를 가동했어야 했는데, 시작하자마자 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 수치가 급락했어!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 정말 미안해. 내, 내가 뭔가를 놓친 게 분명해... 어떤 미지의 변수 같은 걸..."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I-it doesn't work like that, Hunter... \n"
" !dejected\n"
" After 10 years of calculations... I followed Grandpa's notes to the letter... Where could the <#KONJUR>Teffra</> have gone?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7><i>Grandpa... if you can hear me... give me a sign...</></>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그, 그런 식으로 되는 게 아니야, 사냥꾼... \n"
" !dejected\n"
" 10년 동안 계산했고... 할아버지 노트를 한 치도 안 틀리고 따라 했는데... <#KONJUR>테프라</>가 대체 어디로 간 거지?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7><i>할아버지... 들리면... 신호 좀 줘...</></>"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Please tell me the shield is up, but it's just invisible..."
msgstr "방어막 켜진 거 맞지? 그냥 안 보이는 거라고 해줘..."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Why don't we just stuff this thing with {name_multiple.i_konjur_heart} until it works?"
msgstr "이거 작동할 때까지 {name_multiple.i_konjur_heart} 계속 쑤셔 넣으면 안 돼?"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What... <z 0.7><i>I-I don't understand... the fourth <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> was supposed to... what did I miss?</></>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah! Hunter! Y-you startled me."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 뭐지... <z 0.7><i>나, 난 이해가 안 돼... 네 번째 <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>면 됐어야 하는데... 뭘 놓친 거지?</></>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 사냥꾼! 너, 너 때문에 깜짝 놀랐잖아."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ONWARD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ONWARD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" To the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>로 가자!"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! Are you okay?!\n"
" player:\n"
" Yeah! What was that?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" The missing <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>! It must have overloaded the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> and... burst out? B-but that shouldn't be possible!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" My stupid plan just made things worse! What was I thinking?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Pretending to be a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> scientist, risking lives to what? \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Impress my Grandpa? Who I foolishly hoped might somehow be--\n"
" player:\n"
" Snap out of it! The {name_multiple.foxtails} need a leader, so lead!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Y-you're right. <i>(deep breath)</> Okay. One moment...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" <z 0.7>That... account for the... carry the zero...</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Right. The epicenter of that quake looks to be the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Our missing <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> should be there!\n"
" player:\n"
" Lead the way, Flitt!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 사냥꾼! 괜찮아?!\n"
" player:\n"
" 응! 방금 뭐였어?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 사라진 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>야! 그게 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} 파이프라인 에너지 그리드</>를 과부하시켜서... 터져 나온 건가? 하, 하지만 그건 말이 안 돼!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 내 멍청한 계획이 일을 더 키웠어! 내가 무슨 생각이었던 거지?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 과학자인 척하면서 목숨까지 걸게 만들고, 대체 뭘 하려던 거야? \n"
" !disagree\n"
" 할아버지한테 인정받으려고? 어리석게도 어떻게든 살아 계실 거라고 믿으면서--\n"
" player:\n"
" 정신 차려! {name_multiple.foxtails}에겐 리더가 필요해, 그러니까 네가 이끌어!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" 마, 맞아. <i>(깊게 숨 들이쉬며)</> 좋아. 잠깐만...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" <z 0.7>저거... 반영하고... 0 올림하고...</>\n"
" !think\n"
" 좋아. 그 지진의 진앙은 <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>로 보여.\n"
" !point\n"
" 사라진 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>도 거기 있을 거야!\n"
" player:\n"
" 앞장서, 플릿!"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GHOST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GHOST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Heard one, perhaps. I'm <i>positive</> I heard a melody... a melody I've known since I as a young kit... coming from these woods...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter... it was the lullaby sung to me by my <#BLUE>Grandpa</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" Your Grandpa? Famous {name.konjur} science guy? Who <i>died</> in the eruption?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Strange way to sum him up but yes! We were separated in the chaos of the eruption, and I assumed--like everyone--that he'd died. But maybe, just maybe...\n"
" player:\n"
" That's incredible! And what I mean by that is, it's not credible.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !scared\n"
" Please, Hunter. Only he and I know that song. If there's a chance my <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> alive somewhere out there, alone, afraid...\n"
" player:\n"
" ... And whistling a lullaby...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hunter. Please.\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry. One rescue, comin' up!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Thank you.\n"
" !point\n"
" The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</> seem in a frenzy, so move fast!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 본 건 아니고, 들은 것 같아. 난 <i>분명히</> 멜로디를 들었어... 내가 어릴 때부터 알던 멜로디를... 이 숲에서...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 사냥꾼... 그건 <#BLUE>할아버지</>가 내게 불러주던 자장가였어!\n"
" player:\n"
" 네 할아버지? 유명한 {name.konjur}과학자 양반? <i>대폭발 때 죽은</> 그분?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 요약이 좀 묘하긴 한데 맞아! 우리는 대폭발의 혼란 속에서 헤어졌고, 나도 다른 사람들처럼 그분이 죽었다고 생각했어. 하지만 어쩌면, 정말 어쩌면...\n"
" player:\n"
" 대단하네! 라고 하고 싶지만, 말이 되진 않네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !scared\n"
" 제발, 사냥꾼. 그 노래는 그분과 나만 알아. 내 <#BLUE>할아버지가</> 어딘가에서 살아 있고, 혼자 두려워하고 있을 가능성이 있다면...\n"
" player:\n"
" ...그리고 자장가를 휘파람으로 불고 있고...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 사냥꾼. 부탁해.\n"
" player:\n"
" 미안. 구조 하나 바로 간다!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 고마워.\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>에 있는 <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>가 광분한 상태 같아, 서둘러!"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GHOST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GHOST"
msgid "You okay, {name.npc_scout}? You look like you've seen a ghost."
msgstr "괜찮아, {name.npc_scout}? 귀신이라도 본 얼굴이네."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh... <z 0.7><i>Please be okay...</></>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아... <z 0.7><i>제발 무사해야 해...</></>"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Y-yes...\n"
" !point\n"
" We just have to keep looking. M-maybe I heard something else, like the wind whistling through a tree with very specific holes?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I don't know..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 으, 응...\n"
" !point\n"
" 계속 찾아보면 돼. 아, 아마 다른 소리를 들은 걸 수도 있어. 구멍이 유난히 많은 나무 사이로 바람이 휘파람 부는 소리 같은 거?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 나도 잘 모르겠어..."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "It's okay. We'll keep looking. Or listening."
msgstr "괜찮아. 계속 찾아보자. 아니면 계속 들어보자."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "No sign of that mystery song you heard, though."
msgstr "그래도 네가 들었다는 그 수수께끼 노래는 흔적이 없네."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, that last excursion was a doozy. We barely made it out of there in one piece."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 휴, 지난 원정은 진짜 험했어. 거의 간신히 살아 나왔네."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Then let's bundle up and save your <z 0.7>Grandpa</>."
msgstr "그럼 단단히 껴입고 네 <z 0.7>할아버지</>를 구하자."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.EXPLAIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.EXPLAIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" To put it in layneander's terms, it's a machine that locks in on the particular <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> radiological signatures of rare items...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" ... <i>OR</> rare people!\n"
" player:\n"
" You mean <z 0.7>Grandpa</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Precisely!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Anyone who's worked with as much <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> as <z 0.7><#BLUE>Grandpa</></> will have a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> signature through the roof--\n"
" !clap\n"
" --Found him! He's in <#BLUE>{name.sedament_tundra}</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" Hunter. If we rescue my <z 0.7><#BLUE>Grandpa</></>, I'm positive he'd not only fix our <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>, he'd make it even better!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" He's the key to salvaging our whole mission."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 쉽게 말하면, 희귀 물건들의 특정 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 방사선 신호를 추적해 고정하는 기계야...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" ... <i>OR</> 희귀한 사람도!\n"
" player:\n"
" 네 말은 <z 0.7>할아버지</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 정확해!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>을 <z 0.7><#BLUE>할아버지</></>만큼 다룬 사람이라면 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 신호가 엄청 높게 나올 거야--\n"
" !clap\n"
" --찾았다! <#BLUE>{name.sedament_tundra}</>에 계셔!\n"
" !point\n"
" 헌터. 내 <z 0.7><#BLUE>할아버지</></>를 구하면, 우리 <#KONJUR>버블 실드</>를 고쳐 주실 뿐 아니라 더 좋게 만들어 주실 거야!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 우리 임무 전체를 살릴 열쇠는 그분이야."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'm grateful <i>we</> made it out safe, but are you sure you looked everywhere?\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry, {name.npc_scout}, I didn't see your Grandpa.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Please, Hunter, keep your voice down! People will think I've lost it, searching for my <z 0.7><i>long-thought-dead-and-probably-is-dead <#BLUE>Grandpa</></></> to fix everything...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ... M-maybe I just heard the wind, whistling through a tree with very specific, flute-like holes? \n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}]</> I <i>did</> find signs of a struggle, and this weird doo-hickey. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" \"Signs of a struggle\"? Oh dear--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Egads! I've never seen a machine like that. Especialy not dropped by a flute-tree...\n"
" !think\n"
" Is this a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> intake? <z 0.7>And this a <#KONJUR>Teffronic</> resonance sensor... and a lapidary tumbler??</>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Good gravy! This is a <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" A what-what-meter?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>우리가</> 무사히 나온 건 고마운데, 정말 구석구석 다 본 거 맞아?\n"
" player:\n"
" 미안, {name.npc_scout}. 네 할아버지는 못 봤어.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 제발 헌터, 목소리 좀 낮춰! 사람들이 내가 다 끝났다고 생각할 거야. 모든 걸 고치려고 내 <z 0.7><i>오래전에 죽은 줄 알았고 아마 진짜 죽었을 <#BLUE>할아버지</></></>를 찾고 다닌다고...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ... 아, 아마 내가 들은 건 그냥 바람이었을지도. 아주 특정한, 플루트 같은 구멍이 난 나무를 지나는 휘파람 소리?\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[{name.teffrometer_unidentified}을 보여준다]</> 그래도 <i>찾은</> 건 있어. 몸싸움 흔적이랑, 이 이상한 장치.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" \"몸싸움 흔적\"? 이런, 설마--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 세상에! 저런 기계는 본 적이 없어. 플루트나무에서 떨어질 리도 없고...\n"
" !think\n"
" 이건 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> 흡입구인가? <z 0.7>그리고 이건 <#KONJUR>테프로닉</> 공진 센서... 거기에 연마 텀블러까지??</>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 맙소사! 이건 <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>야!\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐, 뭐측정기라고?"

#: Convo.twn_welcome_to_town_refiner.ATTRACT0.first_meet.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_welcome_to_town_refiner.ATTRACT0.first_meet.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" So this is your <#BLUE>{name.town}</>, huh? And <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> the de-facto leader? \n"
" !think\n"
" <i>Hm.</> Despite that, it appears to be a decentralized collectivist cooperative with a souvenir-based barter system...\n"
" player:\n"
" It's not much, but it's home.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" -- Wait. Is that a <i>community garden?!</> <z 0.7>OMG... food security, knowledge sharing, sustainability...EEK!</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sorry. My \"Been in a Lab Under a Volcano With a Mad Scientist for Too Long\" is showing.\n"
" !point\n"
" Mind if I set up my gear here? Good because it's happening.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, and make sure <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> reads <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> <#RED>Diary</> to see I'm not lying, okay? <i>Not</> that I care... \n"
" player:\n"
" Will do. Y'know, you <i>act</> all cool, but <i>I</> think you--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Look, Hunter. I'm down for open info exchanges, but I've had a looong day.  \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Talk to me when you've found some of the three <#RED>Key Fragments</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We need those to stop <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}'s</> <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</> from destroying life as we know it. Cool?\n"
" player:\n"
" Cool! Supes cool. Welcome to the, er, non-hippopotamus, collector's edition, desensitized campoperative!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Cool. <z 0.7><i>\"Hunter... bad... at... words...\"</></> He he he."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 여기가 너희 <#BLUE>{name.town}</>구나? 그리고 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}가</> 사실상 리더고?\n"
" !think\n"
" <i>흠.</> 그래도 보니까 분산형 집단주의 협동체에 기념품 기반 물물교환 시스템이네...\n"
" player:\n"
" 대단하진 않아도, 우리 집이야.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" --잠깐. 저거 <i>공동 텃밭?!</> <z 0.7>세상에... 식량 안정성, 지식 공유, 지속 가능성... 꺄악!</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 미안. \"화산 아래 미친 과학자랑 연구실에 너무 오래 있었음\"이 튀어나왔네.\n"
" !point\n"
" 여기 장비 차려도 돼? 대답 안 해도 돼, 이미 할 거야.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아, 그리고 <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>이 <#BLUE>할아버지의</> <#RED>일기</> 읽고 내가 거짓말 아닌지 확인하게 해. 알겠지? <i>딱히</> 신경 쓰는 건 아니고...\n"
" player:\n"
" 알겠어. 근데 너 <i>겉으로는</> 쿨한 척해도 <i>난</> 네가--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 헌터, 들어. 공개 정보 교환은 나도 좋아하는데 오늘 너무 길었어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>열쇠 파편</> 세 개 중 일부라도 찾고 나서 말 걸어.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}의</> <#KONJUR>두 번째 대폭발</>이 우리가 아는 삶을 날려 버리지 못하게 하려면 그게 필요해. 알았지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 알았어! 완전 알았어. 그, 비-하마형 컬렉터스 에디션 무감각 캠퍼러티브에 온 걸 환영해!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 좋아. <z 0.7><i>\"헌터... 말... 진짜... 못함...\"</></> 히히히."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" It's super important. You've got to follow my instructions <i>exactly</>, okay?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Close your eyes and hold out your hands."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 이거 엄청 중요해. 내 지시 <i>정확히</> 따라야 해, 알겠지?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 눈 감고 두 손 내밀어."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Perfect! Stay just like that for a second...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Okay, now open your eyes!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" 완벽해! 잠깐만 그대로 있어...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...좋아, 이제 눈 떠!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Hope you like it! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> helped me pick it out!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 마음에 들었으면 좋겠다! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>이 같이 골라줬어!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr "뭐가 필요해?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Okay! <i><#RED><z 0.7>(Close your eyes and hold out your hands)</z></></i>"
msgstr "좋아! <i><#RED><z 0.7>(눈 감고 손 내밀기)</z></></i>"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "A {name.holiday_winter} present? Wow, thanks {name.npc_armorsmith}!"
msgstr "{name.holiday_winter} 선물? 와, 고마워 {name.npc_armorsmith}!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hunteerrrrr, over here! I need you to do something for me!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" 헌터어어어, 여기! 네가 해줄 게 있어!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt} Dinnae mention it. Ever."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt} 말 꺼내지도 마. 절대."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "You got me a {name.holiday_winter} present? Thanks {name.npc_blacksmith}!"
msgstr "{name.holiday_winter} 선물 준 거야? 고마워 {name.npc_blacksmith}!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Here."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 헌터.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...여기."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1AB
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1AB"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Everyone needs to take it easy now and then. Even you, Hunter.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But if you're not keen on takin' a break, you can take this instead."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 가끔은 누구나 쉬어야 해. 너도 마찬가지야, 헌터.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그래도 쉬기 싫으면, 대신 이거 받아."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! Wouldn't you like to know!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하! 그걸 내가 알려줄 것 같아?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I can't slow down, there's too much to do!"
msgstr "난 못 쉬어, 할 게 너무 많아!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Bah. Holidays are just used as an excuse to slack off."
msgstr "흥. 휴일은 게으름 피우려는 핑계일 뿐이야."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Aw, thanks {name.npc_dojo_master}! Does this mean I'm your favourite student?"
msgstr "아, 고마워 {name.npc_dojo_master}! 이건 내가 네 최애 제자라는 뜻이야?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Still workin' hard over {name.holiday_winter}, eh kid?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아직도 {name.holiday_winter}에서 열심히 굴리는 중이네, 꼬맹아?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" We've all lost a lot these past ten years. I had a feeling you'd understand.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Look at me getting all sappy, I almost forgot! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here. A little something from me to you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 지난 10년 동안 우리 다 많이 잃었지. 네가 이해해줄 거라 생각했어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 나 왜 이렇게 감성적이냐, 깜빡할 뻔했네!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자. 내가 너한테 주는 작은 선물."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Truer words were never spoken.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Look at me getting all sappy, I almost forgot! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here. A little something from me to you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그보다 더 맞는 말은 없지.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 아! 나 왜 이렇게 감성적이냐, 깜빡할 뻔했네!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자. 내가 너한테 주는 작은 선물."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2AB
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2AB"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Happy Wintertide, Hunter."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 겨울맞이 잘 보내, 헌터."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Me neither..."
msgstr "나도..."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "There's nothing like spending {name.holiday_winter} with good friends."
msgstr "좋은 친구들이랑 {name.holiday_winter} 보내는 것만큼 좋은 건 없지."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2AB
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2AB"
msgid "Thanks, {name.npc_scout}!"
msgstr "고마워, {name.npc_scout}!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" You know, usually I dread this time of year.\n"
" !think\n"
" It always brings up so many memories. But somehow... this time it feels easier.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I suspect you've got a lot to do with that. You, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>, <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I can't remember the last time I was surrounded by so many folks during {name.holiday_winter}."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 있지, 난 보통 이맘때가 싫었어.\n"
" !think\n"
" 늘 너무 많은 기억이 떠오르거든. 근데 이상하게도... 이번엔 좀 괜찮아.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그게 네 덕이 큰 것 같아. 너랑, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>, <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" {name.holiday_winter} 동안 이렇게 많은 사람들한테 둘러싸여 있었던 게 언제였는지 기억도 안 나."

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Hold on everyone! We're coming!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" 다들 잠깐만! 우리가 간다!"

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ONTHREE
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ONTHREE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" Pretty sure you landed <i>directly</> on your brain, but... we'll deal with that later. Let's go rescue our pals!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" 네가 <i>정통으로</> 머리부터 떨어진 건 확실한데... 그건 나중에 처리하자. 일단 친구들 구하러 가자!"

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS"
msgid "{name_multiple.foxtails}!"
msgstr "{name_multiple.foxtails}!"

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ONTHREE
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ONTHREE"
msgid "Did you mean ON three? Or right AFTER three?"
msgstr "셋에 맞춰서라고 한 거야? 아니면 셋 말하고 바로 다음에?"

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK_INTRO
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK_INTRO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! Thank goodness you're alive! How many claws am I holding up?\n"
" player:\n"
" Uh... none. Are <i>you</> okay?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Far from it! Our expedition's barely begun and I've already lost track of half our crew! <z 0.7><i>Grandpa would never have let this happen...</></>\n"
" player:\n"
" It's gonna be alright, {name.npc_scout}. Just breathe. Who's missing?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" While you were out, I flew over and saw <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>, our Battlemaster. He recovered our <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> tech and is setting up camp.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" But I couldn't find <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, our <#RED>{name.job_armorsmith},</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, our <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}.</> They don't stand a chance against these <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Okay, you search the forest. The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>'s still in one piece, so I'll be right above you to scoop up our crew--or you if you, uh, y'know, <z 0.7> \"fall.\"</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Alright now, \"<#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>\" on three. 1... 2... 3! <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 헌터! 살아 있어서 다행이다! 내가 발톱 몇 개 펴고 있는지 보여?\n"
" player:\n"
" 어... 하나도 없어. <i>너</> 괜찮아?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" 전혀 아니야! 원정 시작한 지 얼마 되지도 않았는데 벌써 대원 절반을 놓쳤어! <z 0.7><i>할아버지였다면 절대 이런 일 없었을 텐데...</></>\n"
" player:\n"
" 괜찮을 거야, {name.npc_scout}. 숨부터 고르자. 누가 없어졌어?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 네가 정신 잃은 사이에 날아서 살펴봤는데, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> 우리 배틀마스터를 봤어. <#KONJUR>버블 실드</> 기술을 회수해서 야영지 꾸리는 중이야.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 근데 <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, 우리 <#RED>{name.job_armorsmith},</> 그리고 <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, 우리 <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}.</>는 못 찾았어. 저 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 상대로는 가망이 없어!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 좋아, 넌 숲을 수색해. <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>는 아직 멀쩡하니까 내가 위에서 바로 대원들 태워 올릴게. 아니면 너라도, 그... 알지, <z 0.7>\"떨어지면.\"</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 좋아, 그럼 셋에 \"<#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>\" 외치자. 1... 2... 3! <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].1
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'll follow from the sky, Hunter.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" I believe in you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 내가 하늘에서 따라갈게, 헌터.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" 난 널 믿어."

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].2
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>... <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>... please be okay..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>... <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>... 제발 무사해..."

