" !notebook\n"
" I was looking forward to a break."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" 아, <#RED>업그레이드</>할 게 없네.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 쉬는 시간 좀 기대했는데."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Eh? You've got nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" What a bummer."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 엥? <#RED>업그레이드</>할 게 없네.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 진짜 김 빠진다."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</> today, huh?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe you'll get a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> in the next room."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 오늘은 <#RED>업그레이드</>할 게 없네?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 다음 방에선 <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> 하나 얻을지도 모르지."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just as well, I'm behind on data entry."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" <#RED>업그레이드</>할 게 없어?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 잘됐네, 나 데이터 입력 밀렸거든."

