#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" What a privilege for you, browsing my wares.\n"
" !wink\n"
" You're welcome."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 내 물건을 구경하다니, 너한텐 영광이지.\n"
" !wink\n"
" 고마운 줄 알아."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Peruse at your leisure, culver.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm not going anywhere."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" 천천히 골라봐, 애송이.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 난 어디 안 가."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Handcrafted, artisanal pieces at reasonable prices.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Made from local materials."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 손으로 직접 만든 장인 수제품, 가격도 합리적.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 재료는 전부 지역산."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" All pieces are guaranteed to be one-size-fits-all.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The material is <i>deceptively</i> elastic."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 모든 제품은 프리사이즈 보장.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 소재가 <i>겉보기보다</i> 탄성이 좋아."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !smirk\n"
" Hand-hammered, hand-forged.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And, if you desire, hand-delivered."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !smirk\n"
" 수작업 망치질, 수작업 단조.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 원한다면 수작업 배달도."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh yeah. I hath what the Hunters crave.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 오 그래. 헌터들이 갈망하는 건 다 있지.\n"
" !wink\n"
" 잘 즐겨."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm glad we're doing another Hunt here.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I love flying over the treetops."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" 여기서 사냥을 또 하게 돼서 좋아.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 나무 꼭대기 위로 날아다니는 거 진짜 좋아하거든."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'think there are any squirrels left in this forest?\n"
" !point\n"
" Squirrels are neat."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 이 숲에 다람쥐가 아직 남아 있을까?\n"
" !point\n"
" 다람쥐는 멋져."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" When I was a kid my grandpa and I used to pick berries around here.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway. Be safe on your Hunt."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" 어릴 때 할아버지랑 여기서 열매를 따곤 했어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 어쨌든, 사냥 조심해서 다녀와."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" You know what <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}'d</> say about the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in there.\n"
" !scared\n"
" If one looks like it's about to <#RED>Attack</>, <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>Dodge</> out of the way."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" 안에 있는 <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> 보면 <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}'d</>가 뭐라고 할지 알지.\n"
" !scared\n"
" 하나가 곧 <#RED>Attack</>할 것 같으면, <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>회피</>해서 비켜."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't forget, a <#RED>Dodge</> will always get you out of harm's way quicker than running.\n"
" !point\n"
" As Toot would say, \"You can <#RED>Dodge</> with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\" I usually dodge with my legs."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 잊지 마, <#RED>Dodge</>는 뛰는 것보다 항상 더 빨리 위험에서 벗어나게 해 줘.\n"
" !point\n"
" Toot 말로는 \"<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>로도 <#RED>Dodge</>할 수 있어.\"라더라. 난 보통 다리로 회피해."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> says, time a <#RED>Dodge</> <i>just</> right after starting an <#RED>Attack</> to do what's called a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge} Cancel</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Longer or heavier <#RED>Attacks</> usually have smaller <#RED>Cancel Windows</>, though. <z 0.7>All of <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}'s</> weird terms...</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>가 그러는데, <#RED>공격</>을 시작한 직후에 <i>딱</> 맞춰 <#RED>회피</>하면 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge} 취소</>가 된대.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 근데 길거나 무거운 <#RED>공격</>일수록 <#RED>캔슬 시간</>이 더 짧아. <z 0.7><#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>가 쓰는 용어들은 다 이상하다니까...</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> said when you <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>, you'll roll a short distance and even be <#RED>Invincible</> for a little bit.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Masters can even do a <#RED>Perfect Dodge</> by waiting until the last moment to roll away. <#RED>Dodging</> is a science, an art, <i>and</> a little roll!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>가 그러는데 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>하면 짧게 구르면서 잠깐 <#RED>Invincible</> 상태도 된대.\n"
" !agree\n"
" 고수들은 구르기 직전까지 버텨서 <#RED>Perfect Dodge</>도 해. <#RED>Dodging</>은 과학이자 예술이고, <i>and</> 작은 구르기지!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hunter! <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me to remind you of <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" And I quote, \"One way is to do 'em is to hit <#RED>two or more Targets</> at once with your <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</>.\" End quote."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 헌터! <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>가 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> 잊지 말라고 전해 달랬어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그리고 정확히 인용하면, \"방법 중 하나는 <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</>로 <#RED>two or more Targets</>를 한 번에 치는 거야.\" 끝."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hunter! <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me to remind you of <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" And I quote, \"One way to do 'em is to fully charge your <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}'s</> <#RED>Skill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\""
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 헌터! <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>가 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> 잊지 말라고 했어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그리고 인용하자면, \"방법 중 하나는 <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> <#RED>기술</>(<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>)을 완전히 차지해서 쓰는 거야.\""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, Hunter, do you know what it takes to do a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>? <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> asked me to ask.\n"
" !point\n"
" He said, \"One way to do 'em is with a fully charged <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> <#RED>Heavy Attack</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\""
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 아, 헌터. <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> 하려면 뭐가 필요한지 알아? <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>가 물어보래.\n"
" !point\n"
" 걔 말로는 \"방법 중 하나는 완전히 차지한 <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> <#RED>Heavy Attack</>(<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>)으로 하는 거야.\""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_polearm]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_polearm]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> today, huh?\n"
" !point\n"
" You know what <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> says, \"Hit with the very tip, do a scary <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>.\""
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 오늘은 <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</>을 쓰는구나?\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</1>가 말했듯이, \"끝부분으로 치면, 무시무시한 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</2>이 된다고.\""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Don't forget to keep <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> in mind out there.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> says they do increased <#RED>Damage</>, which appears in <#BLUE>Blue</>, whatever <i>that</> means?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 밖에 나가면 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> 꼭 염두에 둬.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> 말로는 <#RED>Damage</>가 더 들어가고, 그게 <#BLUE>Blue</>로 뜬대. <i>that</>가 뭔 뜻인진 모르겠지만?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hey, Hunter... I just wanted to say I appreciate all the work you do for the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}'</> expedition.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" That's... that's all. Didn't mean to get all mushy."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 있잖아, 헌터... <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}'</> 원정을 위해 네가 해주는 일들, 정말 고맙게 생각해.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 그게... 그게 다야. 너무 감상적으로 굴 생각은 없었어."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Does that look like a trough??"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 저게 구유처럼 보여??"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].10"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" My lost profit sense is tingling."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 잃어버린 수익 감지가 온다."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].11"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ahem."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 흠흠."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].12"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's happening over there?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 거기서 뭐 하는 거야?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].13"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" At least wear a hairnet!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 최소한 머리망은 써!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].14
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].14"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What's that?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 저게 뭐지?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].15
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].15"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Must've been the wind."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 바람 소리였나 보네."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].16
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].16"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I say!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이보게!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].17
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].17"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" No free samples!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 무료 시식은 없어!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hey!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 어이!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What are you doing over there, my fine friend?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 거기서 뭘 하는 거지, 친구?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Keep your paws out of that!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" 거기 손대지 마!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Did I hear something?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 뭐 소리 났나?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What was that?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 뭐였지?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hm?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 흠?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Like I need another health code violation."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" 보건 규정 위반 하나 더 생길 판이네."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].9"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" What's going on over there?"
msgstr "!dubious\n"
" 거기서 무슨 일이지?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" It'sss not easy to brew this stuff up, you know.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I've only got so much oil."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이걸 끓여내는 게 쉽진 않다, 알지.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 기름도 한정돼 있어."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for stopping by the finest little caravan this ssside of the volcano!\n"
" !point\n"
" Be sure to tell your friendsss... <z 0.7>(with money.)</z>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 화산 이쪽에서 제일 끝내주는 작은 행상단에 들러줘서 고마워!\n"
" !point\n"
" 친구들한테도 꼭 말해 줘... <z 0.7>(돈 있는 친구들로.)</z>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}s</>!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Restore your mojo on the go-go!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" {name.npc_doc_lastname}-브랜드 <#RED>Health {name.potion}s</>!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이동하면서 기력도 바로 회복!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[run_has_five_finger_brew].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[run_has_five_finger_brew].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Those nasssty Rots have been getting into my <#RED>Potion</> supply. I'm sure of it.\n"
" !point\n"
" But don't fret-- now I'm storing my brew somewhere safe from their ssssticky fingers.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Got to make sure there's plenty for honest, hard-working Hunters like yourself to buy!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
