" 너 누구야?"

#: Quest.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade,location_sedament_tundra,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_konjurist,role_konjurist].1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade,location_sedament_tundra,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_konjurist,role_konjurist].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Isn't it interesting that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> doesn't freeze in these sub-zero temperatures?\n"
" !think\n"
" I should do some lab-controlled experiments to see what conditions it becomes a solid under."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" 이 영하의 온도에서도 <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>가 얼지 않는 거, 흥미롭지 않아?\n"
" !think\n"
" 어떤 조건에서 고체가 되는지 실험실에서 통제 실험을 해봐야겠어."

#: Quest.dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion.QUIP.chitchat:[any_super_frenzy,in_quest_dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion,increased_potion_refill_price,needs_potion,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion.QUIP.chitchat:[any_super_frenzy,in_quest_dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion,increased_potion_refill_price,needs_potion,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That pallor, the dilation of the pupils...\n"
" !agree\n"
" I know a case of sssticker-shock when I see it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그 창백한 안색, 커진 동공...\n"
" !agree\n"
" 이런 가격 충격 표정은 내가 딱 보면 알아."

#: Quest.dgn_grove_potion.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_grove_potion,location_owlitzer_forest,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_grove_potion.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_grove_potion,location_owlitzer_forest,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Restore your mojo on the go-go!\n"
" !greet\n"
" {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}s</>!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이동 중에도 기력 충전!\n"
" !greet\n"
" {name.npc_doc_lastname}-브랜드 <#RED>체력 {name.potion}s</>!"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.OPT_1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.OPT_1"
msgid "I'm a Hunter. Doing Hunter things. You?"
msgstr "난 헌터야. 헌터답게 일하는 중. 넌?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.OPT_2
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.OPT_2"
msgid "Okaaaay. Y'know, we have a camp. It's safe there--if you wanted to join us."
msgstr "오케이이. 있잖아, 우리 캠프 있어. 거긴 안전해--원하면 같이 갈래?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.OPT_3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.OPT_3"
msgid "Oh. Are you sure?"
msgstr "아. 진짜 괜찮아?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !point\n"
" I don't know you. What are <i>you</> doing here?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !point\n"
" 난 널 몰라. <i>너</> 여기서 뭐 해?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK2
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'm a me. Doing me things."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 난 나야. 내 일 하는 중."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 'Camp'. With... <i>people?</>\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Um... NO."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" '캠프'. 거기... <i>사람들이?</>\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 음... 싫어."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK4
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_apothecary.TALK4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" ... \n"
" !notebook\n"
" ...\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ... okay.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... bye.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" ... \n"
" !notebook\n"
" ...\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ... 알겠어.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... 잘 가.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_1"
msgid "Yep! Well, apart from how worried they were about you."
msgstr "응! 뭐, 다들 네 걱정 엄청 하긴 했지만."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_2A
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_2A"
msgid "Woah! Really?"
msgstr "우와! 진짜?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_2B
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_2B"
msgid "That's... a little hard to believe."
msgstr "그건... 좀 믿기 어렵다."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.OPT_3"
msgid "I'm just relieved to have our resilient {name.job_armorsmith} back!"
msgstr "아무튼 우리 든든한 {name.job_armorsmith} 돌아와서 진짜 다행이야!"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hunter!! You're okay-- wait. Where's your cloak?\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}! My cloak? Um, I think it's in the {name.damselfly}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Phew! I was really worried! Such a nice piece. Brown. Plain. <i>Really</> shadowy hood. *Chef's kiss.*\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh! Speaking of the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>-- how's <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>? Are they okay??"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 헌터!! 괜찮구나--잠깐. 네 망토는 어디 있어?\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}! 내 망토? 음, {name.damselfly}에 있는 것 같은데.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" 휴! 진짜 걱정했잖아! 엄청 좋은 물건인데. 갈색. 단정. <i>정말</> 그늘진 후드. *최고야.*\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 아! <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> 얘기 나와서 말인데-- <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>는 어때? 괜찮아??"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK2
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Aw, they're so sweet-- but they didn't have to worry.\n"
" !point\n"
" I arm-wrestled a <#RED>{name.zucco}</> once, so..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 아, 다들 너무 착해--근데 걱정 안 해도 됐어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 나 예전에 <#RED>{name.zucco}</>랑 팔씨름도 해봤거든, 그래서..."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know... come to think of it, I might've read that in a diary I found.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" The point is, I'm resilient. (And good at finding diaries.)"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 그러고 보니... 내가 주운 일기에서 읽은 걸 수도 있겠다.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 핵심은, 난 끈질기다는 거야. (그리고 일기 찾는 데도 능하고.)"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK4
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_armorsmith.TALK4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" And <i>I'll</> be relieved to get to camp and work on that armour of yours!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I mean, no offense, but <i>WOOF</>...\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 그리고 나도 캠프로 돌아가서 네 방어구 손볼 생각에 <i>진짜</> 안심돼!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 그러니까, 기분 나쁘게 듣진 말고, <i>으악</>...\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_1A
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_1A"
msgid "Maybe you don't recognize me without my cool brown cloak?"
msgstr "내 멋진 갈색 망토 없어서 못 알아본 거야?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_1B
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_1B"
msgid "Just call me 'They Who Saved My Life'."
msgstr "그냥 '내 목숨 구해준 자'라고 불러."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_2A
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_2A"
msgid "I <i>knew</> you'd remember me!"
msgstr "내가 <i>기억할 줄</> 알았지!"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_2B
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_2B"
msgid "That...doesn't <i>sound</> like me... You must be thinking of... you..."
msgstr "그건... 나답게 <i>들리진</> 않는데... 너 자신 얘기하는 거 아냐...?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.OPT_3"
msgid "Err, <i>anyway--</> {name.npc_scout}'s waiting above to take you back to camp."
msgstr "어, <i>아무튼--</> {name.npc_scout}이 위에서 기다리면서 널 캠프로 데려가려 해."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Och, yer an ugly lil' <#RED>{name.rot}</>, aren't ye? Well c'mon, then! I'll peel ye like a grape!\n"
" player:\n"
" Nonono, {name.npc_blacksmith}! It's me! The Hunter! From the {name.i_damselfly}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ... Who?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 오호, 못생긴 꼬마 <#RED>{name.rot}</> 하나 왔네? 좋아, 덤벼! 포도 껍질 벗기듯 벗겨주마!\n"
" player:\n"
" 아니아니, {name.npc_blacksmith}! 나야! 헌터! {name.i_damselfly}에서 왔잖아!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...누구?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK2
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Ah. I remember ye now.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Screamin' an' cryin' as our whirlybird took a nose dive."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" 아. 이제 기억났어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 우리 회전비행기가 급강하할 때 소리 지르고 울던 애."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Like a wee bairn, wailin' for yer ba-ba, ye were."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" 젖병 찾는 애기처럼 엉엉 울어댔지, 너."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK4
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_blacksmith.TALK4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hrm. Best pack me things.|...Done.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 흠. 짐부터 챙겨야겠군.|...다 챙겼다.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.OPT_1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.OPT_1"
msgid "That's terrible! Nice spatula, there. Any chance you're a {name.job_cook}?"
msgstr "그거 끔찍하네! 거기 주걱 멋진데. 혹시 {name.job_cook}야?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.OPT_2
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.OPT_2"
msgid "Wait--we don't have a {name.job_cook}. Would you want to join our camp?"
msgstr "잠깐--우리 {name.job_cook} 없거든. 우리 캠프에 합류할래?"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Woe is me! Woe Woe W-Oh! Is that a st-st-stranger I see?? \n"
" !scared\n"
" Shoot straight with me: y'ain't h-h-here ta steal my meagre belongin's and leave me fer dead, are ya?\n"
" player:\n"
" What? No, of course not. I'm a Hunter. I'm here searching for an Old Fox.   \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well c-c-count my lucky stars! The name's <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</>. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just a poor old gal, lost and freezin' her dern buns off out here, alone 'n' defenseless-like..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 아이고 내 팔자야! 아이고 아이고 아-어? 저거 나, 나, 낯선 사람인가?? \n"
" !scared\n"
" 솔직히 말해줘: 너 내 보잘것없는 짐 훔쳐가고 날 여기 버려두려는 거 아니지?\n"
" player:\n"
" 뭐? 아니, 당연히 아니지. 난 헌터야. 올드 폭스를 찾고 있어.   \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 이야, 오늘 운 좋은 날이네! 이름은 <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</>야. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그냥 불쌍한 늙은 여자지, 여기서 길 잃고 엉덩이 얼어붙기 직전인, 혼자에 무방비 상태..."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.TALK2
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Nice spat-u-what-now? \n"
" !shocked\n"
" M-my back scratcher? Er, I'm just kiddin'! O'course cookin' is what I use it for! All the time I do that. With this! 'Course!\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh, but I don't suppose an outfit like yours has any m-m-mouths what need feedin'. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" What a shame. I'm good too. At cookin'. Welp! Guess I'll just curl up and die, now..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 멋진 주걱이 뭐라고? \n"
" !shocked\n"
" 내, 내 등긁개? 어, 농담이야! 당연히 요리할 때 쓰지! 맨날! 이걸로! 당연하지!\n"
" !point\n"
" 아, 근데 네 복장 보아하니 먹여 살릴 입은 없겠지. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" 아쉽네. 나 요리 잘하는데. 그럼 뭐! 여기서 웅크리고 죽어야지..."

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.TALK3
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_cook.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Really? Truly? Oh, I'd cry happy tears if'n they wouldn't instantly freeze and turn into deadly projectiles! \n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>Hoo-whee!</> See you at camp, ya kind soul! Kindest in the land!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Oh, and I ain't seen no <#BLUE>Old Fox</> 'round here. Sorry!\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 진짜? 정말? 안 얼어붙어 흉기가 되지만 않으면 기뻐서 울 텐데! \n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>이야호!</> 캠프에서 보자, 착한 사람! 세상에서 제일 착해!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 아, 그리고 여기선 <#BLUE>올드 폭스</> 못 봤어. 미안!\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_refiner.ANSWER_CHICKENS
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_refiner.ANSWER_CHICKENS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" ...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ... <i>(sigh)</> You're right. <z 0.7>Dang it. Can't a gal just quiet quit anymore?</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Well, the Shutdown Panel is <i>in</> the lab, which is locked. You'll need a <#RED>Key</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Of course <#RED>Grimhollow</> smashed mine and fed each of the <#RED>Three Key Fragments</> to random <#RED>Frenzy Bosses</>, so...\n"
" flitt:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" If you're right--IF--then we'll just go fight <#RED>Frenzy Bosses</> until we find those <#RED>Key Fragments</>.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" HAH! Okay, kid! \"Just\" like taking candy from <i>super-violent</> babies that already ate the candy! He he he.\n"
" ...\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !laugh\n"
" You're serious! HAH! You guys are wild. Alright, I'm in. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Also, is this <#BLUE>{name.town}</> an anarcho-collectivist type situation or--y'know what? I'll figure it out.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" ...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ... <i>(한숨)</> 네 말이 맞아. <2>젠장. 요새는 그냥 조용히 그만두는 것도 어렵나?</3>\n"
" !think\n"
" 어디 보자, 셧다운 패널은 연구소 <0>안</4>에 있지. 연구소는 잠겨 있고. <#RED>열쇠</5>가 필요할 거야.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 당연하지만 <#RED></6> 녀석이 내 열쇠를 세 조각 내서는 <#RED>그 조각들</7>을 어떤 <#RED>광란 보스</8>들한테 먹여버렸어. 그러니까...\n"
" flitt:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 만약에, 정말 만약에 그 말이 맞다면, 그냥 <#RED>열쇠 조각</9>들을 찾을 때까지 <#RED>광란 보스</10>들을 잡으면 되겠네.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 하! 그래, 맞지! \"그냥\" 애기들한테서 사탕 뺏듯이 말이야. <i>엄청나게 난폭한</11> 애기 말야! 헤헤헤.\n"
" ...\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !laugh\n"
" 진심이구나! 하! 너네 완전 제멋대로구나. 좋아, 나도 같이 갈게. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그나저나, 이 <#BLUE>{name.town}</12>은 무슨 집산주의 아나키즘 공동체 같은 뭐 그런--아니, 됐다. 천천히 알아가야지.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_refiner.QUESTION_CHICKENS
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_refiner.QUESTION_CHICKENS"
msgid "Run?? Run where? A blast that size will destroy everything--even The Brinks!"
msgstr "도망?? 어디로 도망가? 저 정도 폭발이면 전부 날아가--브링크스까지!"

#: Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_refiner.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_intro_meeting_refiner.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Thanks for the rescue--aaand the weird looks?\n"
" player:\n"
" Um, we thought we were rescuing {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}. Who are you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>, <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</>. I work--<i>used</> to work for <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>. \n"
" flitt:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oh! Please! You must let us into his lab! We need my <#BLUE>Grandpa</> to save us--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" \"Save us\"?? Uh, have you felt those quakes lately? \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Well <#BLUE>Doc's</> got all his mining gear maxed out--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" He's trying trigger a <#KONJUR>SECOND ERUPTION</> of this stuff called <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>!\n"
" flitt:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wh-what?? No... He wouldn't... Y-you must be mistaken! \n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" I thought so too, so I stole his <#RED>Diary</>. <#RED>Take it.</> It's missing a few <#RED>Pages</> but it paints the picture.  \n"
" !scared\n"
" This'll be TRIPLE the size of the first eruption. I have to go find my dad and RUN. You better do the same."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" 구해줘서 고마워--그리고 그 이상한 눈빛은 뭐야?\n"
" player:\n"
" 음, 우린 {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}를 구하러 온 줄 알았는데. 넌 누구야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>, <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</>야. 난 <i>일했어</>, 아니 예전에 <#BLUE>박사 {name.flitt_lastname}</> 밑에서 일했어. \n"
" flitt:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" 아! 제발! 박사님 실험실에 들여보내 줘! 우리 <#BLUE>할아버지</>가 우릴 살려야 해--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" \"우릴 살려\"?? 어, 요즘 지진 느껴봤지? \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>박사님</>은 채굴 장비를 전부 최대치로 올려놨어--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 이 <#KONJUR>태고의 {name.konjur}</>라는 물질로 <#KONJUR>두 번째 대폭발</>을 일으키려 한다고!\n"
" flitt:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 뭐, 뭐라고?? 아니... 그럴 리가... 네가 잘못 본 거야! \n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" 나도 그렇게 생각해서 <#RED>일기</>를 훔쳤어. <#RED>받아.</> <#RED>페이지</> 몇 장 빠졌지만, 상황은 충분히 보여줘.  \n"
" !scared\n"
" 이건 첫 대폭발의 세 배 규모야. 난 아빠 찾아서 도망가야 해. 너희도 그래."

