#: Quest.dgn_sdmnt_blizzard_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_sdmnt_blizzard_scout,location_sedament_tundra_r2,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_sdmnt_blizzard_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_sdmnt_blizzard_scout,location_sedament_tundra_r2,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" W-welcome to <#BLUE>{name.sedament_tundra_r2}</>! I sure h-hope you're wearing your l-l-long underwear under that ar-ar-armour.\n"
" player:\n"
" Brr-r-r... This place wins the award for ch-ch-chilliest reception! \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Wh-what's that? I th-think my ears are fr-fr-frozen. The sn-sn-snowy w-winds here will <#RED>Freeze</> y-you solid if you stray too f-far from a heat source.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" L-lucky for you, there's a n-network of old <#RED>Braziers</> t-t-to keep workers w-w-warm back when this place was st-still an functional stone qu-quarry.\n"
" !point\n"
" Stick cl-cl-close to those, and you sh-should be cozy enough--th-though you might need to h-h-hack the ice off some to get them b-b-burning again.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" I'd b-better hurry back to the <#RED>Damselfly</> before my f-f-fingers get too numb to f-fly it! Stay warm, and find my Grandpa, Hunter!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.sedament_tundra_r2}</>에 오, 온 걸 환영해! 그 갑옷 안에 내, 내복 제대로 챙겨 입었길 바라.\n"
" player:\n"
" 부르르... 여긴 차, 차, 차가운 환영상 후보 1등이야! \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 뭐, 뭐라고? 귀가 어, 얼은 것 같아. 여기 눈바람은 열원에서 너무 멀어지면 너를 <#RED>얼려서</> 꼼짝 못 하게 해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 너, 너한텐 운 좋게도 예전 채석장 시절 작업자들 데우려고 쓰던 낡은 <#RED>화로</> 네트워크가 있어.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그 근처에 바, 바짝 붙어 다니면 따뜻할 거야--다만 얼음 깨서 다시 타오르게 해야 할 수도 있어.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" 나, 난 손가락이 너무 굳기 전에 <#RED>Damselfly</>로 돌아가야겠어! 몸 따뜻하게 하고, 우리 할아버지 찾아줘, 헌터!"

