#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.CRITICAL_HITS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.CRITICAL_HITS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>Critical Hits</> deal extra <#RED>Damage</> and appear in <#ATK_CRIT>Pink</>. They happen by random chance when you land an <#RED>Attack</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The likelihood of gettin' them is based on your <#RED>Crit Chance</>, which is affected by your Hunter <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> and gear.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Keep in mind, a <#RED>Critical Hit</> is different from a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>. Landin' <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> is under your direct control."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!point\n"
"<#RED>치명타</>는 두 배의 <#RED>피해</>를 주며 <#ATK_CRIT>분홍색</>으로 표시됩니다.<#RED>공격</>을 가할 때 무작위로 발생합니다.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"획득 가능성은 <#RED>치명타 확률</>에 따라 결정되며, 이는 헌터 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> 및 장비의 영향을 받습니다.\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"<#RED>치명타</>는 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>와 다르다는 점을 명심하세요.Landin' <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>은(는) 귀하의 직접적인 통제하에 있습니다."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.CRITICAL_HITS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.CRITICAL_HITS_BTN"
msgid "Critical Hits"
msgstr "치명타"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.CRITICAL_HITS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.CRITICAL_HITS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Critical Hits, again?"
msgstr "치명타, 한 번 더?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.FOCUS_HITS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.FOCUS_HITS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" This one's <i>important</i>-- each <#RED>Weapon Type's</> got conditions for extra-effective <#RED>Attacks</> called <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" It can't be overstated how much yer <#RED>Damage'll</> skyrocket if you can learn to do 'em consistently.\n"
" !point\n"
" So check your <#RED>Weapon's</> <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> conditions over at the <#RED>Weapon Racks</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You'll know you've performed one correctly if your <#RED>Damage</> numbers turn <#BLUE>Blue</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 이건 <i>중요해</i>. 각 <#RED>무기 유형</>마다 추가 효율 <#RED>공격</>인 <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> 발동 조건이 있어.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이걸 꾸준히 해내면 <#RED>피해가</> 얼마나 치솟는지 아무리 강조해도 모자라.\n"
" !point\n"
" 그러니 <#RED>무기 거치대</>에서 네 <#RED>무기</>의 <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> 조건을 확인해.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>피해</> 숫자가 <#BLUE>파란색</>으로 바뀌면 제대로 한 거야."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.FOCUS_HITS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.FOCUS_HITS_BTN"
msgid "{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}"
msgstr "{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.FOCUS_HITS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.FOCUS_HITS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}, again?"
msgstr "{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.HIT_STREAKS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.HIT_STREAKS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" If you can land multiple <#RED>Attacks</> in a row without receiving <#RED>Damage</> or taking too long between hits, you'll build something called <#RED>Hit Streak</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Lots of <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> interact with <#RED>Hit Streak</>, so it's worth learning how to rack up the hits if you wanna use them.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If y'find it hard to build or maintain <#RED>Hit Streak</>, you can give yourself a leg up by learning to <#RED>Dodge Cancel</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 연속해서 여러 <#RED>공격</>을 맞히고, <#RED>피해</>를 받지 않으면서 타격 간격도 너무 길지 않으면 <#RED>연속 히트</>가 쌓여.\n"
" !think\n"
" 많은 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>가 <#RED>연속 히트</>와 상호작용하니까, 그걸 쓰고 싶다면 히트 수 쌓는 법을 익혀 두는 게 좋아.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>연속 히트</> 유지가 어렵다면 <#RED>회피 캔슬</>을 익혀서 훨씬 수월하게 만들 수 있어."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.HIT_STREAKS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.HIT_STREAKS_BTN"
msgid "Hit Streaks"
msgstr "연속 히트"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.HIT_STREAKS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.COMBAT.HIT_STREAKS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Hit Streaks, again?"
msgstr "연속 히트, 다시?"

