#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>Dodging</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>) is one of the most crucial and fundamental tools in your arsenal, Hunter.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" To survive, you'll have to learn to prioritize <#RED>Dodging</> incoming <#RED>Attacks</> over trying to do <#RED>Damage</> yourself.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" After <#RED>Dodging</> an <#RED>Enemy's Attack</>, they'll usually be wide open for you to safely swing."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>회피</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>)는 네 전투 도구 중에서도 가장 중요하고 기본인 기술이야, 헌터.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 살아남으려면 직접 <#RED>피해</>를 넣으려는 것보다 들어오는 <#RED>공격</>을 <#RED>회피</>하는 걸 우선해야 해.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>적의 공격</>을 <#RED>회피</>하고 나면 보통 적은 크게 빈틈이 생겨서 안전하게 한 방 넣을 수 있어."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_BTN"
msgid "Dodging Basics"
msgstr "회피 기본"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Dodge Basics, again?"
msgstr "회피 기본, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_CANCEL
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_CANCEL"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Every <#RED>Attack</> you can perform's got a window of time where <#RED>Dodging</> will cancel its animation, but not its <#RED>Damage</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And although them animations is real pretty, cancelling them early allows you to <#RED>Attack</> again sooner, making it easier to build <#RED>Combos</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>Attacks</> all got different cancel windows though, so you'll have to practice to get a feel for <#RED>{name.concept_dodge} Cancelling</> your favourite moves."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 네가 할 수 있는 모든 <#RED>공격</>엔 <#RED>회피</>로 애니메이션을 끊을 수 있는 구간이 있어. 대신 <#RED>피해</>는 그대로 들어가.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 그리고 그 애니메이션이 아무리 멋져도, 일찍 끊으면 다음 <#RED>공격</>을 더 빨리 이어서 <#RED>콤보</> 쌓기가 쉬워져.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>공격</>마다 캔슬 타이밍이 다르니까, 좋아하는 기술의 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge} 캔슬</> 감을 익히려면 연습이 필요해."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_CANCEL_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_CANCEL_BTN"
msgid "Dodge Cancels"
msgstr "회피 캔슬"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_CANCEL_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.DODGE_CANCEL_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Dodge Cancels, again?"
msgstr "회피 캔슬, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.PERFECT_DODGE
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.PERFECT_DODGE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" When you <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>, there's tiiiny moment where you're immune to <i>all</i> <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" If you can precisely line up the moment an <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</> would hit you with that sliver of <#RED>Dodge</> invulnerability, you'll perform a <#RED>Perfect {name.concept_dodge}</>.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You'll know you've done it right if you leave a dust cloud behind.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Heck, some <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> are even triggered when you <#RED>Perfect {name.concept_dodge}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>하면 아주 찰나 동안 <i>모든</i> <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>에 면역이 돼.\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</>이 널 때릴 순간을 그 <#RED>회피</> 무적 타이밍에 정확히 맞추면 <#RED>완벽 {name.concept_dodge}</>가 발동해.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 성공하면 뒤에 먼지 구름이 남아서 바로 알 수 있어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 심지어 일부 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>는 <#RED>완벽 {name.concept_dodge}</>을 해야 발동하기도 해!"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.PERFECT_DODGE_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.PERFECT_DODGE_BTN"
msgid "Perfect {name_multiple.concept_dodge}"
msgstr "완벽 {name_multiple.concept_dodge}"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.PERFECT_DODGE_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.DEFENSE.PERFECT_DODGE_BTN_ALT"
