msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.LUCK_STAT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ah yeah, <#RED>Luck's</> an unusual stat. 'Affects a little bit of everything.\n"
" !point\n"
" It can boost yer chances of getting rarer <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>, getting extra loot from <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, double <#RED>Healing</>, or even <#RED>Reviving</> when you should get knocked out.\n"
" !think\n"
" Might even have other effects I don't know 'bout. {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 맞아, <#RED>행운</>은 좀 특이한 능력치야. 이것저것 다 조금씩 영향을 줘.\n"
" !point\n"
" 더 희귀한 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>를 얻을 확률을 올리거나, <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>에서 추가 전리품을 얻거나, <#RED>치유</>가 두 배가 되거나, 쓰러져야 할 상황에서 <#RED>부활</>하기도 해.\n"
" !think\n"
" 내가 모르는 다른 효과가 있을지도 몰라. {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.LUCK_STAT_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.LUCK_STAT_BTN"
msgid "The Luck Stat"
msgstr "행운 능력치"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.LUCK_STAT_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.LUCK_STAT_BTN_ALT"
msgid "The Luck Stat, again?"
msgstr "행운 능력치, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.POTIONS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.POTIONS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You can drink <#RED>Potions</> with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK> to restore a good chunk of yer <#RED>Health</>.\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> will make sure your <#RED>Potion</> bottle's full when you start a Hunt, but use it sparingly.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" It's better to master <#RED>Dodging</> than it is to count on refills. {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>포션</>은 <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>로 마실 수 있고, 그러면 <#RED>체력</>을 꽤 많이 회복해.\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>이 출정 시작할 때 네 <#RED>포션</> 병을 채워주긴 하지만, 아껴 써.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 보충에 기대기보다 <#RED>회피</>를 숙달하는 게 훨씬 낫다. {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.POTIONS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.POTIONS_BTN"
msgid "Potions"
msgstr "포션"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.POTIONS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.POTIONS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Potions, again?"
msgstr "포션, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.WEIGHT_SYSTEM
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.WEIGHT_SYSTEM"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Every piece of gear you equip has a <#RED>Weight</> value, which when added together creates your <#RED>Weight Class</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" If your gear total puts you in the <#RED>{name.light_weight} Class</>, you'll take more <#RED>Damage</>, be easier to <#RED>Knockback</>, and have a faster <#RED>Dodge</> with a short invulnerability window.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" If your gear puts you in the <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} Class</>, you'll take less <#RED>Damage</>, be harder to <#RED>Knockback</>, and have a slow <#RED>Dodge</> with a longer invulnerability window.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" The <#RED>{name.medium_weight} Class</> will give you a balanced mix of the two.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" None of the <#RED>Weight Classes</> are better or worse than the others-- it's up to you to find which style suits you best."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" 장착한 모든 장비에는 <#RED>무게</> 값이 있고, 이를 모두 합산하여 너의 <#RED>무게</>가 결정 돼.\n"
" !point\n"
" 장비 총합이 <#RED>{name.light_weight} 무게</>면 <#RED>피해</>를 더 받고, <#RED>넉백</>에 더 약해지며, 무적 시간이 짧은 빠른 <#RED>회피</>를 하게 돼.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 장비 총합이 <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} 무게</>면 <#RED>피해</>를 덜 받고, <#RED>넉백</>에 더 강해지며, 무적 시간이 긴 느린 <#RED>회피</>를 하게 돼.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name.medium_weight} 무게</>는 둘의 균형형이야.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>무게</>는 어느 쪽이 더 좋다 나쁘다 없으니, 너한테 맞는 스타일을 찾으면 돼."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.WEIGHT_SYSTEM_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.WEIGHT_SYSTEM_BTN"
msgid "Equipment Weight"
msgstr "장비 무게"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.WEIGHT_SYSTEM_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.EQUIPMENT.WEIGHT_SYSTEM_BTN_ALT"
