#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.FRENZIED_HUNTS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.FRENZIED_HUNTS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>Frenzied</> Hunts are tougher than regular Hunts, but you need them for progression-- they're the only way to get those precious <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Be mindful, though. <#RED>Reviving</> allies is free on regular Hunts, but on <#RED>Frenzied</> Hunts, it'll cost you some <#RED>Health</> to pick up a friend.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If you're worried, don't be. <#RED>Frenzies</> might be challenging, but you'll never be given access to one that's beyond your ability."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>광란</> 사냥은 일반 사냥보다 훨씬 어렵지만 진행에 꼭 필요해. 귀한 <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</>를 얻는 유일한 방법이거든.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 다만 주의해. 일반 사냥에선 동료 <#RED>부활</>이 무료지만, <#RED>광란</> 사냥에선 친구를 일으키려면 네 <#RED>체력</>이 조금 든다.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 걱정하진 마. <#RED>광란 사냥</>은 도전적이지만, 네 실력 밖인 건 절대 열리지 않아."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.FRENZIED_HUNTS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.FRENZIED_HUNTS_BTN"
msgid "Frenzied Hunts"
msgstr "광란 사냥"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.FRENZIED_HUNTS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.FRENZIED_HUNTS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Frenzied Hunts, again?"
msgstr "광란 사냥, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.POWER_DROPS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.POWER_DROPS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You can use the <#KONJUR>Power Crystals</> you find during a Hunt to manifest mighty abilities, increasing your power and survivability in the field.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" There are all sorts of different <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>, and many of them pair well together to become extra powerful. Get creative and try different combinations.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Your <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> always wear off by the time you get home, so there's no downside to experimenting."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 사냥 중에 찾은 <#KONJUR>파워 크리스탈</>을 써서 강력한 능력을 발현하면, 현장에서 화력과 생존력을 올릴 수 있어.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 종류가 다양한 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>가 있고, 서로 잘 맞물려 더 강해지는 조합도 많아. 창의적으로 여러 조합을 시험해 봐.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 네 <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>는 집에 돌아올 때쯤이면 항상 사라지니까, 실험해도 손해는 없어."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.POWER_DROPS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.POWER_DROPS_BTN"
msgid "{name.concept_relic} Crystals"
msgstr "{name.concept_relic} 크리스탈"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.POWER_DROPS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.POWER_DROPS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "{name.concept_relic} Crystals, again?"
msgstr "{name.concept_relic} 크리스탈, 다시?"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.REVIVE_MECHANICS
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.REVIVE_MECHANICS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" If one of yer fellow Hunters gets knocked out on a Hunt, you can get them back on their feet by approaching them and holding <p bind='Controls.Digital.ACTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You're vulnerable while you're reviving, and your friend will only come back with <#RED>33% Health</>... so watch yer backs.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If you're hunting in a <#RED>Frenzied</> area, you'll also lose some <#RED>Health</> as it transfers to your revived friend."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 사냥 중 동료 헌터가 쓰러지면, 가까이 가서 <p bind='Controls.Digital.ACTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>을 길게 눌러 다시 일으킬 수 있어.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 부활시키는 동안 넌 무방비고, 친구는 <#RED>33% H 체력</>으로만 돌아오니까 주변을 잘 봐.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>광란</> 지역에서 사냥 중이라면, 부활한 친구에게 체력이 넘어가면서 네 <#RED>체력</>도 일부 줄어."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.REVIVE_MECHANICS_BTN
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.REVIVE_MECHANICS_BTN"
msgid "Reviving Friends"
msgstr "동료 소생"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.REVIVE_MECHANICS_BTN_ALT
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.GENERAL.REVIVE_MECHANICS_BTN_ALT"
msgid "Revives, again?"
msgstr "소생, 또?"

