msgstr "일반 <#RED><z 0.7>(복습)</z></>"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_FOUR.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_FOUR.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter... you've completed all my lessons. Do you know how often a Hunter completes all my lessons?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Not often! You have officially graduated from my Hunter's class.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" This... this is... <i>(snrrff)</>\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_dojo_master}, are those <i>tears</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" No. Shut up. {name.dojo_cough} Class dismissed.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...<z 0.7>Just got a little... dust in my eye, is all...</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" 헌터... 내 수업을 전부 끝냈구나. 내 수업을 전부 끝내는 헌터가 얼마나 되는지 알아?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" 거의 없어! 넌 공식적으로 내 헌터 수업을 졸업했다.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" 이건... 이건... <i>(훌쩍)</>\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_dojo_master}, 그거 <i>눈물</>이야?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 아니야. 조용히 해. {name.dojo_cough} 수업 끝.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...<z 0.7>그냥... 눈에 먼지가 좀 들어간 것뿐이야...</>"

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_ONE.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_ONE.TALK"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know, it's nice to see a Hunter take an interest in their education.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here, have a little treat for completing your first lesson. On me, ghe-he-he."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !thinking\n"
" 헌터가 자기 교육에 관심 갖는 건 보기 좋네.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 자, 첫 수업 끝낸 기념으로 간식 하나 받아. 내가 쏜다, 게헤헤."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_THREE.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_THREE.TALK"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 'Ey, kid. {name.dojo_cough} Take this.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Consider it a gold star for yer studies."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 어이, 꼬마. {name.dojo_cough} 이거 받아.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 공부 열심히 한 금별이라고 생각해."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_TWO.TALK
msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_TWO.TALK"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That's what, three lessons you've done now? Yer rocketing up my ranking list, kid.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" And yes, I keep a mental ranking of all my students."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 이제 수업 세 개 끝낸 거지? 내 순위표에서 쭉쭉 올라가네, 꼬마.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" 그리고 맞아, 난 모든 학생 순위를 머릿속에 매겨 둬."

#: Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.WEAPONS.CANNON_BTN
