#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_END_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_END_1"
msgid "ARGH!! Fighting is useless, Hunter!"
msgstr "크악!! 저항해 봐야 소용없다, 사냥꾼!"

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_END_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_END_2"
msgid "Become one with US! BECOME ROTLESS!"
msgstr "우리와 하나가 되어라! 썩지 않는 존재가 되어라!"

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_INTRO_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_INTRO_1"
msgid "This Hunter has poisoned you against me, Flitt!"
msgstr "이 사냥꾼이 널 선동해 나를 적대하게 만들었구나, 플릿!"

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_INTRO_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_INTRO_2"
msgid "Don't you see? Primeval Teffra will fix you!"
msgstr "안 보이느냐? 태고의 테프라가 널 바로잡아 줄 것이다!"

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_INTRO_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE1_INTRO_3"
msgid "We will fix EVERYTHING!\n"
"STARTING WITH THIS HUNTER!"
msgstr "우리는 모든 걸 바로잡겠다!\n"
"이 사냥꾼부터 시작해서!"

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE2_END_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE2_END_1"
msgid "YOU REJECT OUR ROTLESS PERFECTION."
msgstr "너는 우리의 썩지 않는 완전함을 거부했다."

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE2_END_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE2_END_2"
msgid "BUT YOU CANNOT REJECT THE ERUPTION."
msgstr "하지만 대폭발은 거부할 수 없다."

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE3_END_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE3_END_1"
msgid "B-BUT... WE... CANNOT... ROT...??"
msgstr "하-하지만... 우리... 썩을 수... 없...어...??"

#: STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE3_END_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CINEMATICS.TEFFRAMECH_PHASE3_END_2"
msgid "NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!"
msgstr "안 돼에에에에에에에에에!!!"

