msgid "Gain <#RED>{max_health} Maximum Health</> at the start of each combat room. Lose <#RED>{health_loss} Maximum Health</> for every second you are in combat."
msgstr "각 전투 방 시작 시 <#RED>{max_health} 최대 체력</>을 얻는다. 전투 중에는 매초 <#RED>{health_loss} 최대 체력</>을 잃는다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.stop_loss.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.stop_loss.name"
msgid "Stop-Loss"
msgstr "손절선"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.desc"
msgid "Increase your <#RED>{name.concept_runspeed}</> by a percentage equal to {rarity_text}. \n\n"
"When your <#RED>Hit Streak</> ends, the bonus decays over time."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.concept_runspeed}</>가 {rarity_text}%만큼 증가합니다. \n\n"
"<#RED>연속 타격</>이 끝나면 보너스가 시간에 따라 감소한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.name"
msgid "Excitable"
msgstr "과열됨"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.rarity_text_COMMON
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.rarity_text_COMMON"
msgid "your current <#RED>Hit Streak</>"
msgstr "현재 <#RED>연속 타격</>"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.rarity_text_EPIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.rarity_text_EPIC"
msgid "<#RED>{name.powerdesc_double}</> your current <#RED>Hit Streak</>"
msgstr "현재 <#RED>연속 타격</>의 <#RED>{name.powerdesc_double}</>"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.rarity_text_LEGENDARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.streaking.rarity_text_LEGENDARY"
msgid "<#RED>{name.powerdesc_triple}</> your current <#RED>Hit Streak</>"
msgstr "현재 <#RED>연속 타격</>의 <#RED>{name.powerdesc_triple}</>"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.desc"
msgid "While you are at <#RED>more than half Health</>, your <#RED>Light Attack</> shoots <#RED>{rarity_text}</>."
msgstr "<#RED>체력이 절반 이상</>일 때, <#RED>약공격</>이 <#RED>{rarity_text}</>을(를) 발사한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.name"
msgid "High Ruler"
msgstr "하이 룰러"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.rarity_text_EPIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.rarity_text_EPIC"
msgid "1 Projectile"
msgstr "투사체 1개"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.rarity_text_LEGENDARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.sword_beam.rarity_text_LEGENDARY"
msgid "2 Projectiles"
msgstr "투사체 2개"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.thorns.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.thorns.desc"
msgid "When you're <#RED>Attacked</>, deal <#RED>{reflect} {name.concept_damage}</> back to the <#RED>Attacker</>."
msgstr "<#RED>피격</> 시, <#RED>공격자</>에게 <#RED>{reflect} {name.concept_damage}</>를 되돌려준다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.thorns.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.thorns.name"
msgid "Retaliation"
msgstr "반격"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.time_is_money.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.time_is_money.desc"
msgid "For the first <#RED>{time} seconds</> of every <#RED>{name.dungeon_room}</>, every <#RED>{name.rot}</> you <#RED>Kill</> drops <#KONJUR>{konjur} {name.i_konjur}</>."
msgstr "매 <#RED>{name.dungeon_room}</>의 처음 <#RED>{time}초</> 동안, <#RED>처치</>한 <#RED>{name.rot}</>마다 <#KONJUR>{konjur} {name.i_konjur}</>를 떨어뜨린다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.time_is_money.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.time_is_money.name"
msgid "Time Is Teffra"
msgstr "시간은 테프라"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.twist_the_knife.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.twist_the_knife.desc"
msgid "Your <#RED>Attacks</> against <#RED>Enemies</> with low <#RED>Health</> have a <#RED>+{bonus}% Critical Chance</>."
msgstr "체력이 낮은 <#RED>적</>을 <#RED>공격</>할 때 <#RED>치명타 확률</>이 <#RED>+{bonus}%</> 증가합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.twist_the_knife.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.twist_the_knife.name"
msgid "Twist of the Knife"
msgstr "칼끝 비틀기"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.undamaged_target.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.undamaged_target.desc"
msgid "Your <#RED>Attacks</> against <#RED>Enemies</> with full <#RED>Health</> deal <#RED>+{bonus}% {name.concept_damage}</>."
msgstr "<#RED>체력</>이 가득 찬 <#RED>적</>을 <#RED>공격</>할 때 <#RED>+{bonus}%의 {name.concept_damage}</>을 추가로 입힙니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.undamaged_target.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.undamaged_target.name"
msgid "Strong Start"
msgstr "강한 출발"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.vampirism_after_damaged.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.vampirism_after_damaged.desc"
msgid "After taking <#RED>Damage</>, <#RED>Heal</> for <#RED>{heal}%</> of the damage done by your next <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</>.\n\n"
"Cannot heal more than the amount of damage taken."
msgstr "<#RED>피해</>를 받은 뒤, 다음 <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</>이 가한 피해의 <#RED>{heal}%</>만큼 <#RED>회복</>한다.\n\n"
"회복량은 받은 피해를 초과할 수 없다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.vampirism_after_damaged.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.vampirism_after_damaged.name"
msgid "Hunter's Rally"
msgstr "사냥꾼의 집결"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.volatile_weaponry.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.volatile_weaponry.desc"
msgid "Every <#RED>{count} Hit Streak</>, cause an explosion in an area around the target."
msgstr "<#RED>{count} 연속 타격</>마다 대상 주변 범위에 폭발을 일으킨다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.volatile_weaponry.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.volatile_weaponry.name"
msgid "Volatile Weaponry"
msgstr "불안정한 무장"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.weighted_weaponry.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.weighted_weaponry.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Critical Hits</> increase damage by <#RED>+{percent}%</>."
msgstr "<#RED>치명타</> 시 피해량이 <#RED>+{percent}%</> 증가한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.weighted_weaponry.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.weighted_weaponry.name"
msgid "Weighted Weaponry"
msgstr "중량 무장"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.wrecking_ball.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.wrecking_ball.desc"
msgid "Multiply your <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> by your total <#RED>{name.concept_runspeed} {name.powerdesc_modifier}</>."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>수치에 총 <#RED>{name.concept_runspeed} {name.powerdesc_modifier}</>를 곱하여 적용합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.wrecking_ball.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.wrecking_ball.name"
msgid "Wrecking Ball"
msgstr "레킹 볼"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.bubbling_potion.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.bubbling_potion.desc"
msgid "Immediately <#RED>Heal</> for <#RED>{heal} Health</>."
msgstr "즉시 <#RED>{heal} 체력</>을 <#RED>회복</>한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.bubbling_potion.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.bubbling_potion.name"
msgid "Bubbling Brew"
msgstr "보글 영약"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.misting_potion.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.misting_potion.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Heal</> for <#RED>{heal} Health</> every <#RED>{tick_time}</> seconds until you've been healed <#RED>{num_heals}</> times."
msgstr "<#RED>{tick_time}</>초마다 <#RED>{heal} 체력</>을 <#RED>회복</>하며, 총 <#RED>{num_heals}</>만큼회 회복하면 종료된다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.misting_potion.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.misting_potion.name"
msgid "Misting Mixture"
msgstr "미스트 혼합물"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.soothing_potion.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.soothing_potion.desc"
msgid "Immediately <#RED>Heal</> for <#RED>{heal} Health</>."
msgstr "즉시 <#RED>{heal} 체력</>을 <#RED>회복</>한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.soothing_potion.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.POTION_POWER.soothing_potion.name"
msgid "Soothing Spirits"
msgstr "진정의 영약"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.acid_on_dodge.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.acid_on_dodge.desc"
msgid "[TEMP]When you <#RED>Dodge</>, leave behind a trail of <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</>."
msgstr "[TEMP]When you <#RED>Dodge</>, leave behind a trail of <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</>."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.acid_on_dodge.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.acid_on_dodge.name"
msgid "[TEMP] Seed: {name.concept_toxic} On Dodge"
msgstr "[TEMP] Seed: {name.concept_toxic} On Dodge"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded.desc"
msgid "[TEMP] It... does some stuff!"
msgstr "[TEMP] It... does some stuff!"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded.name"
msgid "[TEMP] Seeded"
msgstr "[TEMP] Seeded"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_heavy_attack.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_heavy_attack.desc"
msgid "[TEMP]Your <#RED>Heavy Attack</> applies <#RED>Seed</> in a large radius."
msgstr "[TEMP]Your <#RED>Heavy Attack</> applies <#RED>Seed</> in a large radius."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_heavy_attack.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_heavy_attack.name"
msgid "[TEMP] Seed: Heavy Attack"
msgstr "[TEMP] Seed: Heavy Attack"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_light_attack.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_light_attack.desc"
msgid "[TEMP]Your <#RED>Light Attack</> applies <#RED>Seed</>."
msgstr "[TEMP]Your <#RED>Light Attack</> applies <#RED>Seed</>."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_light_attack.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SEED.seeded_on_light_attack.name"
msgid "[TEMP] Seed: Light Attack"
msgstr "[TEMP] Seed: Light Attack"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield.desc"
msgid "When you have <#BLUE>4 Shield Segments</>, any <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> taken is reduced to <#RED>{damage}</>, then removes all <#BLUE>Segments</>."
msgstr "<#BLUE>방패 분절 4개</>가 있을 때, 받는 모든 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>은 <#RED>{damage}</>(으)로 감소하고 <#BLUE>분절</>이 모두 사라진다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield.name"
msgid "Shield Segment"
msgstr "방패 분절"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_bonus_damage_on_break.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_bonus_damage_on_break.desc"
msgid "When your <#BLUE>Shield</> breaks, deal an extra <#RED>+{percent}% {name.concept_damage}</> for <#RED>{time}</> seconds."
msgstr "<#BLUE>방패</>가 깨지면 <#RED>{time}</>초 동안 <#RED>+{percent}% {name.concept_damage}</>를 추가로 가한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_bonus_damage_on_break.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_bonus_damage_on_break.name"
msgid "Plan C"
msgstr "플랜 C"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge.desc"
msgid "When you <#RED>Perfect Dodge</>, gain <#BLUE>{shield} Shield Segments</>."
msgstr "<#RED>완벽 회피</> 시 <#BLUE>{shield} 방패 분절</>을 얻는다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge.name"
msgid "Tuck and Roll"
msgstr "구르며 회피"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge_knockback.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge_knockback.desc"
msgid "When you have <#BLUE>Shield</>, your <#RED>Dodge</> becomes an <#RED>Attack</> that deals <#RED>{damage_mod}% Weapon {name.concept_damage}</>."
msgstr "<#BLUE>방패</>가 있으면 <#RED>회피</>가 <#RED>{damage_mod}% W무기 {name.concept_damage}</>를 가하는 <#RED>공격</>으로 바뀐다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge_knockback.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_dodge_knockback.name"
msgid "Inertia"
msgstr "관성"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_explosion_on_break.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_explosion_on_break.desc"
msgid "When your <#BLUE>Shield</> breaks, deal <#RED>{damage_mult}x your {name.concept_weapon_damage}</> to nearby <#RED>Enemies</>."
msgstr "<#BLUE>방패</>가 깨지면 주변 <#RED>적</>에게 <#RED>{damage_mult}x 자신의 {name.concept_weapon_damage}</>을 가한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_explosion_on_break.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_explosion_on_break.name"
msgid "Shield Detonation"
msgstr "방패 폭발"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_focus_kill.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_focus_kill.desc"
msgid "When you <#RED>Kill</> an <#RED>Enemy</> with a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>, gain <#BLUE>{shield} Shield Segment</>."
msgstr "<#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>으로 <#RED>적</>을 <#RED>처치</>하면 <#BLUE>{shield} 방패 분절</>을 얻는다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_focus_kill.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_focus_kill.name"
msgid "Resolute"
msgstr "결연함"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heal_on_surplus.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heal_on_surplus.desc"
msgid "When you gain a <#RED>Shield Segment</> with an already full <#RED>Shield</>, <#RED>Heal</> for <#RED>{heal_per_stack}</>."
msgstr "이미 <#RED>방패</>가 가득 찬 상태에서 <#RED>방패 분절</>을 얻으면 <#RED>{heal_per_stack}</>만큼 <#RED>회복</>한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heal_on_surplus.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heal_on_surplus.name"
msgid "Healing Shield"
msgstr "치유의 방패"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack.desc"
msgid "When your <#RED>Heavy Attacks</> hit <#RED>{targets_required} or more Targets</> at once, gain <#BLUE>{shield} Shield Segment</>."
msgstr "<#RED>강공격</>이 한 번에 <#RED>{targets_required}개 이상의 대상</>을 맞히면 <#BLUE>{shield} 방패 분절</>을 얻는다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack.name"
msgid "Heavy Defense"
msgstr "중량 방어"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack_bonus_damage.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack_bonus_damage.desc"
msgid "When you have <#BLUE>Shield</>, your <#RED>Heavy Attacks</> deal a bonus <#RED>+{percent}% {name.concept_damage}</>."
msgstr "<#BLUE>방패</>가 있으면 <#RED>강공격</>이 <#RED>+{percent}% {name.concept_damage}</>를 추가로 가한다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack_bonus_damage.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_heavy_attack_bonus_damage.name"
msgid "Heavy Hitter"
msgstr "강타자"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_hit_streak.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_hit_streak.desc"
msgid "Every <#RED>{hitstreak} Hit Streak</>, gain <#BLUE>{shield} Shield Segment</>."
msgstr "<#RED>{hitstreak} 연속 타격</>마다 <#BLUE>{shield} 방패 분절</>을 얻는다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_hit_streak.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_hit_streak.name"
msgid "The Best Defense"
msgstr "최선의 방어"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_knockback_on_break.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_knockback_on_break.desc"
msgid "When your <#BLUE>Shield</> breaks, all <#RED>Enemies</> in a <#RED>{radius}-Unit Radius</> radius get <#RED>Knocked Down</>."
msgstr "<#BLUE>방패</>가 깨지면 반경 <#RED>{radius}-유닛</> 내의 <#RED>적</>이 모두 <#RED>넘어짐</> 상태가 된다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_knockback_on_break.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_knockback_on_break.name"
msgid "Aftershock"
msgstr "여진"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_bonus.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_bonus.desc"
msgid "Gain <#RED>+{speed}% {name.concept_runspeed}</> for every <#BLUE>Shield Segment</> you have."
msgstr "보유한 <#BLUE>Shield Segment</>마다 <#RED>+{speed}% {name.concept_runspeed}</>을 얻습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_bonus.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_bonus.name"
msgid "Resistance Training"
msgstr "저항 훈련"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_on_break.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_on_break.desc"
msgid "When your <#BLUE>Shield</> breaks, gain <#RED>+{percent}% {name.concept_runspeed}</> for <#RED>{time}</> seconds."
msgstr "<#BLUE>Shield</>가 깨지면 <#RED>{time}</>초 동안 <#RED>+{percent}% {name.concept_runspeed}</>을 얻습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_on_break.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_move_speed_on_break.name"
msgid "Plan Flee"
msgstr "도망 계획"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_reduced_damage_on_break.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_reduced_damage_on_break.desc"
msgid "When your <#BLUE>Shield</> breaks, take <#RED>{percent}%</> reduced <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> for <#RED>{time}</> seconds."
msgstr "<#BLUE>Shield</>가 깨지면 <#RED>{time}</>초 동안 받는 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>이 <#RED>{percent}%</> 감소합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_reduced_damage_on_break.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_reduced_damage_on_break.name"
msgid "Plan B"
msgstr "플랜 B"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_steadfast.desc_EPIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_steadfast.desc_EPIC"
msgid "When you have <#BLUE>Shield</>, your <#RED>Attacks</> can no longer be interrupted."
msgstr "<#BLUE>Shield</>가 있으면 <#RED>Attacks</>이 더 이상 끊기지 않습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_steadfast.desc_LEGENDARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_steadfast.desc_LEGENDARY"
msgid "Your <#RED>Attacks</> can no longer be interrupted."
msgstr "<#RED>공격</>시 동작이 끊기지 않는다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_steadfast.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_steadfast.name"
msgid "Adamantine"
msgstr "금강불괴"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.desc"
msgid "When your <#BLUE>Shield</> breaks, {rarity_text} of the <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> it prevented."
msgstr "<#BLUE>Shield</>가 깨지면, 막아낸 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>의 {rarity_text}만큼 회복합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.name"
msgid "Inequivalent Exchange"
msgstr "불균등 교환"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.rarity_text_EPIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.rarity_text_EPIC"
msgid "<#RED>Heal</> for half"
msgstr "<#RED>회복</>량 절반"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.rarity_text_LEGENDARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_to_health.rarity_text_LEGENDARY"
msgid "<#RED>Heal</> for all"
msgstr "<#RED>전부 회복</>"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_when_hurt.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_when_hurt.desc"
msgid "When you take <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>, gain <#BLUE>{shield} Shield Segment</>."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>을 받으면 <#BLUE>{shield} Shield Segment</>를 얻습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_when_hurt.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SHIELD.shield_when_hurt.name"
msgid "Automated Defenses"
msgstr "자동 방어"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bananapeel.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bananapeel.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Heals</> for <#RED>{heal} Health</> when eaten.\n\n"
"Leaves behind a <#RED>Banana Peel</> that inflicts <#RED>Knock Down</> on any target that steps on it.\n\n"
"Regain <#RED>1 Banana</> for every <#RED>{damage_til_new_banana} {name.concept_damage}</> dealt."
msgstr "먹으면 <#RED>회복</>하여 <#RED>{heal} Health</>를 회복합니다.\n\n"
"밟은 대상에게 <#RED>Knock Down</>을 부여하는 <#RED>Banana Peel</>을 남깁니다.\n\n"
"가한 <#RED>{damage_til_new_banana} {name.concept_damage}</>마다 <#RED>1 Banana</>를 회복합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bananapeel.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bananapeel.name"
msgid "Banana Peel"
msgstr "바나나 껍질"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_eggzy.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_eggzy.desc"
msgid "Imbue your weapon with power, causing your next hit to explode.\n\n"
"Press <#RED>Skill</> during a <#RED>Heavy Attack</> to queue an explosion on Hit."
msgstr "무기에 힘을 불어넣어 다음 타격을 폭발시킵니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>Heavy Attack</> 중 <#RED>Skill</>을 누르면 적중 시 폭발이 예약됩니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_eggzy.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_eggzy.name"
msgid "Eggsplosion"
msgstr "알폭발"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_grimhollow.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_grimhollow.desc"
msgid "Launch a continuous volley of <#RED>Mortar Shells</> at targets infront of you.\n\n"
"Take <#RED>Reduced Damage</> from the front while held."
msgstr "정면의 대상에게 <#RED>Mortar Shells</>를 연속 발사합니다.\n\n"
"유지하는 동안 전방에서 받는 <#RED>피해 감소</> 효과를 얻습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_grimhollow.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_grimhollow.name"
msgid "Bastion Volley"
msgstr "요새 연발"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_megatreemon.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_megatreemon.desc"
msgid "Summon <#RED>{name.megatreemon}'s Roots</>.\n\n"
"Press <#RED>Skill</> during a <#RED>Heavy Attack</> to queue a summon on Hit."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.megatreemon}'s Roots</>를 소환합니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>Heavy Attack</> 중 <#RED>Skill</>을 누르면 적중 시 소환이 예약됩니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_megatreemon.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_megatreemon.name"
msgid "Mother of Methuselah"
msgstr "메투셀라의 어머니"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_owlitzer.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_owlitzer.desc"
msgid "Summon <#RED>{name.owlitzer}'s Wings</>."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.owlitzer}'s Wings</>를 소환합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_owlitzer.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_owlitzer.name"
msgid "Keeper of the Moon"
msgstr "달의 수호자"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_sedament.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_sedament.desc"
msgid "You find yourself being followed by a <#RED>Crow</>.\n\n"
"Press <#RED>Skill</> to send your <#RED>Crow</> into a <#RED>Shiny Frenzy</>."
msgstr "<#RED>Crow</> 한 마리가 당신을 따라다닙니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>Skill</>을 눌러 <#RED>Crow</>를 <#RED>Shiny Frenzy</> 상태로 보냅니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_sedament.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_sedament.name"
msgid "Holder of Shinies"
msgstr "반짝이의 주인"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_thatcher.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_thatcher.desc"
msgid "While active, your <#RED>Attacks</> coat <#RED>Targets</> in <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</>, which deals <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> and maintains <#RED>Hit Streaks</>."
msgstr "활성화 중, <#RED>공격</> 시 <#RED>대상</>에게 <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</>를 부여합니다. 해당 효과는 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>를 입히고 <#RED>히트스택</>을 유지합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_thatcher.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.boss_thatcher.name"
msgid "Voice of the Myriad"
msgstr "무수의 목소리"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_fan.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_fan.desc"
msgid "Toss <#RED>{name.gnarlic} arrows</> in all directions.\n\n"
"<#RED>Kill</> {kills_to_refill} enemy to recharge, up to a maximum of <#RED>{max_stocks} Stocks</>."
msgstr "모든 방향으로 <#RED>{name.gnarlic} arrows</>를 던집니다.\n\n"
"적 {kills_to_refill}명을 <#RED>처치</>하면 충전되며, 최대 <#RED>{max_stocks} Stocks</>까지 보유합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_fan.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_fan.name"
msgid "Fan of {name_multiple.gnarlic}"
msgstr "{name_multiple.gnarlic}의 난사"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_hypershot.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_hypershot.desc"
msgid "Allow rapid-fire of <#RED>Light Attacks</> for the next <#RED>{seconds_active} seconds</>.\n\n"
"<z 0.8><i>Cooldown: <#RED>{cd}</> seconds</i></z>"
msgstr "다음 <#RED>{seconds_active}초</> 동안 <#RED>Light Attacks</>를 연사할 수 있습니다.\n\n"
"<z 0.8><i>재사용 대기시간: <#RED>{cd}</>초</i></z>"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_hypershot.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_hypershot.name"
msgid "Hypershot"
msgstr "하이퍼샷"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_melee.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_melee.desc"
msgid "Swing your <#RED>{name.weapon_bow}</> as a close-range attack."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_bow}</>을 휘둘러 근거리 공격을 합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_melee.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_melee.name"
msgid "Thwack"
msgstr "퍽치기"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_acid.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_acid.desc"
msgid "Your next <#RED>Heavy Attack</> leaves an <#RED>{name.concept_toxic} Pool</> when hitting the ground."
msgstr "다음 <#RED>강공격</>이 지면에 맞으면 <#RED>{name.concept_toxic} 웅덩이</>를 남깁니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_acid.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_acid.name"
msgid "{name.concept_toxic} Dip"
msgstr "{name.concept_toxic} 딥"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_cold.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_cold.desc"
msgid "Your next <#RED>Heavy Attack</> leaves an <#RED>Ice Cloud</> when hitting the ground."
msgstr "다음 <#RED>강공격</>이 지면에 맞으면 <#RED>빙결 안개</>를 남깁니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_cold.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_cold.name"
msgid "Cold Plunge"
msgstr "콜드 플런지"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_explode.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_explode.desc"
msgid "[TEMP] bow_primearrow_explode desc"
msgstr "[TEMP] bow_primearrow_explode desc"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_explode.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.bow_primearrow_explode.name"
msgid "[TEMP] bow_primearrow_explode"
msgstr "[TEMP] bow_primearrow_explode"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.buffnextattack.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.buffnextattack.desc"
msgid "Pound your fists together to gain <#RED>+{percent_per_trigger}% Critical Chance</> until your next <#RED>Critical Hit</>."
msgstr "주먹을 맞부딪히면 다음 <#RED>치명타</>가 적중할 때까지 <#RED>치명타 확률이 +{percent_per_trigger}%</> 증가합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.buffnextattack.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.buffnextattack.name"
msgid "Fist Pound"
msgstr "주먹 강타"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_aim.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_aim.desc"
msgid "Hold to charge a <#RED>Big Blast</> that deals major <#RED>Damage</>. Press <#RED>Skill</> again upon landing to chain multiple shots together."
msgstr "유지해 강력한 <#RED>Big Blast</>를 충전해 큰 <#RED>Damage</>를 줍니다. 착지 후 <#RED>Skill</>을 다시 눌러 연속 사격할 수 있습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_aim.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_aim.name"
msgid "Big Blast"
msgstr "빅 블라스트"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_butt.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_butt.desc"
msgid "Hit an enemy with the butt of your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>.\n\n"
"On hit, gain <#RED>1 {name.cannon_ammo}</>."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> 개머리판으로 적을 타격합니다.\n\n"
"적중 시 <#RED>1 {name.cannon_ammo}</>를 얻습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_butt.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_butt.name"
msgid "Battering Ram"
msgstr "공성추"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_proximitymine.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_proximitymine.desc"
msgid "Plant one of your <#RED>{name_multiple.cannon_ammo}</> as a <#RED>Mine</> which blows up near enemies. Perform a <#RED>Shockwave</> to explode all <#RED>Mines</>."
msgstr "보유한 <#RED>{name_multiple.cannon_ammo}</> 중 하나를 <#RED>Mine</>으로 설치해 적이 가까이 오면 폭발시킵니다. <#RED>Shockwave</>를 사용하면 모든 <#RED>Mines</>가 폭발합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_proximitymine.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_proximitymine.name"
msgid "Proximity Mines"
msgstr "근접 지뢰"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_singlereload.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_singlereload.desc"
msgid "Reload <#RED>1 {name.cannon_ammo}</>."
msgstr "<#RED>1 {name.cannon_ammo}</>를 재장전합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_singlereload.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.cannon_singlereload.name"
msgid "Reload One"
msgstr "1발 재장전"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_explodingheavy.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_explodingheavy.desc"
msgid "Overcharge your <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> with energy which explodes the next time your <#RED>Heavy Attack</> hits something."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</>를 에너지로 과충전해 다음 <#RED>Heavy Attack</> 적중 시 폭발시킵니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_explodingheavy.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_explodingheavy.name"
msgid "Unstable Equilibrium"
msgstr "불안정 평형"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_reflectinglights.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_reflectinglights.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Light Attacks</> during <#RED>Hypershot</> deal Bonus <#RED>Damage</>."
msgstr "<#RED>하이퍼샷</> 중 <#RED>약공격</>이 추가 <#RED>피해</>를 준다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_reflectinglights.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_reflectinglights.name"
msgid "[TEMP] hammer_reflectinglights"
msgstr "[TEMP] hammer_reflectinglights"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_reflectinglights.variables.hypershot_damage_bonus
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_reflectinglights.variables.hypershot_damage_bonus"
msgid "Damage Bonus"
msgstr "추가 피해"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_thump.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_thump.desc"
msgid "Pound the head of your <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> into the ground, causing <#RED>Knockback</> to any nearby <#RED>Enemies</>.\n\n"
"Hold <#RED>Skill</> to charge."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> 머리를 지면에 내리쳐 주변 <#RED>Enemies</>를 <#RED>Knockback</>시킵니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>Skill</>을 길게 눌러 충전합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_thump.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_thump.name"
msgid "Order in the Court"
msgstr "법정 정리"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_totem.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_totem.desc"
msgid "Sacrifice <#RED>{healthtocreate} Health</> to summon a <#RED>Hazard Idol</>.\n\n"
"<#RED>Everything</> in a large radius of the <#RED>Idol</> deals <#RED>+{bonusdamagepercent}% {name.concept_damage}</>.\n\n"
"The Idol <#RED>Heals</> its destroyer for <#RED>{healthtocreate} Health</>."
msgstr "<#RED>{healthtocreate} Health</>를 희생해 <#RED>Hazard Idol</>을 소환합니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>Idol</>의 넓은 범위 안에 있는 <#RED>Everything</>이 <#RED>+{bonusdamagepercent}% {name.concept_damage}</>을 가합니다.\n\n"
"Idol을 파괴한 대상은 <#RED>Heals</>로 <#RED>{healthtocreate} Health</>를 회복합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_totem.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.hammer_totem.name"
msgid "Hazard Idol"
msgstr "위험 우상"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_bonejaw.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_bonejaw.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Hold</> to stampede, then release to do a rising <#RED>Headbutt</>."
msgstr "<#RED>Hold</>로 돌진하고, 떼면 솟구치는 <#RED>Headbutt</>를 사용합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_bonejaw.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_bonejaw.name"
msgid "{name.bonejaw}'s Charge"
msgstr "{name.bonejaw}의 돌진"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_crystroll.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_crystroll.desc"
msgid "Shoot an <#RED>Ice Chunk</>, or <#RED>Hold</> to shoot all stocked <#RED>Ice Chunks</>.\n\n"
"Regain <#RED>1 Stock</> every <#RED>{hitstreak} Hit Streak</>, up to a maximum of <#RED>3 Stocks</>."
msgstr "<#RED>Ice Chunk</>를 발사하거나, <#RED>Hold</>하여 저장한 <#RED>Ice Chunks</>를 모두 발사합니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>{hitstreak} Hit Streak</>마다 <#RED>1 Stock</>를 회복하며, 최대 <#RED>3 Stocks</>까지 보유합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_crystroll.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_crystroll.name"
msgid "{name.crystroll}'s Ice Puke"
msgstr "{name.crystroll}의 얼음 토사"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_embison.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_embison.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Hold</> to charge, then release to do an <#RED>Invincible</> turn into a punch, releasing all stored energy."
msgstr "<#RED>Hold</>로 충전한 뒤 떼면 <#RED>Invincible</> 회전 후 펀치를 날려 저장한 에너지를 모두 방출합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_embison.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_embison.name"
msgid "{name.embison}'s Turn Around Punch"
msgstr "{name.embison}의 턴어라운드 펀치"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_floracrane.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_floracrane.desc"
msgid "Leap into the air and divebomb the ground in front of you.\n\n"
"Hold to charge, turning your dive into a <#BLUE>Focus Hit</>."
msgstr "공중으로 뛰어올라 전방 지면으로 급강하합니다.\n\n"
"길게 눌러 충전하면 급강하가 <#BLUE>Focus Hit</>으로 강화됩니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_floracrane.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_floracrane.name"
msgid "{name.floracrane}'s Divebeak"
msgstr "{name.floracrane}의 다이브비크"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_gourdo.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_gourdo.desc"
msgid "Channel your inner seedling, restoring <#RED>{heal} Health</> to yourself and all <#RED>Allies</> within a medium radius.\n\n"
"Regain <#RED>1 Stock</> for every <#RED>{damage_til_new_stock} {name.concept_damage}</> dealt, up to a maximum of <#RED>3 Stocks</>."
msgstr "내면의 새싹을 끌어내 자신과 중간 범위 내 모든 <#RED>Allies</>의 체력을 <#RED>{heal} Health</> 회복합니다.\n\n"
"가한 <#RED>{damage_til_new_stock} {name.concept_damage}</>마다 <#RED>1 Stock</>를 회복하며, 최대 <#RED>3 Stocks</>까지 보유합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_gourdo.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_gourdo.name"
msgid "{name.gourdo}'s Community Garden"
msgstr "{name.gourdo}의 공동 정원"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_groak.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_groak.desc"
msgid "<#RED>Vacuum</> all <#RED>Enemies</> standing in front of you in towards yourself, dealing many tiny hits."
msgstr "정면의 <#RED>Enemies</>를 <#RED>Vacuum</>으로 자신 쪽으로 끌어당겨 작은 타격을 여러 번 줍니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_groak.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_groak.name"
msgid "Grody {name.groak} Gulp"
msgstr "징그러운 {name.groak} 꿀꺽"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_yammo.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_yammo.desc"
msgid "Hold to charge a <#BLUE>Focus Attack</>. Any <#RED>Damage</> received while charging is added to the total <#RED>Damage</> of the attack.\n\n"
"On hit, <#RED>Heal</> back all absorbed <#RED>Damage</>."
msgstr "길게 눌러 <#BLUE>집중 공격</>을 충전합니다. 충전 중 받은 <#RED>피해</>는 공격의 총 <#RED>피해</>에 더해집니다.\n\n"
"적중 시 흡수한 <#RED>피해</>를 전부 <#RED>회복</>합니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_yammo.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.miniboss_yammo.name"
msgid "Big {name.yammo} Slammo"
msgstr "거대 {name.yammo} 슬래모"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.parry.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.parry.desc"
msgid "Nullify an incoming <#RED>Attack</> to gain a brief window of <#RED>100% Critical Chance</>."
msgstr "들어오는 <#RED>공격k</>을 무효화하면 잠시 동안 <#RED>100% 치명타 확률</>을 얻습니다."

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.parry.name
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.parry.name"
msgid "Trickster's Gambit"
msgstr "트릭스터의 승부수"

#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.polearm_extend.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.SKILL.polearm_extend.desc"
msgid "Extend the length of your <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> to attack very far away.\n\n"
"Hold <#RED>Skill</> to charge."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> 길이를 늘려 아주 먼 거리까지 공격합니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>기술</>을 길게 눌러 충전합니다."

