"우리가 널 찢어버린다!"

#: STRINGS.MONSTERTRANSLATOR.HUMAN.thatcher.THATCHER_PHASE_TRANSITION_1_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.MONSTERTRANSLATOR.HUMAN.thatcher.THATCHER_PHASE_TRANSITION_1_2"
msgid "You are bad.\n"
"Nasty to the BONE."
msgstr "넌 나빠.\n"
"뼛속까지 고약해."

#: STRINGS.MONSTERTRANSLATOR.HUMAN.thatcher.THATCHER_PHASE_TRANSITION_1_3
