#: STRINGS.UI.MECHANIC_TUTORIALS.BOSS_WEAPON_CRAFTING.DESC
msgctxt "STRINGS.UI.MECHANIC_TUTORIALS.BOSS_WEAPON_CRAFTING.DESC"
msgid "{name.c_npc_refiner}'s breakthrough allows {name.c_npc_blacksmith} to craft <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_crystal}</>.\n\n"
"On a <#RED>{name.run_ascension_plus}</>, your equipped {name_multiple.weapon_crystal} will absorb the essence of the defeated <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</>.\n\n"
"If you fail any run while holding a {name.weapon_crystal}, it will <#RED>Break</> and need to be repaired by {name.c_npc_blacksmith}.\n"
msgstr "{name.c_npc_refiner}의 돌파로 {name.c_npc_blacksmith}이 <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_crystal}</> 제작을 할 수 있게 되었습니다.\n\n"
"<#RED>{name.run_ascension_plus}</>에서 처치한 <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</>의 정수를, 장착한 {name_multiple.weapon_crystal}가 흡수합니다.\n\n"
"{name.weapon_crystal}을 들고 있는 상태로 출격에 실패하면 <#RED>파손</>되며, {name.c_npc_blacksmith}로 수리해야 합니다.\n"

