msgid "Find your <#RED>meals</> at the start of a {name.run} in your <#BLUE>{name.i_lunchbox}</> next to the {name.i_damselfly}.\n\n"
"Each {name.run}, you can eat <#RED>one meal</> to gain a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</>."
msgstr "{name.run} 시작 시 {name.i_damselfly} 옆 <#BLUE>{name.i_lunchbox}</>에서 <#RED>요리</>를 확인할 수 있습니다.\n\n"
