"{name_multiple.konjur_heart_shard} are used to increase your Hunter's Power.\n\n"
"You can view each {name.run}'s challenges in {name.tutorial_playerstatus}."
msgstr "<#RED>{name.concept_talent_tree}</>를 진행해 <#RED>{name.i_konjur_heart_shard}</>을 획득했습니다!\n\n"
"{name_multiple.konjur_heart_shard}은 헌터의 전투력을 높이는 데 사용됩니다.\n\n"
