#: STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.BOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.BOW"
msgid "A long-range weapon that rewards positioning and timing.\n\n"
"All <#BLUE>Focus Hits</> pierce through enemies, but piercing <#RED>Light Attacks</> do less damage per pierce."
msgstr "포지셔닝과 타이밍이 중요한 장거리 무기.\n\n"
"모든 <#BLUE>집중 타격</>은 적을 관통하지만, 관통한 <#RED>약공격</>은 관통할 때마다 피해량이 감소합니다."

#: STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.CANNON
msgctxt "STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.CANNON"
msgid "A mid-to-long-range weapon that can deal <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> at a distance, but is vulnerable when the clip is empty.\n"
"Its <#RED>Heavy Attack</> is a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>!"
msgstr "중장거리에서 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>을 줄 수 있는 무기지만, 탄창이 비면 취약합니다.\n"
"<#RED>강공격</>은 <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>입니다!"

#: STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.HAMMER
msgctxt "STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.HAMMER"
msgid "Specializes in close combat encounters and fighting large groups of enemies."
msgstr "근접전과 다수의 적 상대에 특화된 무기."

#: STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.POLEARM
msgctxt "STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.POLEARM"
msgid "Specializes in high single-target <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> and keeping the enemy at bay."
msgstr "높은 단일 대상 <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>를 입히고 적을 몰아내는 데에 특화된 무기입니다."

#: STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.SHOTPUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.WEAPONS.HOW_TO_PLAY.SHOTPUT"
msgid "A mid-range weapon that mixes ranged and melee attacks."
msgstr "원거리와 근접 공격을 섞어 쓰는 중거리 무기."

